[f. 38v]pa ni 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar gyi dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyi'o/ /thugs la gnas lnga ni zhes pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kar gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /ye shes kyi sku zhes pa ni ye shes kyi sku'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /sangs rgyas zhes pa ni ji ltar gnas pa'i dngos 
