sngags la sogs pa dang ldan par bsgoms te/ de'i rtsibs brgyad la o wr gI shwarr ya te na maH zhes pa'i sa bon bkod nas/ 'khor lo lte ba la sa bon yi ge oM las bskyed pa'i bcom ldan 'das ngag gi dbang phyug sku mdog ser po/ rgyan thams cad dang ldan pa/ zur 
phung lnga pa/ sna tshogs kyi na bza' mnabs pa/ g.yon gyis rin po che/ g.yas kyis shes rab kyi ral gri 'dzin pa bsgoms te/ de'i thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du yi ge oM bsgoms nas/ de bzhin du spro ba dang bsdu ba la sogs pa bya'o/ /de kho na bzhin du dkyil 
'khor gyi dbus na yi ge a las gyur pa'i byang chub kyi sems rdo rje sku mdog dkar po/ /'jo sgeg gi tshul dang ldan pa/ rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan can/ rdo rje snyems pas bzhugs pa/ rgyan thams cad kyis bklubs pa/ rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa bsgoms nas/ de'i thugs kar bcom ldan 'das dang 
po'i sangs rgyas bsgoms te/ de'i thugs kar 'khor lo rtsibs dgu pa rtsa ba'i sngags la sogs pa bkod pa'i rtsibs la oM a ra pa tsa nr ya te na maH zhes pa'i sa bon gyi yi ge dgu rnams bkod nas/ 'khor lo'i lte ba la yi ge a las bskyed pa bcom ldan 'das a ra pa tsa na zhes bya ba ye shes 
sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po/ byis pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa/ zur phud lnga pa can/ sna tshogs kyi na bza' mnabs pa/ phyag na bo ti dang ral gri 'dzin pa bsgoms te/ de'i thugs kar zla ba'i steng na yi ge a bsgoms nas gong ma bzhin du spro ba dang bsdu pa dang zhugs pa dang gnas pa 
brtan par gyur pa la sogs pa byas nas bsgom par bya'o zhes kun la sbyar bar bya'o/ /'dir yang rigs kyi dbye bas dpal sgyu 'phrul dra bas mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i rim pa drug tu rig par bya'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na 'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa la 'khor lo bdun 

[f. 41r]@#/ /rigs bdun du 'gyur te/ de rnams kyang bla ma'i man ngag las shes par bya'o/ /de rnams dang ldan pa ni sgyu 'phrul dra bas mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i rim pa'o/ /'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam 
par lta ba zhes bya ba las sgyu 'phrul dra bas mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa ste bzhi pa tshigs su bcad pa gsum pa'o// //de nas da ni rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i sgo nas byang chub kyi sems rdo rje spro ba la sogs pa gsungs pa ni/ 'di ltar sangs rgyas 
bcom ldan 'das/ /zhes pa la sogs pa'o/ /de la sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi don bshad zin to/ /rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas a las byung*/ /zhes pa ni/ de la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi don ni bshad zin to/ /a las byung ba ni yi ge a las bskyed pa ste/ bcom ldan 'das ye 
shes sems dpa' yongs su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi sku'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro/ /da ni de'i thugs ka'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng gi gang yin pa yi ge a de'i khyad par gsungs pa/ a ni yig 'bru kun gyi mchog /ces pa ste/ rab tu gyur pa ni mchog ste/ mchog gi 
dngos po nyid ni mchog nyid do/ /yi ge kun ni yi ge thams cad do/ /de'i mchog ni rab ste/ de rnams kyi sgo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /don chen zhes pa la/ don yang yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas don chen te/ 'gro ba kun la phan par byed pa'i rgyu nyid kyi phyir ro/ /yi ge dam pa yin zhes pa ni/ /rnam 
grangs gzhan dang gzhan gyis mi 'gyur ba'i phyir na ste/ yang dag pa'i mtha'i ngo bo nyid kyis mi g.yo ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /yi ge yang de yin la dam pa yang de nyid yin pas yi ge dam pa yin zhes so/ /rim pa 'dis kyang ye shes sems dpa' la sogs pa'i yi ge dag gi rang bzhin brjod pa 
gsungs pa ste/ de dag nyid re re yang rnal 'byor pa rang gi sems las byung ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi rang bzhin mi mthun pa'i phyogs ma lus pa las bzlog pa'i ngo bo nyid du so sor brtag par bya ba ni/ de ltar rang gi ting nge 'dzin rnams dang de'i phyin ci log mi dmigs par ston 

[f. 41v]pa nyid kyi phyir dmigs pa mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyi gnyen po stong pa nyid kyi rnam par thar pa'i sgo'i mtshan nyid do/ /de ltar mtshan ma dang*/ log pa'i smon pa dang*/ phyin ci log gi 'du byed dang ldan pa rnams kyi gnyen po'i phyogs kyi ngo bo rim pa bzhin du mtshan ma med pa dang*/ smon pa med 
pa dang*/ mngon par 'du byed pa med pa'i rnam par thar pa'i sgo'i bdag nyid rnams bya ste/ de la yang go rims bzhin du rdo rje sems ma la sogs pa'i rigs kyi yum gyi rang bzhin gyi dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ khong nas 'byung ba skye ba med/ /ces bya ba ni sems ma rdo rje ma'i rang bzhin 
no| /de la yang khong nas 'byung ba ni yi ge a'o/ /de yang skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin te/ de ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir dang me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi rgyu nyid kyi phyir ro/ /tshig tu brjod pa spangs pa ste/ /zhes pa ni rin chen rdo rje ma'i sgo nas te/ tshig rnams brjod pa ni tshig tu brjod 
pa ste| de med pa ni spangs pa ste/ mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes la tshig gi rtsol ba med pa'i phyir ro/ /brjod pa kun gyi rgyu yi mchog /ces pa ni chos kyi rdo rje ma'i sgo nas so/ /mngon par brjod pa ni brjod pa ste/ phung po la sogs pa'i rang bzhin chos thams cad kyi mngon par brjod pa ni brjod pa 
kun te/ da'i rgyu ni byed rgyu ste/ so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes so/ /de nyid kyi phyir mchog ste/ gtso bo zhes pa'i don to/ /tshig kun rab tu gsal bar byed/ /ces pa ni las kyi rdo rje ma'i rang bzhin gyis te/ tshig kyang de yin la don kun yang de yin pas tshig kun te/ 'di lta ste/ lha'i 
skad dang klu'i skad dang gnod sbyin skad ces pa la sogs pa lta bu'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir rab tu gsal bar byed pa zhes bya ba ste/ ji ltar skal ba dang ldan pa'i sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la so sor snang ba 'byung bas so/ /sgo tha dad pa'i chos bstan pa yang bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin 
nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de'i phyir na rdo rje sems ma la sogs pa pha rol tu phyin pa bzhi po 'di rnams ni/ a r aM aHzhes pa'i yi ge bzhi las bskyed par bya'o/ /de nas yang sems gang kho na chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin tha mal pa'i gzung ba la sogs pa'i rnam pa dang bral bas de nyid kho na glo bur gyi dri 

[f. 42r]@#/ /ma med cing 'od gsal ba nyid kyi phyir dang*/ ye shes gzhan 'byung ba'i mtshan ma nyid kyi phyir na me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi bdag nyid do/ /chos la dmigs pa'i snying rje la sogs pa'i bdag nyid kyis rgyud gzhan du byed pa la mchog tu mi 'dzin pa'i phyir na mnyam pa 
nyid kyi ye shes so/ /shes bya thams cad la phyin ci ma log pas so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes so/ /'jig rten kun la phan pa'i rgyu nyid kyi phyir bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi bdag nyid do/ /'di dag kyang go rims bzhin du rtag pa la sogs pa gtso bo'o/ /rang bzhin no/ /de nyid gsungs 
pa| mchod pa chen po 'dod chags che/ /zhes pa la sogs pa'o/ /de la yang dang por snang ba mtha' yas kyis nye bar gzung ba ni 'dod chags gtso bor gyur pas gzung ba'i don te/ de nyid gsungs pa/ 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang*/ /zhes pa'o/ /de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi nam 
mkha' kun la khyab pa'i mchod pa bstan pa'i dus la ni mchod pa chen po zhes gsungs so/ /mahr'i sgra ni mchod pa la brjod pa yin no/ /chen po'i bdag nyid kyi 'dod chags dang 'dod chags chen po'o/ /mchod pa yang de yin la 'dod chags chen po yang de yin pas/ mchod pa chen po 'dod chags 
che| /zhes pa'o/ /de la 'dod chags che ni sems can smin cing grol ba'i mtshan nyid do/ /de yang bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan nyid yin te/ 'dod chags chen po bcom ldan 'das/ /rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs/ /zhes 'byung ba'i phyir ro/ /sems can thams 
cad dga' bar byed/ /ces pa ni 'dod chags la spyod pa'i sems can dga' zhing mgu la bde ba chen po'i bdag nyid byed pas na/ sems can thams cad dga' bar byed pa ste/ snang ba mtha' yas kyi rang bzhin no/ /zhe sdang la spyod pa'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ mchod pa chen po zhe sdang 
che| /nyon mongs kun gyi dgra che ba/ /zhes pa ste/ mchod pa chen po zhes pa'i don ni bshad zin to/ /zhe sdang che ni mi bskyod pa'o/ /de yang nyon mongs kun gyi dgra che ba yin te/ nyon mongs pa dang nye ba'i nyon mongs pa rnams kyi dgra chen po zhes pa'i don to/ /gti mug la spyod pa'i dbang 

[f. 42v]du byas nas gsungs pa/ mchod pa chen po gti mug che/ /gti mug blo ste gti mug sel/ /zhes pa ste/ mchod pa chen po ni gong ma bzhin no/ /gti mug chen po ni rnam par snang mdzad do/ /blo la gti mug pa ni gti mug gi blo ste/ gti mug kyang de yin la blo yang de nyid yin pas gti mug blo'o/ /
de sel bar byed pa ni 'joms par byed pa'o/ /khro ba la spyod pa'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ mchod pa chen po khro ba che/ /khro ba chen po dgra che ba/ /zhes pa ste/ mchod pa chen po ni gong ma bzhin no/ /khro ba chen po ni don yod grub pa'o/ /khro ba chen po dgra che ba/ /sems can dang 
sems can ma yin pa'i yul gyi phyir khro ba chen po ste/ de nyid kyi dgra chen po zhes so/ /chags par byed pa'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ mchod pa chen po chags pa che/ /chags pa thams cad sel bar byed/ /ces pa ste/ mchod pa chen po'i don ni gong ma bzhin du bshad do/ /chags pa chen 
po ni rin chen 'byung ldan no/ /chags pa thams cad sel bar byed pa ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa thams cad kyi phun sum tshogs pa yongs su dag par byed pa'i don nyid kyi phyir ro/ /stong pa nyid la sogs pa'i rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi rnams dang*/ chos dbyings kyi skye mched kyi sgo nas ting nge 
'dzin thams cad kyi rgyu nyid kyi phyir na de nyid kyang yang nang du phyin ci log pa dang mi mthun pa'i gnyen po nang stong pa nyid kyi rnam pa dang*/ phyi rol du dmigs pa dang bral bas na phyi stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin dang*/ de dag gi rten dang lus mi dmigs pa'i rnag bzhin nyid kyis phyi nang stong ba nyid kyi bdag nyid dang*/ snod 
kyi 'jig rten la lhag par chags pa dang bral ba nyid kyis chen po stong pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid de/ /de dag kho na me long lta bu'i ye shes la brten pa rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i bdag nyid ces pa 'di gsungs pa/ 'dod pa chen po bde ba che/ /dga' ba chen po mgu ba che/ /zhes 
pa ni| de la 'dod pa chen po ni rdo rje sems dpa'o/ /'dod par byed pa ni 'dod pa ste/ 'dun pa zhes pa'i don to/ /bde ba chen po ni rdo rje rgyal po'o/ /dga' ba chen po ni rdo rje chags pa'o/ /mgu ba chen po ni rdo rje legs pa'o/ /de nyid kyis mig dang gzugs la sogs pa'i bag chags gnas 

[f. 43r]@#/ /gyur pa'i rang bzhin me long lta bu'i ye shes las grub pa ste/ nang gi bdag nyid mi dmigs pa la sogs pa'i byin gyis brlabs pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /ji ltar rang rang gi phyin ci log gi mthun pa'i phyogs bzlog pa nyid kyang de dag gis byang chub kyi sems 'byung ba dang*/ dgug 
pa dang*/ rjes su chags pa dang*/ legs pa'i dngos po'i rgyud kyi phyir na yang de rnams kyi go rims so/ /de ltar stong pa nyid kyi ye shes de nyid la yang mtshan ma med pa'i phyir na stong pa nyid stong pa nyid dang*/ don dam pa'i mtshan ma la yang mchog tu mi 'dzin pa'i phyir na don dam pa stong pa nyid dang*/ 'dus byas pa'i 
bsod nams kyi tshogs kyi mtshan ma yongs su mi 'dzin pa'i phyir na 'dus byas stong pa nyid dang*/ 'dus ma byas pa'i byang chub kyi tshogs la yang mtshan mar mchog tu mi 'dzin pa'i phyir na 'dus ma byas stong pa nyid rnams te/ de nyid kyi phyir na gsungs pa/ gzugs che lus kyang che ba ste/ /kha dog che 
zhing lus bong che/ /ming yang che zhing rgya che ba/ /dkyil 'khor chen po yangs pa yin/ /zhes pa'o/ /de la gzugs che lus kyang che ba ni rdo rje rin chen no/ /gzugs su rung bas na gzugs te/ mi rtag ces pa'i don to/ /gzugs chen po dang ldan pa gang yin pa de ni gzugs chen po ste/ che ba nyid ni yid 
bzhin gyi nor bu'i gzugs nyid kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi khams gsum pa chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ba'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na lus che zhes pa ste/ gzhal du med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing na snang bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /kha dog che zhing lus bong che/ /zhes 
pa ni rdo rje nyi ma ste/ kha dog kyang de yin la che ba yang de nyid yin pas kha dog che ba ste/ gdong drug dang ldan pa'i phyir ro/ /lus bong chen po dang ldan pa gang yin pa de ni lus bong che ste/ shin tu rnam par dag pa thos pa dang bsam pa dang bsgom pa rnams kyi dngos po ye shes kyi 'od kyi dkyil 'khor nyid kyi 
phyir ro/ /ming yang che zhing rgya che ba ni rdo rje tog go/ /ming yang che ba dang gang ldan pa de ni ming yang che zhing ste/ grags pa chen po zhes bya ba'i don to/ /gang las she na/ sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa mchog tu mthar phyin pa'i phyir na'o/ /de'i phyir na yang rgya che ba ni rgya yang de yin la chen po yang de yin pas 

[f. 43v]rgya chen po ste/ thams cad sbyin pa'i phyir ro/ /dkyil 'khor chen po yangs pa ni rdo rje bzhad pa'o/ /dkyil ni rgyan dang chas par byed pas na dkyil lo/ /dkyil de len par byed pas na 'khor te/ dkyil 'khor ro/ /yangs pa ni rgyas pa ste/ 'jig rten gyi khams kun la khyab par byed pa'i 
phyir ro/ /gang gi bshad pa'i yangs pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi snying po de ni dkyil 'khor chen po yangs pa yin te/ khams gsum snang bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de dag kyang mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi 'khor rdo rje rin chen la sogs pa bzhi'i bdag nyid de/ nyon mongs pa can gyi yid gnas 
gyur pa'i bdag nyid mnyam nyid ye shes la gzung 'dzin dag pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas ji ltar gsungs pa'i mtshan ma med pa'i phyir dang*/ ji ltar rang gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs spangs pa'i sgo nas kyang dbang bskur ba dang*/ 'od 'phel ba dang*/ sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la sbyor ba dang*/ rab tu dga' ba bsgrub 
pa'i phyir na rdo rje rin chen la sogs pa bzhi po de dag gi go rims so/ /de nyid mtha' dang ldan pa'i sems can gyi smon lam la mngon par zhen pa med pa'i phyir na mtha' las 'das pa stong pa nyid dang*/ bdag gi thog ma dang tha ma med pa'i 'khor ba dor bar mi bya'o zhes pa'i smon lam kun du mi 'dzin pas na 
thog ma dang tha ma med pa stong pa nyid dang*/ bdag gis lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings la dge ba ched du dor bar mi bya zhes pa la mngon par ma zhen pa'i phyir na dor ba med pa stong pa nyid dang*/ rang bzhin gyi mtshan nyid dam rigs bdag gis dag par bya'o zhes pa don du gnyer ba dang 
bral ba'i phyir na rang bzhin gyis stong pa nyid rnams so/ /de nyid kyi phyir na gsungs pa/ shes rab mtshon chen 'chang ba ste/ /nyon mongs lcags kyu che ba'i mchog /grags chen snyan grags chen po ste/ /snang ba chen po gsal ba che/ /zhes so/ /de la shes rab mtshon chen 'chang ba ni 
rdo rje chos so/ /de la shes rab ni so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes te/ de nyid mtshon te mtshon cha'o/ /de 'dzin pas na shes rab mtshon chen 'chang ba ste/ de nyid ye shes kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /shes rab mtshon chen 'chang ba yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas shes rab mtshon 

[f. 44r]@#/ /chen 'chang ba'o/ /nyon mongs lcags kyu che ba'i mchog ni rdo rje rnon po'o/ /nyon mongs pa ni 'dod chags la sogs pa'o/ /de rnams kyi lcags kyur gyur pa nyid kyi phyir na nyon mongs lcags kyu'o/ /lcags kyu dang 'dra bas lcags kyu ste/ nyon mongs pa la 
dbang thob pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /nyon mongs pa'i lcags kyu yang de nyid yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas nyon mongs lcags kyu che'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na yang mchog ste/ rab ces bya ba'i don to/ /grags chen snyan grags chen po ni rdo rje rgyu ste/ sems can yongs su smin par byed pa'i thabs su 
gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad rgyud las bstan pa de la 'khor los sgyur ba'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir grags pa chen po dang gang ldan pa de ni grags chen no/ /de nyid kyi phyir na ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams la khyab par snyan grags dang gang ldan ba de ni snyan grags chen po zhes so/ /
snang ba chen po gsal ba che ni rdo rje smra pa'o/ /khams gsum khyab par snang ba'i 'od zer chen po dang gang ldan pa de ni snang ba chen po'o/ /de nas yang tshig gi nyes pa myur ba dang thogs pa dang bar ma rnams yongs su spangs te mi smra ba'i rang bzhin gyis bzlas pa'i dus na sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la rgya 
cher snang ba nyid kyi phyir na gsal ba che'o/ /de rnams kyang rnam par rtog pa'i yid gnas gyur pa'i mtshan nyid so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes la brten pa'i rdo rje chos la sogs pa'i rang bzhin te/ so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes la ji ltar gsungs pa'i phyin ci log byang bas chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid 
so sor kun du rtog pa'i phyir de'i sgo nas rang bzhin dag pa'i chos nyid dang*/ shes rab ye shes dang*/ phyir mi ldog pa dang*/ dgongs pa'i don ma lus pa yongs su shes pa rnams kyi rgyud nyid kyi phyir na 'di nyid rdo rje chos la sogs pa de rnams kyi go rims so/ /de nyid mtshan dang dpe byad kyi bdag 
nyid kyi gzugs kyi sku la 'du byed pa'i phyir rang gi mtshan nyid stong ba nyid dang*/ stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa'i rang bzhin gyi chos kyi sku la 'du mi byed pa'i phyir na chos thams cad stong pa nyid dang*/ gang zag dang chos la sgro 'dogs par 'du mi byed pa'i phyir na dngos po med ba stong 

[f. 44v]pa nyid dang*/ ji skad gsungs pa'i stong pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid la skur pa 'debs pa dang mngon par 'du mi byed pa'i phyir na dngos po med pa'i ngo bo nyid stong pa nyid rnams so/ /de nyid gsungs pa/ mkhas pa sgyu 'phrul chen po 'chang*/ /sgyu 'phrul chen po'i don grub pa/ /sgyu 'phrul chen po dga' 
bas dga'/ /sgyu 'phrul chen po'i mig 'phrul can/ /zhes pa ste/ de la mkhas pa sgyu 'phrul chen po 'chang ni rdo rje las so/ /de la sgyu 'phrul ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sna tshogs shing rgyas pa'i mchod pa mang po'i sprul pa'o/ /de 'dzin pa'i phyir na sgyu 'phrul 'chang ba ste/
chen po yang de yin la sgyu 'phrul yang de nyid yin pas sgyu 'phrul chen po 'chang ba'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na mkhas pa paN+Di ta ste/ mchod pa'i las des bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa'i phyir ro/ /sgyu 'phrul chen po'i don grub pa ni rdo rje bsrung ba'o/ /de la sgyu 'phrul gyi don ni sprul pa'i don to/ /de yis 
sems can le lo can rnams rab tu spro ba sgrub par byed pas na sgyu 'grul don grub ste/ chen po yang de yin la sgyu 'phrul don grub kyang de nyid yin pas sgyu 'phrul chen po'i don grub pa'o/ /sgyu 'phrul chen po dga' bas dga' ni rdo rje gnod sbyin no/ /sgyu 'phrul la dga' ba ni sgyu 'phrul la dga' 
ba ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa'i sprul pa la dga' ba zhes pa'i don to/ /sgyu 'phrul dga' ba la chags pa ni dga' ba ste/ sgyu 'phrul dga' bas dga'o/ /chen po yang de yin la sgyu 'phrul dga' bas dga' ba yang de nyid yin pas sgyu 'phrul chen po dga' bas dga'o/ /sgyu 
'phrul chen po mig 'phrul can ni rdo rje khu tshur ro/ /mig 'phrul can ni sprul pa'i tshogs te/ sku gsung thugs rdo rje rnams gcig tu gyur pa'o/ /de mkhyen pa ni mig 'phrul can no/ /sgyu 'phrul chen po yang de nyid yin la mig 'phrul can yang de nyid yin pas sgyu 'phrul chen po mig 'phrul 
can no/ /'di la ni dam pa'i chos kyi tshig yin pa'i phyir na ring po med par rig par bya'o/ /de rnams kyang bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes la brten pa dang*/ rdo rje la sogs pa bzhi'i bdag nyid de/ mig la sogs pa'i shes pa gnas gyur pa'i bdag nyid bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes su gnas pa ste/

[f. 45r]@#/ /ji skad gsungs pa'i phyin ci log spangs pa'i sgo nas bde bar gshegs pa kun mchod pa dang*/ mngon par srung bar byed pa dang*/ bgegs nye bar zhi bar byed pa dang*/ sku la sogs pa stong pa nyid dang*/ ye shes byed pa nyid kyi phyir dang*/ de nyid kyi phyir rdo rje la 
sogs pa de rnams kyi las kyi las kyi go rims zhes bya'o/ /de bzhin du ser sna dang*/ tshul khrims 'chal pa dang*/ mi bzod pa dang*/ le lo rnams kyi gnyen po'i phyogs nyid kyis de nyid sbyin pa dang*/ tshul khrims dang*/ bzod pa dang*/ brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i 
bdag nyid de/ de'i phyir gsungs pa/ sbyin bdag chen po gtso bo ste/ /tshul khrims chen po 'chang ba'i mchog /bzod chen 'chang ba brtan pa po/ /brtson 'grus chen po brtul ba yin/ /zhes so/ /de la| sbyin bdag chen po gtso bo ste/ /zhes pa rdo rje sgeg mo'o/ /mchod pa 
dang rjes su 'dzin pa'i 'dod pa'i sbyin pas na sbyin pa'o/ /sbyin pa de'i bdag po ni sbyin bdag ste/ sbyin bdag de yin la chen po yang de yin pas na sbyin bdag chen po ste/ zang zing dang*/ skyabs dang*/ chos dang*/ dbang bskur ba'i bdag nyid sbyin la zhig gtong bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /
de'i phyir gtso bo ste/ 'jig rten thams cad kyi rab kyi phyir ro/ /tshul khrims chen po 'chang ba'i mchog ni rdo rje phreng ba ma'o/ /lus ngag yid gsum mnyam par gzhag pas na tshul khrims ni mnyam par gzhag pa'o zhes pa'i skad kyi dbyings zhes pa'i don to/ /mi dge ba bcu spangs pa'i 
mtshan nyid dang*/ so sor thar pa'i rang bzhin te/ de dag 'dzin pas na tshul khrims 'chang ba'o/ /chen po yang de yin la tshul khrims 'chang ba yang de nyid yin pas tshul khrims chen po 'chang ba'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir mchog ste mngon du 'gro ba'i phyir ro/ /bzod chen 'chang ba brtan pa po ni 
rdo rje dbyangs len ma'o/ /sran tshugs par byas pas na bzod pa ste/ de 'dzin pas na bzod pa 'chang ba'o/ /chen po yang de nyid yin la bzod pa yang de nyid yin pas na bzod chen 'chang ba'o/ /de nyid kyang brtan po ste/ sdug bsngal chen po la brtan par sran thub pa'i phyir ro/ /brtson 

[f. 45v]'grus chen po brtul ba yin ni rdo rje gar ma'o/ /brtson 'grus che ba ni dge ba la spro ba ste/ sdig pa la sogs pa la spro ba ni dam pa'i phyir na le lo nyid de brtson 'grus ma yin no/ /de'i brtul ba ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa thams cad kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba las yongs su rdzogs 
par byed pa'o/ /de'i phyir gsang ba'i mchod pa bzhi'i bdag nyid go rims bzhin du me long lta bu'i ye shes la sogs pa las grub par rang gi rnam par thar pa'i sgo rnam par dag pa'i stobs kyis lhun gyis grub pa mngon par dga' ba'i khyad par du gyur par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid shes 
rab 'chal pa dang*/ rnam par g.yeng ba dang*/ yang dag pa'i smon lam med pa dang*/ nyam chung ba rnams dang*/ mi mthun pa'i phyogs zil gyis gnon pa la dga' ba nyid kyis gsungs pa/ bsam gtan chen po ting 'dzin gnas/ /shes rab chen po lus 'chang ba/ /stobs po che 
la thabs che ba/ /smon lam ye shes rgya mtsho che/ /zhes pa'o/ /de la tshigs bcad 'di la ni bsam gtan dang shes rab gnyis bsnor bar shes par bya'o/ /de'i phyir na don 'di lta ste/ shes rab chen po lus 'chang ba ni rdo rje bdug pa ma'o/ /shes rab chen po ni shes rab chen po ste/
de nyid kyi lus de 'dzin pas na shes rab chen po lus 'chang ba'o/ /bsam gtan chen po ting 'dzin gnas ni rdo rje me tog ma'o/ /ting nge 'dzin ni sems rtse gcig pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /de la brten pas na ting 'dzin gnas te/ che ba yang de yin la bsam gtan yang de nyid yin 
pas na bsam gtan chen po'o/ /chen po ni bsam gtan bzhi'i bdag nyid kyi phyir te/ bsam gtan bzhi po de rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'o/ /smon lam ni rdo rje mar me'o/ /smon par byed pas na smon lam ste/ byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni smon lam gyi dbang gis 
skye ba'o/ /thabs che ba ni rdo rje dri chab ma'o/ /chen po yang de yin la thabs kyang de yin pas thabs che ba ste/ thabs nyid dbang gis ma lus shing mi lus pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams kyi re ba dang bsam pa ji lta ba yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid ni shes rab dang*/

[f. 46r]@#/ /bsam gtan dang*/ smon lam dang*/ thabs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rnams kyi mtshan nyid kyis phyi'i mchod pa'i bdag nyid bzhi rnams so/ /longs spyod dang bcas pa'i lam la dga' ba'i rgyu'i dngos pos stobs dang*/ ye shes gnyis kyi chos kyi dbyings la 
'jug pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir/ stobs dang ye shes de dag rab tu rnam par dbye ba ste/ de la stobs ni dad pa la sogs pa lnga'o/ /ye shes ni mthong ba'i lam dang bsgom pa'i lam ste/ de la mthong ba'i lam ni byang chub kyi yan lag bdun no/ /bsgom pa'i lam ni 'phags pa'i lam yan 
lag brgyad do/ /de dag kyang dad pa dang*/ brtson 'grus dang*/ dran pa dang*/ ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo nyid sgo srung bzhi'i bdag nyid de/ theg pa chen po la mngon par yid ches pa dang*/ 'jug pa dang*/ de rgyun mi 'chad pa dang*/ yang dag par mgu bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid 
shes rab yongs su dag pa tsam la ltos pa'i stong pa nyid kyi rab tu dbye ba ji skad bstan pa'i sgo nas byams pa la sogs bcu drug gi ting nge 'dzin gyi bdag nyid do/ /de'i phyir gsungs pa/ byams chen rang bzhin dpag tu med/ /snying rje chen po blo yi mchog /shes rab chen po blo chen ldan/ /
mkhas pa chen po thabs che ba/ /zhes pa'o/ /de la byams chen rang bzhin dpag tu med ni byams pa ste/ 'di la mdza' ba yod pa ni mdza' pa can te/ mjug ni de'i rkyen dang ldan pa'o/ /de ni sems can thams cad la mdza' ba dang ldan pa'i rang bzhin te/ che ba yang de yin la byams 
pa'i rang bzhin yang de nyid yin pas byams chen rang bzhin no/ /de nyid kyi phyir na dpag tu med pa ste/ 'jig rten gyi khams kun la bu gcig ba bzhin du byams pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /snying rje chen po blo yi mchog ni 'jam dpal lo/ /snying rje chen po ni mi dmigs pa'i bdag nyid do/ /de gang 
la yod pa de ni snying rje chen po can no/ /blo'i mchog ni shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes yin no/ /des ni 'di skad gsungs par 'gyur te/ zab cing rgya che ba'i bdag nyid de bcom ldan 'das yin no zhes so/ /shes rab chen po blo chen ldan ni spos kyi glang po ste/ shes 

[f. 46v]rab chen po ste chos rnam par 'byed pa'i bdag nyid do/ /'di dang gang ldan pa de ni shes rab can te/ chen po yang de yin la shes rab kyang de yin pas shes rab chen po nyid blo chen no/ /mkhas pa chen po thabs chab ni ye shes tog go/ /gang zhig thabs che ba yin pa de ni thabs che 
pa'o| /de la mkhas pa chen po ni blo rdzogs pa chen po'o/ /sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa dang bag la nyal ba shes pas dam pa'i chos ston par byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /rdzu 'phrul chen po stobs dang ldan/ /shugs chen mgyogs pa chen po ste/ /rdzu 'phrul chen po cher grags 
pa| stobs chen pha rol gnon pa po/ /zhes de la rdzu 'phrul chen po stobs dang ldan ni bzang skyong ngo*/ /rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs ni rdzu 'phrul stobs te/ de dang ldan pa ni rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs dang ldan pa'o/ /chen po yang de yin la rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs dang ldan pa yang de nyid yin pas rdzu 'phrul chen po'i 
stobs dang ldan pa'o/ /shugs chen mgyogs pa chen po ste blo gros rgya mtsho'o/ /shugs chen pos 'gro ba gang yin pa de ni shugs chen te/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la mchod pa dang sri zhu'i don du du ma'i 'jig rten du bskyod pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na mgyogs pa chen po zhes 
gsungs so/ /rdzu 'phrul chen po cher grags pa ni blo gros mi zad pa ste/ 'jig rten dang nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs dang ldan pa'i phyir na rdzu 'phrul chen po'o/ /de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir na 
cher grags so/ /stobs chen pha rol gnon pa po ni spobs pa brtsegs pa'o/ /chen po yang de yin la stobs kyang de nyid yin pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu gnas dang gnas ma yin pa mkhyen pa la sogs pa phyis 'byung ba rnams gzung ngo*/ /de rnams kyi pha rol gnon pa ni 
de'i brtson 'grus brtsams pa dang gang ldan pa de stobs chen pha rol gnon pa po'o/ /srid pa'i ri bo chen po 'joms/ /mkhregs chen rdo rje chen po 'chang*/ /drag po chen po drag shul che/ /'jigs chen 'jigs par byed pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ de la srid pa'i ri bo chen po 'joms pa ni mthu chen 

[f. 47r]@#/ /po thob pa'o/ /srid pa ni nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga'o/ /de nyid ri bo ste/ mi shes pa'i brag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de dag yang dag par phyin ci ma log pa'i ye shes thob pas 'joms pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de ni 'joms pa'o/ /chen po yang de yin la srid pa'i 
ri bo 'joms pa yang de nyid yin pas/ srid pa'i ri bo chen po 'joms/ /zhes so/ /mkhregs chen rdo rje chen po 'chang ba ni ngan song kun 'dren no/ /rdo rje chen po ni kun du bzang po'i ye shes te/ de 'dzin pas na rdo rje ni chen po 'chang ngo*/ /sra ba'i phyir dang lus dang ldan pa'i phyir na mkhregs pa'o/ /
drag po chen po drag shul che ba ni mya ngan gyi mun pa kun 'joms pa'i blo gros so/ /chen po yang yin la drag po yang de nyid yin pas na drag po chen po ste/ gdul dka' ba'i sems can rnams la khro bo chen po'i gzugs ston pa'i phyir ro/ /drag shul che ni bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de zhi ba yin yang 
sems can gdul ba'i phyir drag shul can du yang ston zhes pa'i don to/ /'jigs chen 'jigs par byed pa po ni dra ba can gyi 'od do/ /'jigs chen ni 'jigs byed chen po'i gzugs 'dzin pas na 'jigs chen no/ /de yang 'jigs par byed pas na 'jigs chen 'jigs par byed pa'o/ /mgon 
po rigs mchog chen po ste/ /bla ma gsang sngags che ba'i mchog /theg pa chen po'i tshul la gnas/ /theg pa chen po'i tshul gyi mchog /ces pa ni/ de la mgon po rigs mchog chen po ni zla 'od gzhon nu'o/ /chen po yang de yin la rigs kyang de nyid yin pas rigs mchog chen po ste/ gzungs 
bzhi'o/ /de yang chig dang*/ don dang sngags dang*/ phyag rgya'i bdag nyid rnams so/ /de nyid ni mgon po ste/ sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid la kun du spyod pa'i sdig pa ma lus par yang dag par sbyong ba'i phyir ro/ /bla ma gsang sngags che ba'i mchog ni 'od dpag tu med pa'o/ /chen 
po yang de nyid yin la gsang sngags kyang de nyid yin pas gsang sngags che ba ste/ phyag rgya chen po'i bdag nyid do/ /de'i mchog ni gtso bo zhes pa'i don to/ /de nyid bla ma ste/ sems can thams cad kyi bsam pa dang bag la nyal ji lta ba bzhin du shes nas mngon par rtogs pa nye bar ston 

[f. 47v]pa'i phyir ro/ /theg pa chen po'i tshul la gnas ni nam mkha'i mdzod do/ /theg pa chen po ni 'og nas gsungs pa ste/ de'i tshul ni lam mo/ /de zhon pa ni gnas pa'i don to/ /theg pa chen po'i tshul gyi mchog ni sgrib pa rnam par sel pa'o/ /'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis brjod du 
med pa'i chos nyid du khong du chud pa'i rtog pa med pa'i ye shes ni theg pa chen po zhes so/ /yang na 'khor ba'i gnas thabs dang spyod yul dang rten gyi rang bzhin te/ bla na med pa rnam pa gsum gyis theg pa chen po bsdus pa yin zhes so/ /gal te de ltar yin na ni de'i chen po ji ltar yin zhe na/ gang 
dag 'jig rten thams cad la phan par byed pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das des de che ba nyid de/ de rnams kyi theg pa 'di ni bskyed pa'i don dam nges par 'byung ba'i don du sgrub pa'o/ /de'i phyir na de dang lhan cig pa'i chen po'i theg pa yin pas theg pa chen po 'am/ chen po nyid kyi theg pa 
pas theg pa chen po'o/ /yang na chen po rnam pa bdun gyi phyir te/ dmigs pa dang*/ sgrub pa dang*/ ye shes dang*/ brtson 'grus dang*/ thabs dang*/ yang dag par grub pa dang*/ las che ba nyid kyi phyir theg pa chen po'o/ /chen po yang de yin la theg pa yang de nyid yin pas theg pa chen po 
ste| theg pa gzhan la de rnams med pa'i phyir ro/ /de bas na de mdor bsdus nas theg pa chen po ni rnam pa gsum ste/ rgyu dang yul dang*/ rten gyi rang bzhin rnams yongs su snang ba'i don du rig par bya'o/ /de nyid thabs tsam la ltos pas sam/ ma lus pa'i 'jig rten dang 'jig rten 
las 'das pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi sku'o/ /'di ltar sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das/ /rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas a las byung*/ /zhes pa nyid la sogs pa mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge tshigs bcad gzhung tshig gi 
bye brag gi khyad par can 'brel tshig med pa rnams kyis khyad par du byas pa'i ye shes sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs la gnas pa 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' 'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog ces bya bar blta'o/ /dkyil 'khor gyi lha sems ma rdo rje ma la 

[f. 48r]@#/ /sogs pa de rnams kyang phyag rgya chen por sbyor bas rang rang gi sku mdog dang phyag mtshan du ldan pa phyung ste/ phyung nas kyang 'jig rten gyi khams kun gyi sems can rnams la sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byas te/ yang phyir log nas mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge rnams kyi rang rang 
gi rigs kyi mdog dang ldan par bsgyur te/ ji ltar don gyi rim pas rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po lngar bkod pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams la bzhugs par bsgoms nas/ 'khor lo de'i lte ba la gnas pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku 'jam dpal ye shes sems 
dpa'i gzugs gong nas gsungs pa bzhin du bdag nyid mos te/ bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi sku de nyid kyi gnyis su med pa'i yang dag pa'i don dam pa'i mtshan yang dag par brjod pa mtshan gyi gtsug gi nor bu 'di rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mo gang yang rung ba sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod 
pa'i byang chub sems dpas dus gsum du kha ton du byed pa'am/ glegs bam du byas pa la klog cing 'don pa dang*/ gtsang ba dang mi gcang bar gyur pas te/ ci yang mi smra bar ji lta ba bzhin du sus kyang mi thos par mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge tshigs bcad de ltar klog pa ni ring por mi thogs 
pa kho nar yon tan las brjod pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs dang*/ gzhan yang 'grub par 'gyur ro/ /don dam pa'i mtshan yang dag par brjod pa yang dag par 'dzin pa'i skyes bu gang zag de ni bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs shin tu bsags te/ shin tu myur bar sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yon tan 
rnams la yang dag par gyur nas bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya zhing*/ bskal pa mang por yongs su mya ngan las mi 'da' ba'i chos su 'gyur la/ sems can thams cad la bla na med pa'i chos ston par byed la/ phyogs bcur dam pa'i chos kyi rnga sgra 
sgrogs pa'i chos kyi rgyal por 'gyur ro/ /rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po de'i mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig rnams gcig tu bsdu ba byas nas mtshan brgyad cu rtsa drug rnams yin te/ de rnams kyang dkyil 'khor chen po'i lha rnams la rnam par phye nas sbyar bar bya'o/ /de la bzhi ni ye 

[f. 48v]shes sems dpa' dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi'o/ /yi ge a ni gsum mo/ /rdo rje sems ma la sogs pa dang*/ rtag pa la sogs pa rnams kyi bcu gcig go/ /dang po rdo rje sems dpa' nas brtsams te/ ji tsam sgrib pa thams cad rnam par sel ba'i mthar thug gi bar du ma lus pa'i 
mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig gi khyad par dang khyad par can gyi ngo bos go rims bzhin du sbyar bar bya'o/ /tshigs bcad ni bcu bzhi ste/ mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig rnams ni brgyad cu rtsa drug ste/ de ni man ngag yin no/ /'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang 
sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba zhes bya ba las byang chub kyi sems rdo rje rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa ste lnga pa'o// //


*********
* ch. 6 *
*********

Symbols for transcription:
...			illegible text for an unknown quantity of syllables
..				illegible for one syllable (one . for half the syllable)
○				string hole
[$X]			$ represents a line break; the number that follows it is the line number
()()			enclosed in the first set of parenthses is a lemma; enclosedc in the second set of parentheses is a note
f.				folio
img.			file number of digital images obtained from the Cambridge University Library Website, late 2020.


[mahāvairocano buddho mahāmaunī mahāmuniḥ |
mahāmantranayodbhūto mahāmantranayātmakaḥ || verse 42 ||]

[sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad che/ /
thub pa chen po thub chen ldan/ /
gsang sngags tshul chen las byung ba/ /
gsang sngags tshul chen bdag nyid can/ /]

[img 50] adhunā dvitīyaṃ vairocanasya cakram ucyate || tataś ca mañjuśrījñānasattvasya sarvvatathāgatajñānakāyasya vajradhātuamahāmaṇḍaladevatāvinyāsakrameṇa māhā[f.31r - img 51]tmyam ūhāvya idānīṃ śuviśuddhadharmadhātujñānasya mahāvairocanadvāreṇa sarvabhāvasvabhāvavyāptiṃ pradarśayitukāmaḥ | svavimokṣamukhena mohacaritānāṃ sattvānāṃ vinayanāya svacakravinyāsam āha || 

da ni gnyis pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor lo bshad de/ de yang 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i lha rnams bkod pa'i rim pas che ba'i bdag nyid bstan nas/ da ni shin tu rnam par dag pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i sgo nas dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin khyad par bstan par 'dod pas rang gi rnam par thar pa'i sgo nas gti mug la spyod pa'i sems can rnams gdul ba'i don du rang gi 'khor lo dgod pa gsungs pa'o/ /


tatra ca vairocanasya mahāvairocanasya ca kiṃ nānākaraṇam iti na jñāyate tad ucyate | 

de la yang rnam par snang mdzad dang rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i khyad par du bya ba ji lta bu zhe na/ de mi shes pas de gsungs pa/ 


svābhāvikarūpakāyanaiṣyandikāśrayaparāvṛttilakṣaṇaś ca akaniṣṭhadevarājabhuvane | tatra devanikāye copapannānām bodhisattvānāṃ dharmasambhogapratyanubhavanārtham abhisambodhisamādhikrameṇa vaipākikaṃ kāyaṃ nivarttya pariśuddhijñānapratibhāsalakṣaṇo naiṣyandikaḥ kāyas tatraiva bhavane mahābodhisatvagaṇaparivṛttoyaḥ pradarśito sau bhagavān vairocanaḥ ||

rang bzhin can gzugs kyi sku'i rgyu mthun pa'i gnas su gyur pa'i mtshan nyid 'og min lha'i rgyal po'i gnas der| lha'i rigs su skyes pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis chos kyi longs spyod rdzogs pa so sor nyams su myong bar byed pa'i don du mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pas rnam par smin pa'i skur gyur pa yongs su dag pa'i ye shes kyi so sor snang ba'i mtshan nyid rgyu mthun pa'i sku ste/ gnas de nyid na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs kyis bskor ba'i ston pa gang yin pa de ni bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad do/ /


yathoktaṃ śrīguhyendutilakatantre || akaniṣṭhabhuvane ramye śuddhāvāsoparisthite | tatra buddyaṃti sambuddhā nirmitas tviha buddyata iti gāthā ||

de ltar zla gsang thig le'i rgyud las gsungs pa/
	gnas gtsang ma rnams spangs pa'o/ /
	'og min gnas ni nyams dga' bar/ /
	rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de [f. 49r]@#/ /sangs rgyas/ /
	sprul pa po ni 'dir sangs rgyas/ /
zhes tshigs su bcad do/ /


mahāvairocanas tu jñānamayaḥ kāyaḥ kleśajñeyāvaraṇātyantavinirmuktaḥ sarvabhāvasvabhāvapratibhā[39v — img. 52]san darśanasamarthaḥ | 

rnam par snang mdzad chen po ni ye shes kyi rang bzhin gyi sku nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa gnyis las shin tu rnam par grol ba dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin du snang zhing ston par nus pa'o/ /


katham asau bhagavān tatvasvarūpād eva sarvvabhāvapradarśanasamartho bhavatīti ||

bcom ldan 'das de kho na nyid kyi rang bzhin de nyid las dngos po thams cad ston par nus par ji ltar 'gyur zhe na/ 


tathā coktaṃ śrīvairocanābhisambodhitantre||
	bhagavantas tathāgatā arhantaḥ samyaksambuddhās sarvajñajñānam prāpya tat sarvajñajñānaṃ sarvvasatvebhyo vibhakṣya nānānayair nānābhiprayair nānopāyanayair ddharman deśayanti sma || 

de ltar dpal rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud las gsungs te/ bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes brnyes nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes de sems can thams cad la rnam par phye ste/ tshul sna tshogs dang*/ bsam pa sna tshogs dang*/ thabs sna tshogs dag gis chos ston te/ 


	keṣāñcit śrāvakayānanayaṃ keṣāñcit pratyekabuddhayānanayaṃ | keṣāñcit mahāyānanayaṃ | keṣāñcit pañcābhijñajñānanayaṃ | keṣāñcid devopayattaye | keṣācit manuṣyopayattaye | yāvat mahoragayakṣarākṣasāsuragandharvvagaruḍakinnarādyutpattaye dharmman deśayanti sma || 

kha cig la ni nyan thos kyi theg pa'i tshul/ kha cig la ni rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i tshul/ kha 
cig la ni theg pa chen po'i tshul/ kha cig la ni mngon par shes pa lnga'i tshul lo/ /kha cig la ni lhar skye bar bya ba dang*/ kha cig la ni mir skye bar bya ba dang*/ ji srid du lto 'phye chen po dang*/ klu dang*/ gnod sbyin dang*/ srin po dang*/ dri za dang*/ lha ma yin dang*/ nam mkha' lding dang*/ mi 'am cer skye bar bya ba'i bar du chos ston to/ /


	tatra kecit satvā buddhavianeyikā buddharūpeṇa paśyanti | kecic chrāvakarūpeṇa | kecit pratyekabuddharūpeṇa | kecid bodhisatvarūpeṇa | kecit maheśvararūpeṇa | kecid brahmarūpeṇa | kecin nārayaṇarūpeṇa paśyanti sma || kecid vaiśravaṇarūpeṇa | yāvat mahoragamanuṣyā[f. 32r - img. 53]manuṣyarūpeṇa paśyanti || 

de la sems can la la sangs rgyas kyis gdul bar bya ba rnams la sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su mthong*/ /la las ni nyan thos kyi gzugs su/ la las ni rang sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su/ la las ni byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs su/ la las ni dbang phyug chen po'i gzugs su| la las ni tshangs pa'i gzugs su/ la las ni sred med kyi bu'i gzugs su/ la las ni rnam thos kyi bu'i gzugs su/ /la las ni lto 'phye chen po dang mi dang mi ma yin pa'i bar du mthong ste/ 


	svakasvakair vacanodāharaṇanayair vividheryāpathavyavasthitaṃ | tac ca sarvvajñajñānam ekarasaṃ yaduta tathatāvinirmuktarasam ity 

rang rang gi tshig brjod pa'i tshul dang*/ spyod lam la rnam par gnas pa ste/ thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes de 'ang 'di ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam par grol ba'i ror ro gcig pa'o zhes gsungs so/ /
	% Based on Tib., tathāgatavinirmukta?


ata āha mahāvairocana iti | virocyate dīpyata iti virocana (dot in the middle of line) virocana eva vairocana | svārthe vṛddhividhānāt | mahāś cāsau vairocanaś ca mahāvairocanaḥ |
 
de'i phyir gsungs pa/ sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad che/ /zhes pa ni/ de la sangs rgyas ni ji ltar gnas pa'i dngos po kun mkhyen pa'o/ /rnam par snang mdzad che ni rnam par gsal [f. 49v]bas na rnam par snang mdzad de/ rnam par snang ba kho nar byed pas na rnam par snang mdzad do/ rang gi don la 'phel bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /chen po yang de yin la rnam par snang mdzad kyang de nyid yin pas rnam par snang mdzad che zhes pa'o/ /

buddha iti yathāvasthitasakalapadārthāvabodhanāt | 
	% Order reversed in Tib. See above. 


kāyavākcittamaunayogāt maunaṃ | mahac ca mauanañ ca mahāmauna((ḥ||)) mahāmauna(tvaṃ)(pc [marginal note]; deest, ac) kutaḥ | satatasamāhitatvāt | tathācāha || ○ satatasamāhitā hi buddhā bhavanta iti vacanāt | kāyādigatadauṣṭhulyābhāvāc ca tad asyāstīti mahāmaunī |  

thub pa chen po ni sku gsung thugs thub pa dang ldan pa ste/ chen po yang de yin la thub pa yang de nyid yin pas thub pa chen po'o/ /thub pa chen po zhes bya ba ji ltar zhe na/ rtag tu mnyam par gzhag pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni rtag tu mnyam par gzhag pa'o zhes pa'i tshig gi phyir ro/ /lus la sogs par son pa'i gnas ngan len med pa'i phyir ro/ /de gang la yod pa de ni thub chen ldan no/ /


mahāntaś ca te munayaś ca mahāmuna○yo vyāsavaśiṣṭhavālmīkaprakṛtayaḥ || tadvineyānān tathārupeṇa pratibhāsanāt | ma[/6]hāmunir ity ucyate | 

chen po yang de yin la thub pa yang de nyid yin pas thub chen te/ gnas 'jog dang*/ ri byi dang*/ grog mkhar la sogs pa drang srong rnams yin no/ /des 'dul ba rnams la de lta bu'i gzugs su so sor snang ba'i phyir na thub pa chen po zhes gsungs so/ /
	% usually ri byi = agastya


mahāmantranayodbhūta iti | mantranayo vajramahāyānan tasmāt mantranayād udbhavatīti mantranayodbhūtaḥ | mahāṃ cāsau mantranaye | mahāṃś cāsau mantranayodbhū[f. 32v - img. 54]taḥ | tata eva niṣpatteḥ | 

gsang sngags tshul chen las byung ba/ /zhes pa la/ gsang sngags tshul chen ni theg pa chen po ste/ gsang sngags tshul de las byung bas na gsang sngags tshul chen las byung ba'o/ /chen po yang de yin la gsang sngags las byung ba yang de nyid yin pas/ gsang sngags tshul chen las byung ba/ /zhes pa ste/ de nyid las grub pa'o/ /


ata eva mahāmantranayātmaka iti | vajramahāyānasvabhāva ity arthaḥ | 

de nyid kyi phyir na/ gsang sngags tshul chen bdag nyid can/ /zhes pa ste/ rdo rje theg pa chen po'i rang bzhin zhes pa'i don to/ /


tataś ca mahāvairocana iti | evam ādibhiś ca bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ śrīmatām vara iti vācyah | 
	daśapāramitā○prāpto daśapāramitāśrayaḥ | 
	daśapāramitāśuddhir daśapāra(mitānaya)(pc; pāmitānaya, ac) iti || [verse 42]

de yang rnam par snang mdzad che/ /zhes pa la sogs pas kyang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog ces pa'i bar la brjod par bya'o/ /
	pha rol phyin bcu thob pa ste/ /
	pha rol phyin pa bcu la gnas/ /
	pha rol phyin bcu dag pa ste/ /
	pha rol phyin pa bcu yi tshul/ /


tatra pāramitānāṃ prāpt((yośr))aya śuddhimārggamukhena da○rśayann āha | daśapāramitāprāpta iti | tatra pāramitā daśeti | tathā coktam madhyāntavibhāge || dānaṃ śīlaṃ kṣamā viryan dyānam prajñā u○pāyatā | praṇidhānaṃ balaṃ jñānam etāḥ pāramitā daśeti | tatra dānan trividham | dha[$5]rmmadānam āmiṣadānaṃ maitrīdānañ ca || śīlan tri○vidhaṃ | samvaraśīlaṃ | kuśaladharmmasaṃgrahakaśīlaṃ satvārthakriyāśīlañ ca || kṣā[$6]ntiḥ trividhā | dharmmanidhyānakṣāntiḥ | duḥkhādhivāsanākṣāntiḥ | parāpakāramarṣaṇākṣāntiś ca |

zhes pa ni/ de la pha rol tu phyin pa rnams thob pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i lam rnams kyi sgo nas bstan pa gsungs pa/ pha rol phyin bcu thob pa ste/ /zhes pa de la yang pha rol tu phyin pa rnams ston pa ni 'di ltar dbus dang mtha' rnam par 'byed pa las gsungs pa/ /sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus/ /bsam gtan dang [f. 50r]@#/ /ni shes rab thabs/ /smon lam stobs dang ye shes dang*/ /'di dag pha rol phyin bcur 'dod/ /ces so/ /de la sbyin pa rnam pa gsum ste/ /zang zing gi sbyin pa dang*/ skyabs kyi sbyin pa dang*/ chos kyi sbyin pa'o/ /tshul khrims la rnam pa gsum ste/ sdom pa'i tshul khrims dang*/ dge ba'i chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims dang*/ sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshul khrims so/ /bzod pa la rnam pa gsum ste/ sdug bsngal dang du len pa'i bzod pa dang*/ gzhan gyi gnod pa byed pa la ji mi snyam pa'i bzod pa dang*/ chos la nges par 
sems pa'i bzod pa'o/ /


vīryan trividhaṃ | sannāhavīryaṃ | (prayogavīryaṃ |)(pc - marginal note, deest ac)  parini[f. 33r - img. 55]ṣṭhāvīryañ ca || dhyānan trividhaṃ | doṣāpakarṣakaṃ | vaihārikaṃ | viabhūtikañ ca || prajñā trividhā | śrutamayī | cintāma(yī)(pc; yi, ac) | bhāvanāmayī || upāya[$2]s trividhaḥ | svadoṣāyakarṣaṇaḥ | satvāvatāraka○ḥ | kṣiprābhisambodhakaś ca || praṇidhis trividhaḥ | svasambhāraprāvindhikaḥ | satvā[$3]rthānuvandhikaḥ | buddhakṣetrapariśodhanaś ca | ba○lan trividhaṃ | karmmavyāvarttakaṃ | kleśāpakarṣakaṃ | māraparapravādivyāva[$4]rttanañ ca || jñānan trividhaṃ | avikalpakaṃ | vi○kalpasamatāvabodhakaṃ | sarvopāyāparokṣañ ca || 

brtson 'grus la rnam pa gsum ste/ go cha'i brtson 'grus dang*/ sbyor ba'i brtson 'grus dang*/ yongs su mthar phyin pa'i brtson 'grus so/ /bsam gtan la rnam pa gsum ste/ nyes pa spong ba dang*/ rnam par gnas pa can dang*/ dbang sbyor ba can no/ /shes rab la rnam pa gsum ste/ thos pa las byung ba dang*/ bsams pa las byung ba dang*/ bsgoms pa las byung ba'o/ /thams la rnam pa gsum ste/ rang gi skyon spong ba dang*/ sems can 'jug par byed pa dang*/ myur du mngon par rdzogs par byang chub ba'o/ /smon lam la rnam pa gsum ste/ rang gi tshogs dang 'brel pa can dang*/ sems can gyi don dang rjes su 'brel pa can dang*/ sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su sbyong ba'o/ /stobs la rnam pa gsum ste/ las ldog par byed pa dang*/ nyon mongs pa spong bar byed pa dang*/ bdud dang pha rol rgol ba ldog par byed pa'o/ /ye shes la rnam pa gsum ste/ rnam par mi rtog pa dang*/ rnam par rtog pa mnyam pa nyid du khong du chud pa dang*/ thabs thams cad las lkog tu ma gyur pa'o/ /

