ata eva vaśī || tattatsvabhāvasandarśanatayā sarvarūpaprakāśaka((tvā))t ||

de nyid kyi phyir na dbang ldan te/ de dang de'i rang bzhin yang dag par bstan pa nyid kyis thams cad kyi rang bzhin bstan pa'i phyir ro/ /


mahānubhāvo dhaireyo | ananyaneyo mahānaya iti | tatra mahānubhāva iti | ānubhāvo mahātmyaṃ mahāṃś cāsāv anubhāvaś ca mahānubhāvaḥ | 

mthu chen gces pa 'dzin pa ste/ /tshul chen gzhan gyi dring mi 'jog /ces pa ni/ de la mthu chen zhes pa ni/ /che ba'i bdag nyid do/ /che ba yang de yin la mthu yang de nyid yin pas mthu chen no/ /


