tshul chen ni chen po yang de yin la tshul yang de nyid yin pas tshul chen te/ thabs chen zhes pa'i don to/ /gzhan gyi dring mi 'jog pa ni gzhan gyi dring mi 'jog pa ste/ chos zab mo la mos pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de ltar yang mos pa gtso bo yin pa'i phyir rang gi grub pa'i mtha' las rgol ba gzhan rnams kyis dbrog par mi nus pas de ni gzhan gyi dring mi 'jog pa'o/ /


[vāgīśo vākpatir vāgmī vācaspatir anantagīḥ |
satyavāk satyavādī ca catuḥsatyopadeśakaḥ || 50 ||]

[tshig rje tshig bdag smra mkhas pa/ /
tshig la dbang ba tshig mtha' yas/ /
tshig bden bden par smra ba dang/ /
bden pa bzhi ni ston pa po/ /]


vāgīśo vā[$3]kpatir vāgmī vācaspatir anantagīr iti | tatra vāgīśa iti | vācām īśo vāgīśaḥ | arthapratisaṃvillābhāt | vākpatir iti | vācāṃ[$4] patir vākpatiḥ svāmīty arthaḥ | niruktipratisaṃvi○llābhāt || vācaspatir iti | pratibhānapratisaṃvillābhāt | sādhumatyāṃ bhūmau catuṣprati[$5]saṃvillābhād dharmabhāśaka ity ucyate || ata evāha | anantagīr iti anantā gīr vāg yasyāsau anantagīḥ sarvabhāṣābhiḥ sarvasatvānāṃ yathā[$6]bhavyatayā dharmmacakrapravarttakatvāt || 

tshig rje tshig bdag smra mkhas pa/ /tshig la dbang ba tshig mtha' yas/ /zhes pa ni/ de la tshig rje ni tshig rnams kyi rje bo ni tshig rje ste/ don so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa'i phyir ro/ /tshig bdag ni tshig kun gyi gtso bo zhes pa'i don to/ /nges pa'i tshig so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa'i phyir ro/ /smra mkhas pa ni chos so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa'i phyir ro/ /tshig la dbang ba ni spobs pa so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa'i phyir ro/ /sa legs pa'i blo gros la so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi thob pas na chos brjod par mkhas pa zhes bya'o zhes gsungs so/ /de nyid kyi phyir tshig mtha' yas zhes gsungs so/ /mtha' yas pa'i tshig gi dag dang ldan pa de ni tshig mtha' yas te/ skad thams cad kyis sems can thams cad la ji ltar skal pa dang ldan pa nyid du chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


satyavāk satyavādī ca catusatyopadeśaka iti ||

tshig bden bden par smra ba ste/ /bden pa bzhi ni ston pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra satyavāg iti | dve satye yaduta saṃvṛtisatyaṃ (paramārthasatyaṃ) (em.; lost to damage in ms.) [f. 41r - img. 71] ca | tatra saṃvṛtiḥ tridhā | prajñaptisaṃvṛtiḥ | pratipatṛisaṃvṛtiḥ | udbhavanāsaṃvṛ(ti)(pc - marginal)ś ca tayā saṃvṛtisatyaṃ || paramārthasatyan tu | ekas (...) (illegible due to tape on ms. - pariniṣpannaṃ veditavyaṃ?) [$2]tavyaṃ| sa punaḥ paramārtham trividhaḥ | arthaparamā○rthaḥ | prāptiparamārthaḥ | pratiprattiparamārthaś ca | tatrārthaparamārthas tathatāḥ | paramasya jñānasyārtha iti kṛtvā || prāptiparamārtho ni(rvā)(em.; vā, ms.)○ṇaṃ paramo 'rtha iti kṛtvā || pratipattiparamārtho mārgaḥ paramo 'asyārtha iti kṛtvā || [$4] tad etat satyadvayam āśṛtya yasya vāk pravarttate sa satya○vāṅ iti bhaṇyate || 

de la tshig bden pa ni bden pa gnyis te/ 'di ltar kun rdzob kyis [f. 56r]@#/ /bden pa dang*/ don dam pa'i bden pa'o/ /de la kun rdzob la rnam pa gsum ste/ brtags pa'i kun rdzob dang*/ shes pa'i kun rdzob dang*/ brjod pa'i kun rdzob ste/ de rnams kyi bden pa'o/ /don dam pa'i bden pa ni gcig pu yongs su grub pa las rig par bya'o/ /de yang don dam pa rnam pa gsum ste/ don dam pa dang*/ thob pa don dam pa dang*/ sgrub pa don dam pa'o/ /de la don don dam pa ni de bzhin nyid de/ dam pa'i ye shes kyi don zhes bya bas so/ /thob pa don dam pa ni mya ngan las 'das pa ste/ dam pa'i don zhes bya bas so/ /sgrub pa don dam pa ni lam ste/ 'di don dam pa zhes bya bas so/ /bden pa de gnyis la brten nas 'jug pa'i tshig de ni bden pa'i tshig ces gsungs so/ /


tathā coktaṃ mūlamadhyamake āryanāgārjjunapādaiḥ ||
	dve satye samupā[$5]sṛtya buddhānāṃ dharmmadeśanā |
	lokasaṃvṛtisatyaṃ ca (satyañ ca)(pc - marginal) paramārthataḥ ||
	ye 'nayor na vijānanti vibhāgaṃ satyayor dvayoḥ | 
	te dharmman na vijānanti gaṃ[$6]bhīre buddhaśāsana iti ||

	% MMK etext reads:
	% ye 'nayor na vijānanti vibhāgaṃ satyayor dvayoḥ |
	% te tattvaṃ na vijānanti gambhīraṃ buddhaśāsane || MMK_24,09

de ltar yang dbu ma'i rtsa ba las 'phags pa klu sgrub zhabs kyis gsungs pa/ sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa/ /bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten/ /'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang*/ /dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o/ /gang dag bden pa de gnyis kyi/ /rnam dbye rnam par mi shes pa/ /de yis sangs rgyas bstan pa yi/ /zab mo'i de nyid rnam mi shes/ /zhes so/ /


tataś ca satyavādīti | satyaṃ bhūtaṃ śūnyatāsvabhāvaṃ evaṃ vaditaṃ śīlaṃ yasya sa tathā || 

de yang bden par smra ba ste zhes pa ni bden pa ni yang dag pa stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no/ /de ltar smra ba'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de ni bden par smra pa ste zhes pa'o/ /


catus satyopadeśaka iti | sakalajñe[f. 41v - img. 72]yābhisaṃkṣepalakṣaṇāni catvāri satyāni duḥkhasatyaṃ skaṃdhādau viparyāsalakṣaṇaṃ | āryāṇāṃ pratikūlatvāt | samudayasatyaṃ samāyato yathoktaṃ duḥkha[$2]m eva avidyāyāḥ saṃskārādipratyayatvena jātyādi○duḥkhahetutvāt || nirodhasatyaṃ sarvvadharmmāṇāṃ yathāyaṃ parikalpalakṣaṇatvād bhagavā[$3]n mohapratipakṣabhūtaḥ | tadadhigamañ ca | mārgasatyaṃ saṃbodhiparipūraṇato maitrīprabhavas tyāgādis teṣāṃ deśakaḥ catuḥ satyopadeśakaḥ || [$4]

bden pa bzhi ni ston pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ de la bden pa ni shes bya kun mdor bsdus pa'i mtshan nyid rnams te bden pa bzhi'o/ /sdug bsngal gyi bden pa ni phung po la sogs pa la phyin ci log pa'i mtshan nyid de/ 'phags pa dang mi mthun pa'i phyir ro/ /kun 'byung ba'i bden pa ni mdor bsdu na ji skad gsungs pa'i sdug bsngal nyid ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed la sogs pa'i rkyen nyid kyis bden pa ste/ sdug bsngal gyi rgyu nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'gog pa'i bden pa ni ji lta ji ltar brtags pa'i chos thams cad ji ltar skye ba med pa'i mtshan nyid kyi phyir bcom ldan 'das so/ /gti mug gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyi gnyen por gyur pa de rtogs pa yang lam gyi bden pa ste/ rdzogs pa'i byang chub yongs su rdzogs par byed pa byams pa'i mthus gtong ba la sogs pa ste/[f. 56v] de rnams ston pa ni bden pa bzhi ston pa po'o/ /


[avaivartiko hy anāgāmī khaḍgaḥ pratyekanāyakaḥ |
nānāniryāṇaniryāto mahābhūtaikakāraṇaḥ || 51 ||]

[phyir mi ldog pa phyir mi 'ong/ /
bse ru so sor 'dren pa ste/ /
nges 'byung sna tshogs nges 'byung ba/ /
'byung ba chen po rgyu gcig pa/ /]


avaivarttiko hy nāgāmī khaḍgapratyekanāyaka iti ○ ||

phyir mi ldog pa phyir mi 'ong*/ /'dren pa rang rgyal bse ru'i tshul/ /zhes pa ni/


tatrāvaivarttika iti | anuttarāyāḥ samyaksaṃbodher yo parāṅmukhaḥ so 'vaivartika[$5] ucyate|| yathā śrāvakagotrena vivarttako 'vivartta○kaḥ te na dīpyatīti avaivarttikaḥ acalāyāṃ tu vivyākaraṇalābhāt ||

de la phyir mi ldog pa ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog pa gang yin pa de ni phyir mi ldog pa zhes gsungs so/ /ji ltar nyan thos kyi rigs ltar phyir mi ldog cing de la gsal bar byed pas na phyir mi ldog pa ste/ sa brgyad pa mi g.yo ba la lung bstan pa thob pa'i phyir ro/ /


anāgamīti [$6] śraddhārdṛṣṭi((prāptas tato)) .. .. kāmāvacaranavakleśaprakāraprahāṇāt | anāgāmīty ucyate | 

phyir mi 'ong ba ni dad pa dang mthong bas thob pa de las gang zhig 'dod pa na spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa rnam pa dgu byang ba de ni phyir mi 'ong ba zhes gsungs so/ /


tathā coktaṃ | kāme 'ṣṭamaprakārasya na (...)(obscured by tape)

[ff. 42–43 missing]

de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	'dod pa'i rnam pa brgyad dang ni/ /
	dgu pa yang ni zad pa yis/ /
	lan cig phyir ni 'ong ba dang*/ /
	gang zag phyir mi 'ong ba skye/ /zhes so/ /

rang sangs rgyas ni rnam pa gnyis te/ bse ru lta bur spyod pa dang*/ tshogs na spyod pa'o/ /de la bse ru lta bu'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ bse ru zhes pa ni bse ru dang 'dra bas bse ru ste/ bse zhes pa ni sems can bse nyid de/ de ni mgo la rwa gcig kho nar 'gyur ro/ /de dang 'dra ba'i phyir na sangs rgyas gcig pur ston pas bse ru'i tshul zhes gsungs so/ /

'dren pa rang rgyal ni tshogs na spyod pa'o/ /so so re rer gtso bo yin pas 'dren pa ste/ tshogs na spyod pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

nges 'byung sna tshogs las byung ba/ /
'byung ba chen po rgyu gcig po/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la/ nges 'byung sna tshogs las byung ba/ /zhes pa la nges 'byung sna tshogs ni nyan thos la sogs pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'o| /de rnams kyis nges par 'byung bas na nges 'byung ste/ gang zhig gdul bya'i sems can rnams kyi sems kyi rgyud la de'i gzugs su 'byung ba so sor snang ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

'byung ba chen po rgyu gcig po/ /zhes pa ni/ de la 'byung ba ni sa la sogs pa bzhi'o/ /nam mkha' yang 'byung ba chen po nyid kyi phyir na 'byung ba chen po lnga yin pa las bzhi zhes gsungs pa ci'i phyir zhe na/ de rnams ni chen po yang yin la 'byung ba yang yin pas 'byung ba chen po ste/ nam mkha'i yul dang phyogs la rgyas par mnan nas gnas pa'i phyir na sa'i khams la sogs pa chen po nyid do/ /yang sa'i khams [f. 57r]@#/ /la sogs pa bzhi po de rnams ni thun mong ma yin pa'i las kyi khyad par las 'byung ba nyid kyi phyir na 'byung ba nyid do/ /de bas nam mkha' ni chen po nyid du yod de/ gzugs thams cad skye ba'i go 'byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'byung ba nyid ni ma yin te/ 'dus ma byas pa nyid kyi phyir dang*/ gang gi phyir 'byung ba'i don ni dngos po'i don yin pas na/ de'i phyir nam mkha' ni 'byung ba chen po ma yin no/ /de'i phyir na 'byung ba chen po ni bzhi kho na'o/ /'byung ba chen po bzhi po de dag ni rgyu ste byed rgyu gcig bu gnyis su med pa gang yin pa de ni de la de ltar gsungs so/ /


[arhan kṣīṇāsravo bhikṣur vītarāgo jitendriyaḥ |
kṣemaprāpto 'bhayaprāptaḥ śītībhūto hy anāvilaḥ || verse 52 ||]

[dge slong dgra bcom zag pa zad/ /
'dod chags bral ba dbang po thul/ /
bde ba rnyed pa 'jigs med thob/ /
bsil bar gyur pa gos pa med/ /]

dge slong dgra bcom zad pa zad/ 'dod chags bral bas dbang po thul/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la dge slong ni chos mngon pa las dge slong bzhi brjod de/ 'di lta ste ming gi dge slong dang*/ slong ba'i dge slong dang*/ bcas pa'i dge slong dang*/ /don dam pa'i dge slong ngo*/ /bzhi po de rnams las 'di ni don dam pa'i dge slong ste/ nyon mongs pa dang bral ba nyid kyi phyir dang*/ bdud thams cad kyis mi phyed pa'i phyir ro/ /

dgra bcom pa zhes pa ni dgra ni nyon mongs pa ste/ de rnams bcom pa dang ldan pas na dgra bcom pa'o/ /'khor bar slar nyams par mi 'gyur ba'i chos nyid kyis sam/ don ma lus par yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir gzhan rnams la rjes su ston par byed pa 'os par nus pa zhes pas sam/ sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun dkon mchog tu 'os pa zhes pas sam/ khams gsum gyi gtso bo rnams kyis rnam pa du mas mchod par bya bar 'os pa zhes pas sam/ bla na med pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la sgrub pa'i mchod par 'os pa'i phyir na dgra bcom pa zhes bshad de/ bcom ldan 'das so/ /

zag pa zad pa zhes pa ni/ de la mi dge ba'i chos kyi rtsa ba bzhi ni zag cing skye bar byed pa'i phyir ram/ /nyon mongs pa'i rnag zag pa zhes bya ste/ srid pa'i rtse mo nas bzung nas ji tsam mnar med pa'i bar du skye mched drug gi rma nas sems can rnams nyon mongs par byed/ gnod par byed pas nyon mongs pa'i zag pa rnams so/ /gzugs la sogs pa'i yul lnga dang*/ ma rig pa dang lhan cig skyes [f. 57v] pa dang kun du brtags pa las byung ba'i rang bzhin gyis yongs su brtags pa nyid dang*/ lta ba drug cu rtsa gnyis rnams ni ma rig pa zhes bya'o/ /'dod pa'i zag pa dang*/ srid pa'i zag pa dang*/ ma rig pa'i zag pa dang*/ lta ba'i zag pa rnams zhes gsungs so/ /mi slob pa'i tshul khrims dang*/ ting nge 'dzin gyi phung pos ni 'dod pa'i zag pa zad do/ /mi slob pa'i shes rab kyi phung pos ni lta ba'i zag pa zad do/ /mi slob pa'i rnam par grol ba'i phung pos ni srid pa'i zag pa zad do/ /mi slob pa'i rnam par grol ba'i ye shes kyi phung pos ni ma rig pa'i zag pa zad do/ /tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs ba'i sa la 'am/ mthong ba'i sa la yang dag par lta bas ni lta ba'i zag pa zad do/ /ting nge 'dzin yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la'am/ phyir mi ldog pa'i lam la yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'dod pa'i zag pa zad do/ /shes rab yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la'am/ dgra bcom pa'i lam la yang dag pa'i rnam par grol bas ni ma rig pa'i zag pa zad do/ /rnam par grol ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la'am/ zad pa dang mi skye ba'i ye shes gnyis kyis srid pa'i zag pa zad do/ /dgra bcom pa'i lam la 'am/ /'dod pa'i nyon mongs pa yongs su shes pa'i phyir na 'dod pa'i zag pa zad do/ /'du byed kyi phung po yongs su shes pa'i phyir na ma rig pa'i zag pa zad do/ /ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed pa'i phyir ro/ /nyon mongs pa'i phung po yongs su shes pa'i phyir na lta ba'i zag pa zad do/ /phung po'i rdzas yongs su shes pa'i phyir na srid pa'i zag pa zad do/ /sdug bsngal gyi bden pa yongs su shes pa'i phyir na lta ba'i zag pa zad do/ /lta ba thams cad nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga la dmigs pa yin no/ /sdug bsngal gyi bden pa dang*/ kun 'byung gi bden pa thams cad spangs pa'i phyir na 'dod pa'i zag pa zad do/ /'gog pa'i bden pa mngon du byas pa'i phyir na srid pa'i zag pa zad do/ /lam gyi bden pa bsgoms pa nyid kyis ma rig pa'i zag pa zad do/ /

[f. 44r - img. 74]... māro bhagno bhavati || iti caturmāraparājayāṭ bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | ata ete āśravāḥ kṣīṇā yasyāsau sa tathā || 

'dod pa'i zag pa spangs pa'i phyir na lha'i bu'i bdud bcom par gyur to/ /srid pa'i zag pa zad pa'i phyir na 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom [f. 58r]@#/ /par gyur to/ /ma rig pa spangs pa'i phyir na nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom par gyur to/ /lta ba'i zag pa zad pa'i phyir na phung po'i bdud bcom par gyur to/ /bdud bzhi las mchog tu rgyal bas bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal ni zag pa zad do zhes so/ /de'i phyir zag pa 'di dag zad pa gang yin pa de la de skad ces bya'o/ /


bhikṣur iti .. .. .. cābhidharmme catvāro bhikṣavaḥ paṭhyante || yaduta saṃjñā○bhikṣuḥ bhikṣaṇaśīlo bhikṣuḥ jñaptibhikṣuḥ | paramārthabhikṣuś ca | teṣāñ caturṇām aya[$3]mam paramārthabhikṣuḥ | bhinnakleśatvāt sarvamārair abhedyatvāc ca | 

	% repeated from above:
	% de la dge slong ni chos mngon pa las dge slong bzhi brjod de/ 'di lta ste ming gi dge slong dang*/ slong ba'i dge slong dang*/ bcas pa'i dge slong dang*/ /don dam pa'i dge slong ngo*/ /bzhi po de rnams las 'di ni don dam pa'i dge slong ste/ nyon mongs pa dang bral ba nyid kyi phyir dang*/ bdud thams cad kyis mi phyed pa'i phyir ro/ /


vītarāga ity enena ca traidhātuke caturāryasatyānāṃ ṣoḍaśākāraprakāreṇāṣṭā[$4]navatikleśānāṃ darśanabhāvanāmārābhyāṃ prahāṇā○d vītarāga ity ucyate |

'dod chags bral ba zhes pa 'dis ni khams gsum na kun du gnas pa'i nyon mongs pa rnams 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi rnam pa bcu drug gi dbye bas nyon mongs pa rnam pa dgu bcu rtsa brgyad mthong ba dang bsgom pa'i lam gnyis kyis spangs pa'i phyir/ 'dod chags dang bral ba zhes gsungs so/ /


ata eva jitendriya iti | sarvvaviṣayair anabhibavanīyatvāt || [$5]

de nyid kyi phyir na dbang po thul zhes pa ste/ spyod yul thams cad kyis zil gyis mi gnon pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


kṣemaprāpto 'bhayaprāptaḥ śītībhūto hy anāvila i○ti || 

bde ba rnyed pas 'jigs med thob/ /bsil bar gyur pas rnyog pa med/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra kṣemaprāpta ity anena kṣemaṃ kāyakarma tatprāpto yaḥ sa kṣemaprāptaḥ | 

de la bde ba rnyed pa ni bde ba ni lus kyi las te/ de rnyed pa gang yin pa de ni bde ba rnyed pa'o/ /


bhītir bha[$6]yan na vidyate bhayaṃ yasya tad abhayaṃ vākkarma sarvvavākdoṣābhāvād vākkarmaṇaḥ | 

'jigs pa ni skrag pa ste/ gang la de med pa ni 'jigs pa med pa'o/ /'jigs pa med pa ngag gi las te/ ngag gi las kyi tshig thams cad skyon med pa'i phyir ro/ /ngag gi las thob pa ni 'jigs med thob pa'o/ /


śītībhūta ity anena śītaṃ śāntatvāt mana[f. 44r - img. 75]ḥkarma sarvvacittopaplavābhāvād aśītaḥ prāg rāgādibhir abhibhūtatvāt paścāt tadapagamāt | śītī bhavatīti śītībhūtaḥ | tata eva hīti yasmādarthe[$2] kāyavākcittadoṣābhāvād anāvila ucyate ||

bsil bar gyur pa ni 'dis bsil ba ste/ zhi ba nyid kyis bdag nyid sems g.yo ba las thams cad med par gzigs te/ dang po 'dod chags la sogs pas zil gyis gnon par gyur la phyis de spangs pa'i phyir na bsil bar gyur pa'o/ /de nyid kyis lus ngag yid skyo ba med pa'i phyir na rnyog pa med ces gsungs so/ /


[vidyācaraṇasaṃpannaḥ sugato lokavit paraḥ |
nirmamo nirahaṃkāraḥ satyadvayanaye sthitaḥ || 53 ||]

[rig pa dang ni rkang par ldan/ /
bde gshegs 'jig rten rig pa mchog /
bdag gir mi 'dzin ngar mi 'dzin/ /
bden pa gnyis kyi tshul la gnas/ /]


vidyā○caraṇasampannaḥ sugato lokavit para iti | 

rig pa dang ni rkang par ldan/ /bde gshegs 'jig rten rig pa'i mchog /ces pa la/


tatra vidyācaraṇasampanna ity anena jñānasatvasya śāstṛsampadaḥ prāptihetuṃ darśayati | vi○dyācaraṇam āryāṣṭāṅāgārggaḥ | samyagdṛṣṭir vidyā seṣāṇyanāni caraṇaṃ | na hy apa[$4]śyan na caraṇo vā gantuṃ samarthya iti kṛtvā tiśro ○ vā śikṣā vidyācaraṇaṃ | adhiprajñāśikṣā adhiśīlaṃ adhicittañca | tatrādyā vi[$5]dyā dve cara(ṇaṃ)(pc; ṇeṃ, ac) prajñāyāḥ pūrvaparikarmakarttrītvāt ○ puraścaraṇaṃ hi caraṇam iti kṛtvā vidyāyās tu pūrvvagrahaṇaṃ tatpariśuddhyā śīlasamā[$6]dhipariśuddhitaḥ | 

de la rig pa dang rkang par ldan ni/ des ni ye shes sems dpa' de ston pa phun sum tshogs pa thob pa'i rgyu ston par byed de/ rig pa dang rkang pa ni 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad las yang dag pa'i lta ba ni rig pa ste/ yan lag gzhan ni rkang pa'o/ /ma mthong zhing rkang pa med na 'gro bar mi nus zhes bya bas so/ /bslab pa gsum ni rig pa dang*/ rkang pa ste/ lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa dang*/ lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa dang*/ lhag pa [f. 58v]sems kyi bslab pa'o/ /de la shes rab ni rig pa'o/ /gnyis ni rkang pa'o/ /shes rab kyis sngon du byas nas bskyod pa ni rkang pa zhes bya'o/ /rig pa sngon du gzung ngo*/ /de yongs su dag pa'i tshul khrims dang*/ ting nge 'dzin yongs su dag pa ste/ 


tathā hi prajñayā cakṣuṣaiva paśyaṃ tābhyāṃ (śīlasamādhibhyāṃ)(margin addition)caraṇābhyām iv gacchan | gantavyam anuprāy?tīti vidyācaraṇaśandeti praḥśikṣa.. .. [f. 45r - img. 76] śyante || ata sti ((sṛ))bhir vidyā(bhiḥ sampanno vidyā)(marginal note)caraṇasampanna ity ucyate || 

'di ltar shes rab kyi spyan nyid kyis bltas nas tshul khrims dang ting nge 'dzin rkang pa dang 'dra bas 'di dag gis 'gro zhing bgrod par bya bas mthun par bslabs pas na rig pa dang*/ rkang pa'i sgras bslab pa gsum nges par bstan pa yin no/ /de'i phyir rig pa la sogs pa dang ldan pas/ rig pa dang ni rkang par ldan/ /zhes gsungs so/ /


sugata ity anena ca yathā gantavyaṅ gatas tad darśayati | suṣṭhagataḥ sugato 'punarāvṛtyarthena su .. .. .. (Tib. tsha ba'i nad shin tu byang ba) [$2] vat || niḥśeṣaṃ gataḥ | niḥśeṣajñeyagamanārthe○na suparipūrṇṇaghaṭavat || etac cārthadvayaṃ bāhyaśrāvakādibhyo viśeṣaṇārthaṃ | 

bde gshegs zhes bya ba des kyang ji ltar bgrod par bya ba dang*/ 'gro ba la ston te/ shin tu legs par 'gro bas bder gshegs te/ phyir mi ldog pa'i don gyis na ste/ dper na tsha ba'i nad shin tu byang ba bzhin no/ /yang na lus pa med par gshegs pas na bder gshegs te/ shes bya ma lus par shes pa'i don gyis na ste/ dper na bum pa legs par gang ba bzhin no/ /don de gnyis ni phyi rol pa dang nyan thos la sogs pa las khyad par du gyur pa'o zhes pa'i don to/ /

bāhyā hi na suṣṭhagatāḥ punar āvṛttitaḥ | śrāvakādayo ya○dy api suṣṭhagatāḥ punaḥ pṛtagjanatāyā abhavyatvāt | na tu niḥśeṣaṅ gatāḥ sarvvajñeye yaj jñānavivandhanatvāt | 

ci'i phyir zhe na/ phyi rol pa ni mthar thug par gshegs pa ma yin te/ phyir ldog pa'i phyir ro/ /nyan thos la sogs pa rnams ni so so'i skye bo'i skal pa dang mi ldan pa'i phyir mthar thug par song ba yin kyang ma lus par song ba ma yin te/ shes bya thams cad la ye shes thogs pa'i phyir ro/ /


evaṃ vidyācaraṇasampadā su○ṣṭhaniḥśeṣaṅgatasya śāstṛsampadaṃ prāptasya bhagavato jñānasatvasya tacchāstṛkarma lo[$5]kavit para ity ābhyām padābhyān darśayati | tat punaḥ ○ śāstṛkarmadvividhaṃ bhavyābhavyalokālokanaṃ | bhavyavinayanañ ca | tatra lokavid ity a[$6]nena bhavyābhavyāvalokanaṃ | lokaṃ vettī(tti)(ms.; iti, em) lokavid bhavyābhavyalokaparijñānād asau lokavid ucyate |
	
de ltar rig pa dang rkang par ldan pa dang*/ legs par dang*/ ma lus par gshegs pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa bcom ldan 'das ye shes sems dpa' yin zhes ston pa'o/ /ston pa de'i phrin las ni/ 'jig rten rig pa'i mchog ces pa'i tshig gnyis kyis ston te/ de yang ston pa'i las rnam pa gnyis te/ skal pa dang ldan pa dang*/ skal ba dang mi ldan pa'i 'jig rten la gzigs pa dang*/ skal ba dang ldan pa 'dul ba'o/ /de la 'jig rten rig pa zhes pa des ni skal ba dang ldan pa dang*/ skal ba dang mi ldan pa'i 'jig rten la gzigs pa ston to/ /'jig rten rtogs pa ni 'jig rten rig pas te/ skal ba dang ldan pa dang skal pa dang mi ldan pa'i [f. 59r]@#/ /'jig rten yongs su shes pa'i phyir na de ni 'jig rten rig pa zhes bya'o/ /


tathā hi bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ triṣ kṛtvā rātres tri[f. 45v - img. 77]s kṛtvādivasasya prajñācakṣuṣā lokaṃ vyavalokayati | ko hīyate ko varddate kaḥ saṃkaṭam anuprāptaḥ ko 'pāyanigraḥ | yam aham apāyād uddhṛtya svarge mokṣe ca pra[$2]tiṣṭhāpayeyaṃ kasyānavaropitāni kuśalamūlāny a○varopayeyaṃ kasyāvaropitāni paripūrayeyaṃ kasyāparipakvāni yācayeyam iti [$3] | ata eva hi para utkṛṣṭo sau bhagavān || 

'di lta ste/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gyis nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du shes rab kyi spyan gyis gzigs te/ su ni rgud/ su ni 'byor/ su ni ngan song la gzhol/ gang zhig ngan song las bton te mtho ris dang thar pa 'di la gzhag /gang gis dge ba'i rtsa ba ma bskrun pa de bskrun par bya ba dang*/ gang dge ba'i rtsa ba bskrun pa rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba dang*/ gang yongs su ma smin pa rnams yongs su smin par bya'o zhes pa'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na mchog ste/ dam pa ni bcom ldan 'di'o/ /


nirmamo ni○rahaṃkāra satyadvayanaye sthita iti || 

bdag gir mi 'dzin ngar mi 'dzin/ /bden pa gnyis kyi tshul la gnas/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra nirmama ity anena padena grāhyāṃso nisi[$4]ddhaḥ | nirahaṃkāra ity anena padena grāhakāṃśas tadu○bhayasyāpi mithyāpratibhāsatvāt | 
	% how to account for tad in or before ubhayasya

de la bdag gir mi 'dzin pa zhes pa'i tshig des ni gzung ba'i phyogs bkag pa'o/ /ngar mi 'dzin zhes bya ba des kyang 'dzin pa'i phyogs bkag pa ste/ de gnyis kyang log par so sor snang ba'i phyir ro/ /


tathā cārya nāgārjjupādair uktaṃ ratnāvalyāṃ | 
	a[$i]styahaṃ mama cāstīti mithyaitat paramārthataḥ |
	yathābhūtaparijñānāt na bhavaty ubhayaṃ yata iti ||

de ltar 'phags pa klu sgrub snying po'i zhabs kyis rin po che'i phreng ba las gsungs pa/ 
	bdag dang bdag gi gnyis ka yang*/ /
	don dam par ni 'di dag log /
	yang dag ji bzhin yongs shes pas/ /
	gang phyir gnyi ga med pas so/ /zhes so/ /


satyadvayanaye sthita iti gatārthaṃ ||

bden pa gnyis kyi tshul la gnas/ /zhes pa'i don ni bshad zin to/ /


[saṃsārapārakoṭisthaḥ kṛtakṛtyaḥ sthale sthitaḥ |
kaivalyajñānaniṣṭhyūtaḥ prajñāśastro vidāraṇaḥ || 54 ||]
['khor ba'i pha rol mthar gnas pa/ /
bya ba byas pa skam sar gnas/ /
ye shes 'ba' zhig nges 'byung ba/ /
shes rab mtshon chas rnam 'joms pa/ /]


saṃsā[$6]rapārakoṭisthaḥ kṛtakṛtyaḥ sthale sthita iti ||

'khor ba'i pha rol mthar son pa/ /bya ba byas pa skam sar gnas/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra saṃsārapārakoṭistha ity anenaitad darśayati | saṃsāro hi bhāvarūpaḥ pañcopādānaskandhatvā[f. 46r img. 78]t | ta eva hi pañcopādānaskandhāḥ kleśakarmāviddhagatayo gater gatyaṃ taraṃ gacchantaḥ saṃsāra ity ucyate | tasya pāro nirvāṇaṃ tac cābhavarū(paṃ | saṃsāraś ca)(concealed by tape)[$2]pāraś ca saṃsārapārau tayoḥ koṭiḥ saṃsārapārako○ṭis tasyān tiṣṭhatīti saṃsārapārakoṭisthaḥ | etad uktam bhavati | bhāvābhāvasvabhāvayoḥ saṃvṛ[$3]tyāsthito sau bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ na paramārthataḥ ka○smāt tayoḥ sūkṣmasyāpi dharmasyānupalabdher iti | tathā coktaṃ | 
	nirvāṇasya ca yā koṭiḥ [$4] koṭiḥ saṃsaraṇasya ca | 
	na tayor antaraṃ kiñcit susū○kṣmam api vidyata iti || [Mulamuadhyamakakārikā 25.20]
	
	% Is kleśakarmāviddhagatayo correct?
	% tasyān tiṣṭhati?

de la/ 'khor ba'i pha rol mthar son pa/ /zhes des 'di ltar ston te/ 'khor ba ni dngos po'i rang bzhin te/ nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga nyid yin pa'i phyir nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga ni nyon mongs pa dang*/ las kyis 'brel zhing 'gro ba dag tu 'gro zhing song la/ 'gro bar byed pas na 'khor ba pa zhes gsungs so/ /'khor ba ni tshu rol/ de'i pha rol ni mya ngan las 'das pa ste/ de'ang dngos po med pa'i ngo bo'o/ /'khor ba dang pha rol 
ni 'khor ba dang pha rol gnyis te/ de gnyis kyi mtha' ni 'khor ba dang pha rol gyi mtha'o/ /de la gnas pas na 'khor ba'i pha rol mthar son pa'o/ /des 'di gsungs par 'gyur te/ dngos po dang dngos po med pa'i rang bzhin gnyis la bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de ni kun rdzob tu [f. 59v]gnas pa ste/ don dam par ni ma yin no/ /ci'i phyir zhe na/ de gnyis kyi chos phra ba nyid kyang mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar gsungs pa/ 
	mya ngan las 'das mtha' ma gang*/ 
	'khor ba'i mtha' ma de nyid de/ /
	de gnyis bye brag 'ga' zhig kyang*/ /
	shin tu phra ba yang med do/ /zhes so/ /

	[Cannonical Tib. translation: mya ngan 'das mtha' gang yin pa, ,de ni 'khor ba'i mtha' yin te, ,de gnyis khyad par cung zad ni, ,shin tu phra ba'ang yod ma yin, ,]


kṛtakṛtya iti | avasyakarttavyaṃ kṛtyam ity ucyate | tatra śīlasa[$5]mādhiprajñāparipūryā sarvvaduḥkhavimokṣapradhānaka○rma tatparisamāptyā kṛtakṛtya ucyate | (ka)(or is it a?)lpeccchāvṛttaṃ saṃtoṣavṛ(ttaṃ dhūtāṃ)(pc - added in margin)gavṛttaṃ saṃrakṣanīyavṛttam ityādayo vṛttaviśeṣāḥ pūrayitavyāḥ kṛtā anenety asau kṛtakṛtya iti ||
	% sarvvaduḥkhavimokṣapradhānakarma:  Tib. suggests sarvvaduḥkhavimokṣas pradhānakarma

bya ba byas zhes pa ni gdon mi za bar bya ba ni bya ba zhes gsungs so/ /de la tshul khrims dang*/ ting nge 'dzin dang*/ shes rab yongs su bsags pas sdug bsngal thams cad las rnam par grol ba ni las kyi gtso bo ste/ de yongs su rdzogs pas na bya ba byas zhes gsungs so/ /'dod pa chung bas 'jug pa dang*/ yan lag bsdams pas 'jug pa dang*/ yang dag par chags par bya ba bsdams pa zhes bya ba la sogs pa bsdams pa'i khyad par rnams rdzogs par bya ba ni byas pa ste/ 'dis ni de ni bya ba byas par bstan to/ /


sthale sthita iti || sthalaṃ nirvāṇaṃ kṣemasthānīyatvāt | tatra sthitaḥ [f. 46 - img. 79] sarvvadā dharmakāyasthitatvād iti || advayadharmatāyām avasthānāt || 

skam sar gnas zhes pa ni skam sa ni mya ngan las 'das pa ste/ bde ba'i gnas nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de la gnas pa ni thams cad chos kyi sku'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir dang*/ gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid la cher gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /


kaivalyajñānaniṣṭhyūtaḥ prajñāśastravidāraṇa iti | 
	% text probably reads niṣṭhūta, but maybe there's no real difference in these ligatures 

ye shes 'ba' zhig las byung ba zhes pa ni/ 


kevalaṃ śuddhaṃ tatra jātaṃ kaivalyaṃ kaivalya[$2]ñ ca tat jñānañ ceti kaivalyajñānaṃ || tasmāj jāto niṣṭhyuta○ḥ sa tathoktaḥ || 

de la 'ba' zhig ni dag pa ste/ de 'byung ba 'ba' zhig pa'o/ /de las skyes pa'i ye shes so/ /'ba' zhig kyang de yin la ye shes kyang de yin pas ye shes 'ba' zhig kyang de'o/ /de las skyes pa ni de las byung ba ste/ 


prajñāśastravidāraṇa iti | prajñā dharmapravicayalakṣaṇātmikā saiva śa[$3]straṃ sarvvakleśanikṛntanatvāt | tena prajñāśastreṇa sarvva○dharmmāṇāṃ heyopādeyavivikṣāvabodhanāt | sa tathoktaḥ || 

de de ltar gsungs so/ /shes rab mtshon chas rnam 'joms pa/ /zhes pa ni/ de la shes rab ni chos rab tu rnam par 'byed pa'i mtshan nyid kyi bdag nyid do/ /de nyid mtshan cha ste nyon mongs pa thams cad gcod pa'i phyir ro/ /shes rab kyi mtshon des chos thams cad la spong ba dang blang ba'i rnam par 'byed pa shes pas na de la de ltar gsungs so/ /


[saddharmo dharmarāḍ bhāsvāṃ lokālokakaraḥ paraḥ |
dharmeśvaro dharmarājā śreyomārgopadeśakaḥ || 55 ||]
[dam chos chos rgyal gsal bar ldan/ /
'jig rten snang bar byed pa'i mchog /
chos kyi dbang phyug chos kyi rgyal/ /
legs pa'i lam ni ston pa po/ /]


saddharmmo dharmmarāḍ bhāsvā((la))[%4]nlokālokakaraḥ paraḥ iti |

dam chos chos rgyal gsal bar ldan/ /'jig rten snang bar byed pa'i mchog /ces pa ste/ 


tatra dvividhaḥ saddharmma○ḥ| gauṇo mukhyaś ca | tatra satāṃ dharmmaḥ saddharmmaḥ santo hi buddhābodhisatvāś ca teṣāṃ dha[$5]rmmo dvādaśāṅgapravacanāni | tatra dvādaśāṅāni | sū○traṃ (jñeyaṃ)(sic for geyaṃ?) gāthāṃ vyākaraṇaṃ udānaṃ nidānaṃ jātakaṃ itivṛttakaṃ avadānaṃ vaipu[%6]lyaṃ niruktir arthaś cety aṅgāni || tīni pravyaktair akṣaraiḥ pūstakeṣu ruṭāni gauṇaḥ yad dharmma ucyate | mukhyās tu dharmarāḍ iti dharmmadhātusvabhāva [f. 47 is missing]
	% final 2 usually adbhūtadharma and upadeśa 

de la dam pa'i chos ni gnyis te/ gtso bo ma yin pa dang gtso bo'o/ /de la dam pa rnam pa gnyis kyi chos ni dam pa'i chos te/ dam pa ni sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams so/ /de rnams kyi chos ni gsung rab yan  [f. 60r]@#/ /lag bcu gnyis so/ /de la yan lag bcu gnyis ni 'di lta ste/ mdo'i sde dang*/ dbyangs kyis bsnyad pa'i sde dang*/ tshigs su bcad pa'i sde dang*/ /lung du bstan pa'i sde dang*/ ched du brjod pa'i sde dang*/ rtogs pa brjod pa'i sde dang*/ skyes pa rabs kyi sde dang*/ chos rmad du byung ba'i sde dang*/ gling gzhi'i sde dang*/ shin tu rgyas pa'i sde dang*/ gtan la phab pa'i sde dang*/ da ltar dang 'das pa'i sde zhes bya ba yan lag de rnams yi ge rab tu gsal bas glegs bam la gnas pa ni gtso bo ma yin pa'i chos so zhes gsungs so/ /

gtso bo'i chos ni chos rgyal zhes pa ste/ chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin ni brjod par bya ba dang*/ rjod par byed pa dang bral ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de ni shes par byar med de/ 'di ltar shes rab sum brgya pa nas gsungs pa/ 
	sangs rgyas rnams ni chos nyid lta/ /
	'dren pa rnams ni chos kyi sku/ /
	chos nyid yang ni shes bya min/ /
	de ni shes par mi nus so/ /
zhes so/ /

de'i phyir na yang gsungs pa/ gsal bar ldan zhes pa ste/ chos de gnyis ka yang ma rig pa'i phyi nang gi mun pa sel bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /

'jig rten snang bar byed pa'i zhes pa ni 'jig rten pa'i mi shes pa'i mun pas bsgribs pa rnams la ji ltar kun du gnas pa'i chos rab tu bstan pa'i phyir na 'jig rten snang bar byed pa'o/ /de yang mchog ste gtso bo ni bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /

chos kyi dbang phyug chos kyi rgyal/ /legs pa'i lam ni ston pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la chos kyi dbang phyug ni dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam gyis chos rnams la dbang byed pas na chos kyi dbang phyug go/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	mi dge bcu la mi 'jug dang*/ /
	rtag tu dge la rab tu 'jug /
	sems kyi las dang lus ngag gi /
	chos 'di rnam pa gsum du 'dod/ /ces so/ /

chos kyi rgyal ni phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa rnam pa gsum du dbye bas phye ba'i chos kyi rgyal po bas chos kyi rgyal po'o/ /

legs pa'i lam ston pa po ni legs pa nyid kyi lam ni legs pa'i lam ste/ de so sor sgrub par byed pa'i chos ni legs pa'i lam du gsungs so/ /ston par byed pa ni legs pa'i lam ni ston pa po [f. 60v]ste| bcom ldan 'das so/ /

de ltar yang rin po che'i phreng ba las gsungs pa/
	nges par legs pa'i chos kyang ni/ /
	phra dang zab mo ston byed pa/ /
	byis pa thos dang mi ldan rnams/ /
	rgyal bas gsungs la skrag par byed/ /
ces so/ /


[siddhārthaḥ siddhasaṃkalpaḥ sarvasaṃkalpavarjitaḥ |
nirvikalpo 'kṣayo dhātur dharmadhātuḥ paro 'vyayaḥ || 56 ||]
[don grub grub pa'i kun rtog ni/ /
kun tu rtog pa thams cad spangs/ /
rnam par mi rtog dbyings mi zad/ /
chos dbyings dam pa zad pa med/ /]

don grub bsam pa grub pa ste/ /kun du rtog pa thams cad spangs/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la don du gnyer bas na don te gzugs la sogs pa'i yul lo/ /de yang gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i dngos pos 'jig rten pa la shin tu grags te/ don yang de yin la grub pa yang de yin pas don grub po/ /'di ni phyi'i don nyid du rnam par rtog pa goms pa rnams kyi gzugs la sogs pa dang*/ bdag dang spyi dang*/ yon tan dang*/ bya ba la sogs pa'am/ mtshan nyid rnams la de kho na nyid du mngon par zhen pa ni kun du brtags pa'i ngo bo nyid do/ /


[yena yena vikalpena yadyad vastu vikalpyate 
parikalpita evāsau svabhāvo na sa vidyate || (Vasubandhu, Triṃśikāvijñaptikārikāḥ, 20)]

de ltar slob dpon dbyig gnyen zhabs kyis gsungs pa/ 
	rnam par rtog pa gang gang gis/ /
	dngos po gang gang rnam brtags pa/ /
	de nyid kun du brtags pa yi/ /
	ngo bo nyid de de med do/ /zhes so/ /


...[f. 48r - img. 82]nasya tatvato 'dvayasyāpi bhrāṃtatayā dvayapratibhāsinaḥ (|)(pc - marginal addition) cittacaittakakalpanālakṣaṇasya paratantrasya yānityatvahetutva | viṣayatvakalpanāsā asau para[$2]tantraḥ ||

bsam pa grub pa ni bsam pa nyid pas bsam pa'o/ /bsam pa yang de yin la grub pa yang de nyid yin pas bsam pa grub pa ste/ gzhan dbang gi ngo bo nyid do/ /rgyu dang rkyen dag la rag las pas na gzhan dbang ngo*/ /de ltar yang dge ba dang mi dge ba dang mi g.yo ba dang 'du byed la sogs pa bag chags rnam pa mang po rjes su 'brang bar rang gi byed rgyu'i tshogs las skad cig so so la skye bar 'gyur ba'i de kho na nyid la rmongs nas gnyis su snang ba'i sems dang sems las byung ba'i rtog pa'i mtshan nyid kyi gzhan gyi dbang gang yin pa mi rtag pa nyid dang rgyu nyid de/ yul nyid du rnam par rtog pa de ni gzhan dbang ngo*/ /


tathā cāha ||
	paratantrasvabhāvas tu vikalpaḥ pra○tyayodbhava iti || (Vasubandhu, Triṃśikāvijñaptikārikāḥ, 21ab)

'di ltar gsungs pa/ 
	gzhan gyi dbang gi ngo bo nyid/ /
	rnam rtog yin te rkyen las byung*/ /zhes so/ /


sarvasaṅkalpavarjjita iti | parinispannasvabhāvaḥ | etasyaiva para[$3]tantraprakṛtyā mārgaviśuddhyā vā sarvvāvaraṇanirmalā○dvayaśūnyatā pariniṣpannasvabhāvaḥ || 

kun du rtog pa thams cad spangs/ /zhes pa ni yongs su grub pa'i ngo bo nyid de/ gzhan dbang 'di rang bzhin gyis lam rnam par dag pa'am/ sgrib pa'i dri ma thams cad dang bral ba gnyis su med pa'i stong pa ni yongs su grub pa'i ngo bo nyid do/ /


tathā coktaṃ ||
	niṣpannas tasya pūrveṇa sadā rahi[$4]tatā tu yeti | [ibid, 21cd]

de ltar yang gsungs pa/ grub ni de la snga ma'o/ /rtag tu med par 'gyur de yin/ /zhes so/ /


tataś ca trisvabhāvo bhagavān sarvvatathā○gatajñānasattvaḥ || 

[f. 61r]@#/ /de'i phyir na ngo bo nyid rnam pa gsum ste/ bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa'o/ /


nirvvikalpo 'kṣayo dhātur dharmmadhātuḥ paro 'vyo iti || 

rnam par mi rtog dbyings mi zad/ /chos dbyings dam pa zad mi shes/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra ni[$5]rvvikalpa iti | pariniṣpannajñāne pi vikalpābhā○vāt || 

de la rnam par mi rtog pa ni yongs su grub pa'i ye shes la rnam par rtog pa med pa'i phyir ro/ /


tathā cāha ||
	na vikalpād ṛte kaścit saṃsāro nāma vidyate |
	tenāpetavikalpa[$6]sya sadaiva tava nirvṛtir iti ||
	[Dignāga’s *Mañjughoṣastotra (D rgyud, nu, 79b), also quoted by *Asvabhāva in a commentary Alokamālā verse 1 (D63b4-5)]

de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	rnam par rtog las ma gtogs pa/ /
	'khor ba zhes bya yod ma yin/ /
	de phyir rtog dang mi ldan pa/ /
	rtag tu khyod ni mya ngan 'das/ /zhes so/ /


akṣaya iti | śūnyatāyā ākāśatulyatvāt ||


dhātuar iti | utpattimatāṃ sarvvasaṃskārāṇāṃ heturūpatvāt || dhātva[f. 48v - img. 83]rtho hy atra hetvarthaḥ |

dbyings zhes pa ni skye ba dang ldan pa'i 'du byed thams cad kyi rgyu'i dngos po nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'dir ni dbyings kyi don ni rgyu'i don to/ /mi zad ces pa ni stong pa nyid de/ nam mkha' dang mnyam pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /
	% word order reversed in Tib root + commentary


dharmmadhātur iti | āryadharmāṇāṃ tadālambanaprabhāvitatvāt | 

chos dbyings ni 'phags pa'i chos rnams de la dmigs na skye ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


para iti | bāhyaśrāvakādibhyo viśiṣṭatvāt ||

dam pa zhes pa ni phyi rol pa dang nyan thos la sogs pa las khyad par nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


avyaya iti | asaṃskṛtatvā[$2]t || 

zad mi shes pa ni 'dus ma byas pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

[puṇyavān puṇyasaṃbhāro jñānaṃ jñānākaraṃ mahat |
jñānavān sadasajjñānī saṃbhāradvayasaṃbhṛtaḥ || 57 ||]

[bsod nams ldan pa bsod nams tshogs/ /
ye shes ye shes 'byung gnas che/ /
ye shes ldan pa yod med shes/ /
tshogs gnyis tshogs dang yang dag ldan/ /]


puṇyavān puṇya puṇyasaṃbhāro jñānaṃ jñānākaram mahat iti ○ ||
	% Vilāsavajra appears to actually read "jñānāntaraṃ mahat" in the commentary. Maybe the scribe was looking at a different version of the mūla?
bsod nams ldan pas bsod nams tshogs/ /ye shes ye shes khyad par che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra punātīti puṇyan tad asyāstīti puṇyavān | 
	% pū pavane
de la gso zhing gnas pas na bsod nams te/ de de la yod pas bsod nams ldan pa'o/ /


puṇyasambhāra iti | sayak bharaṇa saṃbhā[$3]raḥ | puṇyasya saṃbhāraḥ puṇyasambhāraḥ | tataś cātra pada○dvayenaitad uktaṃ bhavati | laukikalokottarapuṇyasambhārair aviyukta ity arthaḥ | 

bsod nams tshogs ni yang dag par bsags pa de ni tshogs te/ bsod nams kyi tshogs ni bsod nams kyi tshogs so/ /de'i phyir na 'dir tshig gnyis kyis 'di ltar gsung bar 'gyur la/ 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs dang mi ldan pa ma yin no zhes pa'i don to/ /


jñānam i[$4]ti | bhāhyaśrāvakādijñānaṃ | 

ye shes zhes pa ni phyi rol pa dang nyan thos la sogs pa'i ye shes so/ /


jñānāṃtaram iti | bāhyaśrā○vakādijñānebhyo 'nyat jñānaṃ jñānāntaraṃ śuviśuddhadharmmadhātujñānaṃ jñānagatañ ca tac cittam i[$5]ti | bāhyasyārthasya pramāṇaviruddhatvenāsatvāt | pra○māṇavirodhasya ca vistareṇa pratipāditatvāt ||
	cittamātraṃ bho jinaputrā yad uta traidhā[$6tukam iti |
āgamāt | sarvabhāvasaṃdarśanasya ca | sarvvapramāṇaviruddhatvāt | jñānāntaraṃ | ata eva mahad iti | aśeṣānavaśeṣasatvadhātupari [f. 49-50 missing]

ye shes khyad par zhes pa ni phyi rol pa dang*/ nyan thos la sogs pa'i ye shes de las gzhan pa'i ye shes ni ye shes khyad par te/ shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so/ /ye shes der ma gtogs pa ni sems yin te/ phyi'i don ni tshad ma dang 'gal ba'i phyir dang*/ tshad ma dang 'gal ba yang rgyas par sgrub pa'i phyir ro/ /
	kye rgyal ba'i sras khams gsum po 'di ni sems tsam mo 
zhes lung las 'byung ba'i phyir dang*/ dngos po thams cad mthong ba yang tshad ma thams cad dang 'gal ba'i phyir ye shes khyad par can [f. 61v]te| de nyid kyi phyir na che ba zhes pa ste ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i sems can gyi khams gsum yongs su bskyab pa'i bsam pa can gyi phyir ro/ /

ye shes ldan pa yod med shes/ /tshogs gnyis tshogs ni bsags pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la ye shes ldan pa ni de 'dra ba'i dngos po'i ye shes dang gang ldan pa de ni ye shes ldan pa'o/ /

yod med shes pa ni yod pa dang med pa ni yod med do/ /de gnyis shes pa ni yod med shas pa'o/ /de de la yod pas na yod med shes te/ de ltar slob dpon 'phags pa lha'i zhabs kyis gsungs pa/ 
	yod med yod med ces pa ni/ /
	phyogs gnyis la yang yod min la/ /
	nye bar dmigs pa ring nas kyang*/ /
	de ni brjod par nus pa min/ /
zhes so/ /

tshogs gnyis tshogs ni bsags pa po ni gong du gsungs pa'i tshogs gnyis bsags pa ste/ yongs su rdzogs pa zhes pa'i don to/ /

[śāśvato viśvarāḍ yogī dhyānaṃ dhyeyo dhiyāṃ patiḥ |
pratyātmavedyo hy acalaḥ paramādyas trikāyadhṛk || 58 ||]
[rtag par kun rgyal rnal 'byor can/ /
bsam gtan bsam bya blo yi bdag /
so so rang rig mi g.yo ba/ /
mchog gi dang po sku gsum 'chang/ /]

rtag pa kun rgyal rnal 'byor can/ /bsam gtan bsam bya blo ldan mchog /ces pa ni/ 

de la rtag pa ni rgyun gyi rtag pa 'khor ba ji srid kyi bar du gnas pa'i phyir te/ chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin gyis mi 'da' ba'o zhes pa'i don to/ /

kun rgyal zhes pa ni/ kun ni 'gro ba sna tshogs te/ rgyal ba ni snang ba'i don to/ /kun gyi rgyal po ni kun te g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba'i dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /

rnal 'byor can ni/ ye shes tsam la snyoms zhugs pa/ rnal 'byor zhes ni bshad pa yin/ /zhes pa'i tshig gi phyir na/ rnal 'byor ni gnyis su med pa'i ye shes so/ /de de la yod pas na rnal 'byor can no/ /

bsam gtan ni bsam gtan bzhi'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

bsam bya ni bsam par bya ba'i yul nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

blo ldan mchog ni blo gros so/ /blo rnams kyi mchog ni gtso bo ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

so so rang rig mi g.yo ba/ mchog gi dang po sku gsum 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni so so rang gis rig par bya bas na so so rang rig ste/ chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis rang rig pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /dper na bu mo shin tu dga' ba'i bde ba bzhin du gzhan rnams la bstan par mi 'byor ba'i [f. 62r]@#/ /phyir ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	gcig min du ma ma yin bdag dang gzhan la phan pa phun tshogs chen po'i gzhir gyur pa/ /
	dngos po dang dngos med ma yin nam mkha' bzhin du ro mnyam rtogs dka'i rang bzhin can/ /
	gos pa med cing mi 'gyur gzhi la mi mnyam mnyam la khyab pa po ste spros med pa/ /
	so so rang rig dpe med rgyal ba rnams kyi chos sku de la bdag ni phyag 'tshal lo/ /zhes so/ /

de nyid kyi phyir na mi g.yo ba zhes pa ni gang gi phyir zhes pa'i don to/ /de nyid kyi phyir na yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de nyid mi g.yo ba ste/ rtog pa kun gyi yul ma yin pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

mchog gi dang po ni dang po'i dngos po ste/ mchog kyang de yin la dang po yang yin pas mchog gi dang po'o/ /de ni bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'o/ /

sku gsum 'chang ni sku gsum ni chos dang longs spyod rdzogs pa dang sprul pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sku gsum rnams so/ /de dag 'dzin pas na sku gsum 'chang ngo*/ /

[pañcakāyātmako buddhaḥ pañcajñānātmako vibhuḥ |
pañcabuddhātmamakuṭaḥ pañcacakṣur asaṅgadhṛk || 59 ||]
[sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can/ /
khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag /
sangs rgyas lnga bdag cod pan can/ /
spyan lnga chags pa med pa 'chang/ /]


sangs rgyas sku lnga'i bdag nyid can/ /khyab bdag ye shes lnga yi bdag / sangs rgyas lnga bdag cod phan can/ /spyan lnga chags pa med pa 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la sangs rgyas ni bshad zin to/ /

sku lnga'i bdag nyid ces pa ni ngo bo nyid dang longs spyod rdzogs pa dang*/ rnam par smin pa dang*/ sprul pa dang*/ chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid rnams te sku lnga'o/ /de'i bdag nyid kyi rang bzhin gang dang ldan pa de ni sku lnga'i bdag nyid can no/ /

khyab bdag ni bshad zin to/ /

ye shes lnga'i bdag ni me long lta bu dang*/ mnyam pa nyid dang*/ so sor kun du rtog pa dang*/ bya ba grub pa dang*/ shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes de dag ni ye shes lnga'o/ /de rnams kyi bdag nyid kyi rang bzhin dang gang ldan pa de ni ye shes lnga'i bdag go/ /

sangs rgyas lnga bdag cod pan can ni mi bskyod pa dang*/ rin chen 'byung ldan dang*/ snang ba mtha' yas dang*/ don yod grub ba dang*/ rnam par snang mdzad rnams ni sangs rgyas lnga'o/ /de nyid kyi bdag nyid dang de'i rang bzhin gyis dbu rgyan dang gang ldan pa de ni sangs rgyas lnga bdag dbu rgyan can no/ /

spyan lnga ni sha dang*/ lha [f. 62v]dang/ shes rab dang*/ chos dang*/ sangs rgyas kyi spyan rnams gang la mnga' ba de ni spyan lnga'o/ /

de nyid kyi phyir na chags pa med pa 'chang ste/ shes bya thams cad la chags pa med pa dang*/ thogs pa med la 'khrul pa med par gzigs pa gang yin pa de ni chags pa med pa gzigs pa'o/ /

de ltar chos mngon pa las gsungs pa/
	dgra bcom bse ru ston rnams kyis/ /
	stong gnyis gnyis dang grangs med mthong*/ /zhes so/ /


[janakaḥ sarvabuddhānāṃ buddhaputraḥ paro varaḥ |
prajñābhavodbhavo 'yonir dharmayonir bhavāntakṛt || 60 ||]
[sangs rgyas thams cad skyed pa po/ /
sangs rgyas sras po dam pa mchog /
shes rab srid 'byung skye gnas te/ /
chos kyi skye gnas srid mthar byed/ /]

sangs rgyas thams cad skyed pa po/ /sangs rgyas sras po dam pa'i mchog /ces pa ni/

de la sangs rgyas thams cad skyed pa po ni 'byung ba po ste/ sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byang chub kyi sems kyi rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /de ltar yang de nyid 'dus pa las gsungs pa/ 
	byung dang 'byung bar 'gyur ba yi/ /
	de bzhin gshegs rnams khyod la brten/ /zhes so/ /

sangs rgyas sras po ni sgrib pa'i bag chags thams cad las rnam par grol ba rnam pa thams cad du chos thams cad mkhyen pa dang*/ sems can thams cad kyi rten du gyur pa'i dngos po rnam par rtog pa med pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par ni sangs rgyas te/ de'i sras po ni sangs rgyas sras po ste/ sras ni bdag las skyes pas so/ /de'ang bdag nyid ni don dam par de bzhin nyid las rab tu byung ba'am/ rtog pa med pa'i ye shes so sor rtog pa las byung bas na sangs rgyas su bshad de/ don des byang chub sems dpa' ni sangs rgyas sras zhes gsungs so/ /dam pa ni rab nyid kyi phyir ro/ /mchog ni mngon par 'gro bar bya ba rnams kyi nang na ma nor ba mchog nyid do/ /

shes rab srid 'byung skye gnas nyid/ /chos kyi 'byung gnas srid pa sel/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la shes rab ni chos rab tu rnam par 'byed pa ste/ de yang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos dang gang zag gnyis kyis rnam par dben pa'o/ /


(prajñābhava iti)(conj.)...[f. 51 - img. 84] skandhāḥ śīlasamādhiprajñāvimuktivimuktijñānadarśanātmakāḥ | tebhya udbhavatīti prajñābhavodbhava ity ucyate bhagavān || 

shes rab srid pa ni dag pa'i phung po lnga ste/ tshul khrims dang*/ ting nge 'dzin dang*/ shes rab dang*/ rnam par grol ba dang*/ rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong ba rnams so/ /de rnams las 'byung ba ni shes rab srid 'byung zhes bcom ldan 'das la gsungs so/ /


yonir iti | ... (lost to damage) tāṃ sāsravāṇā(n dharmāṇā)(pc - marginal note)n tadutpatteḥ || dharmayoginir iti | dharmā○ṇāṃ yonir dharmmayoniḥ | dharmā anāśravāḥ kuśalāḥ karmma ... (lost to damage) [$3] ty arthaḥ ||

skye gnas ni byed rgyu [f. 63r]@#/ /ste/ skye ba dang ldan zhing bsgrub bya dang ldan pa'i chos rnams kyi skyed byed de/ chos rnams 'byung ba zhes pa la/ chos rnams kyi skye gnas ni chos kyi 'byung gnas te/ chos ni zag pa med pa'i dge ba'i las kyi lam rnams so/ /de rnams kyi 'byung ba'i gnas ni rgyu zhes pa'i don to/ /


bhavāntakṛd iti | bhavaḥ saṃsāras taśyāntam a○vasānaḥ | tat karotīti bhavāntakṛt || 

srid pa sel ni srid pa ni 'khor ba ste/ de mthar byed pa ni srid mthar byed do/ /


[ghanaikasāro vajrātmā sadyojāto jagatpatiḥ |
gaganodbhavaḥ svayaṃbhūḥ prajñājñānānalo mahān || 61 ||]
[gcig pu sra mkhregs rdo rje'i bdag /
'phral du skyed pa 'gro ba'i bdag /
nam mkha' las byung rang byung ba/ /
shes rab ye shes me [4v]bo che/ /]


ghanaikasāro vajrātmā sadyojāto jagat(patiriti)(conj.; ms lost to damage)

gcig pu sra mkhregs rdo rje'i bdag /skyes ma thag tu 'gro ba'i bdag /ces pa ni/ 


tatra ghanaikasāra iti | ghanaś cāsāv eka śāraś ca ○ ghanaikasāraḥ | ghano nibiḍaḥ | avidyamānān taratvāt | sāraḥ kleśamalābhāvāt | 
	% nibiḍa = dense, thick, etc.
	% or is it avighna??

de la gcig pu sra mkhregs ni gcig pu sra ba yang de yin la mkhregs pa yang de yin pas gcig pu sra mkhregs so/ /sra ba ni brtan pa ste bar chad med pa de nyid kyi phyir ro/ /mkhregs pa ni nyon mongs pa'i dri ma med pa'i phyir ro/ 


ata eva vajrātmeti vajraṃ jñānam abhedyatvāt | tad evā○tmāsvabhāvo yasyāsau vajrātmā sarvvatathāgatānāṃ jñānakāyatvāt || 

de nyid kyi phyir na rdo rje'i bdag ces pa ste/ rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes mi phyed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de'i bdag nyid kyi rang bzhin gang dang ldan pa de rdo rje'i bdag ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sadyojāta iti [$6] X X X X (damage marks) | yatra yatra satvārtam paśyati tatra tatra sadyas tatkṣaṇam eva janmaparigrahāt | sadyojāta ity ucyate | utpattivaśitālābhāt || 

skyes ma thag ni gang dang gang du sems can gyi don mthong ba de dang der skad cig nyid la skye ba yongs su bzhes pa'i phyir na skyes ma thag ces gsungs te/ skye ba la dbang thob pa'i phyir ro/ /


jagatpatir iti [f. 51v - img. 85] | jagatām patir jjagatpatiḥ | jagatsvāmīty arthaḥ | teṣāṃ sarvvasampattyādhārābhūtatvāt ||

'gro ba'i bdag ni 'gro ba rnams kyi bdag po ni 'gro ba'i bdag ste/ 'gro ba'i rje bo zhes pa'i don te/ de rnams kyi phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyi rten yin pa'i phyir na/


gaganodbhavaḥ svayaṃbhūḥ prajñājñānānalomahān iti || 

nam mkha' las byung rang byung ba/ /shes rab ye shes me bo che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra gaganodbhava iti [$2] gaganaṃ śūnyatājñānaṃ tasmād udbhavatīti gaganodbhavaḥ || ○ 

de la nam mkha' las byung ba ni nam mkha' ni stong pa nyid kyi ye shes te/ de las byung bas nam mkha' las byung ba'o/ /


svayambhūr iti | svayam bhavatīti svayam bhūḥ | bodhicittavajrātmakatvāt || 

rang byung ni rang byung bas na rang byung ste/ byang chub sems rdo rje'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


prajñājñānānala [$3] iti | prajñāyā advayalakṣaṇāyā jñānaṃ prajñājñānaṃ a○vikalpātmakaṃ | tad evānalaḥ svāsanakleśendhanadahanakṣamatvāt || 

shes rab ye shes me bo che/ /zhes pa ni/ shes rab ni gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi mtshan nyid ni shes rab ye shes 
te| rtog pa med pa'i bdag nyid kyi ye shes so/ /de nyid me ste bag chags dang bcas pa'i nyon mongs pa'i bud shing sreg par nus pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


mahān iti || [$4] kṣitijalapavanahūtāśanayajamānākāśasoma○sūryāṣṭamurttitvena mahān | jñānabalavīryatejaḥśaktyaiśvarya((ṣṭaguṇa))yogaāt ||

che zhes pa ni sa dang*/ chu dang*/ me dang*/ rlung dang*/ mchod sbyin bya ba dang*/ nam mkha' dang*/ nyi ma dang*/ zla ba zhes pa brgyad kyi spyi [f. 63v]gzugs nyid pas chen po'o/ /yang na ye shes dang*/ brtson 'grus dang*/ stobs dang*/ gzi brjid dang*/ nus pa dang*/ dbang phyug rnams te/ yon tan drug dang ldan pas so/ /

[vairocano mahādīptir jñānajyotir virocanaḥ |
jagatpradīpo jñānolko mahātejāḥ prabhāsvaraḥ || 62 ||]
['od chen rnam par snang bar byed/ /
ye shes snang ba lam me ba/ /
'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron/ /
gzi brjid chen po 'od gsal ba/ /]


vairo[$5]cano mahādīptir jñānajyotir virocnan iti || 

'od chen rnam par snang bar byed/ /ye shes skar ma lam me ba/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra vai○rocana iti gatārthaṃ || mahādīptir iti | mahatī dīpti mahādī((pti))...(lost to damage) namukhena dīptir jñeyāvabhāsasādharmeṇa || 

de la 'od chen ni cher gsal bar byed pas na 'od chen te/ shin tu rnam par dag pa'i ye shes kyi sgo nas te/ 'od ni shes bya gsal bar byed pas chos mthun pa'o/ /rnam par snang bar byed pa'i don ni bshad zin to/ /


jñānajyotir iti | grāhyagrāhakarahitatvāt advayajñānaṃ | tasya jyotir jñāna(m ādarśajñāna)(conj.; ... lost to damage) [f. 52r - img. 86]svabhāvatvāt | 

ye shes skar ma ni gzung 'dzin med pa'i phyir na gnyis su med pa'i ye shes de'i skar ma ni ye shes skar ma zhes bya ste/ me long lta bu'i ya shes kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


virocyate dīpyata iti virocanaḥ | sāmbhogikakāyena sakalajagadarthakaraṇāt || 

lam me ba ni gsal zhing lam me ba ste/ longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus 'gro ba kun gyi don byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


jagat pradīpo jñāno(lko mahātejāḥ prabhāsvaraḥ || i)(em.; ... lost to damage in ms)ti || 

'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron/ /gzi brjid chen po 'od gsal ba/ /zhes pa ni/ 


jagatpradīpa iti | jagatān pradīpo jagatpradī○paḥ pratyavekṣaṇājñānasvarūpatvāt | 

de la 'gro ba'i mar me ni 'gro ba rnams kyi mar me dang 'dra bas 'gro ba'i mar me ste/ so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


jñānolka iti | jñānasyo ... (lost to damage in ms)[$3]sya sajñānolka iti | samatājñānasvabhāvena || mahāte○jo iti | mahattejo 'vabhāso yasya mahātejāḥ kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñāna ... (lost to damage in ms)[$4]svara iti | 

ye shes sgron me zhes pa ni ye shes kyi sgron me'i 'od dang ldan pa de ni ye shes sgron te/ mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin no/ /gzi brjid chen po ni gzi brjid chen po'i 'od dang gang ldan pa de gzi brjid chen po ste/ bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /

prakarṣeṇa bhā[$4]svaraḥ prabhāsvaraḥ pañcajñā○nātmakatvāt | samantād dīpanaśīlo bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ ||
 
'od gsal ba ni phul du byung bas rab tu gsal ba ste/ ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /kun nas snang ba'i tshul dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal yin no/ /


[vidyārājo 'gramantreśo mantrarājā mahārthakṛt |
mahoṣṇīṣo 'dbhutoṣṇīṣo viśvadarśī viyatpatiḥ || 63 ||]

[rig pa'i rgyal mchog sngags dbang po/ /
gsang sngags rgyal po don chen byed/ /
gtsug tor chen po rmad byung gtsug /
nam mkha'i bdag po sna tshogs ston/ /]


vidyārājo gramantreśo [$5] mantrarājo mahārthakṛd iti ||

sngags mchog mnga' bdag rig sngags rgyal/ /gsang sngags rgyal po don chen byed/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra vidyārāja iti ○ vidyānāṃ rājā vidyārājaḥ sarvāsāṃ vidyānāṃ dhāraṇīmaṇḍalagatānān tajjanyatvā[$6]d 
	% see below for Tib.


agramantreśa iti | agraś cāsau mantraś ceti agramantraḥ | tasyeśaḥ prabhuḥ | agramantraś cātra hūṁkāro draṣṭavyaḥ | tasya mahāmudrātmakatvāt 

de la sngags mchog mnga' bdag ni sngags kyang de yin la mchog kyang de yin pas na sngags mchog ste/ de'i bdag ni gtso bo ste/ 'dir sngags mchog mnga' bdag ni yi ge hUM las shes par bya'o/ /de'i phyag rgya chen po'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


rig sngags rgyal ni rig sngags rnams kyi rgyal po ni rig rgyal te/ thams cad du rig sngags te gzungs kyi dkyil 'khor du gyur pa rnams kyis skyed pa po yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


mantra[f. 52v - img. 87]rāja iti mantrāṇāṃ darhmmamaṇḍalaparipaṭhitānāṃ rājā mantrarājaḥ | 

gsang sngags rgyal po ni chos kyi dkyil 'khor las gsungs pa'i gsang [f. 64r]@#/ /sngags rnams kyi rgyal po ni gsang sngags rgyal po'o/ /


mahārthakṛd iti | mahāś cāsāv arthaś ca mahārthaḥ | taṃ karotīti mahārthakṛd iti | karma[$2]maṇḍaloktābhiḥ sakalalaukikalokottarapūjābhi○s trisṛabhir bāhyaguhyamānasikībhiś ca sarvatathāgatapūjākartṛtvenāmeyapuṇyajñā[$3]nasambhāropārjjakatvena ca sarvvasatvārthakaraṇāt || 

don chen byed ni don yang de yin la chen po yang de yin pas don chen no/ /de byed pas na don chen byed de las kyi dkyil 'khor las gsungs pa'i 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mchod pa ma lus pa phyi dang gsang ba dang sems las byung ba gsum gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mchod par byed pa nyid kyis gzhal du med pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs nye bar sogs par byed pas na sems can thams cad kyi don byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


ma○hoṣṇīṣo 'bbhutoṣṇīṣo viśvadarśī viyatpatir iti ||

gtsug tor chen po rmad byung gtsug /nam mkha'i bdag po sna tshogs ston/ /zhes pa ni/


tatra mahoṣṇīṣa iti | mahāṃ[$4]ś cāsāv uṣṇīṣaś ca mahoṣṇīṣaḥ sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣā○kāreṇa rāśībhūtvāvyavasthitatvāt | sarvatathāgatamūrdhni ataś ca ... (lost to damage in ms-c) [$5]cyate || 

de la gtsug tor chen po ni gtsug tor yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas na gtsug tor chen po ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gtsug tor gyi rnam pas phung por gyur cing 'phungs [\[?\] ]par gyur par rnam par gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi gtsug yin pas de'i phyir yang gtsug tor chen po zhes gsungs so/ /


adbhūtoṣṇīṣa iti | tejorāsimukhena yo ○ sau bhagavān sarvvatathāgatajñānasatvaḥ sarvvatathāgatoṣṇīṣe ... (lost to damage in ms-c) mūrdhnivyavasthitaḥ so dbhūtoṣṇīṣa ucyate || 

rmad byung gtsug ni gzi brjid spungs pa'i sgo nas gang bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang ye shes sems dpa' gang yin pa 'di gzi brjid kyi phung po'i sgo nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gtsug tor las spros pa'i rdo rje'i tshul du spyi bor gnas pa gang yin pa de ni rmad byung gtsug ces gsungs so/ /


viśvadarśīti | sakalalaukikalokottarasamādhisvabhāvena viśvan nānāpra((kā))... (lost to damage in ms-c)[ms-c f. 53r - img. 88]rśituṃ śīlaṃ yasya sa viśvadarśī || 
	% Order of names reversed in Tib. See second paragraph for translation.

viyatpatir iti || viyad ākāśaṃ tasya patiḥ viyatpatiḥ | śūnyatāyāḥ patir ity arthaḥ || tathācoktaṃ—
	(nirālambasya cittasya sthiti)(em.; lost to damage in ms-c)r ākāśalakṣaṇā |
	ākāśabhāvanaivaiṣā śūnyatābhāvanā○mateti || 

	[Nāgārjuna, Bodhicittavivaraṇa verse 51 (see Lindner 1988: 200; Tomabechi 2018: 85); quoted in Āmnāyamañjarī ms-a f. 217v5, D 74v]

nam mkha' bdag po ni nam mkha' ni nam mkha' ste/ nam mkha' de'i bdag po ste stong pa nyid kyi bdag po zhes bya ba'i don to/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	dmigs pa dang ni bral ba'i sems/ /
	nam mkha'i mtshan nyid la gnas te/ /
	nam mkha' sgom par byed pa 'di/ /
	stong pa nyid ni bsgom par 'dod/ /ces so/ /

sna tshogs ston ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa thams cad kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi rang bzhin sna tshogs te/ rnam pa tha dad pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang rnam par thar pa'i sgo ston par byed pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de sna tshogs ston zhes pa'o/ /


[sarvabuddhātmabhāvāgryo jagadānandalocanaḥ |
viśvarūpī vidhātā ca pūjyo mānyo mahāṛṣiḥ || 64 ||]
[sangs rgyas kun bdag dngos po mchog/
'gro ba dga' ba'i mig dang ldan/ /
sna tshogs gzugs can skyed pa po/ /
mchod 'os rjed 'os drang srong che/ /]


sarvvabuddhātmabhāvāgryo jaga(dā)(pc - marginal)nandalocana iti ||

sangs rgyas kun bdag ngo bo mchog /'gro kun dga' ba'i mig dang ldan/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra sarvabuddhātma(bhāvāgrya iti sa)(conj.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$3]rve ca te buddhāś ca sarvabuddhāḥ śāśvatādayas teṣām ātmā sarva○buddhātmā tasya sarvabuddhātmanaḥ svabhāvasya bhāvaḥ sattā sarvabuddhātmabhāvo dharmmadhātuḥ .. (a)[$4]grabhavo 'grāḥ | sarvabuddhātmabhāvena tathatvaikarasatvena ○ agryo bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ sarvatathāgatajñānakāyatvād tasya bhagavataḥ || 

de la sangs rgyas kun bdag ngo bo mchog ni sangs rgyas kyang de yin la kun kyang de yin pas sangs rgyas [f. 54v]kun te/ rtag pa la sogs pa de rnams kyi bdag nyid ni sangs rgyas kun bdag go/ /sangs rgyas kun bdag de'i ngo bo ni rang bzhin no/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid kyi ngo bo yod pa ni chos kyi dbyings te/ mchog gi dngos po ni mchog nyid do/ /sangs rgyas kun bdag ngo bos de'i de bzhin nyid du ro gcig pa nyid kyis bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal te/ bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


jagadānanda[$5]locana iti | jagatām ānando jaga(dā)(em.; tā ms-c)nandas tasya jaga○dānandasya locano bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | yena heyopādeyapravicayātmakatvāt prajñācakṣuḥ | 

'gro kun dga' ba'i mig dang ldan/ /zhes pa ni 'gro ba thams cad dga' ba ni 'gro ba dga' ba ste/ de'i mig dang ldan pa ni bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal te/ gang gis blang ba dang*/ spong ba rab tu rnam par 'byed pa'i snang bas na shes rab kyi spyan no/ /


viśvarūpī vidhā(tā)(em.; deest in ms-c) ca pūjyo mānyo mahāṛṣir iti || 

sna tshogs gzugs can yid las byung*/ /mchod 'os brjod 'os drang srong che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra viśvarūpīti | sthiracalasarvabhāvasvabhāvatayā nānārūpan darśakatvāt | 

de la sna tshogs gzugs can ni g.yo ba dang*/ mi g.yo ba'i dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin nyid kyis na gzugs sna tshogs pa ston pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


vidhā[ms-c f. 53v - img. 89]dheti | sarvvasatvānāṃ yathābhavyatayā sarvamantramudrāsamayamaṇḍalotsarggāt || sarvvalaukikalokottarapūjārhatvena pujyaḥ pūjanīyaḥ | ata eva mānyo mānanīyaḥ sa[$2]rvasatvānāṃ ||

skyed pa po ni sems can thams cad ji ltar skal ba dang ldan pa'i gzugs nyid kyi sngags dang phyag rgya dang dam tshig dang dkyil 'khor thams cad bskyed pa'i phyir ro/ /
	% Order is inexplicably reversed here, since the root verse translation is not altered.


mahāṛṣir iti | mahāṃś cāsāv ṛṣiś ca mahā○ṛṣiḥ| buddho bhagavān mahāṛṣi ity ucyate ||

drang srong che ni drang srong yang de yin la che ba yang de nyid yin pas drang srong che ste/ sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das ni drang srong che zhes so/ /

mchod 'os zhes pa ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa kun gyis mchod par 'os pa nyid kyis mchod 'os te/ mchod par bya ba'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir brjod 'os te sems can thams cad kyis bstod pa'o/ /


[kulatrayadharo mantrī mahāsamayamantradhṛk |
ratnatrayadharaḥ śreṣṭhas triyānottamadeśakaḥ || 65 ||]
[rigs gsum 'chang ba gsang sngags ldan/ /
dam tshig chen po gsang sngags 'dzin/ /
gtso bo dkon mchog gsum 'dzin pa/ /
theg pa gsum mchog ston pa po/ /]


kulatrayadharo mantrī mahāsamayamantradhṛg iti [$3]

rigs gsum 'chang ba gsang sngags 'chang*/ /dam tshig chen po gsang sngags 'dzin/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra kulatrayaṃ kāyavākcittabhedena tan dhārayatīti ku○latrayadharaḥ || 

de la rigs gsum 'chang ba ni sku gsung thugs kyi dbye bas de 'dzin pa ni rigs gsum 'chang ba'o/ /


mantrāḥ sakalalaukikalokottarāḥ te vidyante yasya sa mantrī | sa[$4]rvvamantramūrttidharatvād bhagavato jñānasatvasya ||

gsang sngags 'chang ba ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gsang sngags te/ de rnams dang gang ldan pa de ni gsang sngags can te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das ye shes sems dpa' ste/ gsang sngags kyi sku thams cad 'chang ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


mahāsamaya○mantradhṛg iti | mahāṃś cāsau samayaś ca mahāsamayaḥ sa ca bhagavān bodhicittavajras tasya mantra[$5]ḥ| mantryate trāyana iti mantraḥ | jñānakṛpātmakatvāt | ta○n dhārayatīti mahāsamayamantradhṛg bhagavān sarvvatathāgatajñānakāyaḥ || 

dam tshig chen po gsang sngags 'dzin ni dam tshig kyang de yin la chen po yang de yin pas dam tshig chen po ste/ de ni bcom ldan [f. 65r]@#/ /'das byang chub kyi sems rdo rje'i ngo bo'o/ /de'i sngags ni shes shing skyob bas gsang sngags te/ ye shes dang snying rje'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de 'dzin pas na dam tshig tshin [\[?\] ]po gsang sngags 'dzin ni bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku'o/ /


(ratnatrayadharaḥ śre)(em.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$6]ṣṭhas triyānottamadeśaka iti || 

gtso bo dkon mchog gsum 'dzin pa/ /theg pa mchog gsum ston pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 


ratnatrayadhara iti | ratnānāṃ trayaṃ ratnatrayaṃ durllabhatvāt mahārghatvāt prakāśakatvāc ratnānāṃ ... (lost to damage in ms-c)[f. 54r - img. 90] saṃghākhyāni tāni dhārayaṇḍāti ratnatrayadharaḥ 

sarveṣām abhigamanīyānāṃ yaḥ prathamataram abhigamanam arhati sa śreṣṭha ucyate | 

de la gtso bo ni mngon par 'gro ba thams cad kyi nang na gang dang por shin tu mngon par 'gro bar 'os pa ni de gtso bor gsungs te/ de yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /

dkon mchog gsum ni dkon mchog rnams ni gsum ste/ thob dka' ba'i phyir dang*/ rin thang che ba'i phyir dang*/ rab tu gsal bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /rin po che dang 'dra bas dkon mchog go/ /gsum ni sangs rgyas dang*/ chos dang*/ dge 'dun rnams so/ /de rnams 'dzin pas na dkon mchog gsum 'dzin pa zhes bya'o/ /
	% Order reversed in Tib.


(triyānottamadeśaka i)(conj.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$2]ti| trayāṇāṃ srāvakapratyekabuddhamahāyānānām uttamadeśaka iti sarvasatvānāṃ gotrendriyāśayānuśayajñatvāt || 

theg pa mchog gsum ston pa po ni nyan thos dang*/ rang sangs rgyas dang*/ theg pa chen po gsum rab tu ston pa ste/ sems can gyi rigs thams cad la dbang po dang*/ bsam pa dang*/ bag la nyal ba mkhyen pa'i sgo nas ston pa'i phyir ro/ /
	% Tib. appears to have read gotra in compound with sarvasattvānām


[amoghapāśo vijayī vajrapāśo mahāgrahaḥ |
vajrāṅkuśo mahāpāśo ...]
[don yod zhags pa rnam par rgyal/ /
'dzin pa chen po rdo rje zhags/ /
rdo rje lcags kyu zhags pa che/ /...]


(amoghapāśo vijayī vajrapāśo ma)(em.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$3]hāgrahaḥ | vajrāṃkuśo mahāpāśa iti ||

don yod zhags pa rnam par rgyal/ /'dzin pa chen po rdo rje zhags/ /rdo rje lcags kyu zhags pa che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra amogha○pāśa iti | amogha 'vandhyaḥ pāśa ivpāśo yasyāsāv amo(ghapāśa ...)(em.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$4]vineyānāṃ satvānāṃ tathāpratibhāsanāt |

de la don yod zhags pa ni don yod pa ni 'bras bu yod pa'o/ /zhags pa dang 'dra bas na zhags pa ste/ /de gang dang ldan pa de ni don yod zhags pa ste/ byang chub kyi sems rdo rjes 'dul ba'i sems can rnams la de bzhin du so sor snang ba'i phyir ro/ /


vijayīti trai○lokyasamāpatisamādhimukhyena || 

rnam par rgyal ba ni 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas so/ /
	% Tib indicates trailokyavijayasamādhi?


vajrapāśa iti ratnasambhavadvāreṇa || 

ma(hāgraha iti gra)(conj.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$6]haṇaṃ graho mahāś cāsau grahaś ca mahāgraho vajranigaḍaḥ sa ca amitābhasvabhāvena ||

'dzin pa chen po zhes pa ni 'dzin par byed pas na 'dzin pa ste/ 'dzin pa yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas 'dzin pa chen po ni rdo rje lcags sgrog go/ /de yang snang ba mtha' yas kyi rang bzhin gyi sgo nas so/ /

rdo rje zhags pa ni rin chen 'byung ldan gyi sgo nas so/ /
	% Tib reverses order


vajrāṅkuśa iti | akṣobhyarūpeṇa | 

rdo rje lcags khu ni mi bskyod pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi sgo nas so/ /
	% lcags khu -- etext problem?


mahāpāśa iti | pāśas (tobha)(?) ityā((.. ..))[f. 54v - img. 91]pāyaḥ | mahāṃś cāsau pāśaś ca mahāpāśo vajrāveśaḥ sa cāmoghasiddhirūpeṇeti | 

zhags pa che zhes pa ni zhags pa dang sdom zhes pa 'bebs pa'i rnam [f. 65v]grangs te/ zhags pa yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas zhags pa che ni rdo rje 'bebs pa'o/ /de yang don yod grub pa'i ngo bos so/ /


tato sau bhagavān ity abhimahāvairocanādibhir abhidhāyakaiḥ sabdasamuhair nnāmamantrā .. [$2]ḥ prathamāntavibhaktyutpannair abhidheyo veditavya iti || 

de nas bcom ldan 'das 'dir/ sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad che/ /zhes pa la sogs pa mngon par rjod par byed pa'i sgra'i tshogs rnams kyis sngags kyi yig 'bru'i rnam par dbye ba dang po'i mtha' can gyi bstan pa brjod par bya bar shes par bya'o/ /


tata○ś cāsminn api pūrvavat mahāvairocanādayaḥ śuklavarṇṇāś cakrakhaḍgapāśa((yo)) bhūtvā ... (lost to damage in ms-c)[$3]sya ca sarvabuddhakṣetraṣu ca gatvā satvān svavimokṣamukhena saṃ○śodhya punar āgatya nāmamantrākṣarāṇi bhūtvā svacakre cakrībhūyasthitā ... (lost to damage in ms-c)

de nas 'dir yang sngon bzhin du rnam par snang mdzad chen po la sogs pa sku mdog dkar po dang*/ 'khor lo dang ral gri phyag na 'dzin par gyur pa rnams phyung ste/ phyung nas kyang sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad du song ste/ sems can thams cad rang gi rnam par thar pa'i sgo nas dag par byas te/ yang phyir log nas mtshan gyi sngags kyi yig 'brur gyur nas rang gi 'khor lo la 'khor lo can du gyur te gnas par blta bar bya'o/ /


[$5]ta mantramukhena caryācārī bodhisatvo nāmasaṅgītim pa(ṭha)(pc - marginal note)n tān○ ca guaṇagaṇasamūhān avāpnotīti ||  

de nas gong ma bzhin du sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa'i byang chub sems dpas mtshan yang dag par brjod pa bklag par bya ste/ de yon tan gyi tshogs pa bkod pa de rnams nyid thob par 'gyur ro/ /


dvitīyasya ca mahāvai...(lost to damage in ms-c)[$5]śāśvatādikramabhedena ṣaḍtriṃśat ṣaḍtriśatpravibha((jya)) pūrvva○vat sarvam anuvidheyam ity āmnāyaḥ || 

gāthāś ca ... [$6] tiśatam aṅkato pi || 181 || 

rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i 'khor lo gnyis pa la mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i gzhi rnams ni rtag pa la sogs pa rigs kyi dbye bas sum cu rtsa drug tu rnam par phye ste/ gong ma bzhin du thams cad sngags su bsgrub po zhes pa ni man ngag go/ /tshigs bcad ni tshig rkang gcig ma tshang ba dang nyi shu rtsa lnga ste/ mtshan nyid sngags kyi yi ge rnams ni brgya brgyad cu rtsa gcig brtsis pa yin no/ /


āryanāmasaṅgītiṭikāyāṃ nāmamantrārthāvalokinyāṃ śuviśuddhadharmadhātujñānastutya...(lost to damage in ms-c)

'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lnga ba zhes bya ba las shin tu rnam par dag pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la bstod pa'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa ste drug pa'o// //



