[f. 55r - img. 92]darśajñānasvabhāvaṃ krodhacakraṃ trilokyavijayarupeṇa bhagavataḥ sarvvatathāgatajñānastutim āha || 

da ni gsum pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin khams gsum rnam 
par rgyal ba'i gzugs kyis bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku la bstod pa gsungs te/ 


vajrabhairavabhīkara iti | dvandena nirddeśa(...)(lost to damage in ms-c)vaś ca bhīkaraś ca vajrabhairavabhīkaraḥ | tatra vajrabhairavatantre ○ dvāv imau paripaṭhitatvāt ||    ||

rdo rje 'jigs byed 'jigs par byed/ /ces pa ni zlas dbye ba bstan te/ de'i phyir don ni 'di ltar 'gyur te/ rdo rje 'jigs byed dang 'jigs par byed pa ni rdo rje 'jigs byed [f. 66r]@#/ /'jigs par byed de/ dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi rgyud las 'di gnyis su yongs su brjod pa'i phyir ro/ /


yaduta vajrabhairavo vajra ... (lost to damage in ms-c)[$3]vajrabhairavabhīkaro bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ || kasyād ity a○ta āha | dveṣavineyānāṃ saumyatā'nupayogāt | 

di lta ste/ rdo rje 'jigs byed dang 'jigs par byed pa de ni gnyis nyid kyi rang bzhin dang gang ldan pa de 'jigs byed 'jigs par byed de bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /de ci'i phyir zhe na/ gsungs pa/ zhe sdang gis 'dul ba rnams zhi ba'i rjes su mi 'tsham pa ste/ 


tathācoktaṃ (śrīsaṃvaratantra[$4]
	atyantadu)(Tribe 2016; lost to damage in ms-c)ṣṭarodreṣu somyatā nopayujyate |
	prajñopāyamayaṃ manyuṃ ○ cakruḥ sarvvatathāgatā iti ||

de ltar yang dpal bde mchog gi rgyud las gsungs pa/ 
	shin tu khro zhing gtum pa la/ /
	zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te/ /
	shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo las/ /
	khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad/ /ces so/ /


[krodharāṭ ṣaṇmukho bhīmaḥ ṣaḍnetraḥ ṣaḍbhujo balī |
daṃṣṭrākarālakaṅkālo halāhalaśatānanaḥ || 67 ||]

[khro bo'i rgyal po gdong drug 'jigs/ /
mig drug lag drug stobs dang ldan/ /
keng rus mche ba gtsigs pa po/ /
ha la ha la gdong brgya pa/ /]


krodharāṭ ṣaṇmukho bhīmaḥ ṣaḍnetraḥ ṣaḍbhujo balī(ti | tatra krodha)(em.; lost to damage in ms-c)[$5]rāḍiti krodhavijayeya ((pavya))(ms; guhyata, possible em.)ntre | krodhanarājeta iti ○ krodharāṭ || tathā coktaṃ ||
	athaiṣa mañjughoṣasya nāmnokte ((dho)) yamāntakaḥ
	dṛṣṭā (...)(lost to damage in ms-c)[$6] dhāḥ sarve viśalitāyudhā iti ||
ata eva krodharāḍ iti || 

khro bo'i rgyal po gdong drug 'jigs/ /mig drug lag drug stobs dang ldan/ /zhes pa ni/ de la khro bo'i rgyal po ni dpal khro bo rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las gsungs so/ /khro bo'i rgyal po ni khro bo'i rgyal bo ste/ da ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	de nas 'jam pa'i dbyangs 'di ni/ /
	khro bo'i ming ni gshin rje gshed/ /
	drag la mthu rtsal ldan pa po/ /
	de mthong nas ni khro po gzhan/ /
	thams cad kyis ni lag cha 'chor/ /
zhes pa de nyid kyi phyir ni khro bo'i rgyal po'o/ /


ṣaḍmukha iti śrīmāyājalatantre | ṣaḍmukhāni yasāsau ṣaḍmukhaḥ karacaraṇayor apyārthāt ṣaḍ(...)(lost to damage in ms-c)[f.55v - img 91] ditavyaṃ sa ca bhagavān 

gdong drug ni dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud las gsungs te/ gdong pa drug dang gang ldan pa de ni gdong drug ste/ zhabs dang phyag gnyis kyang don gyis drug nyid du rig par bya'o/ /de yang bcom ldan 'das so/ /


bhīma iti vajrapāṇyabhiṣekatantre bīmo bhayānakaḥ || tathā ca sarvvaṅgeṣu sarvaromakūpeṣu vajratejaḥprabhṛtīni maṇḍalāni niścārya teṣu (...)(lost to damage in ms-c)ṇḍaleṣu krodharājān nānāveśān nānāpraharṇopetān ○ krūbhaṅga ñcitalalāṭāna mahāśmaśrukarālanayanavadanān saṃbhārya bhayopadarśanā(...)(lost to damage in ms-c) ma ity ucyate || 

'jigs zhes pa ni phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las te/ 'jigs pa ni 'jigs su rung ba'o/ /de ltar yang yan lag thams cad dang ba spu'i bu ga thams cad las rdo rje'i gzi brjid la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor 'thon zhing de rnams kyis khro bo'i rgyal po rnam pa sna tshogs kyi gzugs dang sna tshogs kyi mtshon cha dang ldan pa/ smin mtshams kyi khro gnyer gyi rlabs bskyod pa'i dpral ba dang sma ra gzed pa/ mche pa gtsigs pa dang*/ mig bgrad pa'i zhal dang ldan pa rnam par spros te/ 'jigs pa nye bar ston pa'i phyir na 'jigs pa zhes gsungs so/ /


ṣaḍnetra iti | tatraiva ṣadnetrāṇi yasya ○ sa ṣaḍnetraḥ atraikadeśanastutiḥ || avayavesamudāyoya cārāt | yathā bhīmas(...)(lost to damage in ms-c)[$4]ty abhīmābhīmeti | 

mig drug ni de nyid las te/ mig drug dang gang ldan pa de mig drug ste/ de la phyogs gcig gis bstod pa ste/ yan lag la spyi [f. 66v]nye bar btags pa ste/ dper na 'jigs pa'i sde la 'jigs pa dang bden snang la snang ba zhes pa lta bu'o/ /

śaḍbhuja iti śrīvajramaṇḍālaṅkāra○tantre | ṣaḍbhujā yasyāsau ṣaḍbhujaḥ |

lag drug ni dpal rdo rje snying po'i rgyan gyi rgyud las te/ phyag drug dang ldan pa ni yan lag drug go/ /


balīti balaṃ kāyikaṃ sāmarthyaṃ tad(...)(lost to damage in ms-c)[$5]dyottamatantre mahābala iti prasiddhaḥ (|)(pc - above line)

stobs dang ldan ni stobs ni lus las byung ba'i nus pa ste/ de dang gang ldan pa ni stobs dang ldan pa ste/ dpal rig pa mchog gi rgyud chen po las stobs po che zhes rab tu grags so/ /


draṃṣṭṛākarālaka○ṅkālo halāhalaśatānana iti ||

keng rus mche ba gtsigs pa po/ /ha la ha la gdong brgya pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 

tatra draṃṣṭṛākarāla iti | (...)(lost to damage in ms-c)[$6] ((śu)) bhayānike yasyāsau daṃṣṭrākaralaḥ ||

kaṅkāla iti śrīcakramavare ||

de la keng rus ni dpal bde mchog 'khor lo'i rgyud las so/ /

mche ba gtsigs pa ni dpal rdo rje stug po bsdus pa las te/ mche ba gtsigs shing ma rungs pa 'jigs par byed pa dang gang ldan pa de mche ba gtsigs pa'o/ /
	% Order reversed in Tib.


halāhalaśatānana iti ayam api pūrvvavat dvadvavirdeśa (...)(lost to damage in ms-c)[f. 56r - img 94]śatantre || śatrānana itit śrīvajraśeṣaratantre | śtānyānanāni mukhāni yasya śatānanaḥ | 

ha la ha la gdong brgya pa/ /zhes pa ni/ de yang gong ma bzhin du zlas dbye bas bstan te/ ha la ha la ni don yod zhags pa'i rgyud las so/ /gdong brgya pa ni dpal rdo rje rtse mo'i rgyud las te/ gdong ste zhal brgya dang gang ldan pa de gdong brgya'o/ /


[yamāntako vighnarāḍ vajravego bhayaṃkaraḥ |
vighuṣṭavajro hṛdvajro māyāvajro mahodaraḥ || 68 ||]
[gshin rje mthar byed bgegs kyi rgyal/ /
rdo rje shugs can 'jigs byed pa/ /
rdo rje grags pa rdo rje'i snying/ /
sgyu 'phrul rdo rje gsus po che/ /]


yamāntako vighnarāṭ vajravego bhayaṃkara iti ||

gshin rje gshed po bgegs kyi rgyal/ /rdo rje shugs can 'jigs byed pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra yamāntaka iti śrī[$2]samāje | yamasyāntako vināśako yamāntakaḥ | 

de la gshin rje gshed po ni dpal gsang ba 'dus pa las te/ gshin rje gshed po ste/ phung bar byed pa ni gshin rje gshed do/ /


vigha○sarāḍ iti rājata iti rāṭ vighnānāṃ gaṇapatiprabhṛtīnāṃ rāṭ .vighnarāṭ | amṛtrakuṇḍa[$3]liḥ | sa māyājālādau (pratītra)(ms; grags pa, Tib.) iti || 
	% Tib. appears to suggest vairocanamāyājāla

bgegs kyi rgyal ni rgyal po yin pas rgyal po ste/ tshogs bdag la sogs pa'i bgegs rnams kyi rgyal po pas bgegs kyi rgyal po ste/ bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'o/ /de rnam par snang mdzad sgyu 'phrul dra ba la sogs pa'i rgyud las grags so/ /


vajravega i○ti śrīmahāsamayatantre| vajrasya vego vajravegas tadvad vego yasya sa vajravega ||

rdo rje shugs 'chang ni dpal dam tshig chen po'i rgyud las te/ rdo rje shugs ni rdo rje shugs so/ /de 'dra ba'i shugs dang gang ldan pa de ni rdo rje shugs 'chang ngo*/ /


bhayaṅkara[$4] iti || śrīguhyendutilake bhayaṅkaro bhīti bhayaṅkara○ḥ sarvaduṣṭasantrāsanāt || 

'jigs par byed pa ni dpal zla gsang thig le'i rgyud las gsungs te/ sdang ba thams cad 'jigs par byed cing skrag par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


vighuṣṭavajro hṛdvajro (māyāvajro)(pc - written in margin) mahodara iti || 

rdo rje grags pa rdo rje'i snying*/ sgyu 'phrul rdo rje gsus po che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra vighuṣṭavajra i[$4]ti | śrī advayasamatāvijaye | viśeṣair guṣṭo viguṣṭaḥ | mah(ā)(pc; a, ac)śabda ity arthaḥ | sa eva vajro abhedya(tvād y)(pc - written in margin)sya sa vighuṣṭavajraḥ || 

rdo rje grags pa gnyis su med par mnyam pa nyid rnam par sbyong ba'i rgyud las so/ /khyad par du grags pa rdo rje grags pa ste/ sgra chen zhes pa'i don to/ /de nyid rdo rje ste mi shigs pa'i phyir ro/ /de gang dang [f. 67r]@#/ /ldan pa de rdo rje grags pa'o/ /


hṛdvajra iti | śrīgu[$6]hyendutilaka eva | hṛdi vajraṃ yasya sa hṛdvajraḥ

rdo rje snying ni dpal zla gsang thig le nyid las te/ gang rdo rje'i snying yin pa de rdo rje'i snying ngo*/ /


māyāvajra iti | asminn eva ṣoḍaśasāhasrike paṭhyate || māyā nimāṇan tad eva vajram abhedyarūpatvāt yasya sa [f. 56v - img. 95] māyāvajraḥ | 

sgyu 'phrul rdo rje ni khri drug stong pa nyid las gsungs te/ sgyu 'phrul ni sprul pa'o/ /de nyid rdo rje ste mi phyed pa'i gzugs nyid kye phyir ro/ /de gang dang ldan pa de ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje'o/ /


mahodara iti | tatraiva mahad udaraṃ yasyāsau mahodaraḥ | 

gsus po che zhes pa ni de kho na las te/ gsus pa chen po dang gang ldan pa de ni gsus po che'o/ /


[kuliśeśo vajrayonir vajramaṇḍo nabhopamaḥ |
acalaikajaṭāṭopo gajacarmapaṭārdradhṛk || 69 ||]
[rdo rje'i skye gnas rdo rje'i dbang/ /
rdo rje snying po mkha' 'dra ba/ /
mi g.yo ral pa gcig bsgyings pa/ /
glang chen pags pa rlon pa 'chang/ /]


kuliśeśo vajrayoni<rmā>r vajramaṇḍo nabhopama iti |

rdo rje skye gnas rdo rje'i bdag /rdo rje snying po mkha' 'dra ba/ /zhes pa ni/ 


kuliśeśa iti | kuliśo [$2] vajraṃ tasyeśaḥ prabhur ity arthaḥ | sa ca śrīvajrapātāla○tantre || 

vajrayonir iti | śrībhutaḍāmaratantre | vajraṃ yoniḥ kāraṇaṃ yasya sa vajrayoniḥ [$3] ||

de la rdo rje'i skye gnas ni dpal 'byung po 'dul byed kyi rgyud las te/ rdo rje skye gnas te rgyu gang yin pa de rdo rje'i skye gnas so/ /

rdo rje'i bdag ni rdo rje ni de'i bdag po gtso bo zhes pa'i don to/ /de yang dpal rdo rje sa 'og gi rgyud las so/ /
	% Order is reversed in Tib.


vajramaṇḍa iti | śrīvajramaṇḍālaṅkāre vajraṃ ma○ṇḍo yasya sa vajramaṇḍaḥ sāra ity arthaḥ || 

rdo rje snying po ni dpal rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las so/ rdo rje snying po ni rdo rje snying po snye snying khu zhes pa'i don to/ /


nabhopama iti | śrīguhyakośe | na bhavatīti [$4] nabha ākāśaṃ | utpattimatām avakāśadānāt syayaṃ cā○saṃskṛtatvāt | na bhavatīty arthaḥ tac ca śūnyatāsvarūpan tenopamā yasya sa tathoktaḥ śūnyato[$5]pama ity arthaḥ | 

mkha' 'dra ba ni dpal gsang ba mdzod kyi rgyud las so/ /mi 'gyur bas nam mkha' ste skye ba dang ldan pa'i go skabs ster ba'i phyir ro/ /rang nyid kyang 'dus ma byas pa nyid kyi phyir na 'byung ba med do zhes pa'i don to/ /de yang stong pa nyid kyi ngo bo ste/ de'i dpe dang gang ldan pa de de ltar gsungs te stong pa nyid kyi dpe zhes pa'i don to/ /


acalaikajaṭāṭopo gajacarmapaṭā○rddradhṛg iti | 

mi g.yo ral pa gcig gis bsgyings/ /glang chen ko rlon gos su gyon/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra acalaikajaṭāṭopa iti dvadvanirdeśaḥ tataś cāyam arthaḥ | acalaś caika[$6]jaṭāṭopaś ca acalaikajaṭāṭopaḥ | tatrācalaḥ śrīmāyājālādau ekajaṭāṭopaḥ śrīvajrakirīṭitantre | na cālyate na kalyyate sarvamārair (itrā)(ms; ityā, em.)calaḥ ekā cāsau [f. 57r - img. 96]jatā ca ekajaṭā tayā āṭopaḥ sauṣṭhavaṃ yasyāsāv ekajaṭāṭopaḥ || 
	% Tribe spells the latter vajrakirīṭatantra
	% May √kal in the sense of 'to be influence', or kalpyate?

de la/ mi g.yo ral pa gcig gis bsgyings/ /zhes pa ni zlas dbye ba bstan to/ /de'i phyir 'di'i don ni mi g.yo ba dang ral pa gcig gis 
bsgyings pa ste/ mi g.yo ral pa gcig /gis bsgyings so/ /de la mi g.yo ba ni dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba la sogs pa las te/ bdud thams cad kyis mi g.yo zhing mi dngangs pas na mi g.yo ba'o/ /ral pa gcig gis bsgyings zhes pa ni dpal rdo rje cod pan gyi rgyud las so/ /ral pa yang de yin la gcig kyang de nyid yin pas ral pa gcig go/ /de bsgyings pa ni bsgyings pa ste/ ral pa gcig gis bsgyings ba'o/ /


gajacarmapaṭārdradhṛg iti | śrīcakrasamvare | gajasya carma gajacarma paṭaś cāsāv ārdraś ca paṭārdraḥ gajacarmaś ca pa[$2]ṭārdro gajācarmapaṭārdraḥ | tan dhārayatīti gajacarmapaṭārdra○dhṛk ||

glang chen ko rlon gos su gyon/ /zhes pa ni dpal 'khor lo bde mchog gi rgyud las te/ glang po che'i ko ba ni glang chen ko ba ste/ glang chen ko ba yang [f. 67v]de yin la rlon pa yang de nyid yin pas glang chen ko rlon no/ /glang po che'i ko rlon nyid gyon pa yin pas glang chen ko rlon gos su gyon pa ste/ de 'dzin pas na/ glang chen ko rlon gos su gyon/ /zhes pa'o/ /


[hāhākāro mahāghoro hīhīkāro bhayānakaḥ |
aṭṭahāso mahāhāso vajrahāso mahāravaḥ || 70 ||]
[drag chen hA hA zhes sgrogs pa/ /
hI hI zhes sgrogs 'jigs par byed/ /
gad mo chen po gad rgyangs can/ /
rdo rje gad mo cher sgrogs pa/ /]


hāhākaro mahāghoro hīhīkāro bhayānakaḥ 

drag chen ha ha zhes sgrogs pa/ /hi hi zhes sgrogs 'jigs par byed/ /ces pa ni/ 


hāhākāra iti | śrīkrodhavijaye hāhā[$3]bhūtanāmamaṇḍala | tatra hāhākṛtvā tiṣṭhatīti hāhākara○ ity ucyate || mahāghora iti | tatraiva mahaṃś cāsau ghoraś ca mahāghora iti | 

de la drag chen ni dpal khro bo rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las te/ drag po yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas drag chen no/ /ha ha zhes sgrogs zhes pa ni rgyud de nyid kyi ha har gyur pa zhes bya ba'i dkyil 'khor de la ha ha byas nas gnas pas ha ha zhes sgrogs zhes gsungs so/ /


hīhīkara i[$4]ti śrīkrodhendutilako tadanukaraṇenāt chānāt || bha○yānaka iti | śrīsarvatantrasamuccaye | 

hi hi zhes sgrogs ni dpal khro bo zla ba'i thig le'i rgyud de las gsungs te/ de rjes su byed pas langs pa'i phyir ro/ /'jigs par byed pa ni dpal rgyud kun las btus pa las gsungs so/ /


aṭṭahāso mahāhāsa vajrahāso mahārava iti || 

gad mo chen po gad rgyangs can/ /rdo rje gad mo cher sgrogs pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


ta[$5]trāṭṭahāsa iti | śrī asādhāraṇaguhyālaṅkāravyūhatantre | hasanaṃ hāsaḥ | aṭṭair uccair hāso aṭṭahāso mahāhāsa iti | nairattaryeṇa(ms; sic for nairantaryeṇa)

de la gad mo chen po ni rgyun chad pa med pa'i don to/ /de la dpal thun mong ma yin pa'i gsang ba'i rgyan bkod pa'i rgyud las te/ gad rgyangs can ni gad mo ni dgod pa'o/ /gad rgyangs te gsang mthon pos bzhad pa ni gad rgyangs so/ /


vajrahās [$5] iti | jñānahāsaḥ saramānasaḥ | 

rdo rje gad mo ni ye shes kyi bshad pa ste/ de yang yid kyi'o/ /


mahārava iti | trailokyapūrakatvena | mahāṃś cāsau ravaś ca mahāravaḥ | ete catvāro pi tatraiva paṭhyante || 

cher sgrogs pa ni 'jig rten gsum gang bar byed pa ste/ chen po yang de yin la sgrogs pa yang de nyid yin pas cher sgrogs pa'o/ /bzhi po 'di yang rgyud de nyid las bstan to/ /


[vajrasatvo mahāsatvo vajrarājo mahāsukhaḥ |
vajracaṇḍo mahāmodo vajrahūṃkārahūṃkṛtiḥ || 71 ||]
[rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che/ /
rdo rje rgyal po bde ba che/ /
rdo rje gtum po dga' ba che/ /
rdo rje hUM mdzad hUM gi gzugs/ /]

vajrasatvo mahāsatvo [f. 57v - img. 97] vajrarājo mahāsukha iti ||

rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che/ /rdo rje rgyal po bde ba che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra vajrasatva iti | paramādye | mahāsatva iti mahāvajradhara śrīsamāje || vajrarāja iti guhyakośe | mahāsukha iti śrīsamvare | ta[$2]tra mahāsukha iti yat (ta)(pc; tā, ac)thāgatam anāsravaṃ sukhan tat ma○hāsukha ity ucyate | tatraivoktaṃ sukhaṃ śam iti vikhyātaṃ sarvabauddhaṃ mahāsukham iti ||
	% probably should emend to tathāgatānām

de la rdo rje sems dpa' ni dpal mchog dang po'i rgyud las so/ /sems dpa' che ni rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po ste/ dpal gsang ba 'dus pa las gsungs so/ /rdo rje rgyal po ni dpal gsang ba mdzod kyi rgyud las so/ /bde ba chen po ni dpal bde mchog gi rgyud las so/ /de la bde ba chen po zhes pa ni/ de bzhin gshegs pa'i zag pa med pa'i bde ba gang yin pa de ni bde ba chen po zhes gsungs so/ /de nyid las gsungs pa'ang bde ba ni saM zhes pa la sogs pa'o/ /


vajracaṇḍo[$3] mahāmodo vajrahūṁkāra hūṁkṛtir iti | 

rdo rje drag po dga' ba che/ /rdo rje hUM ste hUM zhes sgrogs/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra vajracaṇḍa ○ iti | śrīvajraguhyālaṅkāre tantre | vajrasya caṇḍo vajracaṇḍaś caṇḍo vega ucyate śrīghragama[$4]natvāt || mahāmoda iti | śrīguhyamaṇitilake | ○ mahāś cāsau modaś ca mahāmodaḥ || vajrahūṁkāra hūṁkṛtir iti | śrītatvasaṅgrahe | 
vajrahūṁkāra[$5]<kāra>sya hūṁkṛtayaś catvāro hūṁkārām tavidyante yasyāsau ○ vajrahūṁkārahūṁkṛtiḥ || 

de la rdo rje drag po ni dpal rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyan gyi rgyud las gsungs so/ /[f. 68r]@#/ /rdo rje drag po ni rdo rje drag po ste/ drag po ni shugs chen zhes gsungs te/ mthu myur par 'gro ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /dga' ba chen po ni dpal nor bu gsang ba'i thig le'i rgyud las so/ /dga' ba yang de yin la che ba yang de nyid yin pas dga' ba che zhes pa'o/ /rdo rje hUM ste hUM zhes sgrogs/ /zhes pa ni dpal de nyid 'dus pa'i rgyud las te/ rdo rje hUM hUM zhes sgrogs pa ni hUM bzhi sgrogs pa ste/ de rnams dang gang ldan pa de ni/ rdo rje hUM ste hUM zhes sgrogs pa'o/ /


[vajrabāṇāyudhadharo vajrakhaḍgo nikṛntanaḥ |
viśvavajradharo vajrī ekavajrī raṇaṃjahaḥ || 72 ||]
[rdo rje mda' yi mtshon 'chang ba/ /
rdo rje ral gris gcod mdzad pa/ /
rdo rje kun 'chang rdo rje can/ /
rdo rje gcig pu g.yul sel ba/ /]


vajrabāṇāyudhadharo vajrakhaḍgo nikṛntana iti |

mtshon du rdo rje mda' thogs pa/ /rdo rje ral gris ma lus gcod/ /ces pa ni/ 

tatravajrabāṇāyudha[$6]dhara iti | śrīmahāsamayatantre vajrāṅkitam bāṇan vanuś ca tadevāyudhaṃ tad dhārayatīti vajrabāṇāyudhadharaḥ | vajrakhaḍga iti | atramāyājāle | vajraś ca khaḍgaś ca [f. 58r - img. 98] tāv evāyudhaṃ yasya sa vajrakhaḍgaḥ | ni((kṣya))ntana tatraiva || 

de la mtshon du rdo rje mda' thogs pa ni dpal dam tshig chen po'i rgyud las te/ rdo rjes mtshon pa'i mda' dang gzhu de dag nyid mtshon cha ste/ de 'dzin pas na mtshon du rdo rje mda' thogs pa'o/ /rdo rje ral gri ni dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud las te/ rdo rje dang ral gri ni rdo rje ral gri'o/ /mtshon cha de gnyis dang 
gang ldan pa de rdo rje ral gri'o/ /ma lus gcod pa'ang de nyid la bya'o/ /


viśvavajradharo vajrī ekavajrī raṇañjaha iti || 

rdo rje kun 'chang rdo rje can/ /rdo rje gcig pu g.yul sel ba/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra (vi)(pc - written above line)śvavajradhara iti | śrīmahāvairocanābhisambodhi[$2]tantre viśvavajrañ caturmukhaṃ | taddhārayatīti viśvavajradha○raḥ || 

de la sna tshogs rdo rje 'chang ni dpal rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud las te/ sna tshogs rdo rje ni rdo rje rgya gram ste/ /de 'dzin pas na sna tshogs rdo rje 'chang ngo*/ /


vajrīti tatraiva | vajram iva vajraṁ jñānaṃ | abhedyatvād ekavajrīti | śrī advayasamatāvija[$3]ye | 

rdo rje can ni rgyud de nyid las so/ /de nyid rdo rje dang 'dra bas rdo rje ni ye shes te/ mi phyed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ekaś cāsau vajrī ca ekavajrī advayajñānasvabhāva○tvāt 

rdo rje gcig pu ni dpal gnyis su med pa mnyam pa nyid rnam par rgyal pa'i rgyud las so/ /rdo rje yang de yin la gcig pu yang de nyid yin pas rdo rje gcig pu ste/ gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


raṇañjaha iti śrītrailokyavijaye | raṇaṃ saṃgrāma klesaiḥ saha yudhaṃ taṃ jahātīti [$4]raṇaṃjahaḥ || 

g.yul sel ba ni dpal khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las te/ g.yul ni 'thab pa ste/ nyon mongs pa rnams dang lhan cig 'thab pa'o/ /de 'joms pas na g.yul sel ba'o/ /


[vajrajvālākarālākṣo vajrajvālāśiroruhaḥ |
vajrāveśo mahāveśaḥ śatākṣo vajralocanaḥ || 73 ||]
[rdo rje 'bar ba gtsigs pa'i mig /
mgo skyes rdo rje 'bar ba ste/ /
rdo rje 'bebs pa 'bebs pa che/ /
mig [5r]brgya pa ste rdo rje'i mig /]


vajrajvālākarālākṣo vajrajvālāśiro○ruha iti || vajrajvālākarālākṣa iti | śrīvajrabhairave | tatra vajrasya jvālā vajrajvālā tadva[$5]d vikarāla akṣiṇī yasya sa vajrajvālākarālākṣaḥ | ○

rdo rje 'bar ba mig mi bzad/ /skra yang rdo rje 'bar ba ste/ /zhes pa ni dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi rgyud las te/ de la rdo rje 'bar ba ni rdo rje 'bar ba'o/ /de dang 'dra ba'i mi bzad pa'i mig dang gang ldan pa de/ rdo rje 'bar ba mig mi bzad/ /ces pa'o/ /


vajrajvālāśiroruha iti | śirasi rohantīti śiroruhāḥ kacāḥ || vajrajvālāvac chi[$6]roruhā yasyāsau vajrajvālāśiroruhaḥ |

skra yang rdo rje 'bar ba ste/ /zhes pa ni mgo [f. 68v]las skyes pas na mgo skyes te skra'o/ /rdo rje 'bar ba dang 'dra ba'i skra gang dang ldan pa de/ skra yang rdo rje 'bar ba ste/ /zhes so/ /


vajraveśo mahāveśaḥ śatākṣo vajralocana iti || śrīvajrapāṇabhiṣekatantre | tatra catvāra ete krodhāḥ paṭhyante [f. 58v - img 99]

rdo rje 'bebs pa 'bebs pa che/ /mig brgya pa ste rdo rje'i mig /ces pa ni dpal phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las khro bo 'di bzhir brjod do/ /


tatra vajrāveśa iti | vajrasyāveśo vajraveśa | jñānādhiṣṭhānam ity arthaḥ sa yasyāsau vajraveśaḥ ||

de la rdo rje 'bebs pa ni rdo rje 'bebs pa ste/ ye shes kyi byin rlabs zhes pa'i don to/ /de dang gang ldan pa de ni rdo rje 'bebs pa'o/ /


mahāveśa iti | sarvabhāvasvabhāvātmakatvāt ||

'bebs pa che ba ni dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /


śatākṣa iti [$2] | śatāny akṣīṇi yasya sa śatākṣaḥ || 

mig brgya pa ni mig brgya dang gang ldan pa de ni mig brgya pa'o/ /


vajralocana iti ○ vajraval locane yasyāsau vajralocanaḥ ||

rdo rje'i mig ni rdo rje dang 'dra ba'i spyan dang gang ldan pa de ni rdo rje mig go/ /


[vajraromāṅkuratanur vajraromaikavigrahaḥ |
vajrakoṭinakhārambho vajrasāraghanacchaviḥ || 74 ||]
[rdo rje'i spu ni myu gu lus/ /
rdo rje'i spu ni lus gcig pu/ /
rdo rje rtse mo sen mos brtsams/ /
rdo rje snying po pags pa mkhregs/ /]

vajraromāṃkuratanur vajraromaikavigraha iti || [$3]

rdo rje'i ba spu myu gu'i lus/ /rdo rje spu ni gcig pu lus/ /zhes pa ni/ 


dvāv imau śrīvajramaṇḍālaṅkāre paṭhyete | vajramayāni ○ romāṇi tair aṅkuritā pulakitā tanur yasya sa vajraromākuratanuḥ ||

de gnyis ni dpal rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las gsungs te/ de la rdo rje'i ba spu myu gu'i lus ni rdo rje dngos po'i ba spu ste/ de rnams kyi myu gur gyur cing phur bur gyur pa'i lus dang gang ldan pa de ni rdo rje ba spu myu gu'i lus so/ /


vajraromaikavigraha [$4] iti | ekaś cāsau vigrahaś ca ekavigrahaḥ | vajraro○mabhir jñānaromabhir eko vigraho yasya sa vajraromaikavigrahaḥ || 

rdo rje spu ni gcig pu lus ni gcig pu yang de yin la lus kyang de nyid yin pas gcig pu lus so/ /rdo rje spu ni gcig pu ye shes kyi spu'o/ /des mtshon pa'i lus gcig pu dang gang ldan pa de rdo rje ba spu ni gcig pu lus so/ /


vajrakoṭinakhārambho [$5] vajrasāraghaṇcchavir iti | śrīvajraśekharatantre dvā○v etau paṭhyate | 

sen mo brtsams pa rdo rje'i rtse/ rdo rje'i snying po pags pa mkhregs/ /zhes pa ni dpal rdo rje rtse mo'i rgyud las de gnyis gsungs te/ 


tatra vajrasya koṭir vajrakoṭiḥ | koṭir agrabhāgas tadvan nakhā vajrakoṭinakhā[$6]ḥ || tair ārambho yasya sa vajrakoṭinakhārambhaḥ ||

de la/ sen mo brtsams pa rdo rje rtse/ /zhes pa la/ rdo rje rtse mo ste rtse mo ni thog ma'i cha yin no/ /de 'dra ba'i sen mo ni rdo rje rtse mo'i sen mo can no/ /de rnams brtsams pa skyes pa de dang gang ldan pa de sen mo brtsams pa rdo rje'i rtse mo'o/ /


vajrasāraghanacchavir iti | vajrasāravat ghanāni vi((ḍhā))havir yasyāsau vajrasāraghanacchaviḥ | 

rdo rje snying po pags pa mkhregs ni rdo rje snying po dang 'dra ba sra zhing mkhregs pa'i pags pa dang gang ldan pa rdo rje snying po pags pa mkhregs so/ /


[vajramālādharaḥ śrīmāṃ vajrābharaṇabhūṣitaḥ |
hāhāṭṭahāsa nirghoṣo vajraghoṣaḥ ṣaḍakṣaraḥ || 75 ||]
[rdo rje phreng thogs dpal dang ldan/ /
rdo rje rgyan gyis brgyan pa ste/ /
gad rgyangs hA hA nges par sgrogs/ /
yi ge drug pa rdo rje'i sgra/ /]


vajramālādhara[f. 59r - missing]

rdo rje phreng thogs dpal dang ldan/ /rdo rje rgyan gyis brgyan pa ste/ /zhes pa ni dpal khro bo rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud las/ ha la'i 'khor lo las 'di gnyis gsungs te/ 'di lta ste/ 
	rdo rje phreng thogs dpal dang ldan/ /
	rdo rje rgyan gyis brgyan pa ste/ /zhes pa'o/ /

rdo rje phreng ba 'dzin pas na rdo rje phreng thogs so/ /

dpal ldan ni de nyid kyi khyad par te/ skal pa phun sum tshogs pa'i phyir ro/ /

rdo rje'i rgyan [f. 69r]@#/ /gyis brgyan pa ste ni rdo rje nyid rgyan yin pas na rdo rje'i rgyan no/ /des brgyan cing bklubs pas na/ rdo rje'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa ste/ /zhes gsungs so/ /

gad rgyangs ha ha sgra bral sgrogs/ /yi ge drug pa rdo rje'i sgra/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la gad rgyangs ha ha zhes pa ni dpal dbung bzangs kyi rgyud las te/ gad rgyangs ni skad gsang mthon por bzhad pa ste/ ha ha zhes byas nas bzhad pa ni gad rgyangs ha ha'o/ /

sgra bral ba ni dpal legs par grub par byed pa'i rgyud las so/ /sgra dang bral ba ni sgra dang bral ba ste/ nang du phyogs pa kho na sgra zhes pa'i don to/ /

yi ge drug pa ni dpal ye shes drug dang dam tshig yi ge bde mchog gi rgyud las te/ yi ge drug pa dang ldan pa de yi ge drug go/ /

rdo rje'i sgra ni dpal stong phrag brgya pa de nyid 'dus pa'i rgyud las so/ /rdo rje thog gi sgra lta bu'i sgra dang gang ldan pa de rdo rje'i sgra'o/ /

'jam dbyangs chen po sgra che ba/ 'jig rten gsum na sgra gcig pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la 'jam dbyangs ni 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi rgyud las te/ 'jam zhing mnyen pa'i dbyangs dang gang ldan pa de 'jam dbyangs so/ /de nyid kyi phyir na chen po zhes gsungs so/ /

sgra che ba zhes pa ni dpal mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan gyi rgyud las gsungs te sgra yang de yin la che ba yang de nyid yin pas sgra che'o/ /

'jig rten gsum na sgra gcig pa ni khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyud nyid las so/ /'jig rten gsum ni sa 'og dang sa bla dang sa stengs so/ /de la gcig pu gnyis su med pa'i sgra grag pa dang gang ldan pa de ni 'jig rten gsum na sgra gcig pa'o/ /

nam mkha'i mtha' klas sgra sgrogs pa/ /zhes pa ni 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi rgyud de nyid las te/ gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das shrkya thub pas gshin rje gshed la bka' stsal te/ sems can thams cad kyi don du stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i steng du sngags kyi tshul 'jam dpal gyis bstan pa de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed des ri rab ri'i rtse mo de nyid la gnas te/ sgra chen po gcig kho na bsgrags par gyur te/ sgra gang gis nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa thos pa'i sgras yang dag par go bar byas te/ de nas gsungs pa/ nam mkha'i mtha' klas sgra sgrogs [f. 69v]pa/ /zhes so/ /

de nyid kyi phyir bcom ldan 'das de sgra dang ldan pa rnams kyi mchog ces pa ste/ sgra de gang la yod pa gang yin pa de ni sgra dang ldan pa rnams te/ sgra dang gang ldan pa de rnams kyi nang na dam pa dang phul du byung ba zhes pa'i don to/ /

[f. 60v - img. 102]
yākṣarā(n)(ms; t em.?) sa eva bhagavān mañjuśrī dveṣacaritasatvaānugrahārthaṃ yogacaryākriyātantroktakrodharūpāṇy ālambya trailokyadamanāya tataś ca svakāyāt samantajvālāgarbha[$2]ḥ sabhṛkuṭībhrubhaṅgaākṣaṃcitalalāṭavikaṭadaṃṣṭrākarālamukhaḥ | vajraṅkuśapāśādivajrajvālāgnipradīptapraha(ra)(pc - written in margin)ṇacyagrakarāḥ anekadhavśtra[$3]laṅkārravicitraveśadharāḥ krodhavigrahā viniḥsṛtya ○ sarvalokadhātuṣu sarvaduṣṭavinayanakṣatvāyunarāgtya vajradhātumahāmaṇḍalasya bahiskṛ[$4] tāya cakre ekasaptabhir nāmamantrākṣarāṇi svajala○varṇṇarūpāṇi bhūtvā yathāparipādy sanniviṣṭāni cintayet | 

de nas da ni 'khor lo gsum pa'i spro ba'i cho ga bstan te/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i yi ge las/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de nyid ni zhe sdang spyod pa'i sems can de nyid rjes su gzung ba'i don du rnal 'byor dang*/ spyod pa dang*/ bya ba'i rgyud rnams las gsungs pa'i khro bo'i gzugs su dmigs nas 'jig rten gsum 'dul ba'i don du de dag kyang rang gi lus las rnam par 'thon pa ni kun du 'bar ba'i snying po can/ smin mtshams kyi khro gnyer gyi rlabs bskyod cing bsnyer ba'i dpral ba dang*/ 'jigs pa'i mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal dang ldan pa rnams rdo rje dang lcags kyu dang zhags pa la sogs pa rdo rje 'bar ba'i me 'bar ba'i phyag mtshan gyis phyag mtshan pa rnam pa du ma'i mdog dang rgyan can cha byad rnam pa sna tshogs pa 'chang ba'i khro bo'i sku rnam par phyung nas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du gdug pa can thams cad gdul bar byas te/ yang slar log nas rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol du dkyil 'khor gnyis pa la mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge bdun cu rtsa gcig rnams rang gi rigs kyi kha dog dang gzugs rnams su gyur te ji lta ba'i rim pas yang dag par gnas par bsam par bya'o/ /


tāni pañcadhā vibha((kta)) buddhahūṁkā[$5]rādyekaikasya jalasya caturdaśacaturdaśanāmantākṣaraya○dānikṛtvā spharaṇasaṃharaṇādikaṃcānuvidhāya pūrvoktakrameṇaikanāmamantraktarapadamā[$6]tmānam adhimucyāryanāmasaṅgītiṃ paṭhet || tāneva guṇagṇānan antaprakārānavīghnābhītyām nāya iti || gāthāś ca pādeena sārddhadaśanāmamantrākṣarāṇy akasapta [f. 60v - img. 102]tiraṅkato pi || 71 || 

de rnams rnam pa lngar bgos te/ sangs rgyas hUM mdzad la sogs pa re re'i rigs la bcu bzhi bcu bzhi'i mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig rnams byas te/ spro ba dang bsdu ba la sogs mthun par mdzad nas/ gong du gsungs pa'i rim pas mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig tu bdag nyid mos pas mtshan yang dag par brjod pa bklag ste/ yon tan gyi tshogs mtha' yas pa'i rnam pa 'thob po zhes man ngag go/ /tshigs bcad 'di ni tshig rkang gcig gis lhag pa'i bcu tham pa'o/ /mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge ni bdun cu rtsa gcig gi mtshan yin no/ /


āryanāmasaṅgītiṭikāyāṃ nāmamantrāvalokinyāṃ ādarśajñānasvabhāvastuter adhikāraḥ saptamaḥ || ||

'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang [f. 70r]@#/ /sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba zhes bya ba las me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin gyis bstod pa'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa ste bdun pa'o// //

***********
*  ch. 8  *
***********
idam idānīṃ pratyavekṣaṇājñā[$2]namukhena bhagavato jñānakāyasya mañjuśrījñānasatvasya ○ stotram ā(ha)(pc; āhā, ac)|| 

da ni so sor kun du rtog ba'i ye shes kyi sgo nas bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi sku 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa'i bstod pa gsungs pa/ 


[tathatābhūtanairātmyaṃ bhūtakoṭir anakṣaraḥ |
śūnyatāvādivṛṣabho gambhīrodāragarjanaḥ || 77 ||]
[yang dag bdag med de bzhin nyid/ /
yang dag mtha' ste yi ge med/ /
stong nyid smra ba'i khyu mchog ste/ /
zab cing rgya che'i sgra sgrogs pa/ /]


tathatābhūtanairātmyabhūtakoṭir aṇakṣara iti ||
	% emend to nairātmyaṃ ?
 
yang dag bdag med de bzhin nyid/ /yang dag mtha' ste yi ge med/ /ces pa ni/ 


tathateti (prakṛtyā)(em.; pratyā, ms-c) (grāhakādyavi[$3]veko)(ms-c; emend to *kādiviveko?) jñānājñānavasthatayos tulyarūpatvāt iyam parā bhū○takoṭiḥ | sarvvapramāṇasaṃvādāt || ātmādikalpanāyāś ca ((ebhīrta))bādhitatvat | ata eva mañju[$4]śriyā sarvvatathāgatajñānasatvena skandhādīnām ātmādi○tvenānupalambha eva paraḥ pramāṇatvenopadiṣṭaḥ | 

bhūteti bhūtaṃ satyaṃ tathatāyā avikalpanā[$5]mātratvāt | na caivam āśaṅkanīyam ātmādyabhāvako dharmā○ṇāṃ svabhāvaḥ kiṃ vā phalam iti | yato 'yam eva dharmapudgalādivivekaikalakṣaṇaḥ sarvadha[$6]māṇāṃ pratībhāsavikalpātmānāṃ dhātubhūtaḥ pāramārthiko niścalasvabhāvaḥ balādilakṣaṇānāṃ ca phaladharmāṇāṃ tadhetutvāt tanmārgadharmāṇāṃ ca hetur ddhātus tato [f. 61r - im. 103] nairātmyaṃ dharmadhātur ucyate | 

de la de bzhin nyid ni rang bzhin gyis gzung ba la sogs pa'i rnam pa dang bral ba ste/ shes pa dang shes pa ma yin pa'i gnas skabs gnyis la mnyam pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid ni yang dag pa'i mtha' mchog ste/ tshad ma thams cad kyis mi slu ba'i phyir dang*/ bdag la sogs par rtog pa yang rtogs par gnod pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na 'jam dpal de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' ni phung po la sogs pa'i bdag la sogs par nye bar mi dmigs pa kho nas mchog tu tshad ma nyid kyis nye bar bstan to/ /

yang dag ni bden pa dang*/ de bzhin nyid dang*/ rtogs pa med pa tsam nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'di ltar gal te bdag la sogs pa'i dngos po med na chos rnams kyi rang bzhin ni ci yin/ 'bras bu ni gang yin zhes the tshom za bar bya ba ma yin te/ ci'i phyir zhe na/ 'di kho na chos dang gang zag la sogs pa nyid kyis rnam par dben pa'i mtshan nyid gcig pa dang*/ rnam par rtog pa can gyi bdag gis so sor snang ba'i chos thams cad kyi khams su gyur pa don dam pa can gyi g.yo ba'i rang bzhin no/ /
'bras bu'i chos stobs la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid rnams kyi'ang rgyu de nyid yin pa'i phyir ro/ /de'i lam gyi chos rnams kyang rgyu dang khams te/ 
de'i phyir na bdag med pa ni chos kyi dbyings zhes gsungs so/ /


yasmād etāni ca tathatādīny ādarśajñānādīnāṃ dharmāṇāṃ kāraṇamukhāni yatas tathatākāraṇamukhena sarvadharmāṇāṃ svarūpam avatarati | tataś ca ba[$2]laprabhāvitam ādarśajñānaṃ bhūtakoṭir ity ucyate || tadadhi○gamotkarṣāt | ata evaitāni catvāry ādarśasamatāpratyavekṣaṇākṛtyānuṣṭhānajñānalakṣaṇā[$3]ni yasyāsau bhagavān mañjuśrīs tathatābhūtanairātmyabhūta○koṭir ity ucyate || 

gang gi phyir de bzhin nyid la sogs pa 'di dag rnams ni me long lta bu'i ye shes chos rnams kyi sgo ste| gang gi phyir de bzhin nyid kyi byed pa'i sgo nas chos thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid la 'jug cing*/ de yang stobs rnams rab tu byung bas me long lta bu'i ye shes ni yang dag mtha' ste zhes gsungs te/ de rtogs pa'i phul du byung ba'i phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na de rnams bzhi ni me long lta bu'i ye [f. 70v]shes dang*/ mnyam pa nyid dang*/ so sor kun du rtog pa dang*/ bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi mtshan nyid bzhi po 'di rnams gang dang ldan pa'i bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de ni/ yang dag bdag med de bzhin nyid/ /yang dag mtha' ste zhes gsungs so/ /


anakṣara iti | aparaparyāyeṇa na kṣaratīty anakṣaro darmadhātusvabhā[$4]vatvāt || 

yi ge med ni rnams grangs gzhan gyis 'gyur ba med pas na mi 'gyur ba ste/ chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


śūnyatāvādivṛṣabho gambhīrodāragarjana i○ti ||

stong nyid smra ba'i khyu mchog ste/ /zab cing rgya che'i sgra sgrog pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra śūnyatāvādivṛṣabha iti | trividhā śūnyatā | abhāvaśūnyatā | atadbhāvaśūnyatā [$5] | prakṛtiśūnyateti || tatra abhāvaśūnyatā parikalpi○talakṣaṇaṃ na kenacid ākāreṇāstīty abhāvaśūnyatā | atadbhāvaśūnyatā paratantralakṣaṇaṃ [$6] tathānāsti yathā parikalpyate | na tu sarvvathā nāstīti tasyā tadbhāvaśūnyatā | pariniṣpannalakṣaṇaṃ śūnyatā svabhāvam eveti | prakṛtir eva sā śūnyateti | ata[f.61v - img. 104]ś ca trividhāṃ śūnyatāṃ vadituṃ śīlaṃ yasāsau śūnyatāvādī vṛṣabhaḥ pradhāna ity arthaḥ | sarva((dhaura<va>))yatvāt śūnyatāvādī cāsau vṛṣaś ca śūnyatāvādivṛṣabhaḥ || 

de la stong pa nyid smra ba'i khyu mchog ni stong pa nyid rnam pa gsum ste/ dngos po med pa stong pa nyid dang*/ de'i dngos po ma yin pa'i ngo bo nyid dang*/ rang bzhin stong pa nyid do/ /de la dngos po med pa stong pa nyid ni kun brtags kyi mtshan nyid do/ /rnam pa gang zhig gis kyang yod pa ma yin pas na dngos po med pa stong pa nyid do/ /de'i dngos po med pa'i phyir stong pa nyid ni gzhan dbang gi mtshan nyid de/ ji ltar brtags pa bzhin du de ltar med de/ de thams cad du yang med pa ma yin pas na de'i dngos po ma yin pa stong pa nyid do/ /rang bzhin stong pa nyid ni yongs su grub pa'i mtshan nyid de/ stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin yin pas na de'i rang bzhin stong pa nyid do/ /de'i phyir na stong pa nyid rnam pa gsum smra ba'i tshul gang dang ldan pa de stong pa nyid smra ba'o/ /khyu mchog ni gtso bo zhes pa'i don to/ /thams cad kyis gces par 'dzin pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /stong pa nyid smra ba'ang de yin la khyu mchog kyang de nyid yin pas stong pa nyid smra ba'i khyu mchog go/ /


gambhīro[$2]dāragarjjana iti gambhīro nānānirmāṇānugatena sa○mantasphuraṇatviṣā samantabhadrasvabhāvabuddhavigraheṇa satvārthakriyāni ((cyodanañca)) gambhīraṃ pu[$3]naḥ grāhyagrāhakatvāvikalpavirahaḥ prajñāsvabhāva udā○raḥ upāyam api svacittaikalakṣaṇavyāvṛtti bhedāt bhedena vyavasthāpyate yatas tasmād ābhyāṃ [$4]gambhīrodārābhyāṃ garjjanaṃ sarvatīrthakādyabhibhavanaṃ ya○syāsau (sa)(pc - written in margin) tathocyate || 

zab cing rgya che ba'i sgra sgrogs pa ni zab cing ni gzung 'dzin la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba shes rab kyi rang bzhin no/ /rgya che ba ni sprul pa sna tshogs pa'i rjes su 'brang bas 'od kun du spro ba ste/ kun du bzang po'i ngo bo nyid sangs rgyas kyi skus sems can gyi don gyi bya ba byed pa'o/ /gang gi phyir rgya che ba'i thabs kyang rang gi sems su mtshan nyid gcig mod kyi/ ldog pa'i bye brag gis tha dad par rnam par gzhag ste/ de'i phyir na thab cing rgya che ba gnyis kyi sgra sgrogs pas mu stegs pa la sogs pa thams cad kyi lta ba zil gyis gnon par byed pa dang gang ldan pa de ni de ltar gsungs so/ /


[dharmaśaṅkho mahāśabdo dharmagaṇḍī mahāraṇaḥ |
apratiṣṭhitanirvāṇo daśadigdharmadundubhiḥ || 78 ||]
[chos kyi dung ste sgra chen po/ /
chos kyi gaN+DI sgra bo che/ /
rab tu mi gnas mya ngan 'das/ /
phyogs bcu chos kyi rnga bo che/ /]


dharmaśaṅkho mahāśabdo dharmagaṇḍī mahāraṇa iti ||

chos kyi dung ste sgra chen ldan/ /chos kyi ga N+DI sgra bo che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra dharmaśaṃkha i[$5]ti | yadā tuṣitebhyo devanikāyebhyo jambhūdvīpam avata○rttukāmas tadā bhagavān sarvvatathāgatajñānasatvo (dha)(pc - written in margin)rmaśaṅkham āpuryāvtīrṇṇavān | tato sau bhaga[$6]vān dharmaśaṃkha iti || 

de ltar chos kyi dung ni gang gi tshe lha'i [f. 71r]@#/ /rigs dga' ldan nas 'dzam bu'i gling du 'bab par 'dod pa de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' chos kyi dung bus nas babs pa yin no/ /de'i phyir bcom ldan 'das 'di ni chos kyi dung zhes so/ /


punar api kim viśiṣṭo sāv ity āha || mahāśabda iti || trisāhasramahāsāhasralokadhātuśrāvaṇatvāt || 

gzhan yang khyad par ci 'dra zhe na/ gsungs pa/ sgra chen ldan zhes pa ste/ stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams kun dang thos pa'i phyir ro/ /


dharmagaṇḍīti caturmāraparājayaṃ [f. 62r - img. 105] kṛtvā kṣayānutpādajñānaṃ sākṣātkṛtya tataś ca dharmatāyā duravabodhatām dhigamya ya(dā)(pc - written in margin)ha bhagavān—duradhigamo mayā dharmo 'dhigato 'prakā((sye<ḥ>)) sarvasatvānāṃ duradhigamatvāt alpecchā[$2]vihārīvabhūva | tadā mahābrahmāgatyādhyeṣitavān santi bha○gavan satvās tīkṣṇendriyāḥ [possibly some kind of mark near the top of the line] upacitakuśalā uḍghaṭitajñāḥ śraddhavantaś ca tas(mod)(ms-a; sic for mād?) deśayantu bhagavān i[$3]ti | tadā bhagavān dharmacakram upasaṃkramya dharmaśravaṇārthaṅ gaṇḍī○śabdaṃ dattavān iti ata āha | dharmagaṇīti |  

chos kyi gaN+DI ni bdud bzhi las mchog tu rgyal bar byas nas zad pa dang mi skye ba'i ye shes mngon du byas te/ chos nyid de yang shes dka' bar rig nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa/ rig par dka' ba bdag gis chos rigs pa'i sems can thams cad la mi bstan te/ rig par dka' ba de nyid kyi phyir na thugs khral chung bar gnas par gyur to/ /de'i tshe tshangs pa chen po 'ongs nas bskul bcom ldan 'das sems can rnams dbang po rno ba dge ba'i rtsa ba nye bar bsags pa mgo smos pas go ba dang dad pa dang ldan pa rnams kyang yod do/ /de'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyis bshad du gsol/ /de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das chos kyi 'khor lor nye bar zhugs nas chos bsgrags pa'i don du gaN+DI sgra bsgrags par gyur ba de'i phyir gsungs pa/ chos kyi gaN+DI zhes so/ /


(puna)(ms-c; punar em.) tasyaiva viśeṣaṇam āha || mahāraṇa iti ma[$4]hāś cāsau raṇaś ca mahāraṇaḥ | tataś ca tad uktaṃ bhavati | dharma○śaṅkhasvabhāvena sa eva bhagavān draṣṭavyaḥ || 

de nyid kyi phyir yang khyad par gsungs pa/ sgra po zhes te/ chen po yang de yin la sgra yang de nyid yin la sgra yang de nyid yin pas sgra bo che'o/ /des ni yang 'di skad gsungs par gyur te/ chos kyi dung la sogs pa'i rang bzhin de nyid bcom ldan 'das su shes par bya'o/ /


apratiṣṭhitanirvāṇo daśadigdharmadundubhir iti || [$5]

mi gnas mya ngan 'das pa po/ /phyogs bcur chos kyi rda bo che/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatrāpratiṣṭhitanirvāṇa iti | bhavaḥ saṃsāraḥ sarvathā ○ saṃtānavicchedo nirvāṇaṃ śrāvakanirvāṇavat || tayor apratiṣṭhitaṃ ubhayatā((dhya))navasthānāt | 
	na bhave doṣadarśitvāt kṛpālutvān (na)(em.; deest in ms-c) nirvṛtau | 
	sthiitā[f. 62v - img 106]s tiṣṭhanti ca bhave parārthodayadīkṣitā iti | 
	[Madhyamakahṛdayakārikā, 1.20]
anenāprātaṣṭitanirvāṇam uktan tac ca bhavanirvāṇayor vibhāgakalpanābhāvāt | śūnyataikarasayor dvayor apy abhedopala((bdheḥ)) ta[$2]thā coktaṃ |
	saṃsāranirvṛtau jñānaṃ samyagutpadyate yadā |
	saṃ○sāra evaṃ nirvāṇaṃ bhedā tasya bha <ga>vatyata iti || 
	% Either Tib. or Skt has some problems around here. 
evaṃbhūto sau bhagavān mañjuśrīr apratiṣṭhita[$3]nirvāṇa ucyate || 

de la mi gnas mya ngan 'das pa po ni srid pa'i 'khor ba dang*/ rnam pa thams cad du rgyun chad med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa ltar de dag la mi gnas pas gnyis la gnas pa yang ma yin pa'i phyir ro/ /srid pa la mi gnas te srid pa'i skyon gyis mgos pa'i phyir ro/ /mya ngan las 'das pa yang ma yin te/ snying rjes gzhan dbang nyid kyis 'khor ba ji srid bar du cher gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	nyes pa mthong ba srid la min/ /
	snying rjes mya ngan 'das la min/ /
	gzhan gyi don 'byung mthong bas na/
	[f. 71v]srid par zhugs shing mi bzhugs pa'o/ /
zhes so/ /des na mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das par gsungs so/ /srid ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa de dag tu dbye bar rtog pa med pa'i phyir stong pa nyid du ro gcig pa gnyi gar yang dbyer med pa'i dmigs pa ste/ de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	'khor ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i/ 
	gang tshe yang dag ye shes skyes/ /
	'khor nyid mya ngan 'das pa ni/
	de tshe 'di yi 'dir 'gyur ro/ /
zhes so/ /de 'dra ba'i bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal 'di ni mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa zhes gsungs so/ /

daśadigdharmadundubhir iti | dharmāṇā○n dundunbhayo dharmadundubhayaḥ | daśasu dikṣu dharmadundubhayo yasyāsau sa tathā || 

phyogs bcur chos kyi rnga bo ni chos kyi rnga bo che ste/ phyogs bcud chos kyi rnga bo che bsgrags pa dang ldan pa de ni de ltar ro/ /



[arūpo rūpavān agryo nānārūpo manomayaḥ |
sarvarūpāvabhāsaśrīr aśeṣapratibimbadhṛk || 79 ||]

[gzugs med gzugs ldan dam pa ste/ /
sna tshogs gzugs can yid rang bzhin/ /
gzugs rnams thams cad snang ba'i dpal/ /
gzugs brnyan ma lus 'chang ba po/ /]


arūpo rūpavān agryo [$4] nānārūpo manomaya iti ||

gzugs med gzugs ldan dam pa ste/ sna tshogs gzugs can yid las skyes/ /zhes pa ste/ 


tatrārūpa iti | dharmakāyasvabhāvatvād rūpavān iti sāmbhogikakāyasvabhāvatvād agro dharmadhātuniṣyandatvān nānārū[$5]pa iti nirmāṇakāyātmakatvāt manomaya iti | ○ traya ete kāyā jñānātmakatvāt manomaya iti | ata eva te rūpādayo dharmā bhagavataḥ sa[$6]rvatathāgatajñānakāyasya veditavyāḥ | tatsvabhāvatvād bhagavato mañjuśriya iti ||

de la gzugs med ni chos kyi sku'i rang bzhin nyid yin pa'i phyir ro/ /gzugs ldan ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i rang bzhin nyid yin pa'i phyir ro/ /dam pa ste chos kyi rgyu mthun pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /sna tshogs gzugs can ni sbrul pa'i sku'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /yid las kyes pa ni de dag gi ye shes kyi bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyis na gzugs kyi lus la sogs pa de rnams kyi chos 'di dag ni bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi skur shes par bya ste/ de'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir na bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /


sarvarūpāvabhāsaśrīr aśeṣapratibimbadhṛg iti ||

gzugs rnams thams cad snang ba'i dpal/ /gzugs brnyan ma lus 'chang ba po/ /zhes pa ni/

 
tatra sarvvarūpāvabhā[f. 63r -- missing for ms-b]

de la gzugs rnams thams cad snang ba'i dpal ni 'gro ba 'dul ba'i rang bzhin gyis so/ /gzugs rnam pa sna tshogs thams cad snang ba'i dpal ni gzugs rnams thams cad du snang ba ste/ gzugs rnams thams cad sngags ba'i dpal de dang gang ldan pa de ni de ltar ro/ /


gzugs brnyan ma lus 'chang ba po ni ma lus pa rnams kyi gzugs brnyan ni gzugs brnyan ma lus pa'o/ /de 'dzin pas na gzugs brnyan ma lus 'dzin pa'o/ /


[apradhṛṣyo maheśākhyas traidhātukamaheśvaraḥ |
samucchritāryamārgastho dharmaketur mahodayaḥ || 80 ||]

[snang ba med cing che bar grags/ /
khams gsum dbang phyug chen po ste/ /
'phags lam shin tu mtho la gnas/ /
chos kyi tog ni cher 'byung ba/ /]


tshugs pa med cing cher grags pa/ /khams gsum dbang phyug chen po ste/ /zhes pa ni/ 


de la tshugs pa med pa ni gzhan rnams kyis zil gyis mi non pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


cher grags pa ni bsod nams kyi tshogs mi [f. 72r]@#/ /zad pa'i tshogs bsags pa'i phyir ro/ /


khams gsum dbang phyug chen po ni 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs med pa ni khams gsum ste/ khams gsum po nyid ni khams gsum pa ste khams gsum der dbang phug chen po ni chen po yang de yin la dbang phyug kyang de yin pas dbang phyug chen po'o/ /

'phags lam shin tu mtho la gnas/ /dar ba chen po chos kyi tog/ /ces pa ni/ 

de la 'phags lam shin tu mtho la gnas pa ni/ yang dag par mtho zhing bstod par gyur pa'i 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad po gang yin pa de ni 'phags lam shin tu mtho ba ste/ de la gnas pa ni 'phags lam shin tu mtho la gnas so/ /

dar ba chen po ni de las 'byung bas na dar ba ste/ chen po yang de yin la dar ba yang de nyid yin pas dar ba chen po ste/ cher 'phel ba zhes pa'i don to/ /

chos kyi tog ni chos rnams kyi tog ste/ chos kyi rgyal mtshan zhes pa'i don to/ /


[trailokyaikakumārāṅgaḥ sthaviro vṛddhaḥ prajāpatiḥ |
dvātriṃśallakṣaṇadharaḥ kāntas trailokyasundaraḥ || 81 ||]

['jig rten gsum po gcig gzhon lus/ /
gnas brtan rgan po skye dgu'i bdag /
sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan 'chang ba/ /
sdug gu 'jig rten gsum na mdzes/ /]

'jig rten gsum na gzhon lus gcig /gnas brtan rgan po skye dgu'i bdag /ces pa ni/ 


de la 'jig rten gsum na gzhon lus gcig ni gong nas gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid ni 'jig rten gsum mo/ /de la gcig su gnyis su med pa kho nar gzhon nu'i lus dang 'dra ba'i sku dang ldan pa de ni 'jig rten gsum na gzhon lus gcig go/ /


gnas brtan ni nyan thos la sogs pa de rnams la de'i chos nye bar bstan pa'i phyir ro/ /

rgan po ni rang sangs rgyas kyi mchog nyid kyi phyir dang*/ de'i chos ston pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

skye dgu'i bdag po ni so so so sor skye bas na skye dgu ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams so/ /de rnams kyi bdag ni skye dgu'i bdag ste/ rje bo ni 'jam dpal nyid do/ /

sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan 'chad pa/ /sdu gu 'jig rten gsum na mdzes/ /zhes pa ni/ 

de la sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan 'chang ba ni phyag dang zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldan pa nyid dang*/ zhabs shin tu gnas pa nyid dang*/ phyag dang zhabs kyi sor mo dra bar 'brel ba nyid dang*/ phyag dang zhabs 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags pa nyid dang*/ bdun ma thob nyid dang*/ sor mo ring ba nyid dang*/ rting ba yangs pa nyid dang*/ sku che [f. 72v] zhing drang ba nyid dang*/ zhabs long bu mi mngon pa nyid dang*/ sku'i sbu gyen du phyogs pa nyid dang*/ phyag ring zhing mdzes pa nyid dang*/ mdoms kyi sba ba sbubs su nub pa nyid dang*/ mdog gser dang 'dra ba nyid dang*/ bags pa srab ba nyid dang*/ sbu re re nas g.yas su 'khyil ba nyid dang*/ zhal mdzod sbus brgyan ba nyid dang*/ ro stod seng ge'i 'dra ba nyid dang*/ dpung mgo shin tu zlum pa nyid dang*/ thal gong rgyas pa nyid dang*/ ro bro ba'i mchog mkhyen pa nyid dang*/ shing n+ya gro d+ha ltar chu zheng gab pa nyid dang*/ dbu gtsug tor dang ldan pa nyid dang*/ ljags ring ba nyid dang*/ tshangs pa'i dbyangs dang ldan pa nyid dang*/ 'gram pa seng ge'i 'dra ba nyid dang*/ tshems dkar ba nyid dang*/ tshems mnyam pa nyid dang*/ tshems thags bzang ba nyid dang*/ tshems bzhi bcu mnga' ba nyid dang*/ spyan mthon mthing dang*/ rdzi ma ba'i lta bu nyid do/ /


etāni dvātriṃśanmahāpuruṣalakṣaṇāni | cakravarttiśrāvakādyasādhāraṇāni | na hi sarvajñātābījaprarohabhūtāni | mahāpuruṣalakṣa[$2]ṇāny anyanaraśarīrakhilakṣetreṣu sambhavanti || tathā co○ktam abhidharmme || 
	deśasthottaptapūrṇṇatvair lakṣaṇātśayo muner iti |
	[Abhidharmakośa 3.97ab]

skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis de rnams 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal bo dang*/ nyan thos la sogs pa dang mi mnyam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i sa bon las byung ba'i khes bu chen po'i mtshan rnams ni 'od 'bar ba dang*/ rdzogs pa dang*/ gsal la gnas par gyur ba yin no/ /de ltar yang chos mngon pa las gsungs pa/ 
	gsal la gnas pa 'phags 'bar ba/ /
	rdzogs pa'i mtshan ni thub chen gyi/ /
zhes so/ /

kānta iti | kamanīyaḥ [$3] sarvasatvair abhilaṣaṇīyatvāt | 
sdu gu ni sdug pa ste/ 'dod par bya ba ste/ sems can thams cad kyis 'dun pa skye ba'i phyir ro/ /


trailokyasundara iti | ○ trailokyaṃ pūrvavat | tasmin sundaro darśanīyaḥ | aśe(ṣa)(pc - written in margin; probably connected here, although unwanted. text should read aseca*)canakavigrahatvāt | tatra āśrayavli[$4]śeṣo rūpāsecanakatayā veditavyaḥ | sa hi bhagavā○na | aṅgapratyaṅgeṣu ciram api dṛśyamāno 'pūrvva iva paśyatāṃ prītyāsecanāt asecanake [$5]rūpeṇty ucyate || 

'jig rten gsum na mdzes pa ni/ /'jig rten gsum ni gong ma bzhin no/ /de la mdzes pa ni blta na sdug pa ste/ blta bas mi ngoms pa'i gzugs can gyi phyir ro/ /de la blta bas mi ngoms pa ni rten gyi khyad par nyid las blta bas mi bra bar shes par bya ste/ bcom ldan 'das kyi yan lag dang nyid lag de ni dus ring du lta na yang sngon ma mthong ba bzhin du mthong la/ dga' bas blta bas mi ngoms pa'o/ /blta bas mi ngoms pa'i gzugs so zhes gsungs so/ /

(adv || [puśpikā] ||)(marginal note to be inserted here?) 

[lokajñānaguṇācāryo lokācāryo viśāradaḥ |
nāthas trātā trilokāptaḥ śaraṇaṃ tāyī niruttaraḥ || 82 ||]

[slob dpon 'jig rten yon tan shes/ /
'jig rten slob dpon 'jigs pa med/ /
mgon skyob 'jig rten gsum khyab pa/ /
skyabs dang skyob pa bla na med/ /]


lokajñānaguṇācāryo lokācā○ryo viśārada iti ||

'jig rten shes legs slob dpon te/ /'jig rten slob dpon 'jig pa med/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra lokajñānaguṇācārya iti | jñānaṃ guṇāś ca jñānaguṇā lokā[$6]nāṃ jñānaguṇās teṣvācāryo lokajñānaguṇācāryo bhagavān ||

de la 'jig rten shes legs slob dpon ni shes pa dang*/ legs pa rnams ni shes [f. 73r]@#/ /legs so/ /'jig rten rnams kyi shes legs ni 'jig rten shes legs te/ de rnams kyi slob dpon ni bcom ldan 'das zhes so/ /


lokācārya iti | lokasyeti devamanuṣyāder yathābhavyatayā satmārgopadeśal lokācārya i[f. 64v - img. 109]tucyate | 

'jig rten slob dpon ni lha dang mi la sogs pa rnams la skal ba ji lta ba bzhin du dam pa'i lam nye bar ston pas na 'jig rten 
slob dpon zhes gsungs so/ /


viśārada iti | nānāniryāṇasandarśaṇamukhenāśeṣajagadartha(ka)(pc; kā ac)raṇatvāt || viśārada iti nirbhaya ity arthaḥ || 

'jigs pa med pa ni sprul pa sna tshogs kyi gzugs bstan pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don ma lus pa'i phyir na 'jigs pa med pa ste/ bag tsha ba med pa'i don to/ /


nāthas trātā trilokāptaḥ śaraṇan tāyī ni[$2]ruttara iti |

mgon skyob 'jig rten yid gcugs pa/ /skyabs dang skyob ba bla na med/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra nātha iti | anāthānāṃ saṃsārārṇṇa○vanimagnānāṃ satvānāṃ nāthabhūtatvāt ||

de la mgon ni mgon med pa'i sems can 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor bying ba rnams kyi mgon du gyur ba'i phyir ro/ /


trāteti | rakṣitā trāṇārthināṃ trāṇarupatvāt || 

skyabs ni skyabs 'dod pa rnams skyob pa'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


trilo[$3]kāpta iti | trilokasyāptaḥ trilokāptaḥ | sarvākāre○ṇa mahāśūnyatā prakāśakatvenāśeṣakudṛṣṭigahanagatinirghātanatvāt | (??kvacana)(pc - marginal note)||

'jig rten gsum gyi yid gcugs pa ni/ /'jig rten yid gcugs pa ste/ rnam pa thams cad du stong pa nyid chen po rab tu bstan pa nyid kyis lta ba ngan pa'i thibs po'i 'gro ba ma lus pa 'joms pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


śaraṇam iti [$4] | śaraṇārthināṃ śaraṇyatvā..

skyabs ni skyabs 'dod pa'i sems can rnams kyi skyabs nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

(t tā)(pc - marginal note)yīti | tathāgatavaṃśasyānu○pacchadakatvāt || 
skyob pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung rgyun mi 'chad pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

niruttara iti | sarvatathāgatānuttarajñānalābhāt || 

bla na med pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bla na med pa'i ye shes thob pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[gaganābhogasaṃbhogaḥ sarvajñajñānasāgaraḥ |
avidyāṇḍakośasaṃbhettā bhavapañjaradāraṇaḥ || 83 ||]

[nam mkha' khyab par longs spyod pa/ /
thams cad mkhyen pa ye shes mtsho/ /
ma rig sgo nga'i sbubs 'byed pa/ /
srid pa'i dra ba 'joms pa po/ /]


gaganābhogasam[$5]bhogaḥ sarvajñajñānasāgara iti || 

nam mkha'i longs spyod yang dag spyod/ /thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mtsho/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra gaganābhoga ○ iti | gaganasya samatājñānasyābhuṃjanamābhogaḥ sauṣṭhavajñānasamarthyaṃ samyak bhogaḥ sambhogaḥ | gaganābhogasya sambhogaḥ | gaganābhogasambhogaḥ | traidhātukadharmarājābhiṣekapradānatvāt ||	

de la nam mkha'i longs spyod yang dag spyod ni nam mkha' dang mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rjes su longs spyod pa ni legs par gnas pa'i ye shes kyi mthu'o/ /yang dag par longs spyod pa ni yang dag par longs spyod de/ nam mkha'i longs spyod yang dag spyod do/ /nam mkha'i longs spyod yang dag spyod ni khams gsum gyi chos kyi rgyal srid la dbang sgyur ba'i gtso bo'i phyir ro/ /


sarvajñajñānasāgara iti | (sarvaṃ)(em; sarva, ms-c) jānātīti sarvajñaḥ [f. 65r - img. 110] | (tasya)(em.; tasyā, ms-c) jñānaṃ sarvajñajñānaṃ | kṣayānutpādajñānaṃ tasya sāgaraḥ | ativistīrṇṇatvāt | 

thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mtsho ni thams cad mkhyen pas na thams cad mkhyen pa ste/ /de'i ye shes ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes te/ zad pa dang*/ mi skye ba shes pa'i ye shes so/ /de nyid mtsho ste shin tu rgya che ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


avidyāṇḍakośasambhettā bhavapaṃjaradāra(ṇa)(pc - marginal) iti 

ma rig sgo nga'i sbubs 'byed pa/ /srid pa'i dra ba 'joms pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra avidyā karmaphalasatyaratneṣu mo[$2]ho sāv aṇḍaḥ | tad eva pratītyasamutpādasyādibhūtatvāt ja○gadutpattikāraṇatvāc ca | aṇḍakośa ity ucyate | tasya bhetṛ bhedanaśīlaḥ | vidāraṇasvabhāvatvā[$2]t ||

de la ma rig pa ni las dang 'bras bu bden [f. 73v]pa dang dkon mchog rnams mi shes pa'i bdag nyid kyi gti mug ste/ de nyid rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i dang po nyid kyi phyir dang*/ 'gro ba 'byung ba'i rgyud nyid kyi phyir na ma rig sgo nga'i sbubs zhes gsungs so/ /de 'byed pa ni 'joms pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa ste/ 'dral ba'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ata eva bhavapañjaradāraṇa iti | bhavaḥ pañcopā○dānaskandhāḥ sa eva pañjaraḥ | anirgamasthānīyatvāt | tasya vidāraṇaḥ | bhūtārthabhāvanāpra[$4]karṣaparyaṃtagamanāt || 

de nyid kyi phyir na/ srid pa'i dra ba 'joms pa po/ /zhes pa ste/ srid pa ni nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga'o/ /de nyid dra ba ste mi thar ba'i gnas nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de 'joms pa ni yang dag pa'i don bsgoms pas mchog tu yongs su mthar phyin pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[śamitāśeṣasaṃkleśaḥ saṃsārārṇavapāragaḥ |
jñānābhiṣekamakuṭaḥ samyaksaṃbuddhabhūṣaṇaḥ || 84 ||]

[nyon mongs ma lus zhi byed pa/ /
'khor ba'i rgya mtsho'i pha rol son/ /
ye shes dbang bskur cod pan can/ /
yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgyan/ /]

samitāśeṣasaṃkleśaḥ saṃsā○rārṇṇavapāraga iti ||

nyon mongs lus zhi byed pa/ /'khor ba'i rgya mtsho'i pha rol phyin/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra samitāśeṣasaṃkleśa iti || tridhā saṃkleśā iti || kleśasaṃkleśaḥ [$5] | karmasaṃkleśaḥ | janmasaṃkleśaś ca | tatra kleśasaṃkleśaḥ | a○vidyātṛṣṇopādānāni | karmasaṅkleśaḥ saṃskārābhavaś ca | janmasaṃkleśaḥ śeṣāṇy aṅgāni || pu[$6]nar api dvidhā saṃkleśaḥ | hetusaṃkleśaḥ | phalasaṃkleśaś ca tatra hetusaṃkleśaḥ | kleśakarmasvbhāvair aṅgaiḥ ḥ phalasaṃkleśaś ca śeṣair bhūyo pi saptasaṃkleśāḥ saptavidho he[f.65v - img. 111]tuḥ | viparyāsahetur avidyā ākṣepahetuḥ saṃskārā upanayanahetur vijñānaṃ parigrahahetur nnāmarūpaṣaḍāyatane upabhogahatuḥ | sparśavedane ākarṣaṇahetus tṛṣṇāupadā[$2]nabhavāḥ | udvegahetuś ca jātijarāmaraṇe sarvaś caiṣa saṃkle○ṣo 'bhūtaparikalpāt pravartate | sa ca śamitaupaśamite | aśeṣo niḥśeṣaḥ saṃkleśo [$3] yasāsau tathā | 
	% Most of this is quoted from Vasubandhu's Madhyantavibhaṅga commentary.

de la nyon mongs pa ma lus pa ni rnam pa gsum ste/ nyon mongs pa'i kun nas nyon mongs pa dang*/ las kyi kun nas nyon mongs pa dang*/ skye ba'i kun nas nyon mongs pa'o/ /de la nyon mongs pa'i kun nas nyon mongs pa ni ma rig pa dang| sred pa dang*/ len pa'o/ /las kyi kun nas nyon mongs pa ni 'du byed dang*/ srid pa'o/ /skye ba'i kun nas nyon mongs pa ni yan lag lhag ma rnams so/ /yang nas nyon mongs pa ni rnam pa gnyis te/ rgyu'i kun nas nyon mongs pa dang*/ 'bras bu'i kun nas nyon mongs pa'o/ /de la rgyu'i kun nas nyon mongs pa ni nyon mongs pa dang*/ las kyi rang bzhin gyi yan lag rnams so/ /'bras bu'i kun nas nyon mongs pa ni yan lag lhag ma rnams so/ /yang na nyon mongs pa rnam pa bdun ni rgyu rnams pa bdun te/ phyin ci log pa'i rgyu ni ma rig pa'o/ /brag pa med pa'i rgyu ni 'du byed do/ /nye bar sbyor ba'i rgyu ni rnam par shes pa'o/ /yongs su 'dzin pa'i rgyu ni ming dang gzugs dang skye mched drug go/ /nye bar spyod pa'i rgyu ni reg pa dang tshor ba'o/ /'dren pa'i rgyu ni sred pa dang*/ len pa dang*/ srid pa'o/ /yid 'byung ba'i rgyu ni skye ba dang*/ rga shi ste/ nyon mongs pa de dag ni yang dag pa ma yin pa'i kun du rtog pa las byung ba'o/ /ma lus zhi byed ni ma lus mi lus pa'o nyon mongs pa thams cad nye bar zhi ba dang gang ldan pa de ni de ltar ro/ /


yata evaṃ tasmāt saṃsārārṇavapāraga ○ ity ucyate || 

gang gi phyir de lta yin pa de'i phyir/ 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho'i pha rol phyin/ /zhes gsungs so/ /


jñānābhiṣekamakuṭa samyaksambuddhabhūṣaṇa iti ||

ye shes dbang bskur dbu rgyan can/ yang dag [f. 74r]@#/ /rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgyan/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra jñānābhiṣekamakuṭa [$4] iti | ābhiṣekārtham makuṭaḥ | (abhiṣekamakuṭaḥ samantabhadrajñānābhiṣekamakuṭaḥ (sama)(ms-a; deest in Tib) yasyāsau jñānābhiṣekamakuṭaḥ | tataś ca samyaksambuddhabhūṣaṇa iti | tair alaṃkṛtatvāt || 

de la ye shes dbang bskur dbu rgyan can ni dbang bskur ba'i don gyi dbu rgyan ni dbang bskur dbu rgyan can no/ /kun du bzang bo'i ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba'i cod pan de dang gang ldan pa de ni ye shes dbang bskur dbu rgyan can no/ /de yang dbu rgyan ni/ /yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgyan/ /zhes pa ste/ de rnams kyis brgyan pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[triduḥkhaduḥkhaśamanas tryanto 'nantas trimuktigaḥ |
sarvāvaraṇanirmukta ākāśasamatāṃgataḥ || 85 ||]

[sdug bsngal gsum gyi sdug bsngal zhi/ /
gsum mtha' mtha' yas grol gsum pa/ /
sgrib pa thams cad nges par grol/ /
[5v]mkha' ltar mnyam pa nyid la gnas/ /]


tri)(pc - written in margin)duḥkhaduḥkhaśamana○s tryanto nantas tri((muktiga)) iti ||

sdug bsngal gsum gyi sdug bsngal zhi/ /gsum sel mtha' yas grol gsum 'gro/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra tridukhaduḥkhaśamana iti | dva(ndva)(pc - marginal; nda, ac)nirdeśaḥ triduḥkhe[$5]bhi | duḥkhaduḥkhatā upādānaduḥkhatā lakṣaṇaduḥkha○tā ca | dukhasatya((ve))danānimittārthena yat kiñcid veditam idam atra duḥkhasyeti kṛtvā vedanā[$5]nimittaṃ punar vedanāsthānīyā dharmā veditavyāḥ || tathā coktaṃ | duḥkhaṃ saṃsāriṇaḥ skandhā iti |  
	% See Pramāṇavarttika: 
	% duḥkhaṃ saṃsāriṇaḥ skandhāḥ rāgādeḥ pāṭavekṣaṇāt | 
	% abhyāsān na yadṛcchāto'hetor janmavirodhataḥ ||1-149|| 

de la sdug bsngal gsum gyi sdug bsngal zhi ni gnyis bstan te/ sdug bsngal gsum ni sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal dang*/ nye bar len pa'i sdug bsngal dang*/ mtshan gyi sdug bsngal lo/ /sdug bsngal gyi bden pa'i tshor ba rgyu dang bcas pa'i don de/ gang cung zad myong ba de ni 'dir sdug bsngal zhes bya ba'i phyir ro/ /yang tshor ba'i rgyu ni tshor ba'i gnas su 'os ba'i chos rnams rig par bya'o/ /de ltar gsungs pa/ sdug bsngal ni 'khor ba'i phung po rnams so zhes so/ /


dukheti tannimittapratipattitaḥ samudayasatyaṃ duḥkhasa[f. 66 - img. 112]tyanimittāyā pratipattiḥ śamana iti tayoḥ śamanārthena nirodhasatyaṃ | ata āha | triduḥkhaduḥkhaśamano bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | 

sdug bsngal ni de'i rgyu grub kun 'byung gi bden pa ste/ sdug bsngal gyi bden pa'i rgyu ni grub byed gang yin pa'o/ /zhi ba ni de gnyis ni zhi ba'i don gyis na 'gog pa'i bden pa'o/ /de'i phyir gsungs pa/ sdug bsngal gsum gyi sdug bsngal zhi/ /zhes gsungs pa ni/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal zhes so/ /


tryanta iti | (empty space with wavy lines) [$2] trayāṇāṃ satyānām anto mārgasatyaṃ || tataś caturaśītidharma○skandhasahasraṇi mārgasatyam iti vacanāt | tatra satvānāṃ caturaśīticittacaritasahasrapra[$3]tripakṣodayena caturaśītidharmaskandhopade<ga ka>>śāt || 

gsum mtha' ni bden pa gsum gyi mtha' ma yin pas na gsum mtha' zhes bya ste/ lam gyi bden pa'o/ /de yang chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong lam gyi bden pa zhes bya ba'i tshig gi phyir na'o| /de la sems can rnams kyi sems kyi spyod pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por gyur bas chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong nye bar bstan pa ste/ 


a○ta evāha || ananta iti || 

de'i phyir gsungs pa/ mtha' yas zhes so/ /


trimuktiga iti | trisro muktayaḥ śrāvakādibhedena tāṃ muktiṃ gaccha[$3]tīti trimuktigo bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ ||

grol gsum 'gro ni grol gsum ni nyan thos la sogs pas phye ba'i grol bar 'gro bas na grol gsum 'gro ste/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /


sarvāvaraṇani○rmukta ākāśasamatāṅgata iti ||

sgrib pa kun las nges par grol/ /mkha' ltar mnyam pa nyid la gnas/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra sarvāvaraṇānirmukta iti | sarvāṇi ca āvaraṇāni ce[$4]ti sarvāvaraṇāni kleśakarmavipākajñeyasamāyatyāvaraṇa○bhedāt | pañcasarvāvaraṇānit ucyante | tair nimukto bhagavān sarvatathāgatajñānakāyaḥ | 
 

de la sgrib pa kun las nges par grol ni kun yang de yin la sgrib pa yang de yin pas sgrib pa kun te/ nyon mongs pa dang las dang rnams par [f. 74v]smin pa dang shes bya dang nyon mongs par 'jug pa'i sgrib pa rnams phye nas/ lnga po rnams ni sgrib pa kun/ /zhes gsungs so/ /de rnams las rnam par grol ba ni bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku'o/ /


ata e[$5]vāha || ākāśasamatāṅga(te)(ms-c; ta, em.) iti sarvāvaraṇanirmuktatvāt || 

de nyid kyi phyir na gsungs pa/ mkha' ltar mnyam pa nyid la gnas/ /zhes pa ste/ sgrib pa thams cad las nges par grol ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[sarvakleśamalātītas tryadhvānadhvagatiṃgataḥ |
sarvasatvamahānāgo guṇaśekharaśekharaḥ || 86 ||]

[nyon mongs dri ma kun las 'das/ /
dus gsum dus med rtogs par gnas/ /
sems can kun gyi klu chen po/ /
yon tan thod can rnams kyi thod/ /]


sarvakleśamalātītas tryadhvānadhvagatiṅgata iti ||

nyon mongs dri ma kun las 'das/ /dus gsum dus med rtogs pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra sarvakleśamalātita iti | sarvakleśā uktala[$7]kṣaṇās ta eva malās tān atīto (nikrāntaḥ) (niṣkrānta?) sarvakleṣopkleśamalāpagatatvāt | 

de la nyon mongs dri ma kun las 'das ni nyon mongs kun ni gong du bshad pa'i mtshan nyid rnams te/ de rnams nyid dri ma rnams so/ /de dag las 'das pa ni thal ba ste/ nyon mongs pa dang*/ nye ba'i nyon mongs pa'i dri ma thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir ro/ /


(strīdhveti)(ms-c; trīdhveti, em.) | atītānāgatavarttamānasvarūpatvāt tryadhva iti triḥkālarūpatayā ||  
anadhva[f. 66v - img. 113]gatiṅgata iti | nādhvā anadhvā | tataś cātītasyātītatvāt anāgata(syo)(ms-c; syā, em. )samprāptatvāt varttamānasya cobhayabhāvāt sthitir nnāsti ataś ca traikālyāsiddheḥ tasyānadhvano gatir aṇadhvagatiḥ | tāṃ [$2]tryadhvānadhvagatiṃ gataḥ | 

dus gsum ni 'das pa dang*/ ma 'ongs pa dang*/ da ltar gyi rang bzhin gyi phyir na ste/ gsum gyi dus kyis so/ /
dus med rtogs pa po ni dus med pas na dus med pa ste/ de'i phyir na'ang 'das pa ni 'das pa nyid kyi phyir dang*/ ma 'ongs pa ni/ ma thob pa nyid kyi phyir dang*/ da ltar ni gnyis ka med pa'i phyir gnas pa med do/ /de'i phyir na dus gsum mi 'grub ste/ dus de dag med par rtogs pas na dus gsum dus med rtogs pa po'o/


sarvasatvamahānāgo guṇaśekharaśe○khara iti || 

sems can kun gyi klu chen po/ /yon tan thod can rnams kyi thod/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra sarvasatvamahānāga iti | viśiṣṭādhigamadharmalābhān mahānāgaḥ sarvasatvānāṃ mahānā[$3]gaḥ | sarvasatvamahānāgaḥ pradhāna ity arthaḥ | 

de la sems can kun gyi klu chen ni rtogs pa khyad par can gyi chos de rnyed pa'i phyir na klu chen po'o/ /chen po ni sems can kun gyi klu ste/ dpon zhes pa'i don to/ /


ata eva guṇa○śekharaśekhara iti | sakalalaukikalokottarāṇām ābhigāmikānāṃ guṇānāṃ śekharaś cūḍāmaṇir [$4] guṇaśekhara ity ucyate | yathā puṣpāṇāṃ mūrddhnivyavasthitānāṃ ○ loke śekhara iti vyapadeśaḥ | tathā sarvaguṇagaṇānām upary avasthanāt guṇaśekharaśekhara i[$5]ti 

de nyid kyi phyir na/ yon tan thod can rnams kyi thod/ /ces so/ /'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa kun gyi ngon par 'gro bar bya ba la sogs pa yon tan rnams kyi thod de/ gtsug gi nor bu ni/ /yon tan thod can rnams kyi thod/ /ces gsungs so/ /dper na me tog rnams spyi bor bzhag na/ 'jig rten na thod ces grags pa de bzhin du de ltar yon tan gyi tshogs thams cad kyi steng na gnas pa'i phyir na yon tan thod can rnams kyi thod ces so/ /


[sarvopadhivinirmukto vyomavartmani susthitaḥ |
mahācintāmaṇidharaḥ sarvaratnottamo vibhuḥ || 87 ||]

[lhag ma kun las rnam grol ba/ /
nam mkha'i lam la rab gnas pa/ /
yid bzhin nor bu chen po 'chang/ /
khyab bdag rin chen kun gyi mchog/ /]

sarvopadhivinirmukto vyomavarmani susthita iti || ○ 

lus kun las ni rnam grol zhing*/ /nam mkha'i lam la rab gnas pa/ /zhes pa ni/


tatra sarvopadhivinirmukta iti || upadhayaś catvāraḥ | dharmārthakāmanītilakṣaṇāḥ | taiś caturbhir api [$5] dharmair vimuktatvāt sarvopadhivinirmukta iti |

de la lus kun las ni rnam grol ba ni lus ni bzhi ste/ chos dang*/ nor dang*/ [f. 75r]@#/ /'dod pa dang*/ 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid rnams so/ /chos de bzhi rnams las kyang grol ba nyid kyi phyir na lus kun las ni rnam grol ba'o/ /


sarvadharmai○r akaṃpyatvāt nirvikāratvāc ca || vyomavarma(ni)(pc; nī, ac) susthita iti ākāśamārggaprajñāpāramitāyāṃ sū[$6]pratiṣṭhitatvāt || tathā coktaṃ āryāṣṭasāharyāṃ ākāśabhāvaneṣā subhūte yaduta prajñāpāramitā bhāveneti || 

chos thams cad kyis mi 'jigs pa nyid kyi phyir dang*/ mi 'gyur ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /nam mkha'i lam la rab gnas pa ni nam mkha'i lam shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la shin tu gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar yang 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong ba las gsungs pa/ /rab 'byor 'di ltar ste/ nam mkha' bsgom pa rnams par bsgom pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bsgom pa rnam par bsgom pa'o zhes so/ /


mahācintāmaṇidharaḥ sarvaratnottamo vi[f. 67 r - img. 114]bhur iti || 

yid bzhin nor bu chen po 'chang*/ /khab bdag rin chen kun gyi mchog/ /ces pa ni/ 


mahāṃś cāsau cintāmaṇiś ca mahācintāmaṇiḥ | yathā'bhilaṣitārthasiddhisaṃpādakatvāt taddhārayātīti mahācintāmaṇidharaḥ | 

de la yid bzhin nor bu chen po 'chang ni yid bzhin nor bu yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas yid bzhin nor bu chen po ste/ 'di ltar 'dod pa'i don yang dag par grub par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /de 'dzin pas na yid bzhin nor bu chen po 'chang ngo*/ /de nyid kyi phyir/ /


ata eva sarvaratnottama iti | sarvara[$2]tnānāṃ uttamatvāt | 

rin chen kun gyi mchog ces pa ste/ rin po che thams cad kyi nang na mchog tu gyur ba'i phyir ro/ /


vibhur iti gatārthaṃ || 

khyab bdag gi don ni bshad zin to/ /


[mahākalpataruḥ sphīto mahābhadraghaṭottamaḥ |
sarvasatvārthakṛt kartā hitaiṣī satvavatsalaḥ || 88 ||]

[dpag bsam shing chen rgyas pa ste/ /
bum pa bzang po che ba'i mchog/ /
byed pa sems can kun don byed/ /
phan 'dogs sems can mnyes gshin pa/ /]

mahākalpataru sphī○to mahābhadraghaṭottama iti ||

dpag bsam shing chen rgyas pa ste/ bum pa bzang po che ba'i mchog/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra mahākalpatarur iti | mahāṃś cāsau kalpataruś ca mahākalpa[$3]taruḥ | abhimatārthasiddhidāyakatvāt 

de la dpag bsam shing chen rgyas pa ni dpag bsam gyi shing yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas dpag bsam shing chen te/ mngon par 'dod pa'i don gyi dngos grub rab tu sbyin pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ata eva sphītaḥ sa○rvasamṛddhatvāt || 

de nyid kyi phyir na rgyas pa ste/ thams cad yang dag par 'phel ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


bhadraghaṭaś cāsāv uttamaś ca bhadraghaṭottamaḥ mahāś cā[$4]sau tadughaṭottamaś ca mahābhadraghaṭottamaḥ || 

bum pa bzang po che ba'i mchog ni bum pa bzang bo che ba yang de yin la mchog kyang de nyid yin pas bum pa bzang po che ba'i mchog go/ /


sarvasatvārtha○kṛ(ta)(ms-b; t em.) kartā hitaiśī satvavatsala iti ||

byed pa sems can kun don byed/ /phan 'dogs sems can mnyes gshin pa/ /zhes pa ni/


tatra sarvasatvārthakṛd iti | ata etaiś cintāmaṇyādibhiḥ [$5] sarvasatvārthaṅ karotīti sarvasatvārthakṛt mañjuśrīḥ ||

de la sems can kun don byed pa ni yid bzhin gyi nor bu la sogs pa de rnams kyis sems can thams cad kyi don byed pa'i phyir na sems can kun don byed de 'jam dpal lo/ /


ata ○ evoktaṃ candragomipādair jambha(la)(pc - marginal)stotre ||

	bhadraghaṭakalpapādapacintāmaṇayo pya(te)(ms-b; ce, em.)tanāvantaḥ | 
	te pi [$6]sukhayanti satvān kimu bhagavān svīkṛtaḥ kṛpayoti | 
