GLL LGL GG / LLLL GG L GLL G |

de nyid kyi phyir na dge bsnyen tsan+d+ra go mi'i zhabs kyis dzam+b+ha la'i bstod pa gsungs pa/ 

	bum pa bzang bo dang ni dpag bsam shing*/ /
	yid bzhin nor rnams sems dang mi ldan yang*/ /
	des kyang [f. 75v]sems can rnams ni bde 'gyur na/ /
	snying rjes dbang med bcom ldan smos ci dgos/ /

zhes pa ste/ 

satva○vinayavaśāt sthāvaranāmarūpeṇāpi pratibhāsanāt || kartteti yathābhavyatayā dharmopadeśakara[$7]ṇāt || 

sems can 'dul dbang gis mi gyo ba rnams kyi gzugs kyis kyang so sor snang ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /byed pa skal ba ji lta ba dang bsam pa'i dbang nyid kyis chos nye bar ston pa nyid kyi 
phyir ro/ /


hitaiṣīti hitam āyati pathyaṃ | tad eṣituṃ śīlam asyeti hitaiṣī || 

phan 'dogs pa ni phyi mar phan pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de ston pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de phan 'dogs so/ /


satvavatsala iti | jagadekaputraprematvāt || 

sems can mnyes gshin pa ni 'gro ba la bu gcig pa bzhin du byams pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

[śubhāśubhajñaḥ kālajñaḥ samayajñaḥ samayī vibhuḥ |
sattvendriyajño velajño vimuktitrayakovidaḥ || 89 ||]

[bzang ngan shes shing dus shes pa/ /
khyab bdag dam shes dam tshig ldan/ /
dus shes sems can dbang po shes/ /
rnam grol gsum la mkhas pa po/ /]


śubhāśubhajñaḥ kālajñaḥ samayajña samayī vibhur iti ||

bzang ngan shes shing dus shes la/ /khyab bdag dam shes dam tshig /dan/ /zhes pa ni/ 


[ms-c f. 67 - img. 115] tatra śubhāśubhajña iti | śubha ((ce '))śubhañ ca śubhāśubhaṃ | kuśalākuśalam ity arthaḥ | taj jānātīti śubhāśubhajño bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | kvacid aśubham api vetti satvārthavaśāt | tathā coktaṃ || [$2] sadaya((tyā))śubhaṃ nāstīti || 

de la bzang ngan shes shing ni bzang po dang ngan pa ni bzang ngan te/ dge ba dang mi dge ba'i don to/ /de mkhyen pas na bzang ngan shes pa bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /kha cig tu mi dge ba yang shes te/ sems can gyi don gyi dbang gi phyir ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ /
	snying brtser byas na nyes ba mad/ /
ces so/ /


kālajña iti | kālaṃ jānātīti kā○lajñaḥ | ayam avatārakālo yam dharmadeśanākālo yaṃ satvārthakriyākālo yaṃ upekṣakālo 'yaṃ parinirvā[$3]ṇakāla ity evam bhāgīyaḥ samajña iti | 

dus shes pa ni dus mkhyen pas na dus shes pa'o/ /de ni 'jug pa'i dus so/ /'di ni chos bstan pa'i dus so/ /'di ni sems can gyi don bya ba'i dus so/ /'di ni btang snyoms kyi dus so/ /'di ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i dus so zhes de lta bu'i cha dang mthun pa'o/ /


hṛnmudrāmantravidyānāṃ ○ svarūpaṃ jānāti vett(ī)(pc; i ac)ti samayajñaḥ || ata eva samayī || vibhur iti gatārthaṃ || 

khyad bdag gi don ni bshad zin to/ /

dam shes ni snying po dang*/ phyag rgya dang*/ sngags dang*/ rig pa rnams kyi ngo bo nyid shes shing rtogs pas na dam shes so/ /de nyid kyi phyir na dam tshig ldan zhes so/ /


satvendriyajño velajño vimuktitrayakovida iti || tatra 

dus shes sems can dbang don shes/ /rnam grol gsum la mkhas pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra satvendriyajña iti | satvānām i○ndriyāṇi satvendriyāṇi satvasambandhīni mṛdvindryādī((rni)) tāni jānātīti satvendriyajñaḥ |

velajña i[$5]ti | velāṃ jānātīti velajñaḥ | yācakasatvānām abhiprāyaṃ ○ viditvaiva kāle dīyamānasya dānāder akṣayatvāt |

de la dus shes ni dus rnams shes pas dus shes te/ slong ba'i sems can rnams kyi bsam pa shes nas dus su sbyin pa la sogs pa'i sbyin pa ni mi zad pa'i phyir ro/ /

sems can dbang don shes ni sems can rnams kyi dbang po ste/ sems can thams cad dang 'brel ba'i dbang po rtul bo la sogs pa de rnams mkhyen pas na sems can dbang po shes so/ /


vimuktitrayakovida iti | śrāvakādivimukti[$6]traye vibhāgakalpanālakṣaṇe nipuṇanatvāt kovida ity u○cyate || 

rnam grol gsum la mkhas pa po ni nyan thos la sogs pa rnam par grol ba gsum gyi char brtag pa'i mtshan nyid la zhib tu mkhyen pa nyid kyi phyir na mkhas pa po zhes gsungs [f. 76r]@#/ /so/ /


[guṇī guṇajño dharmajñaḥ praśasto maṅgalodayaḥ |
sarvamaṅgalamāṅgalyaḥ kīrtir lakṣmīr yaśaḥ śubhaḥ || 90 ||]

[yon tan ldan zhing yon tan shes/ /
chos shes rab zhi bkra shis 'byung/ /
bkra shis kun gyi bkra shis pa/ /
grags pa dpal mo snyan pa dge/ /]


guṇīguṇajño dharmajñaḥ praśasto maṅgalodaya iti ||

yon tan ldan zhing yon tan shes/ /chos shes bkra shis 'byung*/ /zhes pa ni 
	% Tib missing reflect of praśasta, both in verse here and in commentary.

tatra guṇīti svayaṃ | guṇajño bāhyaśrāva[$7]kādīnāṃ guṇā(na)(pc - marginal) jānātīti guṇajñaḥ || 

de la yon tan ldan zhing ni rang gi'o/ /yon tan shes ni phyi rol pa dang*/ nyan thos pa rnams kyi yon tan mkhyen pas na yon tan shes so/ /


dharmajña iti | laukikalokottaraṃ dharmaṃ jānātīti dharmajñaḥ ||

chos shes ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos rnams mkhyen pas na chos shes so/ /


praśasta iti | asādhāraṇamahāpuruṣādilakṣaṇopetatvāt | 

maṅgalodaya [ms-c f. 68r – im. 116] iti | udety asmād ity udayaḥ | maṅalānāṃ laukikādīnāṃ udayo 'asmād iti | maṅgalodayo bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ ||

bkra shis ni thun mong ma yin pa'i skyes bu chen po la sogs pa'i mtshan dang ldan pa'i phyir ro/ /

bkra shis 'byung ni 'di las 'byung ba ste/ 'jig rten la sogs pa'i bkra shis rnams de las byung bas na bkra shis 'byung ste/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /


sarvvamāṅalyamāṅgalyaḥ kīrttir lakṣmīr yaśaḥ śubha iti 

bkra shis kun gyi bkra shis snyan grags dge/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra sarvamāṅgalya[$2]māṅgalya iti | maṅgale sādhur māṅgalya iti sarvamāṅalyānāṃ ○ sarvapavitratarāṇāṃ madhye māṅgalyaḥ ||

de la bkra shis kun gyi bkra shis pa ni bkra shis kyi nang nas legs pa bkra shis so/ /bkra shis kun te shin tu dga' bar byed pa'i nang nas bkra shis pa'i phyir ro/ /


kīrttir iti || viśvantaraśaśajātakādāv anekādbhutasatvārthaka[$3]raṇāt | adyāpy avinasvarī kīrttir iti tanmūrttattvāt tasya bha○gavataḥ ||

grags pa ni rgyal bu thams cad sgrol dang*/ ri bong gi lus kyis rmad du byung ba du mas sems can gyi don byed pa'i phyir na deng sang yang mi nyams par grags pa zhes ba ni bcom ldan 'das de'i ste/ de'i mi zad pa'i lus yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


lakṣmīr iti | ekāgracittatayā bhāvanābhiyuktānāṃ kulaputrādīnāṃ sarvasampadyodhārabhū[$4]tatvāt lakṣmīr bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ ||
	% Perhaps sarvasampadādhārabhūtatvāt?
bkra shis ni sems rtse gcig tu bsgom pa la brtson pa'i rigs kyi bu la sogs pa rnams kyi phun phum [\[?\] ]tshogs pa thams cad kyi rten du gyur pa nyid kyi phyir na bkra shis te/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /


yaśa iti dānādīnāṃ pra○karṣaparyantagamanāt | sarvadoṣamalābhāc ca nirmalayaśaḥ((puṅkta))tvāt yaśa ucyate | 

snyan grags ni sbyin pa la sogs pa mchog tu yongs su mthar phyir dang*/ dri ma'i skyon thams cad med pa'i phyir dang*/ dri ma med pa'i grags pa'i phung po nyid kyi phyir na yang snyan grags zhes gsungs so/ /


śubha iti [$5] | daśakuśalakarmayathātmakatvāt |

dge zhes pa ni dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam gyi bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[mahotsavo mahāśvāso mahānando mahāratiḥ |
satkāraḥ satkṛtir bhūtiḥ pramodaḥ śrīr yaśaspatiḥ || 91 ||]

[dbugs 'byin chen po dga' ston che/ /
dga' ba chen po rol pa che/ /
bkur sti rim gro phun sum tshogs/ /
rab tu dga' ba grags bdag dpal/ /]


mahotsavo mahāsvā○so mahānando mahāratir iti |

dbugs 'byin chen po dga' ston che/ /dga' chen rol mo chen po ste/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra mahotsava iti mahāś cāsāv utsavaś ca mahotsavaḥ | [$6] yāyāvara ucyate | 
	anusaṃvatsaraṃ śrā(ddhaṃ)(em.; rddhaṃ, ms-c) yaḥ karoti yathāvidhi 
	nityapravṛttayāgaś ca sa yāyāvara ucyate | 
	mokṣaamārgaṃ gatan nityam anye yāyāvaraṃ vidur iti || 
ubhayathā [f. 68v – img 117] .. bhagavān majñuśrīr eva yāyāvaraḥ satatapravṛttadānatvāt ‡nityaco‡mokṣamārgagatatvāt kuśalapakṣaikanimnatayā | mahotsavatvāt || 

mahāsvāsa iti | āśvāsanam āśvāsaḥ mahāṃś cāsāv āsvāsaś ca mahāśvāsaḥ śrīvajrasatvādi○samādhinā rāgādyadhimuktikānāṃ satvānāṃ samāśvāsanāt sa tathā || 

de la dbugs 'byin chen po ni dbugs 'byin pas na dbugs 'byin pa ste/ dbugs 'byin pa yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas dbugs 'byin chen po ste/ dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'dod chags la sogs pa la mos pa'i sems can rnams la yang dag par dbugs 'byin pa'i phyir de skad ces bya'o/ /

dga' ston che [f. 76v] ni dga' ba yang de yin la chen po yang de yin bas dga' ston che ste/ mchod sbyin mchog tu gsungs so/ /
	lo re rjes mthun dad pa yis/ /
	gang zhig cho ga ji bzhin byed/ /
	rtag tu mchod sbyin mchog tu bshad/ /
	gzhan du thar pa'i lam du gshegs/ /
	rtag tu mchod sbyin mchog rig pa'o/ /
zhes te/ rnam pa gnyis ka ltar yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal nyid mchog tu 'gro ba ste/ rtag tu sbyin pa la 'jug pa'i phyir dang*/ rtag tu mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam nyid du gshegs pa'i phyir dang*/ dge ba'i phyogs la gzhol bas na dga' ston che ba'i phyir ro/ /


mahānanda iti | mahāś cā[$3]sāv ānandaś ca mahānandaḥ | sarvalokānāṃ yathābhavyatayānutta○radharmadeśakatvenānandajanakatvāt || 

dga' chen ni dga' ba yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas dga' chen te/ 'jig rten thams cad kyi skal pa ji lta ba bzhin gyi gzugs nyid kyis bla na med pa'i chos ston par byed pas dga' ba skye pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


mahāratir iti | mahatī ratiḥ | prītir aṇāśravalakṣaṇā ya[$4]syāsau mahāratir bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ || 

rol mo chen po ste ni rol mo chen po'i dga' ba zag pa med pa'i mtshan nyid dang gang ldan pa de rol mo chen po ste bcom ldan 'das de'o/ /


satkāraḥ satkṛtir bhū○tiḥ pramodaḥ śrīyasaspatir iti | 

bkur sti rim gro phun sum tshogs/ mchog tu dga' ba grags bdag dpal/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra satkāra iti | traidhātukeṣu sanmānapūjārhatvān |

de la bkur sti ni khams gsum du dam pa'i bkur sti dang mchod par 'os pa'i phyir ro/ /


satkṛti[$5]r iti | karaṇaṃ kṛtiḥ satāṃ kṛtiḥ satkṛti santo hi śṛā○vakādayas teṣāṃ yathārhan pratipattiḥ | tathā coktaṃ |
	satkṛtyādhyāpayati yaḥ sāṅgaṃm vaidaṃ yathāvidhi [$6] |
	vivṛṇoti ca mantrārthaṃ satkṛtiḥ so bhidhīyate || 
bhagavān mañjuśrīś ca satkṛtya paramārthavedasya dvādaśāṅgasya pravacanasyādhyāpanāt sarvamantraṇāñ ca yathāvad vivaraṇāt sa[f. 69r – img. 118]tkṛtir ucyate ||
 
byed pa ni rim gro ste/ rim gro mchog ni nyan thos la sogs pa gang yin pa de rnams kyi mchod pa ji ltar 'os pa grub pas na dam pa ste/ de ltar yang gsungs pa/
	rim gro mchog gi lung dpog dang*/ 
	ji bzhin yan lag bcas par rig /
	sngags don yang ni rnam par dpyad/ /
	rim gro mchog tu de brjod do/ /
zhes so/ /bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal yang mchog byed pa ste/ don dam pa'i rig pa dang*/ gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis kyi lung dpog pa dang*/ sngags thams cad kyi don rnam par dpyod pa'i phyir na yang mchog ces gsungs so/ /


bhūtir iti | sarvavibhūtyādhārarūpatvāt | 

phun sum tshogs pa'i phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyi rten gyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


pramoda iti sarvapraharṣasvabhāvatvāt | 

mchog tu dga' ba ni rab tu dga' ba thams cad kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


śrīyaśaspatir iti śriyo devatyas tāsāṃ yaśāṃsi sukhasaumanasyāni teṣāṃ pa[$2]tiḥ svāmī bhagavān || 

grags bdag dpal zhes pa la/ dpal ni lha mo ste/ de'i grags pa ni bde ba dang yid bde ba rnams so/ /de rnams kyi bdag po ste/ gtso bo ni bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[vareṇyo varadaḥ śreṣṭhaḥ śaraṇyaḥ śaraṇottamaḥ |
mahābhayāriḥ pravaro niḥśeṣabhayanāśanaḥ || 92 ||]

[mchog ldan mchog sbyin gtso bo ste/ /
skyabs kyi dam pa skyabs su 'os/ /
rab mchog 'jigs pa chen po'i dgra/ /
'jigs pa ma lus sel ba po/ /]


vareṇyo varadaḥ (śra)(ms-c; śre, em.)ṣṭhaḥ śaraṇyaḥ śa○raṇottama iti | 

mchog ldan mchog sbyin gtso bo ste/ /skyabs kyi [f. 77r]@#/ /dam pa skyabs su 'os/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra vareṇya iti | sarvābhigamanīyānām agratvāt ||

de la mchog ldan ni mngon par 'gro bar bya ba rnams kyi nang na mchog nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


varada iti | varan dadā[$3]tīti varadaḥ | yathābhiprāyaparipūraṇāt ||

mchog sbyin ni mchog sbyin pas na mchog sbyin te/ bsam pa ji lta ba bzhin du yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


śreṣṭha i○ti bāhyaśrāvakādīnāṃ uttamatvāt | 

gtso bo ste ni phyi rol pa dang nyan thos la sogs pa thams cad kyi nang na mchog tu gyur ba'i phyir ro/ /


śaraṇya iti | hīnānāṃ duḥkhitānām aśaraṇānāṃ śaraṇā[$4]rhatvāt | ata eva śaraṇottama iti | 

skyabs su 'os pa ni dman zhing sdug bsngal ba dang skyabs med pa rnams kyi skyabs su 'os pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na skyabs kyi dam pa'o/ /


mahābhayāriḥ prava○ro niḥśeṣabhayanāśana iti || 

'jigs chen dgra ste rab kyi mchog /'jigs pa ma lus sel ba po/ /zhes ba ni/ 


tatra mahābhayārir iti | daivānyaṣṭhau mahābhayāni vyādhir marakaṃ [$5] durbhikṣo gnir udakaṃ (rakṣaḥ)(ms-c; rakṣāḥ em.) (śalabhā)(ms-c; śalabho em.) mūṣikāś ca teṣām ariḥ ○ vyādhyādinirghātanatayā ity upadravanāśakatvāt || 

de la 'jigs chen dgra ni gnam gyis bskos pa la sogs pa 'jigs pa chen po brgyad de/ nad dang*/ 'chi ba dang*/ mu ge dang*/ me dang*/ chu dang*/ srin po dang*/ chag ba dang*/ byi ba rnams so/ /de rnams kyi dgra ste/ nad la sogs pa nges par 'joms pa nyid kyis yams dang nye bar 'tshe ba rnams zad par byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ata eva pravara ity ucyate | 

de nyid kyi phyir na rab kyi mchog ces gsungs so/ /


niḥśeṣa[$6]bhayanāśana iti | niravaśeṣabhayāny aṣṭau mahābhayāni tāni harikariśikhītyādi | teṣāṃ niḥśeṣāṇāṃ bhayānāṃ nāśakatvāt | niḥśeṣabhayanā[$7].. .. .. gavān mañjuśrīḥ | tadanusmaraṇamātreṇāśeṣabhayanāśanād iti ||

'jigs pa ma lus sel ba po ni lus pa med pa'i 'jigs pa chen po brgyad de/ de dag ni seng ge dang*/ glang po che dang*/ me dang*/ sbrul dang*/ rkun ma dang*/ rgyal po'i chad pa dang*/ mtshon dang*/ lce 'bab pa rnams la sogs pa'o/ /'jigs pa de rnams ma lus par sel bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir na/ 'jigs pa ma lus sel ba po ste/ bcom ldan 'jam dal te/ de rje su dran pa rtsam gyis 'jigs pa ma lus pa zad par byed pa'i phyir ro/


idānīṃ sarvasatvānāṃ jagadvinayasvabhāvena tattadbhaktānāṃ tatta(drūp)(pc-marginal; dru ac) pe<na>ṇāṃ pi bhāsata iti |||

da ni sems can thams cad la 'gro ba 'dul ba'i rang bzhin gyis gang la gus pa rnams la de'i gzugs kyis kyang snang bar byed par bstan pa'i phyir ro/ /


[śikhī śikhaṇḍī jaṭilo jaṭī mauṇḍī kirīṭimān |
pañcānanaḥ pañcaśikhaḥ pañcacīrakaśekharaḥ || 93 ||]

[gtsug phud phud bu ral pa can/ /
ral pa mgo reg cod pan ldan/ /
gdong lnga gtsug phud lnga dang ldan/ /
zur phud lnga dang ldan pa'i thod/ /]


[f. 69v - img. 119] śikhī śikhaṇḍī jaṭilo jaṭī mauṇḍī kirīṭimān iti ||

gtsug phud phud bu lcang lo can/ /ral pa mu ni cod pan thogs/ /zhes pa ste/ 


tatra śikhīti | śikhāsyāstīti śikhī | kvacid bālakāyeṇa pratibhāsata iti |  

de la gtsug phud ni 'di la gtsug phud yod pas na gtsug phud can te/ kha cig tu byis pa'i gzugs su snang ba'o/ /phud pu ne lha gzhon nu'i gzugs so/ /


śikhaṇḍīti | kārttikeyarūpeṇa ||


[$2]jaṭila iti | jaṭā vidyate yasyāsau jaṭilaḥ | jaṭādhara○rūpeṇa |

lcang lo ni lcang lo dang gang ldan pa de lcang lo can te/ ral pa can gyi gzugs kyis so/ /



jaṭīti | ekaśikhārūpeṇa |

ral pa ni thor tshugs gcig pa'i gzugs kyis so/ /



mauṇḍīti muṇḍadhararūpeṇa ||

muny+dza [f. 77v]ni mgo bo 'chang ba'i gzugs kyis so/ /


kirīṭimān iti | kirīti[$3]r mukuṭaḥ sa vidyate yasāsau kirīṭimān ādityādirū○peṇa | yadyadvineyānāṃ satvānāṃ tattatrūpeṇa eteṣāṃ cittasantāneṣu pratibhāsodayāt || tathāco[$4]ktaṃ 

cod pan thogs ni cod pan ni dbu rgyan no/ /de dang gang ldan pa de ni cod pan thogs te ni ma la sogs pa'i gzugs kyis so/ /gang dang gang gis 'dul ba'i gzugs can rnams la de dang de'i gzugs kyis de rnams kyi sems kyi rgyud la so sor snang bar byed pa'i phyir na de ltar gsungs so/ /


pañcānanaḥ pañcaśikhaḥ pañcacīrakaśekhara i○ti ||

gdong lda gtsug phud lnga dang ldan/ /zur phud lnga pa me tog thod/ /ces pa ni 

ayam a((ndra))varddhaś cādibuddha[candra bindu-like mark]sya gurūpadeśenādiyoge draṣṭavyam tatraiva vyākhyātatvāc ca punar i[$5]ha nocyate ||

[mark probably corresponds somewhat with the marginal note, which reads as follows:]
ihaiva māyājālābhisambodhikramokta(sya)(pc; syā ac) mahāvairocana((hṛdga))tasya '

tshig bdun pa'i tshigs su bcad pa phyed pos ni bla ma'i man ngag gis dang po sangs rgyas kyi sbyor ba dang po'i bsgom khog de kho na las shes par bya zhing de yang bshad zin pa nyid kyis phyir na yang 'dir yang ma bshad do/ /


[mahāvratadharo mauñjī brahmacārī vratottamaḥ |
mahātapās taponiṣṭhaḥ snātako gautamo 'graṇīḥ || 94 ||]

[mgo zlum brtul zhugs chen po 'chang/ /
shangs par spyod pa brtul zhugs mchog/ /
dka' thub mthar phyin dka' thub che/ /
khrus ldan go'u ta ma mchog/]


mahāvratadharo mauñjī brahmacārī vratottama ○ iti ||  

brtul zhugs che 'chang mun rdza can/ /tshangs par spyod pa brtul zhugs mchog /ces pa ni/ 


tatra mahāvratadhara iti | kvacit pañcamudrālaṅkārarūpeṇāpi pratibhāsanāt || 

mauñja[$6] iti muñjamekhalāvratadhāraṇarūpeṇa || 

de la mun rdza zhes pa ni rtsa mun dza'i ske rags can gyi brtul zhugs 'dzin pa'i gzugs kyis brtul zhugs chen po pa ni la las phyag rgya lnga'i rgyan dang ldan par so sor snang ba'i phyir ro/ /


brahmacārīti ○ anantakalpabrahmacaryācaraṇāt || vikārahetāv api yasya ceto na vikriyata ity asāveva [$7] bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | brahmacārīrūpēṇa kvacin pratibhāsate || ]

tshangs par spyod pa ni bskal pa mtha' yas par tshangs par spyod pa la cher spyod pa'i phyir rnam par 'gyur ba'i rgyu gang gi pa 'di mi 'gyur ba de nyid kyis na bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal tshangs par spyod pa'i gzugs kyis kha cig tu so sor snang ngo*/ /


vratottama iti alam paryāptam prativedaṃ dvādaśavarṣāṇi brahmacaryañ cartvā gṛhāśramam akṛtveva bhi[f. 70r – img. 120]kṣatvena vānam prasthyabhāvena vā yo janma sakalan nītavān tam alam uṣitabrahmacaryam āhur vratottamañ ca | ata eva vratānāṃ sarveṣām uttamatvāt mañjuśrīr eva yu((jya))te | apari[$2]mitakalpajñānacaryācaraṇāt | 

brtul zhugs mchog ni de yongs su 'os pa ste/ so sor shes pa'i lo bcu gnyis su tshangs par spyod pa la spyad pas so sor nyam su myong ba yongs su mthar thug pas chog gis khyim du ngal so ba ma byas pa nyid du slong mo byed pa nyid dam/ nags khrod na gnas pa'i dngos po nyid kyis gang zhig skye ba ma lus drangs pa dang ldan zhing smyung bas chog pa de ni tshangs par spyod par bshad de/ brtul zhugs mchog ni de nyid kyi phyir na brtul zhugs thams cad kyi nang na mchog tu gyur pa nyid kyi phyir na 'jam dpal kho na rigs te/ bskal pa grangs med par ye shes kyi spyod pa la spyad pa'i phyir ro/ /


mahātapās taponiṣṭha○ḥ snātako gautamo graṇīr iti | 

dka' thub mthar phyin dka' thub che/ /gtsang gnas dam pa gau ta ma/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra mahātapā iti | mahat tapo sayāsau mahātapās tilārddhaṃ[$3] bhaktayitvā ṣaṭvarṣāṇi duskaracaryāyām avasthānāt | tat pra○darśakatvaṃ tu tadvineyānām ‡āvarṣaṇārthaṃ‡ | tataś cāsau bhagavān mañjuśrīr mahātapā ity ucyate |

ta[$4]poniṣṭha iti | sarvasya lokasya yat tapa indriyopaśa○malakṣaṇam tasya niṣṭhā avaśānaṃ yatra sa taponiṣṭhaḥ sa ca mañjuśrīḥ || 

de la dka' thub mthar phyin ni 'jig rten thams cad kyi dka' thub ni gang dbang po nye bar zhe bar byed pa'i mtshan nyid de na dka' thub po/ /de mthar phyin pa rdzogs pa dang gang [f. 78r]@#/ /ldan pa de ni dka' thub mthar phyin te/ de la yang 'jam dpal lo/ /

dka' thub chen po ni dka' thub chen po dang gang ldan pa de ni dka' thub kyi spyod pa la spyi cher gnas pa'i phyir te/ de rab tu bstan pa'ang des 'dul ba rnams gzhung ba'i phyir ro/ /de'i phyir yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de dka' thub che zhes gsungs so/ /


snātaka iti | adhī[$5]tavedaḥ samāptavrataḥ snātakaḥ | sarvavratānāṃ sarvavi○dyānāṃ ca paryantagamanād āryamañjuśrīr eva snātaka ity ucyate | 

gtsang gnas ni rig byed 'don pa dang*/ brtul zhugs gsum rdzogs pa ni gtsang gnas te/ brtul zhugs thams cad dang rig byed thams cad yongs su mthar phyin pa'i phyir na 'phags pa 'jam dpal nyid gtsang gnas zhes gsungs so/ /


gautama iti gotranāma te[$6]nāsau bhagavān avyapadiśyate | 

go ta ma ni rigs kyi mtshan des bcom ldan 'das de la btags pa'o/ /


ata evāgranīr iti ○ svagotreṣu jyeṣṭhatvaṃ sarvajñajñānalābhāt || 

de nyid kyi phyir na dam pa zhes pa ste/ thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob pa'i phyir dang*/ rang gi rigs la gong na med pa'i phyir ro/ /



