bram zhe tshangs pa tshang pa shes/ /mya ngan 'das pa tshangs pa thob/ /ces pa ni/ 


tatra brahmavid iti | brahmaśabdena vedā ucyate | tāna jānāti vettīti brahmavit anūcāna ucyate | brahmādayaḥ kilānūcānāḥ | evaṃ hi smaryate | viṣṇur maheśvaraś ca prathama [f. 70 – img. 121] .. .. .. mākāśastham anugamya proktavantau prajāpataye | prajāpatir indrāya | indro vaśiṣṭhāya | vaśiṣṭhaḥ pārāsarāya | pārāsaraḥ kṛṣṇadvaipāyanāya | kṛṣṇadvaipāyano jaimi[$2]nāya | ityādi | sa evaṃ lakṣaṇo bhagavān mañjuśrīr evā○nūcānāy uktaḥ | yato bhagavān | yānatrayasaṃgṛhītaṃ niśeṣaṃ pravacanam anugamya vinayebhya u[$3]ktavān | tasmād asau mañjuśrīr brahmavidrūpeṇāpi tadbhakta○nāṃ pratibhāsata iti || 

brāhmaṇa iti | 
	tapaḥ śrutaṃ ca yoniś ca etad brāhmaṇakāraṇam iti 
ya[$3]to bhagavān evānantakālajanitena tapasānantāparyantana○ śrutena yuktatvāt | anāśravamārgotpayiyonitvāc ca guṇatrayeṇa yukta iti | paro brāhmaṇo bha[$5]gavān | athavā mantrabrāhmaṇabhedena dvidhāvedaḥ tatra yo ○ sau brāhmaṇātmako vedaḥ sa bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | tatsādhyasya kāryasya bhagavataiva sādhyatvāt | ta[$6]drūpeṇāpi kvacitpratibhāsate ||

brahmeti | rūpadhātau pratha○madhyānasamāpanno brahmā((gṛdbha))te | tadrūpeṇāpi pratibhāsamānatvāt || 

de la bram zhe ni/ /
	dka' thub thos dang skye gnas te/ /
	'di dag bram ze byed pa'o/ /
zhes so/ /gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das nyid dus mtha' yas pa las skyes pas dka' thub dang ldan pa dang*/ /yongs su mthar thug pa med pa'i thos pa dang ldan pa'i phyir dang zhag pa med pa'i lam las skyes pa'i skye gnas kyi phyir te/ yon tan gsum dang lnga pas na gzhan du ni bram zhi ni bcom ldan 'das yin no/ /yang na sngags dang bram ze rnams dbye bas na gnyis su dbye ba rnam pa gnyis te/ de la gang bram ze'i bdag nyid rig pa ste 'di ni bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal te/ de dag gis bsgrub par bya ba'i 'bras bu ni bcom ldan 'das kho na bsgrub par bya ba nyid yid pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /kha cig tu de dag gi gzugs kyis kyang snang bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /

tshang pa ni gzugs khams kyi bsam gtan dang po grub pa tshangs pa gzhung ste/ de'i gzugs kyis kyang snang bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /

tshang pa shes pa ni tshangs pa'i sgras ni rig byed du bshad de/ de mkhyen pas na tshangs pa shes pa'o/ /tshangs pa la sogs pa'i rjes su brjod pa la bshad par grags te/ rjes su brjod pa rnams ni 'di ltar dran par bya'o/ /[f. 78v] khyab 'jug dang*/ dbang phyug chen po de dag gis mchog tu dang po rig byed nam mkha' la gnas pa rjes su rtogs te bshad par gyur pa 'di ni skye dgu'i bdag po la'o/ /skye dgu'i bdag pos ni dbang po la'o/ /dbang pos ni drang srong gnas 'jog la'o/ /drang srong gnas 'jog gis rtsib logs skyes la'o/ /rtsib logs skyes kyis kriSh+Na rde ba yan la'o/ /kriSh+Na rde ba yan sa ni rgyal dpog pa la'o/ /zhes pa la sogs pa ste/ de lta bu'i mtshan nyid ni bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal kho na ste rjes su brjod par rigs so/ /gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das kyis the sa pa gsum du 'dus pa'i gsung rab ma lus par rjes su rtogs shing 'dul ba rnams la brjod pas na/ de'i phyir na 'jam dpal de tshangs pa shes pa'i gzugs kyang de la gus pa rnams so sor snang zhes so/ /

brahmanirvāṇam iti | bra[$7]hmaṇo nirvāṇaṃ brahmanirvāṇan tac cānandan tathā cokta
	ānandam brahmaṇo rūpaṃ cetaneti tad ucyate |
tadrūpeṇāpi bhagavān eva | 

mya ngan 'das pa tshang pa thob ni tshangs pa'i mya pa na las 'das pa ni tshangs pa mya ngan las 'das pa'o/ /tshang pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa yang dga' ba'o/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	dga' ba tshangs pa'i ngo bo ste/
	'di min 'di min zhes gsungs so/ /
zhes so/ /'di gzugs kyis kyang bcom ldan 'das nyid do/ /


āptavān iti | avisaṃvādaka āptaḥ || ta[f. 71r – img 122]thā coktaṃ ||
	pitṛmitrādir āptaḥ syā(da)(pc - marginal)duṣṭakāraṇaḥ kvacit |
	sarvajño tīndriyārtheṣu ((śru))tiś ced yadyakṛtimeti |
mañjuśrīś ca niratiśayābhyāṃ jñānānugrahopāyābhyāṃ yogāt para[$2]ma āptaḥ | sa vidyate yasya sa āptaḥvān || 

gcugs ldan ni mi slu bas na gcugs ldan te/ de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	pha dang grogs la sogs gcugs ni/ /
	dka' ba dga' yad byed mod kyi/ /
	thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang don la/ /
	'phro ba'o zhes na bcom ma min/ /
