	muktis tu śūnyatādṛṣṭes tadarthā śeṣabhāva○neti || [3.255]
tataś ca bhagavān eva muktiḥ | śūnyatā 'vinirbhāgavarttitvāt ||

de la grol ba ni stong pa mthong ba'o/ /de ltar yab chos kyi grags pas gsungs pa/ 
