	bsgom pa ma lus de yi don/ /
zhes so/ /de yang bcom ldan 'das kho na grol ba ste/ stong pa nyid rnam par dbye ba las 'jug pa'i phyir ro/ /

mokṣa iti | vairāgyapra[$4]tipannasya yoginas tasyārthapratisaṃvedino dharmaprati○saṃvedinaś cotpadyate prāmodyaṃ pramuditasya prītirjāyate prītamanasaḥ kāyaḥ praśrabhyate | [$5] prayuddhakāyaḥ sukhaṃ vedayate sūkhitasyavittaṃ samādhī○ yate samāhita citto yathābhūtam prajānāti | yathābhūtam paśyati | yathābhūtam prajānan | yathā[$6]bhūtam paśyan | nirvidyate nirvvṇovirakṣate | virakto ○ vimucyata ity evaṃ yathābhūtam paśyato (yoginaḥ)(pc - marginal; not sure where to insert) vimuktacittatā vyavasthāpitā bhagavatā | tasya bhūta.. .. tvāt ||

thar pa ni chags pa dang bral ba nyid la zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa de'i don so so yang dag par rig pa dang*/ chos so so yang dag par rig pa skye [f. 79r]@#/ /ba na rab tu mgu ba dang*/ rab tu dga' ba dang tshim pa 'byung zhing yid dga' ba'i lus shin tu sbyangs par 'gyur ro/ /lus shin tu sbyangs pas bde ba tshor ro/ /bde bar gyur pa'i sems mnyam par 'jig go/ /mnyam par gzhag pa'i sems kyis yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du shes shing*/ yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong ngo*/ /yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du shes shing yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong nas yid 'byung ngo*/ /yid byung ngo*/ /yid byung bas chags pa dang bral lo/ /chags pa dang bral nas rnam par grol ba yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong ba ni bcom ldan 'das kyis rnam par grol ba'i sems nyid cher gzhag ste/ de yang dag par mthong ba'i phyir ro/ /

tathā coktaṃ ||
	āsaṃlīnena kāyena vedanām adhivāsayet |
	pradyotasyava nirvāṇaṃ vimoktas tasya cetasa iti || 
