	mdor bsdus nas ni rgyal bas bshad/ /
ces so/ /


tad evaṃ śrāvakādikānāṃ mokṣas ((ta))dyāna bhagavatā vyavasthāpitaḥ sa ca bhagvān ma[$2]ñjuśrīr eva veditavyaś tasya sarvagatatvāt |
	% Tib indicates 'sarvatathāgatatvāt'

de lta bu'i tshul gyis nyan thos la sogs pa'i theg pa la bcom ldan 'das rnam par gzhag ste/ de yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal nyid du rig par bya ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad de'i yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


vimokṣāṅga i○ti | vimokṣasyāṅgāni vimokṣāṅgāni | vimokṣo bodhiḥ | tasyāṅgāni saptabodhyāṅgāni | a[$3]ṣṭau mārgāṅgāṇi ca || yad uta smṛti(saṃ)(pc - marginal)bodhyaṅgam | dharmapravicayā○sambodhyaṅgam prītisambodhyaṅgam | prasrabdhisambodhyaṅgam | samādhisambodhyaṅgam | vīryasambodhya[$4]ṅgam | upekṣāsambodhyaṅgam iti | 

grol yan lag ni rnam par thar pa'i yan lag rnams ni grol yan lag ste/ rnam par thar pa ni byang chub po/ /de'i yan lag ni byang chub kyi yan lag bdun rnams dang*/ 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad rnams so/ /ji ltar gsungs pa/ dran pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang*/ chos rnam par 'byed pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang*/ brtson 'grus yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang*/ dga' ba yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang*/ shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang*/ ting nge 'dzin yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag dang*/ btang snyoms yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag ste/ 

etāni ca sambodher aṅgā○ny avayavabhūtāni iti bodhyaṅgāni | etebhyaḥ kleśāvaraṇapratipakṣabhūtebhyo anantaraṃ jñeyāva[$5]raṇaprahāṇāya bhāvanāmārgasamprabhāvitāni aṣṭau mā○rgāṅgāṇi || tad yathā samyadṛṣṭiḥ samyaksaṃkalpaḥ samyagvāk | samyakkarmāntaḥ | samyagājīvaḥ [$5] | samyagvyāyāmaḥ | samyaksmṛtiḥ | samyaksamādhiś ca | sa eva darśanamārgau bhāvanāmārgaś ca | vimokṣasya bodher aṅgānīti kṛtvā | sa evāsau bhagavān mañju[$7]śrī vimokṣāṅga ity ucyate | tayos tatsvabhāvatvāt ||
 
'di dag ni yang dag pa byang chub kyi yan lag dang cha shas su gyur pa ste/ byang chub kyi yan lag rnams so/ /nyon mongs pa'i sgrib [f. 79v]pa'i gnyen po'i dngos po de rnams las gzhan shes bya'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i don du bsgom pa'i lam rab tu goms pa'i 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad po rnams so/ /'di lta ste/ yang dag pa'i lta ba dang*/ yang dag pa'i rtog pa dang*/ yang dag pa'i ngag dang*/ yang dag pa'i las kyi mtha' dang*/ yang dag pa'i 'tsho ba dang*/ yang dag pa'i rtsol pa dang*/ yang dag pa'i dran pa dang*/ yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin rnams te/ 'di ltar de dag ni mthong ba'i lam dang*/ bsgom pa'i lam la rnam par thar pa byang chub kyi yan lag rnams te/ kha cig tu bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de grol yan lag ces gsungs so/ /de gnyis su de'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

vimuktir iti rāgādibhyo bandhanebhyaḥ || tathā ca || trīṇi vandhāni | rāgo bandhanaṃ | moho bandhanaṃ | dveṣo bandha(na)(pc - marginal)m iti [ms-c f. 72r – img 124] ((ebhir bandhanair)) .tridhātukād anatikramād bandhanāni | tair vimuktatvāt vimuktir ity ucyate || 

rnam grol ni 'dod chags la sogs pa'i bcings pa las so/ /'di lta ste/ bcings pa ni gsum ste/ 'dod chags kyis 'ching ba dang*/ zhe sdang gis 'ching ba dang*/ gti mug gis 'ching ba'o/ /de rnams kyis bcings pas khams gsum las mi 'da' ba'i phyir na 'ching ba rnams te/ rnam par grol bar byed pas na rnam grol zhes gsungs so/ /

tathā cātra vakṣaty anusaṃśāyāṃ
	vimuktiḥ sarvabandhanānām iti ||

de ltar yang 'dir yon tan phyi nas gsungs pa/ 
	'ching ba thams cad las rnam par grol pa'o zhes gsungs so/ /


śāntateti | sarvacittopa((pla))[$2]vānāṃ grāhyagrāhakādivikalpānāṃ śāntatvāt śāntatety ucya○te || 

śiva iti | nirodhādibhir (anirodham anutpādam anuccedam ityādirūpaṃ)(pc - marginal) aṣṭābhir vivādaspadair vimukto yaḥ pratītyasamutpādaḥ sarvaprapañco[$3]paśamalakṣaṇaḥ sa śivaḥ sa ca bhagavān sarvatathāgatajñānasa○tvaḥ śūnyatājñānasvahāvatvāt śiva ity ucyate || tathā coktam āryapādaiḥ |
	anirodham anutpādam anu[#4]cchedam aśāśvataṃ |
	anekārtham anānārtham anāgamam anirgamaṃ || ○ 
	yaḥ pratītyasamutpādam prapañcopaśamaṃ śivam ityādi ||

zhi ba ni 'gog pa la sogs pa rtsod pa'i dpa'i gnas brgyad po rnams las rnam par grol ba gang rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba spros pa thams cad ne bar zhi ba'i mtshan nyid zhi ba'o/ /de yang bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir na zhi ba zhes gsungs so/ /de ltar yang slob dpon glu sgrub zhabs kyis gsungs pa/ 
	gang gis rten cing 'brel par 'byung*/ /
	'gag pa med pa skye med pa/ /
	rtag pa med pa chad med pa/ /
	thad da don med don gcig min/ /
	'ong ba med pas 'gro med pa/ /
	spros pa nyer zhi zhi spyod pa/ /
	rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas smras rnams kyi/ /
	dam pa de la phyag 'tshal lo/ /
zhes so/ /

zhi ba nyid ni sems kyi ne bar g.yo ba gzhung 'dzin la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog pa thams cad ne bar zhi ba nyid kyi phyir na zhi ba nyid ces gsungs so/ /


[nirvāṇaṃ nirvṛtiḥ śāntiḥ śreyo niryāṇam antakaḥ |
sukhaduḥkhāntakṛn niṣṭhā vairāgyam upadhikṣayaḥ || 96 ||]

[mya ngan 'das zhi mya ngan 'das/ /
legs par nges 'byung mthar byed pa/ /
bde dang sdug bsngal mthar byed gnas/ /
