sukhadukhāntakṛd iti | ratnasambhavaḥ | mātsaryacaritānāṃ satvānāṃ[$2] dānaviśuddhipraḍānasvabhāvena teṣāṃ sukhaduḥkhāntakaraṇāt || 

bde sdug mthar byed ni chen 'byung ldan te/ ser sna la spyod pa'i sems can rnams sbyin pa rnam par dag par tu sbyin pa'i rang bzhin gyis de rnams kyi bde ba dang sdug bsngal mthar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


niṣṭhety amitābhaḥ rāgacaritānāṃ satvānāṃ rāgaviśuddhidharmatāprakāśanadvāreṇa pratya[$3]vekṣaṇājñānasya niṣṭhāgamanāt || 

mthar thug pa ni snang ba mtha' yas te/ 'dod chags la spyod pa'i sems can rnams 'dod chags rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid rab tu bstan pa'i sgo nas so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes mthar thug par son pa'i phyir ro/ /


vairāgyam ity amoghasi○ddhiḥ | kauśīdyacaritānāṃ satvānāṃ svavimokṣarūpeṇa teṣāṃ vairāgyam utpādya kuśalapakṣe cittā[$4]niyojanirvāṇapathaprakāśanāt ||

chags bral ni don yod grub pa ste/ le lo la spyod pa'i sems can rnams rang gi rnam par thar pa'i gzugs kyis de rnams la chags pa dang bral ba bskyed nas dge ba'i phyogs la sems nges par sbyor ba ste/ mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam rab tu sten par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


upadhikṣaya iti ○ vairocanaḥ | upadhir vāśaṇā tasyāḥ kṣayo vināśaḥ | upadhikṣayaḥ | mohacaritānāṃ satvānāṃ [$5] yathābhūtadharmatāprakāśanamukhena suviśuddhadharmadhātu○jñānodyotanāt || 

lus ni zad pa po ni rnam par snang mdzad de/ lus ni bag chags so/ /de'i zad pa ni rnam par 'jig par byed ste/ gti mug la spyod pa'i sems can rnams yang dag pa ji lta ba'i chos bstan pa'i sgo na shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes gsal bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


tataś ca dvividhau hi mokṣaḥ sopadhiśeṣo nirupadhiśeṣaś ca | tatra bāhyādī[$6]nāṃ śoṣadhiśeṣaḥ | samyaksaṃbuddhānāṃ nirupadhiśeṣaḥ || ○ ata evoktaṃ || 
	savāsanāś ca te doṣā na santy ekasya tāyina iti || 
% Prasādapratibhodhava (= Śatapañcāśatka) of Mātṛceṭa, verse 3
	[savāsanāś ca te doṣā na santy ekasya tāyinaḥ |
	sarve sarvavidaḥ santi guṇās te cānapāyinaḥ || 3]

de yang thar pa rnam pa gnyis te/ phung po lhag ma dang bcas pa dang*/[f. 80v]phung po lhag ma med pa'o/ /de la phyi ba la sogs pa rnams kyis lhag ma dang bcas pa'o/ /yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ni lhag ma med pa'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na gsungs pa/ /
	bag chag bcas pa'i skyon rnams te/ /
	skyo ba khyod kyi skyon rnams ni/ /
	bag chags bcas par gcig mi mnga'/ /
	de'i phyir mya ngan 'das gnyis dang*/ /
	rang bzhin gyis ni de nyid do/ /
zhes gsungs so/ /

tataś caubhayanirvāṇasvabhā[$7]venāpi sa eva bhagavān mañjuśrīr eva gantavya ity ata āha nirvāṇam ityādi | 

de gnyis ka'i rang bzhin gyis kyang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal nyid par bya'o/ /de'i phyir na gsungs te/ mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs pa'o/ /


[ajayo 'nupamo 'vyakto nirābhāso nirañjanaḥ |
niṣkalaḥ sarvago vyāpī sūkṣmo bījam anāsravaḥ || 97 ||]

[thub pa med pa dpe med pa/ /
gsal min mi snang gos pa med/ /
cha med kun 'gro khyab pa po/ /
phra mo sa bon zag pa med/ /]


ajayo 'nupamo vyakto nirābhāso nirañjana iti ||

tshugs pa med pa dpe med pa/ /mi mngon mi snang gsal byed min/ /zhes pa ni 


tatrājaya iti | parair nijīya[ms-c f. 73r - img 126]ta ity ajayaḥ ||

de la tshugs pa med pa ni gzhan rnams kyis dbang bya bar mi nus pas na tshugs pa med pa'o/ /


anupama iti || sarvopamārahitatvāt | 

dpe med pa ni dpe thams cad med pa'i phyir ro/ /


avyakta iti stryādirūpābhāvāt |

mi mngon pa ni bud med la sogs pa'i gzugs med pa'i phyir ro/ /


nirābhāsa iti | ābhāsarahitatvāt | 

mi snang ba ni snang ba dang bral ba'i phyir ro/ /


nirañjana iti | nirlepatvāt [$2] yataḥ sa eva bhagavān paramārthasvabhāvatvāt ((ma))ñcabhi○r ebhir viśeṣaṇapadair gṛhyate ||

gsal byed mi ni gos pa med pa'i phyir ro/ /gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das de nyid don dam pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir na khyad par gyi tshig ldas bzung ba'o/ /


niṣkalaḥ sarvago vyāpī sūkṣmo bījam anāśrava iti |

mi 'gyur kun 'gro khyab pa po/ /phra zhes zhag med sa bon bral/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra ni[$3]skala iti | kalārahitatvāt |

de la mi 'gyur ba ni 'gyur ba dang bral pa'i phyi ro/ /


sarvaga iti sarvaga○bhatvāt | 

kun 'gro ni thams cad du song ba'i phyir ro/ /


vyāpīti sthiracalapadārthasvabhāvatvāt |

khyab pa ni g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba'i don gyi rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /


aṇoḥ sūkṣmād apy aṇīyā((nu))sūkṣmaḥ ||

rngul phran ni phra ba'i phyir na phra zhing ngo*/ /


[$4] bījam iti | dharmādharmāneñjyavāsanābījasvacitam ā○layavijñānaṃ | 

anāśrava iti mārgasatyasvabhātvāt catur vidhaḥ | asanskṛtasvabhāvatvāt[$5] | caturvidhaḥ ākāśam pratisaṃkhyānirodhaḥ | aprati○saṃkhyānirodhaḥ | tathatā ca | sa eva bhagavān tatsvabhāvatvāt || 
(anāsravāmārgasatyan trividhañ cā<sya>py asaṃskṛtam ity ukteḥ | śūnyādibhedāt anāsrava)(marginal note - not sure where to add; doesn't appear to correspond to Tib.)

zhag med ni lam gyi bde na pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /yang na 'dus ma byas pa bzhi'i rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /de rnam pa bzhi ni nam mkha' dang*/ so sor brtags pa'i 'gog pa dang*/ /so sor brtags pa ma yin pa'i 'gog pa dang*/ de bzhi nyid do/ /

sa bon ni chos dang chos ma yin pa dang mi g.yo ba'i sa bon bas kun gzhi rnam par shes pa'o/ /de nyid kyang bcom ldan 'das de'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


[arajo virajo vimalo vāntadoṣo nirāmayaḥ |
suprabuddho vibuddhātmā sarvajñaḥ sarvavit paraḥ || 98 ||]

[rdul med rdul bral dri ma med/ /
[6r]nyes pa spangs pa skyon med pa/ /
shin tu rab sad rnam sad bdag /
thams cad ye shes kun rig mchog /]


arajo varajo vimalo [$6] vāntadoso nirāmayaḥ ||

rngul med rngul bral dri ma med/ /nyes pa spangs pa skyon med pa/ /zhes pa ni 


araja iti rāgādirajopagatvāt |

de la rngul med ni 'dod chags la sogs pa'i rngul dang bral ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


viraja iti | tathatāviśuddheḥ sthityanyathātvābhāvāt |

rdul bral ni de bzhin nyid rnam par dag pa las gzhan du gyur pa med pa'i phyir ro/ /


vimala iti | dharmāṇāṃ śūnyatayāma[ms-c f. 73v – img. 127]lānām āgantukatvāt | sa eva bhagavān vimala ity ucyate | 

dri ma med ni chos thams cad stong pa nyid la dri ma ni glo bur ba'i phyir na/ bcom [f. 81r]@#/ /ldan 'das de nyid dri ma dang bral ba zhes gsungs so/ /


vāntadoṣa iti | vānto nigīṇo doṣo rāgādir yena sa vāntadoṣaḥ | 

nyes pa spangs pa ni 'dod chags la sogs pa'i nyes pa gang gis bor ba de ni nyes pa spangs pa ste/ 


ata eva nirāmaya iti | nirgata ā[$2]mayo vyādhir yasya sa nirgamaya iti | evaṃ guṇaviśi○ṣṭaś ca sa eva bhagavān | 

de nyid kyi phyir na skyon med pa zhes pa ste/ skyon nad las 'das pa gang yin pa de ni skyon med pa'o/ /de 'dra ba'i yon tan gyi don khyad par can yang bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


suprabaddho vibuddhātmā sarvajñaḥ sarvavitpara iti ||

shin tu sad pa rnams sad bdag /kun shes kun rig dam pa'o/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra suprabuddha iti [$3] || suṣṭhu prakarṣeṇa buddhaḥ suprabuddhaḥ yathāvasthita yadā○rthāviparītāvabodhanāt |

de la kun shes pa ni shin tu legs shing phul du byung bas shin tu sad pa ste/ ji bzhin du gnas pa'i dngos po phyin ci ma log par mkhyen pa'i phyir ro/ /


vibuddhātmeti | śrāvakādibhyo viśeṣeṇa buddho vibuddhaḥ | tasyā[$4]tmā śūnyatāsvabhāvaḥ | sa eva yasyāsau vibuddhātmā | 

rnam sad bdag ni nyan thos la sogs pa las khyad par du sad pa ni sad pa ste/ de'i bdag nyid ni stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no/ /de nyid gang dang gang ldan pa de rnams sad pa'i bdag go/ /


sa○rvajña iti | sarvan niravaśeṣaṃ jñeyaṃ jānātīti sarvajñaḥ | 

kun shes ni kun te ma lus pa'i shes bya mkhyen pa nyid kyi phyir na kun shes so/ /


sarvavid iti | sarvasatvānāṃ cittaca[$5]ritam āśayānuśayañ ca vettīti sarvavit | 

kun rig ni sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi spyod pa bsam pa dang bag la nyal rig pas na kun rig ste/ 


ata eva ○ para utkṛṣæo sau bhagavān || 

de nyid kyi phyir na dam pa po ni rab ste bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


[vijñānadharmatātīto jñānam advayarūpadhṛk |
nirvikalpo nirābhogas tryadhvasaṃbuddhakāryakṛt || 99 ||]

[rnam par shes pa'i chos nyid 'das/ /
ye shes gnyis med tshul 'chang ba/ /
rnam par rtog med lhun gyis grub/ /
dus gsum sangs rgyas las byed pa/ /]


vijñānadharmatātīto jñānam advayarūpadhṛk ||

rnam par shes pa chos dbyings 'das/ /ye shes gnyis med tshul 'chang ba/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra vijñānadharma[$6]tātīta iti | vijñānacakṣurādivyatiriktam ālayavijñānam asti | tad (paraḥ - pc, margin - not sure how to add) eva ca sarvabījakaṃ na cakṣurvijñānādīti kuta etat | āgamād yuktitaś ca | tatra yuktir ane[ms-c f. 74 – img 128]ka mukhena savistarā ' ..tra pratipāditeti nehaṃ pratanyate | āgamas tu vivādāspadarahitatvāt alpavaktavyatvāc ca vaktavyaḥ tathā coktam abhidharmasūtre 
	anādikā[$2]liko dhātuḥ sarvadharmasamāśrayaḥ |
	tasmiṃ sati gatīḥ○ sarvā nirvāṇādhigamo pi ceti ||
tasya dharmatā vijñānadharmatā śūnyatā tayātīto tikrānta[$3]s tasyā apy anupalabdheḥ || 

de la rnam par shes pa chos nyid 'das ni rnam par shes pa ni mig la sogs pa ma gtogs pa kun gzhi rnam par shes pa yod de/ de nyid kyang sa bon thams cad pa yin gyi/ mig la sogs pa'i rnam par shes pa ni ma yin no/ /de ji ltar shes par bya zhe na/ lung dang rigs pas so/ /de la rigs pa ni sgo du mas rgyas pa dang bcas pa bsgrubs pas 'dir ma bris so/ /lung la ni rtsod pa'i gzhi dang bral ba'i phyir dang*/ tshig nyung ba nyid kyi phyir yang brjod do/ /de'i phyir gsungs pa/ de yang chos mngon pa'i mdo las/ 
	thog ma med pa dus kyi dbyings/ /
	chos rnams kun gyi gnas yin te/ /
	de yod pas na 'gro kun dang*/ /
	mya ngan 'das pa'ang thob pa yin/ /
zhes so/ de'i chos nyid ni rnam par shes pa'i chos nyid do/ /de yis 'das pa ni 'das pa ste/ de yang mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro/ /


jñānam iti | sarvatra cādhipa○tya prabhāvitatvāt | śuviśuddhadharmadhātujñānaṃ || 

ye shes ni thams cad du yang bdag por bsgoms pa'i phyir shin tu rnam par dag pa chos nyid las te/


ata eva advayarūpadhṛg iti | audāryagā[$4]mbhīryātmakatvāt ||

de nyid kyi phyir na gnyis med tshul 'chang ba zhes pa ste/ zab cing rgya che ba'i bdag [f. 81v]nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


nirvikalpo nirābhogas tryadhvasambu○ddhakāryakṛd iti ||

rnam par rtog med lhun gyis grub/ /dus gsum sangs rgyas don byed pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra nirvikalpa iti | paramārthavikalpe pi (avikatvāt) (ms-c; avikalpatvāt em.) || tathā coktaṃ [$5] ||
	paramārthavikalpe pi nāvalīyate paṇḍitaḥ 
	ke hi ○ bhedo vikalpasya śubhe cāpy aśubhe pi ceti ||
	% cf. Edgerton avalīyate, nshrinking, downcast, despondent
tataś ca sa eva bhagavān nirvikalpaḥ || 

de la rnam par rtog med ni don dam par rnam par rtog pa la yang mi rtog pa la yang mi rtog pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	don dam pa yi rnam rtog la'ang*/ /
	mkhas pas rtag tu bying mi byed/ /
	dge ba dang yang mi dge ba'i/ /
	rnam par rtog la dbyer ci yod/ /
ces so/ /de'i phyir na bcom ldan 'das de nyid rnam par rtog med do/ /


nirā[$6]bhoga iti | nirabhi(saskāra)(ms-c; saṃskāra em.) ity arthaḥ nirgata ā○bhogo nirābogaḥ | tataś cāyam artho bhavati | pūrvasmin sābhisaṃskāravāhini prajñāpravā .. .. (prani)(em; .. .. ms-c)dhāna((ś)) cintāmaṇivad avikalpasyāpi mama yathābhavyaṃ satvārtho bhaviṣyatīti tatpūrvapraṇidhānaṃ tenābhimatam ākṣiptaṃ satataṃ nityam anābhogaṃ praya[ms-c f. 74v – img. 129] ... kārya .. sya sarvatathāgagajñānasatvasyāsau nirābhoga ity ucyate | ābhyām padābhyām prajñopāyātmakaḥ sa bhagavān ity utkam bhavati | tathā coktaṃ
	pūrvapraṇi[$2]dhānāhitasatatānābhogavāhi parakāryam iti ||
		% also found in Tattvasaṃgraha

lhun gyis grub ni mngon par 'du byed pa med ces bya ba'i don to/ /rtsol ba dang bral bas na lhun gyis grub pa ste/ de yang don 'dir 'gyur te/ sngon gyi dus na mngon par 'du byed pa dang bcas pa'i 'jug pa'i shes rab kyis rab tu dpyad pas smon lam gang yin pa yid bzhin gyi nor bu bzhin du rtog pa med na yang mnyam par skal pa ji lta ba bzhin du sems can gyi don phyis byed par gyur cig ces gang sngon gyi smon lam 'debs pa des mngon par 'dod pas 'phags pa rtag tu 'jug pa lhun gyis grub pa nan tan med pas gzhan gyi don bya ba dang gang ldan pa de de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku thams cad lhun gyis grub pa gsungs so/ /tshig de gnyis kyis thabs dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das zhes gsungs par 'gyur ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	sngon gyi smon lam gyis 'phangs rtag tu ni/ /
	lhun gyis grub pas gzhan gyi don rnams 'byung*/ /
zhes so/ /


stryadhva○sambuddhakāryakṛd iti | triṣu adhvasu sambuddhām tryadhvasambuddhās teṣāṃ kāryāṇi tryadhvasambuddhakārya[$3]ṇi tāni karotīti tryadhvasambuddhakāryakṛt | sa eva bha○gavān ||

dus gsum sangs rgyas don byed pa ni dus gsum gyi rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni dus gsum sangs rgyas te/ /bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


[anādinidhano buddha ādibuddho niranvayaḥ |
jñānaikacakṣur amalo jñānamūrtis tathāgataḥ || 100 ||]

[sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med/ /
dang po'i sangs rgyas ris med pa/ /
ye shes mig gcig dri ma med/ /
ye shes lus can de bzhin gshegs/ /]


anādinidhano buddha ādibuddho niranvaya iti 

sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med/ /dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pa/ /zhes pa ni 


anādinidhana iti | ādi[$4]ś nidhanaś ca ādinidhane na vidyate ādinidhane yā○syāsaāv anādinidhanaḥ utpādinirodhābhāvāt tasya bhagavataḥ | 

