buddha iti | atha buddha i[$5]ty etat katham bhagavati varttate | kathañ ca na syāt budhor jñānā○rthatvāt | tasmāt ktaḥ | bhāvakarmaṇoḥ prayogo pra((śṛ))vyaḥ | buddhan devadattenādhātaṃ buddhaṃ śāstraṃ dai[$6]vad atteneti karmaṇi vā buddha śarddha iṣyate | iha hi buddha○vān sarvadharmān iti | karttari buddhaḥ | sakalapadārthāv abodhinī buddher asyeti vā akāroma[$7]tvarthāyo bhiśayārthe | atha vāyurvara ca gamanārthatvāt | avagamanañ ca gatiḥ | gatyarthebhyaś ca kto bhāvakarmakarṭṣu bhavatīti krtṛr yas tu sarvadharmān svalakṣaṇa[ms-c f. 75 – img. 130]sya sāmyalakṣaṇato buddhavān iti buddha sa bhagavān | 

de la sangs rgyas zhes bya ba la 'on te/ sangs rgyas zhes bya ba 'di ji ltar na sangs rgyas la 'jug par 'gyur zhe na/ ci ste mi 'gyur te/ sangs rgyas ni ye shes kyi don nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de yang gcig nyid kyis dngos po dang las gnyis su sbyor ba mthong ngo*/ /lha sbyin sangs rgyas la rag las par gyur to/ /lha sbyin gyis sangs rgyas bstan zhing bcos so/ /las su yang sangs rgyas kyi dgrar 'dod de/ 'di ni sangs rgyas dang ldan no/ /las thams cad ces bya bas na sangs rgyas te/ sangs rgyas 'di ni dngos po thams cad shes pa'i blo dang gang ldan [f. 82r]@#/ /pa de'o/ /yi ge a ni ldan pa'i don dang*/ phul du byung ba'i don to/ /

yang na sangs rgyas ni thugs su chud pa'i don yin la phul du byung ba yang rtogs pa ste/ rtogs pa'i don du yang gsungs so/ /dngos po dang las dang byed par 'gyur ba las byed pa gang yin pa yang las thams cad de/ rang gi mtshan nyid dang spyi'i mtshan nyid shes pa dang ldan pa ni sangs rgyas te/ bcom ldan 'das so/ 

thog ma tha ma med pa ni thog ma dang tha ma ni thog ma dang tha ma gnyis so/ /thog ma dang tha ma med pa gang dang ldan pa de thog ma dang tha ma med pa ste/ bcom ldan 'das de skye ba dang 'gag pa dang bral ba'i phyir ro/ /


ādibuddha iti | ādāv eva buddha ādibuddhaḥ sa ca pañcajñānātmakaḥ | katham iti cet || atrāha (māyājāle)(pc - marginal) |
	balaprabhāvitamād[$2]rśajñānaṁ |
tatra balāni pañca śraddhāvīryasmṛtisamādhiprajño○palakṣitāni | taiḥ prabhāvitatvāt | bhūtakoṭyā tadadhigamauktarṣaṃ | (dai..raryotkarṣasamatājñānaṃ)(ms-c pc - marginal)  

dang po'i sangs rgyas ni dang po kho na'i sangs rgyas te/ de yang ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid do/ /gal te ji lta zhe na/ de'i phyir gsungs pa/ 
	stobs kyis rab tu bsgoms pa ni/ /
	me long lta bu'i ye shes so/ /
de la stobs ni lnga ste/ dad pa dang*/ dran pa dang*/ brtson 'grus dang*/ ting nge 'dzin dang*/ shes rab kyis nye bar mtshon pa rnams te/ de rnams kyis rab tu bsgoms pa nyid kyi phyir na yang dag pa'i mtha' thugs su chud pa'i phul du byung ba'o/ /


abheviśāradyalakṣaṇaṃ [$3] samatajñānaṃ | tatra vaiśāradyāni jñānavaiśāradyaṃ prahāṇa○vaiśāradyaṃ saṃkleśahetūpadaśavaiśāradyaṃ vyavadānahetūpadeśavaiśāradyañ ceti | tataś caturbhi[$4]vaiśāradyaiḥ samatajñānasya lābhāt ||

mi 'jigs pa'i mtshan nyid ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so/ /de la mi 'jigs pa rnams ni ye shes la mi 'jigs pa rnams dang*/ zag pa zad pa la mi 'jigs pa dang*/ nyon mongs pa'i rgyu nye bar bstan pa la mi 'jigs pa dang*/ rnam par byang pa'i rgyu bstan pa la mi 'jigs pa ste/ de bas na mi 'jigs pa ste/ de bas na mi 'jigs pa bzhis mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes thob bo/ /


anamittena śū○kṣmakalpanāviśuddha ataḥ pratisaṃvitsvabhāvaṃ pratyavekṣaṇājñānaṃ || tatra ca catusraḥ pratisaṃ[$6]vidaḥ | arthadharmaniruktipratibhānayogaṭ tābhiḥ ○ pratyavekṣaṇājñānalābhāt | 

kun du mtshan ma med pas shin tu phra ba'i rtogs pa rnam par dag pa de'i phyir so so yang dag par rig pa'i rang bzhin ni so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes so/ /de la so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi ni don dang*/ chos dang*/ nges pa'i tshig dang*/ spobs pa rnams kyi tshul gyis so/ /de rnams kyis so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes thob pa'i phyir ro/ /


dharmadhātunāṃ sarvadharmasāratām adhigamāṇayatvañ ca tato maitrī[$6]karuṇākāraṃ kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñānaṃ || 

chos kyi dbyings kyi chos thams cad kyi snying po nyid lhag par mos pa'i bsam pa yang ste/ de'i phyir snying rje chen po dang byams pa'i tshul ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes so/ /

sarvādhipatya jani○tatvāt śuviśuddhadharmadhātujñānam iti | evaṃ pañcjñānātmakaḥ pañcavarṇātmakaś cāsau bhaga[$7]vān | sarvadharmasamatāmukhenaikālaśvanatvena draṣṭavyaḥ sa ca bhagavān mañjuśrīr ata evāśau || niranvaya iti anvayaḥ kramaḥ | navidyate 'anvayaḥ kramo ' [ms-c f. 74 – img 131] ... utpādanirodhābhāvāt | 
(duḥkhajñānaṃ sarvadharmābhisambodhaḥ nirodhāptiḥ prajñāṇaṃ | vivaddhapratibādhanaṃ samudayadeśanāt | mārga khyānañ ca 4) (marginal note, not sure where to connect)
(nyāgātkṛtyānuṣṭhānasyāt jagataḥ kṛtyāyādhigamāya ca pravṛtte 3)(also marginal, not entirely sure where to connect)

bdag po thams cad shes pa ni shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes te/ [f. 82v] da ltar ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid dang*/ rigs lnga'i bdag nyid ni bcom ldan 'das 'di lta ste/ chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi sgo nas dmigs pa gcig pa nyid du blta bar bya'o/ /de 'ang 'jam dpal kho na ste/ 'di ni rgyud med pa zhes bya ba'o/ /rgyud ni rim pa ste/ rgyud dang rim pa gang la med pa de ni rgyud med pa ste/ skye ba dang 'gag pa med pa'i phyir ro/ /

jānaikacakṣur amalo jñānnamurttis tathāgata iti | 

ye shes mig gcig dri ma med/ /ye shes lus can de bzhin gshegs/ /zhes pa ni


tatra jñānaikacakśur iti | jñānam evaikaṃ cakṣur yasya sa jñānaikacakṣuḥ || ata eva [$2] amala iti | rāgādimalābhāvāt | jñānamūrttir iti ○ jñānam eva mūrttir na kāyādi sasyāsau jñānamūrttiḥ sa eva tathāgata iti | gatārthañ ca || 

de la ye shes mig gcig ni ye shes nyid gcig pu'i mig dang gang ldan pa de ni ye shes mig gcig go/ /de nyid kyi phyir na dri ma med ces pa ste/ 'dod chags la sogs pa'i dri ma med pa'i phyir ro/ /ye shes lus can zhes pa ni ye shes nyid lus te/ gzugs la sogs pa med pa gang yin pa de/ ye shes lus can no/ /de nyid de bzhin gshegs pa ste/ de'i don ni bshad zin to/ /


[vāgīśvaro mahāvādī vādirāḍ vādipuṃgavaḥ |
vadatāṃ varo variṣṭho vādisiṃho 'parājitaḥ || 101 ||]

[tshig gi dbang phyug smra ba che/ /
smra ba'i skyes mchog smra ba'i rgyal/ /
smra ba'i dam pa mchog gi gnas/ /
smra ba'i seng ge thub pa med/ /]


vāgīśva[$3]ro mahāvādī vādirāḍ vādipuṅgavaḥ 
vadatām varo variṣṭho vādisiṃho 'parājita iti || 

tshig gi dbang phyug smra ba che/ /smra ba'i skye mchog smra ba'i rgyal/ /smra ba'i dam pa mchog gi gnas/ /smra ba'i seng ge tshugs pa med/ /ces pa ni


tatra vāgīśvarādīnāṃ aṣṭānāṃ padānāṃ hetuhetumatabhāvena [$4] phalasadbāvo vyākhyāyaḥ || tataś cāha | vāgīśvara iti | ○ (vāgīśvaro)(ms-c ac; vācā īśvara ms-c pc) vāgīśvaraḥ | ata eva vadatām varo bhavati |

de la tshig gi dbang phyug la sogs pa'i tshig brgyad po rnams kyis rgyu dang rgyu las byung ba can gyi dngos pos 'bras bu mchog tu yod pa la sogs pa bshad de/ de yang gsungs pa tshig gi dbang phyug ni tshig rnams kyi dbang phyug go/ /de nyid kyi phyir na smra ba che ste/ /
	% Tib. appears to be in error here for the last sentence.

mahāvādī mahāś cāsau vādī ca mahā[$5]vādī | ata eva ca variṣṭḥaḥ || 

smra ba yang de chen po yang de nyid yin pas smra ba che'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na smra ba'i skyes mchog yin no/ /


vādirāḍ iti | rājata iti ○ rāṭ vādināṃ rāṭ vādirāṭ | ata eva vādisiṃha iti |

de nyid kyi phyir na/ smra ba'i rgyal zhes pa la mdzes pas na rgyal po ste/ smra ba rnams kyi rgyal po ni smra ba'i rgyal po'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na smra ba'i dam pa ste/ gtso bo zhes gsungs te/ smra ba rnams kyi dam pa ni smra ba'i dam pa'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na mchog gi gnas so/ /de nyid kyi phyir na smra ba'i seng ge zhes so/ /


vādipuṅgava iti puṅavaḥ pradhāna[$6] ity ucyate | vādinā puṅgavaḥ | vādipuṅgavaḥ | ata e○vāparājita iti | parair na jāyata iti aparājitaḥ | sa caivaṃ guṇaviśiṣṭo sau bhagavān ma[$7]ñju((śrī)) 

de nyid kyi phyir na tshugs pa med pa ste/ gzhan rnams kyis mi tshugs pas na tshugs pa med do/ /de nyid kyi yon tan gyi khyad par yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /


[samantadarśī prāmodyas tejomālī sudarśanaḥ |
śrīvatsaḥ suprabho dīptir bhā bhāsurakaradyutiḥ || 102 ||]

[kun tu lta ba mchog tu dga'/ /
gzi brjid phreng ldan blta na sdug /
'od bzang 'bar ba dpal gyi be'u/ /
snang ba gsal bar byed pa'i 'od/ /]


((sa))mantadarśī prāmodyas tejomālī sudarśana iti ||

kun du lta ba mchog tu dga'/ /gzi brjid phung po blta na sdug/ /ces pa ni 


tatra samantradarśīti | samantād draṣṭuṃ śīla yasyāsau samantadarśī <|> samantabhadrajñānalābhāt | ata eva bha[ms-c 75 – img 132]gavān samantaspharaṇaṃtviṭ |

de la kun du lta ba ni kun nas lta ba'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de kun du lta ba ste/ kun du bzang po'i ye shes brnyes pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na bcom ldan 'das kun [f. 83r]@#/ /du spro ba mkhyen pa'o/ /


prāmodya iti | arthadharmapratisaṃvittvāt |  

mchog tu dga' ni don dang chos so so yang dag par rig pa'i phyir ro/ /


tejomālīti | tejasāṃ raśmīnāṃ mālā paṃktiḥ | tejo mālā sā vidyate uasya sa tejomālī | 

gzi brjid phung po ni brjid ni 'od do/ /phung po ni phreng ba'o/ gzi brjid phung po gang dang ldan pa de gzi brjid phung po'o/ /


sudarśana i[$2]ti | sobhanaṃ darśanaṃ jñānaṃ yasya sa sudarśanaḥ | śobhanam i○ti yuktiyuktvāt | 

blta na sdug ni ye shes mdzes pa dang gang ldan pa de blta na sdug ste/ sdu gu ma zhes pa ni rig pa dang gang ldan pa de nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


śrīvatsaḥ suprabho dīptrr bhā bhāsvarakaradyutir iti ||

'od bzangs 'bar ba dpal gyi be'u/ /lag pa 'od 'bar snang ba po/ /zhes pa ni/


tatra śrīvatsa iti | [$3] sarvatathāgatānāṃ hṛdaye śīvatsākāraṃ sarvaśrāvakādya○sādhāraṇaṃ sarvajñabījaprarohabhūtaṃ sakalajagadutpattikāraṇaṃ tāthāgatalakṣaṇam asti | ta[$4]c cāsādhāraṇatvāt | bhagavān sarvatathāgajñānasattva eva ta○ddhṛdaye vihāritvāt ||

suprabha iti | sobhanā prabhā suprabhā maṇḍalayogena vyavasthitatvāt [$5] |

dīptir iti | aśeṣānavaśeṣalokadhātu avabhā○sanatvāt ||

de la 'od bzangs ni 'od bzang pos dkyil 'khor byas nas rnam par gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /

'bar ba ni ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i 'jig rten la cher snang ba'i phyir ro/ /

dpal gyi be'u ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kan na dpal be'u'i gzugs can nyan thos la sogs pa thams cad dang thun mong ma yin pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyis bon las byung ba'i dngos po 'gro ba thams cad skyed par byed pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan yod do/ /de yang thun mong ma yin pa'i phyir na bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' kho na ste/ de rnams kyi thugs kar gnas pa'i phyir ro/ /


bhābhāsvarakaradyutir iti | bhāśabdo raśmiparyāya ākārānto py asti | bhāśvarā[$6]ś ca te karāś ca | bhāsvarakarāḥ krodhadīdhitayaḥ | bhānāṃ ○ bhāsvarakarāḥ | bhābhāsvarakarāḥ | teṣāṃ dyutir bhābhāsvarakaradyutiḥ | tataś ca krodhavineyā[$7]nāṃ satvānāṃ tadākāra | raśmispharaṇamukhena vinayanārthaṃ sa eva bhagavān bhābhāsvarakaradyutir ity ucyate | 

lag pa 'od 'bar snang ba po ni 'od kyi sgra ni gzi brjid kyi rnam grangs te/ mtha' na yang ye ge a yod pa'o/ /lag pa yang de 'od kyang de nyid yin pas lag pa'i 'od rnams ni khro bo 'bar ba'i 'od kyis lag pa 'bar ba ni lag pa'i 'od 'bar ba ste/ de rnams kyi snang ba ni lag pa'i 'od 'bar snang ba po'o/ /de khro bos 'dul ba'i sems can rnams la de'i gzugs 'od zer 'phro ba'i sgo nas 'dul bar byed pa'i don te/ 'di lta bu'i bcom ldan 'das lag pa'i 'od 'bar snang ba po zhes gsungs so/ /


[mahābhiṣagvaraḥ śreṣṭhaḥ śalyahartā niruttaraḥ |
aśeṣabhaiṣajyataruḥ kleśavyādhimahāripuḥ || 103 ||]

[sman pa che mchog gtso bo ste/ /
zug rngu 'byin pa bla na med/ /
sman rnams ma lus ljon pa'i shing/ /
nyon mongs nad kyi dgra che ba/ /]


mahābhiṣag varaḥ śreṣṭhaḥ sallyahartā niruttara i[ms-c f. 75v – img 133]ti ||

sman pa che mchog gtso bo ste/ /zug rdu 'byin pa bla na med/ /ces pa ni 


tatra mahābhiṣag iti | mahāṃś cāsau bhiṣa(k ca)(ms-c pc; kva ms-c ac) mahābhiṣak | mahāvaidyarāja iti ity arthaḥ | rāgādisarvavyādhinirghātanatvāt | 

de la sman pa che ni sman pa yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas sman pa che na ni sman pa'i rgyal po che zhes pa'i don to/ /'dod chags la sogs pa'i nad thams cad 'joms pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


vara iti | ajñānavyādhipraśamanārtham a[$2]viparītopadeśabhaiṣajyadānāt vara ity ucyate |

mchog ni mi shes pa'i nad rab tu zhi bar byed pa'i don du phyin ci ma log pa'i man ngag gi sman gtong bar byed pa'i phyir na/ mchog ces gsungs so/ /


ata ○ eva śreṣṭhaḥ sakalajagadabhyudvaraṇāt | 

de nyid kyi phyir na gtso bo zhes pa ste/ 'gro ba thams cad mngon par 'don pa'i [f. 83v] phyir ro/ /


śalyahartteti śalyānā harttā śalyaharttā | haraṇaśāla[$3]ḥ sarvasatvānāṃ rāgādihṛcchalyāpanayanāt yathābhūta○tatpratipakṣadharmatāprakāśanatayā | ata eva niruttaro sau bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | 

zug rdu 'byin pa ni zug rdu 'byin mkhan no/ /zug rdu 'byin pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa ste/ sems can thams cad kyi 'dod chags la sogs pa'i snying gi zug rdu 'byin par byed ba'i phyir yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du de'i gnyen po chos nyid rab tu bstan pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na bla na med ces te/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /


aśeṣa[$4]bhaiṣajyataruḥ kleśavyādhimahāripur iti ||

sman rnams ma lus ljon pa'i shing*/ /nad do cog gi dgra che pa/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra bhaiṣajya○tarur iti | aśeṣāni niravasēṣabhaiṣajyāni | teṣān taru aśeṣa[$5]bhaiṣajyataruḥ | yato sau bhagavān sakalajagadanugrahā○rtham mahābhaiṣajyarājabhūtatayā pratibhāsate || tathā coktaṃ
	te drumabhonti mahāaṭavīṣṭhiti || 

de la sman rnams ma lus ljon pa'i shing ni ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i sman rnams ni sman rnams so/ /de rnams kyi ljon shing ni sman rnams ma lus ljon pa'i shing ngo*/ /gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das des 'gro ba kun rjes su gzung ba'i don du sman rnams kyi rgyal po chen por gyur par so sor snang ngo*/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	de dag dgon chen ljon pa'i shing du gyur/ /zhes so/ /


kle[$6]śavyādhimahāripur iti | kleśā rāgādayas ta eva vyā○dhayaḥ kleśavyādhayas teṣām mahāripuḥ tatpratipakṣadharmatā prakāśakatvāt | 

nad do cog gi dgra che ba ni 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs pa de nad de yin pas nad do cog go/ /de rnams kyi dgra chen te de'i gnyen po chos nyid rab tu bstan pa'i phyir ro/ /


[trailokyatilakaḥ kāntaḥ śrīmāṃ nakṣatramaṇḍalaḥ |
daśadigvyomaparyanto dharmadhvajamahocchrayaḥ || 104 ||]

[sdug gu 'jig rten gsum gyi mchog /
dpal ldan rgyu skar dkyil 'khor can/ /
phyogs bcu nam mkha'i mthar thug pa/ /
chos kyi rgyal mtshan chen po bsgreng/ /]


trailokyati[$7]lakaḥ kāntaḥ śrīmān nakṣatramaṇḍala iti | 

sdu gu 'jig rten gsum na mdzes/ /dpal ldan rgyu skar dkyil 'khor can/ /zhes pa ni de la 


tatra trailokyatilaka iti sakalajagadasādhāraṇaṃ trailokyamūrddhamakuṭamaṇitilakatvāt | kānta iti gatārthaṃ [f. 77r - img 134] 

sdu gu'i don ni bshad zin to/ /

'jig rten gsum na mdzes ni 'gro ba thams cad dang mi mnyam pas 'jig rten gsum gyi spyi gtsug dbu rgyan thub pa nyid kyi phyir na de de ltar gsungs so/ /


śrīmān iti | tathaiva |

dpal ldan ni de bzhin no/ /


nakṣatramaṇḍala iti nakṣatrāṇāṃ maṇḍalaṃ nakṣatramaṇḍalaṃ | tad evaṃ rūpaṃ yasya bhagavataḥ sa nakṣatramaṇḍalaḥ tatsvabhāvatvāt |

rgyu skar dkyil 'khor can ni/ rgyu skar rnams kyi dkyil 'khor ro/ /de 'dra ba'i gzugs dang gang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das de ni rgyu skar dkyil 'khor can te de'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


daśadigvyomaparyanto dha[$2]rmadhvajamahocchraya iti || 

phyogs bcu can mkha'i mtha' gtugs par/ /chos kyi rgyal mtshan legs par 'dzugs/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra daśāṃ vyoma daśadik○vyoma | tasya paryanto daśadigvyomaparyantaḥ | 

de la phyogs bcu rnams kyi nam mkha' ni phyogs bcu'i nam mkha' ste/ de yongs su mthar thug pa ni phyogs bcu nam mkha' mtha' gtugs pa'o/ /


dharma eva dhvajo dharmadhvajaḥ | mahāṃś cāsāv ucchrayaś ca mahocchrayaḥ tataś cāyam arthaḥ daśadigvyomaparyanteṣu dha○rmadhvajarūpeṇa mahānuccrayo yasyāsau mahat sa tathoktaḥ sarvalokasya puṇyajñānam abhibhūyadhvaja[$4]((syau yo))cchritatvāt || 

chos kyi rgyal mtshan yin pas na chos kyi rgyal mtshan te/ chen po yang de yin la 'dzugs pa yang de yin pas chen po 'dzugs so/ /de'i don ni 'di lta ste/ phyogs bcu nam mkha' mthar thug pa rnams su chos kyi rgyal mtshan chen po bsgreng ba dang gang ldan pa de ni de ltar gsungs te/ 'jig [f. 84r]@#/ /rten thams cad bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rnam par 'phel ba'i rgyal mtshan btsugs pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[jagacchatraikavipulo maitrīkaruṇāmaṇḍalaḥ |
padmanarteśvaraḥ śrīmāṃ ratnacchatro mahāvibhuḥ || 105 ||]

['gro ba'i gdugs gcig yangs pa ste/ /
byams dang snying rje'i dkyil 'khor can/ /
dpal ldan pad+ma gar dbang phyug /
khyab bdag chen po rin chen gdugs/ /]


jagacchratraikavipulo maitrīkaruṇama○ṇdala iti || 

gro ba'i gdugs gcig yangs pa ste/ byams dang snying rje'i dkyil 'khor can/ /zhes pa ni


tatra jagacchratraikavipula iti | jagatāṃ cchatraṃ jagacchatraṃ | eko 'dvitrīyaḥ | vipu[$5]laṃ vistīrṇṇaṃ yata sa bhagavān jagac catrekavipulaḥ | sarva○kleśatāpāpaharaṇāt | 

de la 'gro ba'i gdugs gcig yangs pa ste ni 'gro ba rnams la gdugs ni 'gro ba'i gdugs te/ gcig pu ni gnyis su med pa'o/ /yangs pa ste rgya che ba gang yin pa ste/ bcom ldan 'das 'gro ba'i gdugs gcig yangs pa ste/ nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba thams cad 'joms pa'i phyir ro/ /


maitrīkaruṇamaṇḍala iti | maitrī ca karuṇā ca maitrīka(ru)(ms-c pc marginal)ṇā tayo[$6]r maṇḍalaḥ | tatsārādānāt | 

byams dang snying rje'i dkyil 'khor can ni byams dang snying rje ste/ de rnams kyi dkyil 'khor ni de'i snying po len pa'i phyir ro/ /


padmanarteśvaraḥ śrīmān ratna○cchatro mahāvibhur iti ||

dpal ldan pad+ma gar gyi bdag /khyab bdag chen po rin chen gdugs/ /zhes pa 


tatra padmanarteśvara iti | pratītasamādhiḥ sa ca bhagavān ||

de la dpal ldan gyi don ni bshad zin to/ /pad+ma gar gyi bdag ni ting nge 'dzin rtogs pa ste/ de yang bcom ldan 'das so/ /


śrīmān i[$7]ti | gatārthaṃ | 

ratnacchatra iti | sarvaratnamayatvāt |

mahāvibhur iti mahāṃś cāsau vibuś ca mahāvibhuḥ | sarvabhāvasvabhāvatvāt | 

khyab bdag chen po ni khyab bdag kyang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas khyab bdag chen po ste/ dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

rin chen gdugs ni rin chen thams cad kyi dam tshig nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[sarvabuddhamahārājā sarvabuddhātmabhāvadhṛk |
sarvabuddhamahāyogaḥ sarvabuddhaikaśāsanaḥ || 106 ||]

[sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal po che/ /
sangs rgyas kun bdag dngos po 'dzin/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi rnal 'byor che/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi bstan pa gcig /]

sarvabuddhamahārājaḥ sarvabuddhātmabhā[ms-c f. 77 - img. 135]vadhṛg iti |

sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal po che/ /sangs rgyas kun bdag ngo bo 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni 


sarvabuddhamahārāja iti | mahāṃś cāsau rājā ca mahārājaḥ sarvabuddhānāṃ trydhvavarttināṃ mahārājaḥ sarvabuddhamahārājo bodhicittasvabhāvatvāt || 

de la sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal po che ni rgyal po yang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas rgyal po che'o/ /dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rgyal po chen po ni sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal po che ste/ byang chub kyi sems rdo rje'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvabuddhātmabhāva[$2]dhṛg iti | sarvabuddhā(nām ā)(ms-c pc - marginal)tmā sarvabuddhātmā | sarvadharmaśūnyatā ta○syābhāvaḥ sattā | tan dhārayatīti | sarvabuddhātmabhāvadhṛk || 

sangs rgyas kun bdag ngo po 'chang ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag nyid ni sangs rgyas kun bdag ste/ chos thams cad stong pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de'i ngo bo ni yod pa'o/ /de 'dzin pas nas na sangs rgyas kun bdag ngo bo 'chang ngo*/ /


sarvabuddhamahāyogaḥ sarvabuddhekaśā[$3]sana iti |

sangs rgyas kun gyi rnal 'byor che/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi bstan pa gcig/ /ces pa ni


tatra sarvabuddhamahāyoga iti | mahāś cāsau ○ yogaś ca mahāyogaḥ sarvabuddhānāṃ mahāyogaḥ sarvabuddhamahāyogaḥ | tathā hi 
	mahāyogo hi bha[$4]gavān vajrasattvas tathāgata iti | 
sarvatathāgatahṛdaya○vihāritvāt | sa tathoktaḥ |

de la sangs rgyas kun gyi rnal 'byor che ni rnal 'byor che ni rnal 'byor yang de yin la chen po yang de yin pas rnal 'byor che'o/ /sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rnal 'byor chen po ni sangs rgyas kun gyi rnal 'byor che ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kar gnas pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'di lta ste/ yang gsungs pa/ 
	rnal 'byor chen po bcom ldan 'das/ /
	rdo rje sems [f. 84v]dpa' de bzhin gshegs/ /
zhes so/ /de de ltar gsungs so/ /


sarvabuddhekaśāsana iti | sarvabuddhānāṃ tryadhvavarttināṃ eka śāsanaṃ yā[$5]naṃ yasya sa sarvabuddhaikaśāsanaḥ | tathā hi || 
	ekam eva yānaṃ ud uta mahāyānam
iti vacanāt ||

sangs rgyas kun gyi bstan pa gcig ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bstan pa gcig ste/ theg pa chen po gang yin pa de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi bstan pa gcig go/ /de ltar theg pa ni gcig kho na ste/ 'di ltar theg pa chen po zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro/ /


[vajraratnābhiṣekaśrīḥ sarvaratnādhipeśvaraḥ |
sarvalokeśvarapatiḥ sarvavajradharādhipaḥ || 107 ||]

[rdo rje rin chen dbang bskur dpal/ /
rin chen kun bdag dbang phyug ste/ /
'jig rten dbang phyug kun gyi bdag/
rdo rje kun 'chang mnga' bdag ste/ /]


vajraratnābhiṣekaśrīḥ sarvaratnādhipeśvaraḥ
sarvaloke[$6]śvarapatiḥ sarvavajradharādhipaḥ
sarvabuddhamahācitta○ iti ||

rdo rje rin chen dbang bskur dpal/ /rin chen kun bdag dbang phug ste/ 'jig rten kun gyi dbang phyug rje/ /rdo rje 'chang ba kun gyi bdag/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs che ba/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra vajraratna ity akṣobhyaḥ tasyābhiṣekaśrīḥ satvavajrī | 

de la rdo rje rin che ni mi bskyod pa'o/ /de bzhin du dbang bskur dpal ni rdo rje sems ma'o/ /


sarvaratnādhipeśvara iti [$7] sarvaratno ratnasambhavas tasyādhipeśvara iti ratnavajrī |

rin chen kun bdag dbang phyug ste ni rin chen kun ni rin chen 'byung ldan no/ /de'i bdag po dang dbang phyug ni rin chen rdo rje ma'o/ /


sarvalokeśvarapatir iti | sarvalokeśvaro 'mitābhas tasyapatir iti | dharmavajrī | 

'jig rten kun gyi dbang phyug ni snang ba mtha' yas so/ /de'i rje bo ni chos kyi rdo rje ma'o/ /


sarvavajradharādhipa [ms-c f. 78 missing]

rdo rje 'chang ba kun ni don yod grub pa'o/ /de'i bdag ni las kyi rdo rje ma'o/ /

[sarvabuddhamahācittaḥ sarvabuddhamanogatiḥ |
sarvabuddhamahākāyaḥ sarvabuddhasarasvatiḥ || 108 ||]

[sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs che ba/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gnas/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi sku che ba/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi mtsho dang ldan/ /]


sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs che ba ni sangs rgyas kun ni rnam par snang mdzad do/ /de'i thugs che ba ni rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o/ /de yang don 'di ltar 'gyur te/ rdo rje rin chen la sogs pa de bzhin gshegs pa lnga dang gang 'brel pa de rnams kyi rigs kyi yum lnga gang yin pa de'i rang bzhin bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal te/ rdo rje dang*/ rin po che dang*/ pad+ma dang*/ sna tshogs rdo rje dang*/ 'khor lo rnams thob pa'i phyir ro/ /

sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gnas/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi sku che ba/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yang yin/ /zhes pa ni 

de la sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gnas ni thugs kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

sangs rgyas kun gyi sku che ba ni sku'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yang yin ni/ gsung gi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud las gsungs pa/
	de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje zhes so/ /
de yang bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa'o/ /


[vajrasūryo mahāloko vajrendruvimalaprabhaḥ |
virāgādimahārāgo viśvavarṇojjvalaprabhaḥ || 109 ||]

[rdo rje nyi ma snang ba che/ /
rdo rje zla ba dri med 'od/ /
chags bral dang po chags pa che/ /
kha dog sna tshogs 'bar ba'i 'od/ /]

rdo rje nyi ma snang ba che/ /rdo rje zla ba dri med 'od/ /ces pa ni 


de la rdo rje nyi ma snang ba che ni rdo rje nyi ma ni ye shes kyi snang ba chen pos khams gsum pa [f. 85r]@#/ /thams cad cher snang bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir dal de skad cas gsungs so/ /

rdo rje zla ba dri med 'od/ /ces pa ni rdo rje zla ba ni ye shes zla ba ste/ de'i dri ma med pa ni nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi bag chags kyi skyon thams cad dang bral ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'od ni gsal ba ste grangs med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams snang bar byed pa dang gang ldan pa de la de ltar gsungs so/ /chog de gnyis 'di ltar pa stan par 'gyur te/ sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa'i rigs kyi bu la sogs par rang gi snying gar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ram zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan par byas te/ de'i steng du yi ge a bsams nas ming gi don gzhan dang gzhan so so gang yang rung ba don mngon du byas te 'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa bklag par bya'o zhes man ngag tu'o/ /


chags bral la sogs chags pa che/ /kha dog sna tshogs 'bar ba'i 'od/ /ces pa la/ 

de la chags bral la sogs chags pa che/ /zhes pa ni/ des ni rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi rang bzhin phye ba gsungs te/ 'dod chags dang 'dod chags dang bral ba la zhugs pa ni pha rol tu phyin pa la spyod pa dang*/ sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa rnams kyi de'i rang bzhin med pa de kho na la bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[ms-c f. 79r - img. 137]... dibhedena daśabalavaiśārdyādi buddhadharmabhedena ca || nānābhāṣyabhir nānāmukhair nānānidānair nānāprasthānair nānāyānair nānāphalādhigamais tasmin naiva kṣaṇe eke nadeśanā[$2]jñānena dharmapraṃkāśapatītyata āha | 

- saṅgānaṃ -- noted in margin for line 2
viśvavarṇājvala○prabha iti 

kha dog sna tshogs 'bar ba'i 'od/ /ces pa la kha dog sna chogs ni kha dog sna tshogs pa ste/ de'i 'bar ba'i 'od ni mun pa thams cad rnam par 'joms shing gsal ba gang la yod pa de la de skad ces bya'o/ /de ltar yang 'dir bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal de nyid kyis 'od sna tshogs pa'i sgo rnams kyis sna tshogs pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams na gnas pa'i gdul bya sna tshogs pa'i rigs dang*/ bsam pa dang*/ spyod dang*/ mos pa dang*/ dbang po rnams skad cig gis dus gcig kho nar mi rtag pa dag sdug bsngal dang*/ mi skye ba dang*/ mi 'gag pa la sogs pa zhi ba dang rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs pa'i dbye ba dang*/ phung po dang khams dang*/ skye mched dang*/ rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba dang*/ 'phags pa'i bden pa la sogs par phye ba dang*/ dran pa nye bar gzhag pa nas yang dag par spong ba dang*/ rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang*/ dpang [f. 85v] po la sogs pa'i dbyibs dang*/ stobs bcu dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos rnams kyi dbye bas dang*/ skad sna tshogs dang sgo sna tshogs dang*/ mngon par brjod pa sna tshogs pa dang*/ cho 'phrul sna tshogs dang*/ 'jug pa sna tshogs dang*/ theg pa sna tshogs dang*/ 'bras bu rtogs pa sna tshogs rnams kyis skad cig ma de nyid kho na la bstan pa'i mkhyen pas chos rab tu bstan par mdzad pas na/ kha dog sna tshogs 'bar ba'i 'od/ /ces bya ba 'di gsungs so/ /


asya <nā>nāmamantrapadasya ca vyākhyānaṃ gurupadeṇāt bhagavati sarvatathāgatajñā[$3]nasatveṣojanīyam iti | 

mtshan gyi sngags kyi tshig 'di yang bla mas bstan pa'i man ngag gang las bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' la sbyar bar bya'o zhes so/ /


[saṃbuddhavajraparyaṅko buddhasaṃgītidharmadhṛk |
buddhapadmodbhavaḥ śrīmāṃ sarvajñajñānakośadhṛk || 110 ||]

[rdo rje skyil krung rdzogs sangs rgyas/ /
sangs rgyas brjod pa'i chos 'dzin pa/ /
dpal [6v] ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes/ /
kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin pa/ /]


sambuddhavajraparyaṅko buddhasa○ṅgītidharmadhṛg iti || 

rdo rje skyil krung rdzogs sangs rgyas/ /sangs rgyas 'gro ba'i chos 'dzin pa/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra sambuddhavajraparyaṅka iti | sambuddhasya bhagavataḥ śākyamuner vajrapa[$4]ryaṅkaḥ sambuddhavajraparyaṅkaḥ | yenāsau bhagavān caturo ○ mārān parājitya kṣayānutpādajñānaṃ sākṣātkṛatavān | sa ca bhagavān eva || 

de la rdo rje skyil krung rdzogs sangs rgyas ni bcom ldan 'das rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas shrkya thub pa'i rdo rje skyil krung ni rdo rje skyil krung rdzogs sangs rgyas zhes so/ /bcom ldan 'das gang yin pa 'dis bdud bzhi las mchog tu rgyal bas na zad pa dang mi skye ba mkhyen pa mngon du byed pa dang ldan pa'i phyir de yang bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


buddhasaṅgītidharmadhṛ[$5]g iti | (saṅgānaṃ)(ms-c pc - marginal) saṅgītiḥ | buddhānāṃ saṅgītir buddhasaṅgīti || ta○thā hi saṅgāyiṣyāmo na vivadiṣyāma iti vacanāt 
	% see Kāṣyapaparivartasūtra
saiva dharmas tān dhārayatīti buddhasaṅgī[$6]tidharmadhṛg iti | sa eva bhagavān || 

sangs rgyas 'gro ba'i chos 'dzin pa ni 'gro bar mdzad pas na 'gro ba ste/ sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'gro ba ni sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'gro ba'o/ /de ltar yang 'gro bar bya zhing bdag gis brtsad par bya'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi chos te de 'dzin pas na sangs rgyas 'gro ba'i chos 'dzin te de yang bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


buddhapadmodbhavaḥ śrī○mān sarvajñajñānakośadhṛg iti ||

dpal ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes/ /kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin pa/ /zhes pa na


tatra buddhapadmodbhava iti | buddhā eva padmā buddhapadmāḥ kleśavāśa[$7]nāmalair anupaliptatvāt | tebhya udbhavatīti buddhapadmodbhavaḥ sa eva bhagavān || 

de la dpal ldan ni bshad zin to/ /sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes ni sangs rgyas nyid pad+ma bas sangs rgyas pad+ma rnams te/ nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma rnams kyis nye bar ma gos pa'i phyir ro/ /de las byung bas na sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes so/ /de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


śrīmān iti gatārthaḥ ||

sarvajñajñānakośadhrg iti | sarvajñasya jñānaṃ sarvajñajñānaṃ | tad eva [ms-c f. 79v - img 138] kośo bhāṇḍāgāran taddhārayatīti sarvajñajñānakośadhṛk ||

kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin pa ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes ni kun mkhyen ye shes so/ /de nyid mdzod dang snod khyim ste/ de 'chang bas na kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin no/ /


[viśvamāyādharo rājā buddhavidyādharo mahān |
vajratīkṣṇo mahākhaḍgo viśuddhaḥ paramākṣaraḥ || 111 ||]

[rgyal po sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs 'chang/ /
che ba sangs rgyas rig pa 'chang/ /
rdo rje rnon po ral gri che/ /
rnam par dag pa 'gyur med mchog /]


viśvamāyādharo rājā buddhavidyādharo mahān iti ||

rgyal po sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs 'chang*/ /che ba sangs rgyas rig sngags 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra viśvamāyādhara iti | viśvamāyā nānāprakāraṃ nirmāṇam tān dhāra[$2]yatīti viśvamāyādharaḥ ||

rājeti | daśakuśalakarmapatha○deśanā subhāṣitair lokaṃ rañjayatīti rāja sa eva ||

de la rgyal po ni [f. 86r]@#/ /dge ba bcu'i las kyi las bstan cing legs par bshad pa dag gis 'jig rten la bsgo bar byed pas na rgyal po ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /

sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs 'chang ni sgyur 'phrul sna tshogs 'chang ni sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs pa ste/ sprul pa rnam pa sna tshogs pa'o/ /de 'dzin pas na sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs 'chang ngo*/ /


buddhavidyādhara iti | buddhānāṃ vidyā buddhavidyā[$3]ś catasro dhāraṇyaḥ | dharmārthamantrakṣāntilakṣaṇāḥ | tān dhāra○yatīti buddhavidyādharo sau 

che ba sangs rgyas rig sngags 'chang*/ / zhes pa la sangs rgyas rnams kyi rig sngags ni sangs rgyas rig sngags te/ sangs rgyas rig sngags ni gzungs bzhi ste/ chos dang don dang sngags dang bzod pa'i mtshan nyid rnams so/ /de rnams 'dzin pas ni 'di sangs rgyas rig 
sngags 'chang ngo*/ /

mahān iti | sarvagatatvāt || 

de nyid che ba zhes pa ste/ /kun du 'gro ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


vajratīkṣṇo mahākhaḍgo viśuddhaḥ paramā[$4]kṣara iti || 

rdo rje rnon po ral gri che/ /yi ge mchog ste rnam par dag /ces pa ni


tatra vajratīkṣṇa iti mahāmudrārūpeṇa || 

de la rdo rje rnon po ni phyag rgya chen po'i ngo bos so/ /


ma○hākhaḍga iti | karmamudrāsvabhāvena ||

ral gri che ni las kyi phyag rgya'i rang bzhin no/ /


viśuddha iti | prajñāpāramitāpustakam sa ca samayamu[$5]drādvāreṇa ||

rnam par dag pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i glegs bam ste/ de yang dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i sgo nas so/ /


paramākṣara iti | dharmamudrāmukhena | tata○ś cāyaṃ bhagavān ādibuddha eva | caturmudrāmudrito vajratīkṣṇa ity ucyate || 

yi ge mchog ni chos kyi phyag rgya'i sgo nas so/ /de yang bcom ldan 'das dang po'i sangs rgyas de kho na phyag rgya bzhis rgyas btab pas rdo rje rnon po zhes gsungs so/ /


[duḥkhacchedamahāyāno vajradharmamahāyudhaḥ |
jinajig vajragāmbhīryo vajrabuddhir yathārthavit || 112 ||]

[theg pa chen po sdug bsngal gcod/ /
mtshon cha chen po rdo rje chos/ /
rdo rje zab mo dzin dzika /
rdo rje blo gros don bzhin rig /]


duḥkhacchedamahāyāna[$6]vajradharmamahāyudha iti ||

theg pa chen po sdug bsngal gcod/ /mtshon cha chen po rdo rje chos/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra duḥkhaṃ pañcopādānaskaṃ○dhāḥ | eteṣāṃ cchedaḥ dukhacchedaḥ sa eva mahāyānaṃ mārgastyatvāt | tasya vajradharmo jñānadharma[$7]ḥ sa eva dharmo vipakṣacchedanāt mahadāyudhaṃ yasya sa duḥkhacchedamahāyānavajradharmamahāyudha iti bhagavānt || 

de la sdug bsngal ni nye par len pa'i phung po rnams te/ de rnams gcod pas na sdug bsngal gcod pa'o/ /de nyid theg pa chen po ste/ lam gyi bden pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de'i rdo rje chos ni ye shes kyi chos te/ chos de mi mthun pa'i phyogs gcod pa'i phyir mtshon cha chen pa'o/ /de dang gang ldan pa de ni/ theg pa chen po sdug bsngal gcod/ /mtshon cha chen po rdo rje chos te/ bcom ldan 'das so/ /


jinajigvajragāmbhīryo vajrabuddhir yathārthavit || 

rdo rje zab mo dzin dzika /rdo rje blo gros don bzhin rig /ces pa ni 


tatra jina[ms-c f. 80 – missing] [ms-b p. 17]g iti jinā akṣobhyādayas tathāgatās tān ((jāya))ty abhibhavaty ādhipatyeneti jinajig bhagavān mahāvairocanaḥ sa eva bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ || 

de la rdo rje zab mo rdo rje ste/ ye shes zab mo 'di rdo rje zab mo'o/ /yang na zab mo ni gzung 'dzin la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba shes rab kyi rang bzhin dang gang ldan pa de la de ltar gsungs so/ /

dzin ni de bzhin gshegs pa mi bskyod pa la sogs pa rnams so/ /de rnams las rgyal ba dang zil gyis gnon pa la bdag po yin pas na dzin dzika ste/ bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad de/ [f. 86v] de yang bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal nyid do/ /




rdo rje blo gros ni rdo rje 'dra ba'i mi phyed pa'i blo gros dang gang ldan pa de rdo rje blo gros te/ gzung 'dzin la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog pas bsdus pa thams cad kyis mi phyed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

don bzhin rig ni ji ltar gnas pa'i don rnam par rig pas don bzhin rig go/ /


[sarvapāramitāpūrī sarvabhūmivibhūṣaṇaḥ |
viśuddhadharmanairātmyaṃ samyagjñānenduhṛtprabhaḥ || 113 ||]

[pha rol phyin pa kun rdzogs pa/ /
sa rnams thams cad rnam par brgyan/ /
rnam par dag pa bdag med chos/ /
yang dag ye shes zla 'od bzang/ /]

pha rol phyin pa kun rdzogs pa/ /sa rnams kun gyi rgyan dang ldan/ /zhes pa la 

pha rol phyin pa kun rdzogs pa ni pha rol phyin pa kun ni sbyin pa la sogs pa rnams so/ /de rnams rdzogs pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de la de ltar gsungs so/ /

sa rnams kun gyi rgyan dang ldan ni sa rnams kun ni rab tu dga' ba la sogs pa rnams so/ /de nyid kyi rgyan te dkyil 'khor gang yin pa de la de ltar gsungs so/ /


rnam par dag pa chos bdag med/ /yang dag ye shes zla 'od bzang*/ /zhes pa ni

da la rnam par dag pa'i chos ni rnam par dag pa so sor rtog pa'i mtshan nyid grub pa ste/ bdag med pa ni snang ba med par byed pa'o/ /

yang dag pa'i ye shes de nyid zla ba ste/ kun du bzang po'i sems bskyed pa ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku nyid kyi phyir te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /'od bzang ba ni zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i ye shes te de dang gang ldan pa de la de ltar ro/ /

	% It seems like Vilāsavajra reads three words here. Not so sure. Ms is corrupt. 

[māyājālamahodyogaḥ sarvatantrādhipaḥ paraḥ |
aśeṣavajraparyaṅko niḥśeṣajñānakāyadhṛk || 114 ||]

[sgyu 'phrul dra ba rnal 'byor che/ /
rgyud kun gyi ni bdag po mchog /
ma lus rdo rje skyil krung ste/ /
ye shes sku rnams ma lus 'chang/ /]


brtson chen sgyu 'phrul dra ba ste/ rgyud kun gyi ni bdag po mchog /zhes pa ni 

de la/ brtson chen sgyu 'phrul dra ba ste/ /zhes pa ni/ sgyu 'phrul dra ba ni sprul pa'i tshogs te/ brtson chen dang gang ldan pa de la de ltar ro/ /

rgyud kun gyi ni bdag po ni rgyud kun ni rnal 'byor gyi rgyud la sogs pa'i bdag po ni gtso bo ste/ de'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

mchog ni bshad zin to/ /

rdo rje gdan ni ma lus ldan/ /ye shes sku rnams ma lus 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni 

ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rang bzhin gyi skyil mo krung dang gang ldan pa de ni rdo rje gdan ni ma lus ldan no/ /

de nyid kyi phyir/ ye shes sku rnams ma lus 'chang*/ /zhes pa ste/ ye shes lnga po ma lus pa'i sku rnams ma lus 'chang do/ /


[samantabhadraḥ sumatiḥ kṣitigarbho jagaddhṛtiḥ |
sarvabuddhamahāgarbho viśvanirmāṇacakradhṛk || 115 ||]

[kun tu bzang po blo gros bzang/ /
sa yi snying po 'gro ba 'dzin/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po che/ /
sna tshogs sprul pa'i 'khor lo 'chang/ /]

kun du bzang po blo gros bzang*/ /sa yi mngal te 'gro ba 'dzin/ /zhes pa ni 

de la kun du bzang po ni kun las bzang zhing dge ba gang yin [f. 87r]@#/ /pa de ni kun du bzang po ste/ byang chub kyi sems rdo rje'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

blo gros bzang ni legs pa'i blo gros ni blo gros bzang po ste/ rtog pa'i dra ba thams cad med pa'i phyir ro/ /

[ms-c f. 81r img 140] ... tigarbhaḥ |

sa'i mngal zhes pa ni/ de la sa'i khams te snod kyi 'jig rten no/ /de'i mngal ni skyed par byed pa gang yin pa de sa'i mngal lo/ /


jagaddhṛtir iti | jagad iti satvalokaḥ | tasya dhṛtir dhāraṇaṃ | jagaddhṭiḥ sakalajagadādhāra ity arthaḥ | tasya (thi)(ms-c; sthi em.)racalabhāvasvabhāvatvāt | 

'gro ba 'dzin ni 'gro ba ni sems can gyi 'jig rten no/ /de 'dzin pa ni 'dzin par byed pas na 'gro ba 'dzin te 'gro ba kun gyi rten zhes pa'i don to/ /tshig de gnyis kyis g.yo pa dang mi g.yo ba'i dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin de yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


sarvabuddhamahāgarbho viśvani[$2]rmāṇacakradhṛg iti | 

sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po che/ /sprul pa'i 'khor lo sna tshogs 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra sarvabuddhamahāgarbha iti | sarva○tathāgatānāṃ tryadhvavarttināṃ utpattihetutvāt | yasmād (sau)(ms-c pc - marginal)bhagavān bodhicittavajrātmakas tasmāt sarva[$3]buddhamahāgarbha ity ucyate || 

de la sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po che ni dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bskyed pa'i rgyu nyid kyi phyir te/ gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das de byang chub kyi sems rdo rje'i bdag nyid yin pa de'i phyir/ sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po che/ /zhes gsungs so/ /


ata eva viśvanirmāṇaca○kradhṛg iti | viśvaṃ nānāprakāraṃ laukikaloko tṛraṭevatā sa darśanātmakaṃ nirmāṇaviśvanirmā[$4]ṇaṃ | tasya cakraṃ viśvanirmāṇacakraṃ maṇḍalan tad dhārayatīti ○ viśvanirmāṇacakradhṛk || 

de nyid kyi phyir na/ sprul pa'i 'khor lo sna tshogs 'chang*/ /zhes pa sna tshogs ni rnam par sna tshogs pa'o/ /'jig rten dang 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta rnams yang dag par ston pa'i bdag nyid kyi sprul pa ni sna tshogs sprul pa'i/ /de'i 'khor lo ni sprul pa'i 'khor lo ste dkyil 'khor ro/ /de 'dzin pas na sprul pa'i 'khor lo sna tshogs 'chang ngo*/ /


[sarvabhāvasvabhāvāgryaḥ sarvabhāvasvabhāvadhṛk |
anutpādadharmā viśvārthaḥ sarvadharmasvabhāvadhṛk || 116 ||]

[dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin mchog /
dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin 'dzin/ /
skye med chos te sna tshogs don/ /
chos kun ngo bo nyid 'chang ba/ /]


sarvabhāvasvabhāvāgryaḥ sarvabhāvasvabhāvadhṛg (itiḥ)(ms-c; iti em.) || 

dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin mchog /dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin 'dzin/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra sarvabhāvasva[$5]bhāvāgrya iti | sarve ca (te)(ms-c pc - marginal) bhāvāś ca sarvabhāvāḥ | sthiracalāda○yaḥ | teṣāṃ svabhāvaḥ sarvabhāvasvabhāvaḥ sarvabhāvsvabhāvaś cāsāv agryaś ca sarvabhāvasvabhāvāgryaḥ [$6] kuta iti cet | bhūtakoṭirūpatāpariśuddhatathāgatajñā○nakāyasvabhāvatvāt tasya bhagavataḥ | 

de la dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin mchog ni dngos po yang de yin la kun yang de yin pas dngos po kun ni g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba dang mi g.yo la sogs pa rnams so/ /de rnams kyi rang bzhin ni dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin te/ dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin yang de yin la mchog kyang de nyid yin pas dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin mchog go/ /de ji ltar zhe na/ bcom ldan 'das de'i yang dag pa'i mtha'i de bzhin nyid kyi yongs su dag pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes kyi sku'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvabhāvasvabhāvadhṛg iti | ata eva sarvabhāvasvabhāvaṃ sa[$7]rvadharmanairātmyam vibhartti dhārayatī sarvabhāvasvabhāvadhṛk || sarvākāramahāśūnyatāsvabhāvatvāt || 

dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin 'dzin ni de nyid kyi phyir na dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin te/ chos thams cad bdag med par 'jug pa 'dzin pas na dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin 'dzin te/ rnam pa thams cad du chen po stong pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


anutpādadharmā viśvārthaḥ sarvadharmasvabhāvadhṛg iti | 

skye med chos de sna tshogs [f. 87v] don/ /chos kun ngo bo nyid 'chang ba/ /zhes pa ni


tatrānutpādadharmeti | anutpādo nisvabhāvo dharmo yasyāsāv anutpādadharmā paramārthataḥ pratītyasamutpannatvāt || 

de la skye med chos ni skye ba med cing rang bzhin med pa'i chos dang gang ldan pa de skye med chos te/ rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba nyid ni don dam par skye ba med pa'i phyir ro/ /


viśvārtha iti | saṃvṛttyā sakalajagadanu(gra)(ms-c pc; grā ms-c ac)hārthasmpādakatvāt || 

sna tshogs don ni kun rdzob tu 'gro ba thams cad rjes su 'dzin pa'i don byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvadharmasvabhā[$2]vadhṛg iti | tatra sarvadharmāḥ katame | yad uta skandhadhātvāyata○napratītyasamutpā((deḥ)) pāramitābhūmiśūnyatābodhipakṣasatyadhyānāpramāṇārūpyasamāpattivi[$3]mokṣamukhābhijñānasamādhidhāraṇībalavaiśāradyapratisaṃvi○tmahāmaitrīmahākaruṇāveṇikabuddhadharmaśrīmaṇyaphalasarvākārajñatātathatābhūtakoṭyānimi[$4]ttadharmadhātavaś ceti sarvadharmās teṣāṃ svabhāvaḥ sarvadharmasva○bhāvaḥ | sa ca yathābhūtaparijñānaṃ tad dhārayatīti sarvadharmasvabhāvadhṛk || tathā coktaṃ jñānapādaiḥ
	sambhodhicittamutpādya mahāmaitrīprayogataḥ |
	sarvadharmā nirātmāna iti jñātvā vimucyata iti ||
[Jñānapāḍa, Mahāyānalakṣaṇasamuccaya, opening verse] - ed reads jñātvā 'dhimucyate - incomprehensible. Maybe jñānam vidhīyate? Or jñātvā taducyate ? 


chos kun ngo bo nyid 'chang ba ni de la chos kun gang zhe na/ 'di lta ste/ phung po dang*/ khams dang*/ skye mched dang*/ rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba dang*/ pha rol tu phyin pa dang*/ sa dang*/ stong pa nyid dang*/ byang chub kyi phyogs dang*/ bden pa dang*/ bsam gtan dang*/ tshad med pa dang*/ gzugs med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang*/ rnam par thar pa dang*/ mngon par shes pa dang*/ ting nge 'dzin dang*/ gzungs kyi sgo dang*/ stobs dang*/ mi 'jigs pa dang*/ so so yang dag par rig pa dang*/ byams pa chen po dang*/ snying rje chen po dang*/ snying rje chen po dang*/ sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa dang*/ dge sbyong gi 'bras bu dang*/ rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang*/ de bzhin nyid dang*/ yang dag pa'i mtha' dang*/ mtshan ma med pa dang*/ don dam pa dang*/ chos kyi dbyings zhes bya ba chos de rnams kyi rang bzhin ni chos kun rang bzhin te/ de yang ji lta ba bzhin du yongs su shes nas de 'dzin pas na chos kun ngo bo nyid 'chang ngo*/ /de ltar yang ye shes zhabs kyi gsungs pa/ /
	yang dag byang chub sems bskyed nas/ /
	byams pa chen po rab sbyor te/ /
	chos rnams thams cad bdag med pa/ /
	de ltar shes na rnam par grol/ /
zhes so/ /


ekakṣaṇamahāprājñaḥ sarvadharmāvabodhadhṛg iti || 

shes rab chen po'i skad cig la/ /chos kun mngon par rtogs pa 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni


e[$6]kaś cāsau kṣaṇaś ca ekakṣaṇaḥ | mahāṃś cāsau prājñaś ca mahāprā○jña<śca> sarvadharmavivekātmakaḥ | tataś cāyam arthaḥ sampadyate | ekenaiva kṣaṇena mahāprājñatayā ya[$7]thoktasarvadharmāvabodhanatayā | ekakṣaṇamahāprājñasarvadharmāvabodha | s tan dhārayatīti ekakṣaṇamahāprājñasarvadharmāvabodhadhṛk || 

de la shes thab kyang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas shes rab chen po ste/ chos thams cad rnam par 'byed pa'i bdag nyid do/ /skad cig kyang de yin la gcig kyang de nyid yin pas skad cig go/ /de bas na de'i don ni 'di ltar 'gyur te/ dus kyi skad cig ma nyid la shes rab chen po nyid kyis ji ltar gsungs pa'i chos thams cad du shes pa'i phyir na/ shes rab chen po'i skad cig la/ /chos kun khong du chung pa'o/ /de 'dzin pas na shes rab chen po'i skad cig la chos kun mngon par rtogs pa 'chang ngo*/ /


sarvadharmābhisamayo bhūtāntamunir agradhīr i[ms-c f. 82r]ti

chos kun mngon par rtogs pa ste/ yang dag [f. 88r]@#/ /mthar thug mchog gi blo/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra sarvadharmābhisamaya iti | sarvadharmāṇām abhisamayaḥ sarvadharmābhisamayaḥ samyagavabodho yasya sa sarvadharmābhisamayaḥ || 

de la chos kun mngon par rtogs pa zhes pa la/ chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin mngon par rtogs pa ni chos kun mngon par rtogs pa ste/ yang dag par thugs su chud pa dang gang ldan pa de ni chos kun mngon par rtogs pa'o/ /


bhūtāntamunir iti | bhūtaṃ satyaṃ tathate[$2]ti yāvat tasyānto bhūtānataḥ sa cāsau muniś ca bhūtāntamuniḥ ○ | ata evāśradhāḥ | bhūtārthabhāvanā prakarṣaparyantagamanāt yogijñānasya || 

yang dag mthar thug ces pa la yang dag pa ni bden pa ste/ de bzhin nyid ces pa'i bar du'o/ /de'i mtha' ni yang dag mtho/ /mthar thug pa yang de yin la yang dag mtha' yang de nyid yin pas yang dag mthar thug go/ /de nyid kyi phyir na mchog gi blo ni rnal 'byor can gyi skye shes te/ yang dag pa'i don bsgoms pas rab kyi mthar phyin pa yin pa'i phyir ro/ /


[stimitaḥ suprasannātmā samyaksaṃbuddhabodhidhṛk |
pratyakṣaḥ sarvabuddhānāṃ jñānārciḥ suprabhāsvaraḥ || 118 ||
pratyavekṣaṇājñānagāthā dvācatvāriṃśat]

[mi g.yo rab tu dang ba'i bdag /
rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas byang chub 'chang/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi mngon sum pa/ /
ye shes me lce 'od rab gsal/ /
so sor gzigs pa'i ye shes kyi tshigs su bcad pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so// //]


stimi(ta)(ms-c pc; ti ms-c ac) suprasannā[$3]tmā samyaksambuddhabodhidhrg iti ||

mi g.yo rab tu dang ba'i bdag /yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni


tatra stimita iti | laya○auddhatyābhāvāt | 

de la mi g.yo ba ni ting nge 'dzin gyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs su song ba'i bying ba dang rgod pa med pa'i phyir ro/ /


ata eva suprasannātmā samādhir iti | (stha)(ms-c; sthi em.)racaladvayābhāvāt |

de nyid kyi phyir na rab tu dang ba'i bdag ces pa ste/ ting nge 'dzin gyi bar chad gnyis med pa'i phyir ro/ /


samyaksambuddhabodhi[$4](.. ..)(ms-c; dhṛgi em.)ti | anuttarasamyaksambbodhidhāraṇatvāt sa bhagavān ○ samyaksambuddhabodhidhṛk ity ucyate || 

yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'chang ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dzin pa'i phyir na bcom ldan 'das de yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'chang zhes gsungs so/ /


pratyakṣas sarvabuddhānāṃ jñānārcciḥ suprabhāsvara iti ||

sangs rgyas kun gyi mngon sum pa/ /ye shes me lce 'od rab gsal/ /zhes pa la/ /


tatra pra[$5](.. ..)(ms-c; tyakṣa em.) iti svasaṃvedyalakṣaṇatvāt | sarvabuddhānāṃ tryadhvartti○nāṃ ||

de la/ sangs rgyas kun gyi mngon sum pa/ /zhes pa ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mngon sum pa ni yang dag par rang gis rig pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


jñānārccir iti | prajñāpradīpaḥ || 

ye shes me lce ni shes rab kyi mar me'o/ /


suprabhāsvara iti | anatilāpyānabhilāpyabuddhakṣetrāva[$6](.. ..)(ms-c; bhāsa em.)tvāt | 

'od rab gsal ni brjod kyis mi lang ba'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing kun du snang bar byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


ata evāsau sarvatathāgatajñānakāyo bhagavā○n jagaddhitasvabhāvenāpi vineyānāṃ satvānāṃ mṛdvamdhyādhimātrendriyāṇām anugrahakāmaḥ | sarvalau[$7](.. ..)(ms-c; kika)lokottarasamādhisandarśanamukhena puṇyajñānasambhārabhumipāramitādikrameṇa kvacid ātmabhāvasandarśanāt kvacit samyaksambuddhabhāvena kvacil laukikalokottarajñā[ms-c f. 82 – img 143]... tmanā kvacid daridrasatvānām anugrahārthaṃ bhadraghaṭādirūpeṇa kvacit mahāvyādhiparipīḍitānāṃ satvānāṃ mahābhaiṣajādirūpeṇetyevam ādibhiḥ sthiracalasarvabhāvasvabhāvai jagadanu[$2]... ārtham anuvidhāya nāmamantrākṣarapadāni pañcasaptabhi○śatadvayāni saṃsphārya 

de nyid kyi phyir na bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku 'gro ba thams cad la phan pa'i rang bzhin gyis dbang po 'ang rab 'bring tha chungs kyi sems can gdul bya rnams la phan 'dogs pas na 'jig rten las 'das pa thams cad kyi ting nge 'dzin bstan pa'i sgo nas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs dang*/ sa dang pha rol tu phyin pa rnams kyi 'bras bu rab tu rdzogs pa'i don du gzugs sna tshogs ston par byed pa yin no/ /de la dbang po rtul po'i sems can 'ga' zhig 'dul ba la tshangs pa'i gzugs kyis dang*/ dbang po [f. 88v]'bring po nyan tshogs dang rang sangs rgyas kyi rigs rnams kha cig la phan 'dogs pa'i don du de'i gzugs kyis kun snang ngo*/ /dbang po rnon po byang chub sems dpa'i rigs rnams la 'ga' zhig tu byang chub sems dpa' dang*/ tshogs dang*/ sa dang*/ pha rol tu phyin pa'i rim pas bdag gi dngos po bstan pas dang*/ 'ga' zhig tu bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo dang*/ 'ga' zhig tu bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo dang*/ 'ga' zhig 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes kyi bdag nyid rnams dang*/ sems can bkres pa rnams kha cig la phan 'dogs pa'i don du bu ma pa bzhad po la sogs pa'i gzugs kyis dang*/ nad chen pos gzir ba'i sems can kha cig la sman chen po la sogs pa'i gzugs kyis dang*/ de la sogs pa rnams kyis g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba la sogs pa'i dngos po thams cad kyis 'gro ba la phan 'dogs pa'i don du rjes su sgrub par byed pa'i sngags kyi yi ge tshig nyis brgya bdun cu rtsa lngar rnam par spros te/ 


tac ca kulabhedena pañcadhā pravibhajya ekaikasmin kule pañca pañcāśan nāmamantrā[#3]... ṇisaṃniyojyai tāni ca nāmamantrākṣarāṇi daśadiga○nantāparyantāni buddhakṣetrāṇi (satvā)(ms-c; gatvā em?) sarvatathāgatakṛtyam anuvidhāya sarvatathāgataparṣadaṃ bodhisa[$4]..(ms-c; tva)((ci))parṣadaṃ cāvabhāsya rāgacaritān satvān svavimokṣa○mukhena saṃśodhya svakulavarṇṇoparañjitāni punar āgatya vajradhātumahāmaṇḍalasya bihis tṛtī[$5]yacakre yathākramato vyavasthitāni paśyet 

de rnams kyi rigs kyi dbye bas rnam pa lngar phye la/ rigs re re la yang mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig lnga bcu rtsa lngar sbyar nas mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge de rnams kyis kyang phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnams su song ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi mdzad pa mthun par bsgrubs nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'khor dang*/ byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi 'khor yang snang bar byas nas 'dod chags la spyod pa'i sems can rnams rang gi rnam par thar pa'i sgo nas dag par byas te/ rang gi rigs kyi kha dog gis nye bar bsgos pa rnams yang phyir log nas rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyi rol 'khor lo gsum pa la ji lta ba'i rim pas rnam par gnas par blta'o/ /


tato mantramu○(khe)(ms-c; khena em.) caryācārī kulaputro vā kulduhitā vā purastātpratipāditaṃ trividharūpam ātmānam ālambyāryanāmasaṅgītiṃ paṭhan yathoktaguṇagaṇānavāpnotī○ty āmnāyaḥ || 

de bas na sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa'i rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mos sngar bstan pa'i gzugs rnam pa gsum du dmigs te/ 'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa bklag go/ /yon tan gyi tshogs thob bo zhes pa na man ngag go/ /

gāthā dvācatvārīśatanāmamantrākṣarāṇi | pañcasaptatiśatadvayasaṅkato pi 275 || [$7] ā((ryanā))masaṅgītiṭikāyāṃ nāmamantrārthāvalokinyāṃ pratyavekṣaṇājñānamukhena stutyadhikāro 'ṣṭamaḥ || || 

tshigs bcad ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis te/ mtshan gyi sngags kyi sgo yi ge'i tshig ni nyis brgya bdun cu rtsa lnga ste grangs so/ /'phags pa mtshan yang [f. 89r]@#/ /dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba las so sor kun du rtog pa'i rim par phye ba ste brgya pa'o// //


