idam idānīṃ samatājñānamukhena bhagavataḥ sarvatathāgata[ms-c f. 83r - img 144].. mañjuśrījñānakāyasya stotraṃ adhikṛtyāha || 

de ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi sgo nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' 'jam dpal ye shes kyi sku'i bstod pa'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ 


[iṣṭārthasādhakaḥ paraḥ sarvāpāyaviśodhakaḥ |
sarvasatvottamo nāthaḥ sarvasatvapramocakaḥ || 119 ||]

['dod pa'i don sgrub dam pa ste/ /
ngan song thams cad rnam sbyong ba/ /
mgon po sems can kun gyi mchog /
sems can thams cad rab grol byed/ /]


iṣṭārthasādhakaḥ paraḥ sarvāpāyaviśodhakaḥ sarvasatvottamo nāthaḥ sarvasatvapramocaka iti ||

'dod pa'i don grub dam pa ste/ ngan song thams cad rnams sbyong ba/ mgon po sems can kun gyi mchog /sems can thams cad rab grol byed/ /ces pa la sogs pa ste/ 


tatra i[$2]... tyarthaḥ | iṣṭaś cāsāv artha○ś ca | iṣṭārthaḥ | tasyasākado niṣpādako tarnasambhavaḥ | mātsaryābhibhūtānāṃ dānaviśuddhimukhena [$3] ... n |

de la 'dod pa'i don grub ni don du gnyer bar bya bas na don te/ 'dod pa yang de yin la don yang de nyid pas 'dod pa'i don te/ de sgrub par byed cing skyed par byed pa ni rin chen 'byung ldan te/ ser snas sdug bsngal ba'i sems can rnams par dag pa'i sbyin pa'i sgo nas yang dag par sbyor bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir na de yang bcom ldan 'das nyid do/ /


ata eva paraḥ striko○ṭipariśuddhadānapravarttakatvāt | 

de nyid kyi phyir na yang dam pa ste/ 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i sbyin pa rab tu 'jug pa'i phyir ro/ /


sarvāpāyaviśodhaka iti | sarvāpāyāḥ strayo narakapreta[$4]... varttinīyakarmasaṃśodha○nena tadapāyadvārāṇāṃ ((pitha))nāt | 

ngan song thams cad rnam sbyong ba/ /zhes pa la/ ngan song thams cad ni dmyal ba dang*/ yi dgas dang*/ byol song rnams so/ //de rnams rnam par sbyong ba ni der 'jug pa'i las yang dag par sbyor bas de dag ngan song las 'don par bsgrub pa'i phyir ro/ /


sa eva sarvasatvottama iti | ata eva sarvasatvānām uttama[$5]... tataś cānāthānāṃ satvānāṃ ○ nātha ity ucyate | 

de nyid kyi phyir na sems can tham las cad kyi mchog ste/ gzhan don bya ba la mngon par brtson pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir yang mgon med pa'i sems can gyi mgon zhes gsungs so/


sarvasatvapramocaka iti | vineyānā gotracaritāśayānuśayādhimuktīndri[$6]...deśapadānamukhena pramokṣaṇatvāt | 

sems can thams cad rab grol byed ni gdul bya'i rigs dang*/ spyod pa dang*/ bag la nyal dang*/ mos pa dang*/ dbang po rnams kyis 'dul ba rnams la nyan thos la sogs pa'i byang chub kyi lam gyi man ngag rab tu sbyin pa'i sgo nas rab tu grol bar byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /



[kleśasaṃgrāmaśūraikaḥ ajñānaripudarpahā |
dhīḥ śṛṅgāradharaḥ śrīmān vīrabībhatsarūpadhṛk || 120 ||]

[nyon mongs g.yul du gcig dpa' ba/ /
mi shes dgra yi dregs pa 'joms/ /
blo ni sgeg 'chang dpal dang ldan/ /
dpa' bo mi sdug gzugs 'chang ba/ /]

kleśasaṃgrāmasūraika ajñānaripudarppahā dhīḥ śṛṅgāradharaḥ śrīmān vīrabībhatsarūpa[$7]... 

nyon mongs g.yul du gcig dpa' ba/ /mi shes dgra yi dregs pa 'joms/ /dpal ldan d+hIH ste sgeg 'chang zhing*/ dpa' bo mi sdug gzugs 'chang ba/ /zhes pa ni 


... ti | kleśā rāgādayas tais saha saṅgrāmaḥ kleśasaṅgrāmas tasmin śūra eka evādvitīyaḥ sarvakleśopakleśasamaraparikarāra[ms-c f. 83v img. 145] ... ajñānaṃ mohaḥ | 

de la nyon mongs pa'i g.yul du gcig dpa' ba ni nyon mongs pa ni 'dod 'chags la sogs pa de rnams dang lhan cig 'thab pa gang yin pa de nyon [f. 89v] mongs gul der dpa' po gcig bu kho na gnyis su med ni nyon mongs pa'i gul dug gcig dpa' ba ste/ nyon mongs pa dang nye pa'i nyon mongs pa thams cad ro mnyam par yongs su skyong bar rtsom zhing chos rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


... ((ajñānaripudarpahā)) | ajñānaṃ mohaḥ | satyādiṣu yā vimatis tad eva ripuḥ kuśalapakṣapratibandhakatvāt tasya darpo 'haṅkāraś taṃ hantīti | ajñānaripudarpahā | 

mi shes dgra yi dregs pa 'joms ni mi shes pa ni gti mug ste/ bden pa la sogs pa la blo phyin ci log gang yin pa'o/ /de nyid dgra ste dge ba'i phyogs so sor 'ching ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de'i rgyal ni dregs pa'o/ /de 'joms pas na mi shes dgra'i dregs pa 'joms so/ /


... bījaṃ sa eva śṛṅgāradhara i○ti | śṛṅa śukraṃ ((ābhāsan tā tarāti))dadhāti iti śṛṅkāṛa(dhara)(pc - marginal)ḥ sarvendriyavyāpakatvāt | taddhārayatī[$3] ((śrīmān iti garthāṛthaḥ |))

dpal ldan ni shad zin to/ /

d+hIH zhes bya ba ni dang po sangs rgyas bskyed pa'i sa bon te/ de nyid sgeg par ldan te/ sgeg pa ni shu kra'o/ /kun nas bskyed pa dang 'byin pas na sgeg 'chang ste/ de yang dbang po la khyab par byed pa nyid kyi phyir de 'dzin pas na de la de skad ces bya'o/ /


vīrabībhatsakāyadhṛg i○ti | virarasopetā bībhatsarasopetaś ca ye krodhaviśeṣās teṣāṃ rūpaṃ vīravībhatsarūpaṃ taddhārayatī[$4](...)(ms-c; ti vīrabībhatsarūpadhṛk em.)

dpa' bo mi sdug gzugs 'chang ba ni dpa' bo'i nyams dang ldan pa dang*/ mi sdug pa'i nyams dang ldan pa'i khro bo'i khyad par gang yin pa de rnams kyi gzugs ni dpa' bo mi sdug gzugs te/ de 'dzin pas nad pa'i bo mi sdug gzugs 'chang ba'o/ /


[bāhudaṇḍaśatākṣepaḥ padanikṣepanartanaḥ |
śrīmacchatabhujābhogo gaganābhoganartanaḥ || 121 ||]

[lag pa'i dbyug pa brgya bskyod cing/ /
rkang pa bskyod pas gar byed pa/ /
dpal ldan lag pa brgyas gang la/ /
nam mkha' khyab par gar byed pa/ /]


((bā))hudaṇḍaśatākṣepapadani○kṣepanarttanaḥ śrīmatśatabhujābhogo gaganābhoganarttana iti || 

lag pa brgya po kun bskyod cing*/ /gom pa'i stobs kyis gar byed pa/ /dpal ldan lag pa brgyas rtsol ba/ /nam mkha' khyab par gar byed pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra bāhudaṇḍaśatākṣepapada [$5] ... daṇḍaśatā(śatair vā - marginal note)nām ākṣepo bahirā○varttanaṃ padaṃ sthānam ā((lī))ḍhādi tasya nikṣepaḥ pañcavitastyādi | ābhyāṃ bāhudaṇḍaśatākṣepapada [$6] ... yasya sa tathoktaḥ | bhūmi○caryānutyaṃ darśayitvā ... kāśacaryā ... darśayitum āha | 

de la lag dpa' brgya po kun bskyod cing*/ gom pa'i stabs kyis gar byed pa ni lag pa brgya po rnams kun bskyod cing zhes pa ni/ lag pa brgya po rnams kun du bskyod pas phyi rol du bskor zhing gom pa'i gnas la g.yas brkyang pa la sogs pa'o/ /de'i stobs kyis mtho lnga la sogs par bskyod pa ste/ lag pa rgya po kun bskyod pa dang gom pa'i stobs de gnyis kyis gar byed pa dang gang ldan pha de de ltar ro/ /sa la spyod pa'i gar bstan nas gzhan yang nam mkha' la spyod pa'i gar bstan par 'dod pas gsungs pa/


śrīmacchatabhujābhogo gaganābhoga... 

dpal ldan lag pa brgyas rtsol ba/ /nam mkha' khyab par gar byed pa/ /

... śvaraḥ | tasya śatabhujāḥ śrīmañchatabhūjāḥ teṣām ābhogaḥ | (.. .. ..) (sauṣṭhava - msb) śrīmacchabhujābhogaḥ | tena gagane | ākāśe ābhogaḥ parivarttanaṃ [ms-c f. 84r im. 146] bhūjaśatānāṃ yasyāsau sa tathoktaḥ ||

dpal ldan ni pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug go/ /de'i lag pa brgya ni dpal ldan lag pa brgya ba'o/ /de rnams kyis rtsol pa ni mdzes par gnas pa ste/ dpal ldan lag pa brgyas rtsol ba'o/ /des nam mkha'i ste nam mkha' la kun du rtsol zhing [f. 90r]@#/ /yongs su bskor ba'i phyag rgya dang gang ldan pa de la de ltar gsungs so/ /


[ekapādatalākrānta- mahīmaṇḍatale sthitaḥ |
brahmāṇḍaśikharākrānta- pādāṅguṣṭhanakhe sthitaḥ || 122 ||]

[rkang pa gcig gis mthil gnon pa/ /
sa yi snying po'i mthil la gnas/ /
[7r]tshangs pa'i sgo nga'i rtse mo gnon/ /
rkang mtheb sen mo la gnas pa/ /]


ekapādatalākrāntamahīmaṇḍatale sthitaḥ | brahmāṇḍaśikharākrāntapādāṅguṣṭhanakhe sthita iti ||

sa yid dkyil 'khor gzhi gnod pa/ /rkang pa ya gcig mthil gyis gnon/ /rkang mtheb sen mo'i khyon gyis kyang*/ /tshang pa'i yul sa rtse nas gnon/ zhes pa 


tatra ekapādatalākrāntamahīma[$2]ṇḍatale sthita iti | ekaś cāsau pādaś ca ekapādaḥ | tasya ○ tala ekapādatalaṃ | mahāmaṇḍatalaṃ mahīmaṇḍatalaṃ lakāralopaṃ kṛtvā yaṃ nirdeśaḥ saddharmmapāṭhā[$3]d vā | ekapādatalenākrāntaṃ mahīmaṇḍa(ta)(pc - marginal)laṃ ekapādatalā○krāntamahīmaṇḍatalaṃ tatra sthitaṃ yasya sa ekapādatalākrāntamahīmaṇḍatalesthitaḥ |

de la/ sa yi dkyil 'khor gzhi gnon pa/ rkang pa ya gcig mthil gyis gnon/ /zhes pa la/ sa'i dkyil 'khor gzhi ni sa'i dkyil 'khor gzhi ni sa'i dkyil 'khor ngos te/ 'khor gyi sgra mi snang bar byas nas 'dir bstan pa'am/ dam pa'i chos kyi tshig gi yang phyir ro/ /rkang pa'ang de yin la ya gcig kyang de yin la ya gcig kyang de nyid yin pas rkang pa ya gcig ste/ de'i mthil ni rkang pa ya gcig gi mthil lo/ /rkang pa ya gcig mthil gyis sa'i dkyil 'khor gzhi gnas pa gnon pa ni sa'i dkyil 'khor ngos gnas pa/ rkang pa ya gcig mthil gyis gnon pa ste/ sa'i dkyil 'khor ngos gnon pa dang gang ldan pa de sa'i kyil 'khor ngos gnon pa'o/ /


dvitīya[$4]sya vyāpāram āha || brahmāṇḍetyādi | pādasyāṅguṣṭhaḥ pā○dāṅguṣṭhas tasya nakhaḥ pādāṅguṣṭhanakhaḥ | brahmāṇḍasya śikharaṃ brahmāṇḍaśikharaṃ | tenākrāntaṃ pādāṅguṣṭhanakhasthitaṃ yasya sa bramhāṇḍaśikharākrānta○pādāṅguṣṭhanakhasthitaḥ | anena padadvayena ((jhaddhiḥ)) pradarśitā | tasya bhagavataḥ | tatvine[$6]yajanāva((rtta))anyarthaṃ |

rtsom pa'i las gsungs pa/ rkang mtheb sen mo'i khyon gyis kyang*/ /tshangs pa'i yul sa rtse nas gnon ni rkang ba'i mthe ba mo ni rkang pa'i mthe bo ste/ de'i sen mo ni rkang mthe ba sen mo'o/ /tshangs pa'i yul gyi sa'i rtse mo ni tshangs pa'i yul sa'i rtse mo'o/ /des gnon pas rkang mtheb sen mos gnon pa dang gang ldan pa de rkang mtheb sen po khyon gyis kyang*/ tshangs pa'i yul sa rtse nas gnon te/ tshig de gnyis kyis ni des 'dul ba'i skyes bo la phan gdags pa'i don du bcom ldan 'das de'i rdzu 'phrul rab tu bstan pa yin no/ /


[ekārtho 'dvayadharmārthaḥ paramārtho 'vinaśvaraḥ |
nānāvijñaptirūpārthaś cittavijñānasantati || 123 ||]

[don gcig gnyis med chos kyi don/ /
dam pa'i don de 'jig pa med/ /
rnam rig sna tshogs rang bzhin don/ /
sems dang rnam shes rgyud dang ldan/ /]


ekārtho 'dvayaddharmārthaḥ (parārtho)(ms-c; paramāṛtho em.) 'vinaścaraḥ | nānāvijñaptirūpārthaś cittavijñānasantatir iti || 

don gcig gnyis med chos kyi don/ dam pa'i don de 'jigs pa med/ /rnam rig sna rig sna tshogs gzugs don can/ sems dang rnam par shes pa'i rgyud/ /


tatra ekārtha iti || paramārthasvabhā[ms-c f. 84 – img. 147]vatvāt || 

ces pa ni de la don gcig ni yang dag pa'i don dam pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ 


ata evādvayadharmāṛtha iti | grāhyagrāhakānupapatteḥ || 

de nyid kyi phyir na gnyis med chos kyi don zhes te/ gzung 'dzin gnyis mi 'thad pa'i phyir ro/ /


paramāṛtha iti | arthaprāptipratipattibhedāt tridhaivaparamāṛthaḥ |

dam pa'i don ni don dang*/ thob pa dang*/ sgrub pa dag las thob pa don dam pa nyid do/ /


avinaścara (i)(ms-c pc - marginal)ti ākāśatulyatvāt || 

'jigs pa med ni nam mkha' dang 'dra ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


nā[$2]nāvijñaptirūpārthacittavijñānasantatir iti || nānā○vijñaptirūpārtha iti | ṣatpravṛttivijñānāni | cittam ity ālayavijñānaṃ | vijñānam iti [$3] kliṣṭaṃ manaḥ | tataś cāyaṃ kramo bhavati || cittād ālayavi○jñānalakṣaṇāt kliṣṭaṃ manaḥ | tasmāc ca ṣaṭpravṛttivijñānāni viṣayavijñaptilakṣaṇāni [$4] | tadvāsanāś ca punar ālayavijñāne vāsitāc cālayavi○jñānāt punaḥ kliṣṭaṃ manaḥ tasmāc ca punaḥ pravṛtivijñānānīty evaṃ sūkṣmapratītyasamutpāda[$5]cakraṃ paribhramati | tathācoktaṃ ||

	vipāko mananākhyāś ca ○ vijñaptir viṣayasya ceti || [Vasubandhu, triṃśikāvijñaptikārikāḥ 2ab]

rnam rig sna tshogs gzugs don can ni 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa drug go/ /sems ni kun gzhi rnam par shes pa'o/ /[f. 90v] rnam par shes pa ni nyon mongs pa can gyi yid do/ /de yang rim pa 'di yin te/ sems kun gzhi rnam par shes pa'i mtshan nyid las nyon mongs pa can gyi yid do/ /de las kyang 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa drug rnams te/ yul la rnam par g.yo ba'i mtshan nyid rnams so/ /yang de'i bag chags kun gzhi rnam par shes pa las bsgos pa kun gzhi rnam par shes pa las kyang nyon mongs pa can gyi yod de/ de las kyang yang 'jug pa'i rnam par shes pa drug go/ /de ltar rten cing 'brel par 'byung pa'i 'khor lo phra mo yongs su 'khor ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ /
	rnam par smin dang ngan sems dang*/ yul la rnam par rig pa'o/ /zhes so/ /


ataś ca kim uktam bhavati | yāni ṣadviṣyavijñaptilakṣaṇāni | ya[$7]c ca cittaṃ yac ca kliṣṭaṃ manaḥ tat sarvaṃ sa eva bhagavān || 

des ci gsungs par 'gyur zhe na/ gang yul rig pa'i mtshan nyid rnams la ngar sems dang*/ gang nyon mongs pa can gyi yid de/ de rnams ni bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


