bhava○rāgādyatītaś ca bhavatrayam attāratir iti || bhavarā(gā)(ms-c pc - marginal)dyatīti iti | tatra kāmabhāvo rūpa[$4]bhavo ārūpy abhava iti | taryo bhavā | tad evaṃ kāmarāgādibhir atīto ○ 'tikrānto bhavarāgādyatīta ity ucyate | sa eva bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | bhavatrayamahā[$6]ratir iti | tathāpi bhavatraye kāmādhātvādau tat bhūmi○janāṃ devaputrāṇām anugrahārthaṃ tatra tatra janmasandarśanāt bhavatrayamahāratir iti || 

srid pa'i dod chag sogs las 'das ni/ /de 'dod pa'i srid pa dang*/ gzugs kyi srid pa dang*/ gzugs med pa'i srid pa gsum las 'dod chags so/ /gzugs dang gzugs med pa'i srid pa ni srid pa'i 'dod chags kho na ste/ 'dod pa'i 'dod chags ni ma yin no/ /de ltar yang chos mngon pa las gsungs pa/ khams gnyis las skyes srid [f. 91r]@#/ /'dod chags/ /zhes so/ /de de ltar 'dod pa'i 'dod chags la sogs pa las 'das shing brgal bas na/ srid pa'i 'dod chags sogs las 'das/ /zhes gsungs te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal lo/ /srid gsum dga' ba chen po pa ni 'dod pa'i khams la sogs pa'i srid pa gsum po yang snga ma de bzhin te/ sa de las skyes pa'i lha'i bu rnams la phan gdags pa'i don du de dang de ru skye ba bstan pa'i phyir na/ srid gsum dga' ba chen po pa/ /zhes so/ /


