skra mchog mthon ka chen po 'chang/ /
nor bu chen po 'od chags dpal/ /
sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyan dang ldan/ /]

śu[$7] (...)(ms-c; ddhaśubhrā)dhavalaḥ śaraccandrāṃ śusudrābhaḥ | bālārkamaṇḍalacchāyo mahārāganakhaprabhaḥ || indranīlāgrasaccīro mahānīrlakacāgradhṛk | mahāmaṇimayūkha[ms-c f. 85 - img 149] śrī((r)) buddhanirmāṇabhūṣaṇa iti | 

sprin dkar dag pa bzhin du dkar/ /'od bzangs ston ka'i zla ba'i 'od/ /nyi ma 'char ka'i dkyil ltar mdzes/ /sen mo'i 'od ni shas cher dmar/ /cod pan bzang po mthon ka'i rtse/ /skra mchog mthon ka chen po 'chang*/ /nor bu chen po 'od chags dpal/ /sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyan dang ldan/ /zhes pa ni 


