de nyid kun brtags dang*/ gzhan dbang dang/ yongs su grub pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /ngo bo nyid gsum po 'di la de nyid du ci ltar 'dod ce na/ ngo bo nyid gsum rtag med dang*/ /yod dang kho na ma yin dang*/ /yod dang med de kho na ste/ ngo bo nyid ni gsum du 'dod/ /ces so/ /kun brtags kyi mtshan nyid ni rtag tu med pa'o/ /de ni kun brtags pa'i mtshan nyid la kho na zhes bya ste/ phyin ci ma log pa'i phyir ro/ /gzhan gyi dbang gi mtshan nyid ni yod kyang yang dag pa ma yin te 'khrul pa'i phyir ro/ /de bas na 'di ni gzhan gyi dbang gi ngo bo nyid kyi de kho na zhes bya'o/ /yongs su grub pa'i mtshan nyid ni yod pa dang med pa kho na ste/ de bas 'di ni yongs su grub pa'i mtshan nyid kyi de kho na nyid la de kho na nyid de/ de kho na gsum sbyor bas bcom ldan 'das de nyid la de nyid ces gsungs so/ /

dran pa chen po 'chang ni shin tu che ba'i dran pa ni dran pa chen po ste/ de yang 'dres pa'i dngos po ma brjed pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /de 'dzin pas na de la de skad gsungs so/ /


catuḥsmṛtismādhirā○ḍ iti | catvāri smṛtyupasthānāni | tad yathā kāyasmṛtyupasthānaṃ | nānāvayavasaṃnive[$6]... yaṃ kāyo grāhyādiviviktatālakṣaṇaś ceti smṛter upasthānaṃ | evaṃ vedanāsmṛtyupasthānaṃ | cittasmṛtyupasthānaṃ | dharmasmṛtyupasthānaṃ ca | cā... [ms-c f. 85v - img. 151]vīryasamādhismṛtisaṃprajanyayogāt || rājata iti rāṭ | (samāś[sic for samādhiś?] cittaikāgratāyārāt |)(ms-c pc - marginal) caturṇāṃ smṛtyupasthānānāṃ samādhirāṭ catuḥsmṛtisamādhirāṭ sa eva bhagavān || 

dran pa bzhi bo ting 'dzin rgyal ni dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi'o/ /'di lta ste/ lus dran pa nye bar gzhag pa ni yan lag sna tshogs pa la zhen pa tsam gyi dngos po ni ma lus te/ gzung ba la sogs pa rnams dben pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid do zhes lus dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o/ /de ltar tshor ba dran pa nye bar gzhag pa dang*/ chos dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o/ /rnam pa bzhi ral yang brtson 'grus dang*/ ting nge 'dzin dang*/ dran pa dang*/ shes bzhin du sbyor ba'i phyir ro/ /ting nge 'dzin ni sems rtse gcig pa'o/ /de rgyal bas rgyal ba'o/ /dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi po rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin rgyal ba ni dran pa bzhi po ting nge 'dzin rgyal te/ bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /

[bodhyaṃgakusumāmodas tathāgataguṇodadhiḥ |
aṣṭāṅgamārganayavit samyaksaṃbuddhamārgavit || 128 ||]

[byang chub yan lag me tog dga'/ /
de bzhin gshegs pa yon tan mtsho/ /
lam gyi yan lag brgyad tshul rig /
yang dag sangs rgyas lam rig pa/ /]


bodhya[$2](...)(ms-c; ṅgakusumā em.) modas tathāgataguṇodadhiḥ | aṣṭāṅgamā○rganayavit samyaksambuddhamārgavid iti ||

byang chub yan lag me tog dga'/ /de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan mtsho/ /lam gyi yan lag brgyad tshul rig /yang dag sangs rgyas lam rig pa/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra bodhyaṅgakusumāmoda iti | anabhisaṃ[$3]skāravāhibhyo grabhūtebhyaḥ śraddhādibhyo darśanamāṛga○paryāyannāni dharmadhātugocarāṇi saptabodhyaṅgāni uktalakṣaṇāni tāny eva kusu[$4]māni | bhāvanāmārgaphalahetubhūtatvāt bodhyaṅgaku○sumānīty ucyaṃte | teṣām āmodaḥ śrutamayena jñānenādhigatasya | māyāsvapnamarī[$5]cigandharvanagarākāsapratibhāsalakṣaṇasya jagatā○s taddarśanamāṛge sākṣātkaraṇatvāt mahān āmodo harṣaś cittasya bhavatīti | bodhyaṅga[$6]kusumāmoda iti bhaṇyate | 

de la byang chub yan lag me tog dga' ni mngon [f. 92r]@#/ /par 'dus ma byas par 'jug cing mchog tu gyur ba'i dad pa la sogs pa rnams mthong ba'i lam yongs su chub pa chos kyi dbyings kyi spyod yul byang chub kyi yan lag bdun po gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid de rnams nyid ni me tog ste/ bsgom pa'i lam 'bras bu'i rgyu'i dngos po nyid kyi phyir na byang chub kyi yan lag ni me tog rnams zhes gsungs so/ /de rnams kyi dga' ba ni thos pa'i rang bzhin gyi ye shes kyis rig pa'i ngo bo nyid kyis 'gro ba rnams rmi lam dang*/ smig rgyu dang*/ dri za'i grong khyer rnams kyi tshul du so sor snang ba'i mtshan nyid kyi mthong ba'i lam de mngon du byed pa nyid kyi phyir sems rab tu dga' bar gyur bas na/ byang chub yan lag me tog dga'/ /zhes gsungs so/ /


tathāgataguṇodadhir iti | tathāgatānāṃ guṇās tathāgataguṇāḥ | aṣṭādaśāveṇikādayo buddhadharmās ta evodadhayaḥ pra[ms-c f. 87r]bhūtatvād anyeṣāñ ca guṇaratnānāṃ ākaratvāc ca tathāgataguṇodadhi bhagavān |

de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan mtsho ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan rnams ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan rnams te/ ma 'dres pa bco brgyad la sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi chos rnams so/ /de rnams nyid mtsho ste rgya che ba'i phyir dang*/ gzhan yon tan rin po che rnams kyi yang 'byung gnas yin pa'i phyir na de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan mtsho ni bcom ldan das so/ /


aṣṭāṅgamārganayavid iti || bhāvanāmārgaprabhāvitāny aṣṭau māṛgāṅgāṇi pu[$2]rastān pratipāditāni | teṣām nayo mārga upāya i○ti yāvat | taṃ vetti jānātīti aṣṭāṅgamārganayavit ||

lam gyi yan lag brgyad tshul rig ni bsgom pa'i lam rab tu bsgoms pa'i 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad sngon du bshad pa rnams so/ /de rnams kyi tshul ni lam ste/ thabs zhes ba'i bar du ste/ de rig cing shes pa ni lam gyi yan lag brgyad tshul rig go/ /


samyaksambuddhamārgavid i[$3]ti | samyaksambuddha iti | svayam aparopadeśādiṣṭa○tatvāvabodhāt sanmārgāvabodhāc ca samyaksambuddhasya mārgo dharmadhātus tam vettīti sa[$5]myaksambuddhamārgavit sa eva bhagavān ||

yang dag sangs rgyas lam rig pa ni yang dag sangs rgyas ni gzhan gyis mnang gnye bar ma bstan par rang nyid kyis de kho na thugs su chud pa'i phyir dang*/ dam pa'i lam kun du rtogs pa'i phyir ro/ /yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de'i lam ni chos kyi dbyings so/ /de shes pas nas yang dag sangs rgyas lam rig ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[sarvasatvamahāsaṅgo niḥsaṅgo gaganopamaḥ |
sarvasatvamanojātaḥ sarvasatvamanojavaḥ || 129 ||]

[sems can kun la shas cher chags/ /
nam mkha' lta bur chags pa med/ /
sems can kun gyi yid las skyes/ /
sems can kun gyi yid ltar mgyogs/ /]


sarvasatva○mahāsaṅgo niḥsaṅgo gaganopamaḥ | sarvasatvamanojātaḥ sarvasatvamanojava iti [$5] ||

sems can kun la shas cher chags/ /nam mkha' lta bur chags pa med/ /sems can kun gyi yid las skyes/ /sems can kun gyi yid ltar mgyogs/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra sarvasatvamahāsaṅga iti | mahāś cāsau saṃga○ś ca mahāsaṅgaḥ | sarvasatvānāṃ mahāsaṅgaḥ sarvasatvamahāsaṅgaḥ | tatra catvāri saṅga[$6]havstūni dānaṃ priyavacanam arthacaryā samānārthatā ceti | dānenārthajñaḥ | priyavacanena kālajñaḥ | arthacaryayā parārṣajjñaḥ | samānārthatayā dharmajña[ms-c f. 87v - img 153]ḥ | sarvaparāparajñatayā nityādibhānisaṅgrahavastūnī | ebhiḥ saṅgrahavastubhiḥ sarvasatvānātma(sākṣā)(ms-c pc – marginal; mā ms-c ac)karotīti sarvasatvamahāsaṅga ity ucyate | saṃvṛtita[$2]ḥ sa eva bhagavān || paramāṛthatas tu sa eva bhagvān niḥsaṅgaḥ śūnyatāsvabhāvatvāt | 

(venan dānañca calaṃ yatra prastāve yā dṛśīdharmādeśanā sā priyavacanaṃ tasyāḥ jājapanyārthākhyānaṃ pānānām ekārthabhākhyānaṃ etac ca (mṛdu)madhyādhimātratadadhimātrajaṃ kṛtvākramāt) (marginal note of 87r; mostly cannot read this)

de la sems can kun la shas cher chags ni chen po yang de yin la chags pa yang de yin pas na shas cher chags pa ste/ sems can kun la shas cher chags pa ni sems [f. 92v] can kun la shas cher chags so/ /de la bsdu ba'i dngos po ni bzhi ste/ sbyin pa dang*/ snyan par smra ba dang*/ don mthun pa dang*/ don bzhin spyod pa rnams las sbyin pa ni rngas shes pa'o/ /snyan par smra ba ni dus shes pa'o/ /don mthun pa ni 'khor shes pa'o/ /don sbyor pa ni chos shes pa'o/ /sems can mchog dang mchog ma yin pa shes par bsgrub pa bsdu ba'i dngos po de rnams kyis sems can thams cad la bdag nyid mngon du byed pas na/ sems can kun la shas cher chags/ /zhes gsungs so/ /bcom ldan 'das de nyid kun rdzob tu'o/ /don dam par ni bcom ldan 'das de nyid chags pa med pa zhes pa ste/ stong ba nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ata eva gaganopamaḥ prajñāpāramitāsvabhāvatvā[$3]t || 

de nyid kyi phyir na bcom ldan 'das nam mkha' lta bu zhes te/ shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvasatvamanojāta iti | manasi jāto manojātaḥ sarvasatvānāṃ manojātaḥ sarvasatvamanojātaḥ || tathācoktaṃ || tathāgatagarbhā[$4]ḥ sarvasatvā iti ||

sems can kun gyi yid las skyes pa ni sems can gyi yid las skyes so/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ sems can thams cad ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can zhes so/ /


sarvasatvamanojava iti ma○nojavas tathāga(ta)vega ity ucyate | sarvasatvānāṃ manojavaḥ sarvasatvamanojavaḥ | [$5] sarvasatvacittacaritān varttitvāt | 

sems can kun gyi yid ltar mgyogs ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i shugs zhes gsungs pa ste/ sems can thams can gyi yid ltar mgyogs pa ni sems can thams cad kyi yid ltar mgyogs pa ste/ sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi sbyor pa la 'jug pas so/ /


[sarvasatvendriyārthajñaḥ sarvasatvamanoharaḥ |
pañcaskandhārthatatvajñaḥ pañcaskandhaviśuddhadhṛk || 130 ||]

[sems can kun gyi dbang don shes/ /
sems can kun gyi yid 'phrog pa/ /
phung po lnga don de nyid shes/ /
rnam dag phung po lnga 'chang ba/ /]

sarvasatve○ndiyārthajñaḥ sarvasatvamanoharaḥ pañcskandhārthatatvajñaḥ pañcaskandhaviśuddhadhṛk || [$6]

sems can kun gyi dbang don shes/ /sems can kun gyi yid 'phrogs pa/ /phung po lnga don de nyid shes/ /rnam dag phung po lnga 'chang ba/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra sarvasatvendriyārthajña iti | sarvasatvānām indriyāṇi mṛdumadhyādhimātrāṇi teṣāṃ arthaḥ sarvasatvendriyārthas taj jānātīti sarvasatvendriyārtha[mc-s f. 88r img. 154]jñaḥ sa eva bhagavān || 

de la sems can kun gyi dbang don shes ni sems can thams cad kyi dbang bo rtul po dang*/ 'bring po dang*/ rnon po de rnams kyi don ni sems can gyi dbang don te/ de mkhyen pas na sems can gyi dbang don shes te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


sarvasatvamanohara iti | sarvasatvānāṃ manāṃsi cittāni yathābhahvyatayā dharmadeśanāmukhena (na)(ms-c pc – marginal) haratīti sa tathā ||
	% Tib suggests the pc reading is incorrect.

sems can kun gyi yid 'phrogs pa ni sems can thams cad kyi yid kyi cha ste/ sems can rnams kyi skal pa ji lta ba bzhin du chos bstan pa'i sbo nas 'phrogs pas de de la de skad ces bya'o/ /


pañcaskandhārthatatva[$2]jña iti | tatra pañcaskandhā rūpavedanāsaṃjñāsaṃskāra○vijñānalakṣaṇāḥ tatra rūpaskandhaś ca cakṣusrotraghrāṇajihvākāyarūpaśabdagandharasaspra[$3]ṣṭavyāvijñaptilakṣaṇaḥ | vedanāskandhabhayasvabhāva○ḥ | 
	% appears to be a problem with vedanaskandhā
saṃjñāskandho viṣayanimittodgrahaṇātmakaḥ | saṃskāraskandhaś cittasamprayukta(viprayukta)(ms-c pc – marginal)rūpaḥ | [$4]aṣṭau vijñānakāyā vijñānaskandha iti | ete pañcaskandhāḥ teṣām arthaḥ pañcaskandhārthaḥ | sa ca rāśyārthaḥ | tasya tatvaṃm vivekārthāvabodhaḥ | ta[$5]cca pañcaskandhārthatatvaṃ | 

phung bo lnga don de nyid shes ni/ de la phung bo lnga ni gzugs dang*/ tshor ba dang*/ 'du shes dang*/ 'du byed dang*/ rnam par shes pa rnams kyi mtshan nyid do/ /de la gzugs kyi phung po ni mig dang*/ rna ba dang*/ sna dang* [f. 93r]@#/ /lce dang*/ lus dang*/ gzugs dang*/ sgra dang*/ dri dang*/ ro dang*/ reg bya rnams dang*/ rnam par rig byed ma yin pa rnams kyi mtshan nyid do/ /tshor ba'i phung po ni bde ba dang*/ sdug bsngal dang*/ gnyis ka ma yin pa'i rang bzhin no/ /'du shes kyi phung bo ni yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /'du byed kyi phung po ni sems dang mtshungs par ldan pa ma yin pa nyid do/ /rnam par shes pa'i phung po ni rnam par shes ba tshogs brgyad rnams so/ /de rnams kyi don ni phung po lnga'i don te/ de yang spungs pa'i don to/ /de'i de nyid ni rnam par dben pa'i don du khong du chud par bya ste/ phung po lnga don de nyid de/ 


ekatvādigrāhanivṛttila○ṣaṇaṃ tannivṛttir nairātmyaṃ tasmāc cānupadhiśeṣanirvā(ṇāvā)(ms-c pc)ptir iti | tad evaṃ bhūtaṃ pañca[$6]skandhārthatatvaṃ jānātīti pañcaskandhārthatatvajñaḥ | sa ○ eva bhagavān ||

de yang gcig la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid de log pa ni bdag med pa ste/ de las ni lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa thob par 'gyur ro/ /de de ltar gyur ba'i phung bo lnga'i don mkhyen pas na phung po lnga'i don de nyid shes te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


tathā coktaṃ āryavasubandhupādaiḥ || 
	dharmāṇāṃ pravicayam antareṇa nāsti[$7] kleśānāṃ yata upaśāntaye bhyupāya ity evam ādi | 
	
[Vasubandhu, Abhidharmakośa 1.3:
dharmāṇāṃ pravicayamantareṇa nāsti kleśānāṃ yata upaśāntaye 'bhyupāyaḥ |
kleśaiśca bhramati bhavārṇave 'tra lokastaddhetorata uditaḥ kilaiṣa śāstrā || ]

de ltar yang slob dpon dbyig gnyen zhabs kyis gsungs pa/ 
	chos rnams rab tu rnams 'byed med par nyon mongs rnams/ /
	gang phyir nye bar zhi bar bya ba'i thabs med pa/ /
	nyon mongs las kyang 'jig rten srid mtsho 'dir 'khyams te/ /
	de bas de'i phyir 'di ni ston pas gsungs so lo/ /
zhes pa la sogs pa'o/ /


pañcaskandhaviśuddhadhrg iti | pañcaskandhāś ca te viśuddhāś ca pañcaskandhaviśuddhāḥ śīlasamādhipra[ms-c f. 88r – img 155]jñāvimuktivimuktijñānadarśanalakṣaṇāḥ | tān dhārayatīti pañcaskandhaviśuddhadhṛk | sa eva bhagavān ||

rnam dag phung po lnga 'chang ni rnam par dag pa yang de yin phung po yang de nyid yin pas rnam dag phung po lnga ste/ tshul khrims dang*/ ting nge 'dzin dang*/ shes rab dang*/ rnam par grol dang*/ rnam par grol ba'i ye shes ba'i mtshan nyid rnams so/ /de rnams 'dzin pas na rnam dag phung po lnga 'chang ba ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[sarvaniryāṇakoṭisthaḥ sarvaniryāṇakovidaḥ |
sarvaniryāṇamārgasthaḥ sarvaniryāṇadeśakaḥ || 131 ||]

[thams cad nges 'byung mtha' la gnas/ /
thams cad nges par 'byung ba mkhas/ /
thams cad nges 'byung lam la gnas/ /
thams cad nges 'byung ston pa po/ /]


sarvaniryāṇakoṭisthaḥ sarvaniryāṇakovidaḥ | sa[$2]rvaniryānamārgasthaḥ sarvaniryānadeśaka iti  ||

nges 'byung kun gyi mtha' la gnas/ /nges par 'byung ba kun la mkhas/ /nges 'byung kun gyi lam la gnas/ /nges par 'byung ba kun ston pa/ /zhes pa ni 


ta○tra sarvaniryāṇakoṭistha iti | yāni kānicil laukikanirvāṇāni teṣāṃ koṭin niṣṭhā[$3] tatra tiṣṭhatīti sarvaniryāṇakoṭisthaḥ | 

de la nges 'byung kun gyi mtha' la gnas ni 'jig rten gyi mya ngan las 'das pa gang cung zad de rnams kyi mthar thug par gyur ba'o/ /de la gnas pas na nges 'byung kun gyi mtha' la gnas so/ /


sarvaniryā○ṇakovida iti | śrāvakāṇāṃ nirvāṇe kovido nipunaḥ sarvaniryāṇakovidaḥ || 

nges par 'byung ba kun la mkhas ni nyan thos rnams kyi mya ngan las 'das pa la mkhas shing byang bas na nges par 'byung ba kun la [f. 93v]mkhas so/ /


sa[$4]rvaniryāṇamārgastha iti | pratyekabuddhānāṃ nirvāṇa○mārghasthitaḥ | sarvaniryāṇamārgasthaḥ || sarvaniryāṇadeśaka iti | samyaksambuddhānāṃ [$5] ni((rvāṇa))ṃ sarvaniryāṇaṃ tasya deśakaḥ prakāśakaḥ | sa ○ eva bhagavān || 

ngas 'byung kun gyi lam la gnas ni rang sangs rgyas rnams kyi mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam la gnas pa ste/ /nges 'byung kun gyi lam lag gnas so/ /nges bar 'byung ba kun ston pa ni yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi mya ngan las 'das pa ni des par 'byung ba kun no/ /de ston pa ni rab tu ston pa ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[dvādaśāṅgabhavotkhāto dvādaśākāraśuddhadhṛk |
catuḥsatyanayākāro aṣṭajñānāvabodhadhṛk || 132 ||]

[yan lag bcu gnyis srid rtsa bton/ /
dag pa rnam pa bcu gnyis 'chang/ /
bden bzhi'i tshul gyi rnam pa can/ /
shes pa brgyad po rtogs pa 'chang/ /]


dvādaśāṅgabhavotakhāto dvādaśākāraśuddhadhṛk | catuḥsatyanayākā[$6]ra aṣṭhajñānāvabodhadhṛg iti ||

yan lag bcu gnyis srid rtsa bton/ /dag pa rnam pa bcu gnyis 'chang*/ /bden bzhi'i tshul gyi rnam pa can/ /shes pa brgyad po rtogs pa 'chang*/ /zhes pa la 


tatra dvādaśāṅgabhavo○takhāta iti | dvādaśāṅgāni | tad yathā || avidyāsaṃskāravijñānanāmrūpaṣaḍāyata[$7]nasparśavedanātṛṣṇā-upādānabhavajātijarāmaraṇāni tatvacchādanād avidyayā yathābhimatadarśanavibandhanāt | ropaṇāt saṃskārair vijñāne ka[ms-c f. 89 – img 156]rmavāsanāyāḥ pratiṣṭhāpanāt | nayanāt vijñānenopapatti((ṣṭhā))(sic for sthā)naprāpaṇāt || sa(mpa)(ms-c pc; mpra ms-c ac)rigrahāt nāmrūpeṇātmabhāvasya [$2] | pūraṇāt ṣaḍāyatanena | triparicchedāt sparśana | upa○bhogād vedanayā | karṣaṇāc ca tṛṣṇayā karmavikṣiptasya punarbhavasya nibandhanāt upādā[$3]nair vijñānasyopapattyanukuleṣu kāmādiṣu | ābhi○mukhyāt bhavena kṛtasya karmaṇaḥ punarbhave vipākadānāyābhimukhīkaraṇāt | duḥ[$4]khanāt | jātyā jarāmaraṇena ca tad ebhir dvādaśāṅgai○ḥ pratilomavibhaver bhavaḥ pañcāyatānalakṣaṇna utkhāta utmūlito yena sa dvādaśā[$5]ṅgabhavotkhāt ity ucyate || tathācoktaṃ madhyāntavi○bhāge || 
	cchādanād ropaṇā caiva nayanāt samparigrahāt |
	pūraṇā triparicchedād upa[$6]bhogāc ca karṣaṇāt ||
	nibandhanād ābhimukhād duḥkhanāt kli(kṣa)(ms-c; ṣya em.)te jagat ||
[Madhyāntavibhāṅa, 1.10–11b]

[Commentary follows Vasubandhu:
	tatra cchādanād avidyayā yathābhūtadarśanavibandhanāt, ropaṇāt saṃskārair vijñāne karmavāsanāyāḥ pratiṣṭhāpanāt, nayanād vijñānenopapattisthānasaṃprāpaṇāt, saṃparigrahān nāmarūpeṇātmabhāvasya, pūraṇāt ṣaḍāyatanena, triparicchedāt sparśena, upabhogād vedanayā, karṣaṇāt tṛṣṇayā karmākṣiptasya punarbhavasya, nibandhanād upādānair vijñānasyotpattyanukūleṣu kāmādiṣu, ābhimukhyād bhavena kṛtasya karmaṇaḥ punarbhave vipākadānāyābhimukhīkaraṇāt. duḥkhanāj jātyā jarāmaraṇena ca, parikliśyate jagat. so 'yam—
]

de la yan lag bcu gnyis srid rtsa bton ni/ /yan lag bcu gnyis rnams ni 'di lta ste/ ma rig ba dang*/ 'du byed dang*/ rnam par shes pa dang*/ ming dang*/ gzugs pa dang*/ skye mched drug dang*/ reg pa dang*/ tshor ba dang*/ sred pa dang*/ len pa dang*/ srid pa dang*/ skye ba dang*/ rga shi rnams so/ /de la de kho na nyid la sgrib pa'i phyir na ma rig pa ni ji ltar mngon par 'dod pa'i don mthong ba la 'gags byed pa nyid kyi phyir de kho na nyid la sgrib pa'o/ /'debs ba'i phyir na 'du byed de/ des rnams par shes pa la las kyi bag chags so sor 'jog pa'i phyir ro/ /khrid pa'i phyir na rnam par shes pa ste/ skye ba'i sar phyin par byed pa'i phyir ro/ /kun 'dzin par byed pa'i phyir na ming dang gzugs so/ /bdag gi dngos po rdzogs par byed pa'i phyir na skye mched drug go/ /gsum 'dus nas yongs su gcod pa'i phyir na reg pa'o/ /nye bar spyod pa'i phyir na tshor ba'o/ /sdud pa'i phyir na srid pa'o/ /las kyis 'phangs pa'i srid pa phyi ma dang sbyar ba'i phyir na len ba'o/ /rnam par shes pa skye ba dang mthun pa'i dod chags la sogs pa mngon du bye dpa'i phyir na srid pa ste/ las byas ba'i srid pa phyi ma la rnam par smin pa 'byung zhing mngon du byed pa'i phyir ro/ /sdug bsngal gyi phyir na skye ba dang rga shi rnams so/ /de bas na yan lag bcu gnyis/ /de rnams kyi 'khor ba'i srid rtsa ni nye bar len pa'i phyir phung go lnga'i bdag nyid do/ /de gang gis rtsa nas phyung zhing bton pa de/ yan lag bcu gnyis srid rtsa bton/ /zhes gsungs so/ /de ltar yang dus dang*/ mtha' rnam par 'byed pa las gsungs pa/ 
	sgrib pa'i phyir dang 'debs pa dang*/ 
	khrid pa'i phyir dang*/[f. 94r]@#/ /'dzin pa'i phyir/ /
	rdzogs byed phyir dang gsum gcod phyir/ /
	nye bar spyod cing sdud pa'i phyir/ /
	sbyor ba'i phyir dang mngon du'i phyir/ /
	sdug bsngal phyir na 'gro nyon mongs/ /zhes so/ /


dvādaśākāraśuddhadhṛg iti | dvādaśākārāṇi dvādaśāyatanāni tāni [ms-c f. 89v – img. 157] ca śuddhāni | grāhagrāhakākāraviviktatvāt tāni dhārayatīti dvādaśākāraśuddhadhṛk || 

dag pa rnam pa bcu gnyis 'chang ni/ /rnam pa bcu gnyis ni skye mched bcu gnyis rnam par dag pa ste/ gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa gnyis dben pa'i phyir ro/ /de rnams 'dzin pas na dag pa rnam pa bcu gnyis 'chang ngo*/ /


catuḥsatyanayākāra iti | duḥkhasamudayanirodhamārgākhyāni ca[$2]turāryasatyāni | teṣāṃ catuḥsatyānāṃ nayo mārgaḥ sa ○ evākāra ākṛtir yasya sa catusstyanayākāro bhagavān ||

bden bzhi'i tshul gyi rnam pa can ni sdug bsngal dang*/ kun 'byung dang*/ 'gog pa dang*/ lam rnams ni 'phags pa'i bden pa rnams so/ /bden pa bzhi po de rnams kyi tshul ni lam mo/ /de nyid kyi rnam pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de bzhin bzhi'i tshul gyi rnam pa can te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


aṣṭajñānāvabodhadhṛg iti | [$3] tatrāṣṭau jñānāni yad uta dharmajñānaṃ advayajñānaṃ duḥkha○jñānaṃ samudāyajñānaṃ nirodhajñānaṃ mārgajñānaṃ ((kṣa))yajñānaṃ anutpādajñānam iti | teṣām ava[$4]bodhaḥ sākṣātkaraṇaṃ taṃ dhārayatīti | aṣṭajñānāva○bo(dha)(em.; ms-c deest)k | sa eva bhagavān ||

shes pa brgyad po rtogs pa 'chang ni/ de la shes pa brgyad ni ji skad gsungs pa'i chos shes pa dang*/ rjes su shes pa dang*/ sdug bsngal shes pa dang*/ kun 'byung shes pa dang*/ 'og pa shes pa dang*/ lam shes pa dang*/ zad pa shes pa dang*/ mi skye ba shes pa rnams so/ /de rnams rtogs pa ni mngon du byed pa'o/ /de 'dzin pas na shes par brgyad po rtogs pa 'chang ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[dvādaśākārasatyārthaḥ ṣoḍaśākāratattvavit |
viṃśatyākārasaṃbodhir vibuddhaḥ sarvavit paraḥ || 133 ||]

[bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis ldan/ /
de nyid rnam pa bcu drug rig /
rnam pa nyi shus byang chub pa/ /
rnam par sangs rgyas kun rig mchog /]

dvādaśākārasatyārthaḥ ṣoḍaśākāratatvavit | 
viṃśatyākā[$5]rasaṃbodhi vibuddhaḥsarvavitpara iti ||

bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis ldan/ de nyid rnam pa bcu drug rig /rnam pa nyi shus byang chub pa/ /rnam pa sangs rgyas kun rig mchog /ces pa ni 


tatra dvādaśā○kārasatyārtha iti | satyānām arthaḥ satyārthaḥ | dvādaśākāraiḥ pravibhajya triparivartta[$6]dvādaśākāraṃ dharmacakraṃ yad uta anityato duḥkhataḥ śūnyata iti | duḥkhasatyasya || hetutaḥ samudayataḥ prabhavata iti | samudayasatyasya || nirodhataḥ śā[ms-c f. 90 – img. 158]ntataḥ praṇītata iti | nirodhasatyasya || mārgato nyāyataḥ pratipattitaś ceti | mārgasatyasya || tad evaṃbhūtaṃ | yathā bhavyatayā dvādaśākārasaty((ārya))dharmacakrapravarttanā[$2]d asau bhagavān dvādaśākāra ity ucyate | 

de la bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis ldan ni bden pa rnams kyi don ni bden pa'i don te/ de dag pa rnam pa bcu gnyis kyi rang tu rnam par 'byed pas chos kyi 'khor lo rnam par bcu gnyis lan gsum du bskor ba ni 'di lta ste/ sdug bsngal gyi bden pa la mi rtag pa dang*/ sdug bsngal ba dang*/ stong ba'o/ /kun 'byung gi bden pa la kun 'byung ba dang*/ rgyu dang tu skyed pa'o/ /'gog pa'i bden pa la 'gog pa dang*/ zhi ba dang*/ gya nom pa'o/ /lam gyi bden pa la lam dang/ rigs pa dang*/ sgrub pa'o/ /de de ltar gyur ba skal ba ji lta ba bzhin du bden pa rnam pa bcu gnyis kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i phyir na bcom ldan 'das 'di ni/ bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis ldan/ /zhes gsungs so/ /


ṣoḍaśākāra○tatvavid iti | tatra kāmāvacaraṃ duḥkhasatyaṃ anityato duḥkhataḥ śūnyato 'nātmataś ca mana[$3]sikṣarvato dukhe dharmajñānakṛāttiḥ duḥkha dharmajñānañcaotpa○dyate | tābhyāṃ daśāpyete | kāmāvacarāḥ kleśāḥ prahīyante | 

de nyid rnam pa bcu drug rig ni/ de la 'dod pa na spyod pa'i sdug bsngal gyi bden pa [f. 94v] la mi rtag pa dang*/ sdug bsngal ba dang*/ stong ba dang*/ bdag med ba rnams yid la byed pas sdug bsngal la chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang*/ sdug bsngal la chos shes pa 'byung ngo*/ /de nyis kyis kyang 'dod pa na spyod pa'i nyon mongs pa bcu po de rnams rab tu spong ngo*/ /


rūparūpyāvacaraduḥkhasatyaṃ[$4] tathaiva manasikurvato duḥkhe 'anvayajñānakṣāntiḥ ○ du○ḥkhe 'nvayajñānañ cotpadyate | tābhyāṃ ta eva pratighavarjitā nava rūpāvacarā nava<ca> cārū[$5]pyāvacarā ity aṣṭādaśa prahīyante | 

gzugs dang gzugs med pa na spyod pa'i sdug bsngal gyi bden pa la de bzhin du yid la byed pas sdug bsngal la rjes su chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang*/ sdug bsngal la rjes su shes pa 'byung ngo*/ /de gnyis kyis kyang de rnams nyid las khong khro ma gtogs pa gzugs na spyod pa dgu dang*/ gzugs med pa na spyod pa dgu ste/ de ltar bco brgyad yod par 'gyur ro/ /


ity evaṃ traidhātu○kaduḥkhasatyābhisamayena caturbhir dharmānvayajñānakṣāntikṣaṇair aṣṭāviṃśatir anuśayā[$6] duḥkhadarśanāt prahīyante | 

de ltar khams gsum gyi sdug bsngal gyi bden pa mngon par rtogs pas na chos dang*/ rjes su dang*/ bzod pa dang*/ shes pa'i mtshan nyid bzhi rnams kyi phra rgyas nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni sdug bsngal gyi bden pa mthong ba las spong bar 'gyur ro/ /


eṣām eva daśānām anuśa○yānāṃ satkāyadṛṣṭim antagrāhadṛṣṭiṃ śīlavrataparāmarṣaṃm uktānye saptānuśayāḥ kāmadhā[$7]tau kāmāvacaraṃ samudayasatyaṃ hetutaḥ samudayataḥ prabhavaḥ pratyayataś ca manasikurvataḥ | 

phra rgyas bcu po 'di rnams nyid las 'jig tshogs kyi lta ba dang*/ mthar 'dzin pa'i lta ba dang*/ tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin pa rnams ma gtogs par 'dod pa'i khams kyi gzhan phra rgyas bdun ni 'dod pa na spyod pa'i kun 'byung gi bden pa la rgyu dang kun 'byung ba dang rab tu bskyed pa dang rkyen nyid du yid la byed pas de nyid kun 'byung la chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang*/ chos shes pa de gnyis kyis spong bar 'gyur ro/ /


ta eva samudaye dharmajñānakṣāntijñānābhyāṃ prahīyante | ta e[ms-c f. 90v - img 159]va pratighavivarjjitā dhātudvaye dvādaśānuśayā rūpārūpyāvacarāḥ samudayasatyadarśanāt samudaye 'nvayajñānakṣāntijñānābhyāṃ prahīyanta ity ekonaviṃśatir anu[$2]śayāḥ samudayasatyadarśanāt prahīyante | 

de rnams nyid las khong khro ma gtogs pa khams gnyis la phra rgyas bcu gnyis kun 'byung gi bden pa mthong bas te kun 'byung la rjes su shes pa'i bzod pa dang*/ shes pa gnyis kyis spong bar 'gyur bas na de de ltar phra rgyas dgu bcu kun 'byung gi bden pa mthong bas spong bar 'gyur ro/ /


tathā kāmā○vacaraṃ duḥkhanirodhasatyaṃ nirodhaśāntapraṇītaninssaraṇākāraiś caturbhir manasikurvata[$3]ḥ | samudayoktās ta eva saptānuśayā nirodhe dharma○jñānakṣāntijñānābhyāṃ prahīyante | evam anvayajñānakṣāntijñānābhyāṃ rūpārūpyāvacarā dvā[$4]daśānuśayāḥ prahīyante | etyevam ekānnaviṃśatir a○nuśayās traidhātukaduḥkhanirodhasatyadarśanāt prahīyante | 

de bzhin du 'dod pa na spyod pa'i sdug bsngal 'gog pa'i bden pa dang*/ zhi ba dang*/ gya nom pa dang*/ nges par 'byung ba bzhir yid la byas pas kun 'byung la gsungs pa'i phra rgyas bdun po de kho na 'gog pa la chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang*/ chos shes pa gnyis kyis yongs su spong bar 'gyur ro/ /de ltar rjes su bzod pa dang*/ rjes su shes pa gnyis kyis gzugs dang gzugs med pa na spyod pa'i phra rgyas bcu gnyis spong bar byed pas na khams gsum gyi phra rgyas bcu dgu sdug bsngal 'gog pa'i [f. 95r]@#/ /bden pa mthong ba las spong bar 'gyur ro/ /


tathā kāmāvacaraṃ duḥkhaniro[$5]dhagāmi mārgasatyaṃ mārganyāyapratipannairyāṇikākā○raiś caturbhir manasikurvataḥ | mārge dharmajñānakṣāntijñānābhyāṃ pūrvokteṣv evaṃ saptasu śīlavra[$6]taparāmarṣam adhikam aṣṭamam prakṣipyāṣṭau mārgasatyada○rśanena prahīyante | mārge 'nvayajñānakṣāntijñānābhyāṃ rūpārūpyāvacarāś caturddaśamārga[$7]darśanaprahātvāḥ | ity evaṃ dvāviṃśatir anuśayāmārgadarśanapraheyā ity evaṃ ṣoḍaśabhir ākāraiś caturāryasatyam abhimukhīkurvatas traidhātukakleśaśābhāvā [f. 91 – 92 missing] ...

de bzhin du 'dod pa na spyod pa'i sdug bsngal 'gog par 'gro ba'i lam gyi bden pa lam dang*/ rigs pa dang*/ nges par 'byin pa dang*/ sgrub pa dang*/ rnam par bzhir yid la byas pas lam la chos shes pa'i bzod pa dang*/ chos shes pa de gnyis kyi gong du gsungs pa'i bdun kho na la tshul khrims dang*/ brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin pa bsnan pas brgyad ni lam gyi bden pa mthong bas spong bar 'gyur ro/ /lam rjes su bzod pa dang*/ shes pa gnyis kyi gzugs dang gzugs med pa na spyod pa bcu bzhi ni lam mthong ba las spong bar 'gyur bas na de ltar na phra rgyas nyi shu rtsa gnyis lam gyi bden pa mthong bas spong bar 'gyur ro/ /

de ltar bas na rnam par bcu drug gis 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi mngon du byed pas khams gsum pa'i nyon mongs pa med cing phyin ci ma log pa'i dngos po rtogs pa'i de kho na skye ba ste/ de rig cing mkhyen pas na/ de nyid rnam pa bcu drug rig ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /

rnam pa nyi shus byang chub pa ni phung po lnga rnams rnam pa nyi shu so sor kun du rtog pa'i rnam pas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon du mdzad pa ni 'di lta ste/ gzugs nyid bdag yin/ /gzugs la bdag gnas/ /gzugs bdag gi yin/ /bdag gzugs dang ldan/ tshor ba bdag yin/ tshor ba la bdag gnas/ tshor ba bdag gi yin/ bdag tshor ba dang ldan/ 'du shes bdag yin/ 'du shes la bdag gnas/ 'du shes bdag gi yin/ /bdag 'du shes dang ldan/ 'du byed bdag yin/ 'du byed la bdag gnas/ /'du byed bdag gi yin/ bdag 'du byed dang ldan/ rnam par shes pa bdag yin/ rnam par shes pa la bdag gnas/ rnam par shes pa bdag gi yin/ bdag rnam par shes pa dang ldan pa'o/ /de ltar phye ba'i rnam pa nyi shu rnams kyis gang gis rdzogs pa'i byang chub rtog pa med pa'i ye shes la lhag par rtogs pa ste/ de rnam pa nyi shus byang chub pa zhes gsungs so/ /de ltar klu sgrub zhabs kyis gsungs pa/ 
	rig pa yis ni rnam dpyad na/ /
	phung po las ni gzhan kun na/ /
	mu stegs rnams kyis gang brtags pa'i/
	[f. 95v]bdag ni 'ga' yang yod ma yin/ 
	phung po yin na mi rtag/ /
	de yang bdag gi tshul ma yin/ /
	rtag dang mi rtag med pa'i phyir/ 
	rten dang brten pa'ang nam yang med/ 
ces so/ 

rnam par sangs rgyas kun rig mchog gi tshig gsum gyi don ni bshad zin to/ /


[ameyabuddhanirmāṇa- kāyakoṭivibhāvakaḥ |
sarvakṣaṇābhisamayaḥ sarvacittakṣaṇārthavit || 134 ||]

[dpag med sangs rgyas sprul pa yi/ /
sku ni bye ba 'gyed pa [7v]po/ /
skad cig thams cad mngon par rtogs/ /
sems kyi skad cig don kun rig /]


sangs rgyas kun gyi sbrul pa'i sku/ /dpag med mtha' yas 'byed pa po/ /skad cig thams cad mngon par rtogs/ /sems kyi skad cig don kun rig/ /ces pa ni 

de la dpag tu med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sbrul pa'i sku rnams ni dpag med sangs rgyas sbrul ba ste/ de rnams kyi sku ni 'dus pa ste/ dpag med sangs rgyas sbrul pa'i sku'o/ /ji lta ji ltar 'dul ba'i sems can rnams yongs su smin pa'i dbang gi phyir na dpag tu med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa'i mtha' 'gyed par byed pa ste/ 'phro ba gang yin pa de nyid bcom ldan 'das kho na yin pas na/ sangs rgyas rnams kyi sbrul pa'i sku/ /dpag med mtha' yas 'gyed pa po/ /zhes gsungs so/ /


skad cig thams cad mngon par rtogs pa ni skad cig kyang de yin la/ thams cad kyang de yin pas skad cig thams cad de/ skad cig bcu drug gi bdag nyid rnams so/ /de rnams shes pa ni rgyun du zhugs pa'i mngon par rtogs pa ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /de ltar yang chos mngon pa las gsungs pa/ 
	go rims bzhin du cher 'jug pa/ /
	skad cig bcu drug mthong lam gyis/ /
	de yi 'bras bu spangs pa'o/ /
zhes so/ /

sems kyi skad cig don kun rig ni sems can thams cad kyi skad cig kun no/ /de'i don mkhyen pas ni sems kyi skad cig don kun rig ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[nānāyānanayopāya- jagadarthavibhāvakaḥ |
yānatritayaniryāta ekayānaphale sthitaḥ || 135 ||]

[theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis/ /
'gro ba'i don gyi rnam dbye can/ /
theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung ni/ /
theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas/ /]


theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis/ /'gro ba'i don la 'phro bar byed/ /theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la/ /theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas/ /zhes pa ste/ de la 

theg pa sna tshogs zhes pa la sogs pa ni sna tshogs par gyur ba'i theg pa ni theg pa sna tshogs te/ nyan thos la sogs pa rnams kyi'o/ /de rnams kyi tshul ni lam mo/ /de'i thabs ni theg pa sna tshogs thabs kyi tshul lo/ de'i phyir theg pa sna tshogs thabs kyi tshul des 'gro ba rnams kyi don byed pa ni 'gro don te/ de la rnam par rtogs shing 'phro bas na/ /theg pa sna tshogs thabs tshul [f. 96r]@#/ /gyis/ /'gro ba'i don la 'phro bar byed do/ /

theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la ni 'dul ba'i dbang gis theg pa gsum gyis nges par 'byung bas na theg pa gsum gyis nges par 'byung ba la'o/ /

don dam par ni theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas zhes pa ste/ gcig kho na'i theg pa ni theg pa gcig go/ /de'i 'bras bu ni bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi mtshan nyid do/ /de la gnas pas na theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas te/ de ltar yang theg pa ni gcig kho na ste/ 'di lta ste/ theg pa chen po'o zhes so/ /de ltar yang kam+pa la'i zhal snga nas gsungs pa/ 
	'thab pa'i glang chen mgon po bor nas mgon med bong bu'i theg pas su zhig 'gro/ /
	rigs ldan phyug po'i bud med khyad par spang nas smad 'tshong 'dod pa bzhin/ /zhes so/ /


[kleśadhātuviśuddhātmā karmadhātukṣayaṃkaraḥ |
oghodadhisamuttīrṇo yogakāntāraniḥsṛtaḥ || 136 ||]

[nyon mongs khams rnams dag pa'i bdag/
las kyi khams rnams zad byed pa/ /
chu bo rgya mtsho kun las brgal/ /
sbyor ba'i dgon pa las byung ba/ /]

nyon mongs khams rnams dag pa'i bdag /las kyi khams rnams zad byed pa/ /chu bo rgya mtsho kun las brgal/ /sbyor ba'i dgon pa las byung ba/ /zhes pa ni 


de la nyon mongs khams dag pa'i bdag ni nyon mongs pa'i bdag nyid kyi khams rnams ni nyon mongs khams rnams te/ khams bco brgyad do/ /de'i phyir na de rnams las rnam par dag pa'i bdag nyid gang yin pa de ni nyon mongs khams rnams dag pa'i bdag go/ /

las kyi khams rnams zad byed pa ni dge ba la sogs pa'i las kyi khams rnams ni las kyi khams rnams te/ 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs med pa'i khams zhes bya'o/ /de rnams zad par byed pas na zad par byed pa ste/ 'joms par byed pas zhes pa'i don te/ de rnams 'jig par 'gyur ba'i las byed pa'i phyir ro/ /

chu bo rgya mtshe kun las brgal ba ni chu bo ni bzhi ste/ 'dod pa'i chu bo dang*/ srid pa'i chu bo dang*/ lta ba'i chu bo dang*/ ma rig pa'i chu bo'o/ /de la lta ba dang ma rig pa las gzhan la 'dod pa'i zag pa nyid 'dod pa'i chu bo rnams te/ rdzas nyi shu rtsa dgu rnams so/ /srid pa'i zag pa nyid srid pa'i chu bo ste/ /rdzas nyi shu rtsa brgyad rnams so/ /khams gsum gyi lta ba rnams ni lta ba'i chu bo ste rdzas sum cu rtsa drug rnams so/ /ma rig pa'i zag pa nyid ma rig pa'i chu bo rnams te rdzas bco lnga rnams so/ /de nyid [f. 96v]rgya mtsho ste/ mang ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /chu bo rgya mtsho de rnams las gang gis yang dag par brgal ba de de ltar gsungs te/ nyon mongs pa dang nye ba'i nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi pha rol tu phyin pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

sbyor ba'i dgon pa las byung ba/ /
	ye shes tsam la snyoms 'jug pa/ /
	rnal 'byor zhes ni mngon par bshad/ /
ces pa ni de nyid dgon pa ste/ shes dka' ba'i phyir dang*/ rgal dka' ba'i phyir ro/ /de las nges par 'byung ba ni brgal ba ste/ 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyor ba rnams kyi yongs su mthar phyin pa nyid kyi phyir na sbyor ba'i dgon pa las byung ba ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[kleśopakleśasaṃkleśa- suprahīṇasavāsanaḥ |
prajñopāyamahākaruṇā amoghajagadarthakṛt || 137 ||]

[nyon mongs nye nyon kun nyon mongs/ /
bag chags bcas pa rab spangs pa/ /
snying rje chen po shes rab thabs/ /
don yod 'gro ba'i don byed pa/ /]

nyon mongs nye ba'i kun nyon mongs/ /bag chags bcas par gtan spangs pa/ /snying rje chen po shes rab thabs/ /don yod 'gro ba'i don byed pa/ /zhes pa ni 


de la nyon mongs nye ba'i kun nyon mongs la sogs pa ni/ nyon mongs pa ni 'dod chags la sogs pa drug go/ /nye ba'i nyon mongs pa ni khro ba la sogs pa nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o/ /kun nyon mongs ni sdug bsngal bdun no/ /nyon mongs pa dang nye ba'i nyon mongs pa dang kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos de rnams nyid bag chags dang bcas par gtan du spangs pa dang gang ldan pa de ni/ nyon mongs nye ba'i kun nyon mongs/ /bag chags bcas par gtan spangs pa/ /zhes gsungs so/ /yang na nyon mongs pa ni ma rig pa dang*/ srid pa dang*/ len pa rnams so/ /nye ba'i nyon mongs pa ni 'du byed dang*/ srid pa'o/ /gzhan rnams ni gong ma bzhin no/ /


prajñopāyātmikā mahākaruṇā yasya | sa prajñopāyamahākaruṇā | sa eva bhagavān ||

snying rje che dang shes rab thabs/ /zhes pa ni shes rab dang thabs ni shes rab dang thabs te/ snying rje yang de yin la shes rab chen po yang de yin pas snying rje chen po'o/ /shes rab dang thabs dang snying rje chen po gang yin pa de ni/ snying rje dang shes rab thabs te/ de ni bcom ldan 'das so/ /


amoghajagadarthakṛd iti | amogho avarthyaḥ sa cāsau jagadarthaś cāmoghajaga[$2]darthaś taṅ karotīty amoghajagadarthakṛt | (sa eva)(ms-c pc – marginal) 
	% paragraph should probably end with `sa eva bhagavān', bhagavān not making its way into the marginal note.

don yod 'gro ba'i don byed pa ni don yod pa ni 'bras bu yod pa'o/ /don yod kyang de yin la 'gro ba'i don yang de nyid yin pas don yod 'gro ba'i don byed pa'o/ /de byed pas na don yod 'gro ba'i don byed pa ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[sarvasaṃjñāprahīṇārtho vijñānārtho nirodhadhṛk |
sarvasatvamanoviṣayaḥ sarvasatvamanogatiḥ || 138 ||]

['du shes thams cad rab spangs don/ /
rnam shes don ni 'gog pa 'chang/ /
sems can kun gyi yid kyi yul/ /
sems can kun gyi yid gnas pa/ /]


sarvasaṃjñāprahī○ṇārtho vijñānārtho nirodhadhṛk | sarvasatvamanoviṣayaḥ sarvabuddhamanogatir iti |

'du shes kun gyi don spangs shing*/ /rnam shes don ni 'gog par 'dzin/ /sems can kun yid yul [f. 97r]@#/ /dang ldan/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs rig pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra [$3] sarvasaṃjñāprahīṇārtha iti | asaṃjñisamāpattyāsaṃjñi○kaṃ | nirodhasamāpattiś ca rūpdhātau | ārūpyadhātau ca prathamopapattisthānam ākāśantyā[$4]yatanaṃ | tad evan triprakāram api sarvasaṃjñā((śande))nocyate ○ tābhiḥ | tisṛbhiḥ prahīṇaḥ cittacaittasiko rtho yasyāsau sarvasaṃjñāprahīṇārthaḥ sa eva [$5] bhagavān || 

de la 'du shes kun gyi don spangs ni 'du shes med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dang*/ 'du shes med pa dang*/ 'gog pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams te/ gzugs kyi khams su'o/ /gzugs med pa'i khams su yang nye bar skye ba'i gnas dang po ni na ma mkha' yas skye mched de/ de rnams gsum ni 'du shes kyi sgrar gsungs so/ /'du shes gsum po de rnams kyis spangs pa'i sems dang sems las byung ba'i don gang yin pa de 'du shes don spangs shing ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so| /


vijñānārtha iti | vijñānam evārtho vijñā○nārthaḥ | ārūpyadhātāveva | dvitīyam upapattisthiāna vijñānānantyāyatanaṃ tatra vijñā[$6]nam eva lambyamānatvāt tad evārthho yasya nirodha sa○ vijñānarthaḥ sa eva bhagavān ||

rnam shes don ni rnam par shes pa'i don yin pas rnam shes te/ gzugs med pa'i khams nyid do/ /skye ba'i gnas gnyis po ni rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched de/ de rnam par shes pa kho na la dmigs par byed pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi don dang gang ldan pa de rnam shes ta de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


nirodhadhṛg iti | tatraiva caturtham upapattisthānaṃ niro[$7]dhasamāpattir nirodha ucyate | tad dhārayatīti dhṛk | sa eva bhagavān ||

'gog pa 'dzin ni de nyid kyis skye ba'i gnas bzhi pa dang*/ 'gog pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa ni zhes gsungs te/ de 'dzin pas na 'gog pa 'dzin te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


sarvasatvamanoviṣaya iti | sarvasatvānāṃ mana iti kliṣṭham manaḥ sarvasatvamana[ms-c f. 92v – img. 162]s tad eva viṣayo gocaro yasya sarvasatvamanoviṣayaḥ | sa eva ||

sems can kun yid yul dang ldan ni sems can thams cad kyi yid ni nyon mongs pa can gyi yid de/ sems can kun gyi yid do/ /de nyid yul dang gang ldan pa de sems can kun yid yul dang ldan te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


sarvabuddhamanogatir iti | sarvabuddhānāṃ tryadhvavarttinām manaḥ śuciśuddhadharmadhātujñānaṃ tasya gatiḥ | [$2] sarvabuddhamanogatiḥ | tathā coktaṃ ||
	saṃkliṣā ca viśuddhā ○ ca samalānirmalā ca sā | 
	apdhātukanakākāśaśuddhivac chuddhir iṣyate |
[Madhyāntavibhāga 1.17] 
(kliṣṭamanaḥ prītiḥ)(marginal note indicated for line one, I think)

sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs rig pa ni dus gsum na gnas pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs ni shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so/ /de rig pas na sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs rig pa'o/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	kun nas nyon mongs rnam par dag /
	de ni drir bcas dri ma med/ /
	chu khams gser dang nam mkha' rnams/ /
	dag pa bzhin du dag par 'dod/ /
ces so/ /


[sarvasatvamano 'ntasthas taccittasamatāṃgataḥ |
sarvasatvamanohlādī sarvasatvamanoratiḥ || 139 ||]

[sems can kun gyi yid nang gnas/ /
de dag sems dang mnyam nyid son/ /
sems can kun yid tshim par byed/ /
sems can kun gyi yid dga' ba/ /]


sarvasatvamano'ntaḥ[$3]sthas taccittasamatāṃgataḥ | sarvasatvamanohlādī sarvasa○tvamanoratir iti 

sems can kun gyi yid la gnas/ de dag sems ni mnyam nyid son/ /sems can kun yid tshim par byed/ /sems can kun gyi yid dga' ba/ /zhes pa ni 


sarvasatvamanontaḥstha iti | sarvasatvānāṃ manaś cittaṃ tasyāntar madhye ti[$4]ṣṭhatīti sarvasatvamanontaḥsthaḥ sa eva bhagavān ||

de la sems can kun gyi yid la gnas ni sems can thams cad kyi yid ni sems so/ /de'i dkyil du gnas pas na sems can kun gyi yid [f. 97v]la gnas te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


a○ta eva taccittasamatāṅgata iti | teṣāṃ satvānāṃ cittaṃ taccittaṃ | tasya samatā taccittasamatā [$5] tathatā | śūnyateti yāvat || tathācoktaṃ aṣṭasāhasryāṃ | yā pṛthagjanatathatā yā śrāvakatathatā yā pratyekavuddhatathatā yā ca samyaksambuddhatathatā [$6] ekaiveṣā tatatheti kṛtvā tān tathatāṃ sarvacittasama○tāṅ gataḥ prāptaḥ sa tathā ||

de nyid kyi phyir na de dag sems ni mnyam nyid son te/ sems can de dag gi sems ni mnyam pa nyid de dag sems dang mnyam nyid de/ de bzhin nyid stong pa nyid kyi bar du'o/ /de ltar yang shes rab brgyad stong ba las gsungs pa/ 
	gang so so'i skye bo'i de bzhin nyid dang*/ gang nyan thos kyi de bzhin nyid dang*/ gang rang sangs rgyas kyi de bzhin nyid dang*/ gang byang chub sems dpa'i de bzhin nyid dang*/ gang yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi da bzhin nyid rnams ni de bzhin nyid gcig kho na'o zhes gsungs 
pa de ltar byas nas sems can kun gyi sems kyi de bzhin dang*/ de dag mnyam pa nyid du son par thob pa de ni de bzhin nyid do/ /


tataś ca sarvasatvamanohlādī tatraiva cetasi vidāryā sa vyāvṛ[$7]ttatayā mahāsukhajñānasyodāratayā sarvasatvamanohlādīti bhaṇyate || 

de'i phyir na/ sems can kun yid tshim par byed/ /ces te/ /sems can de dag nyid phyin ci log las 'das pas bde ba chen po'i ye shes bskyed pa nyid kyis sems can kun gyi yid tshim par byed ces gsungs so/ /


ata eva sarvasatvamanoratir iti | sarvasatvānām manoratiḥ sarvasatvamanoratiḥ |

de nyid kyi phyir na/ sems can kun gyi yid dga' ba/ /zhes gsungs te/ sems can thams cad kyi yid dga' ba ni thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i zag pa med pa'i bde ba'o/ /


[ms-c f. 94 - missing]

ngo bo lhag par chags pas bskyod pas g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba'i dngos po thams cad bdag nyid kho na'o zhes yid kyi 'du byed kyi dbye bas lhag par chags pa kho nas rab tu 'jug pa'o/ /


[siddhānto vibhramāpetaḥ sarvabhrāntivivarjitaḥ |
niḥsandigdhamatis tryarthaḥ sarvārthas triguṇātmakaḥ || 140 ||]

[grub mtha' 'khrul pa ldan pa min/ /
'khrul pa thams cad rnam par spangs/ /
don gsum the tsom med pa'i blo/ /
kun don yon tan gsum gyi bdag/]


grub pa'i mtha' la 'khrul pa med/ /nor pa thams cad rnam par spangs/ /don gsum the tshom med pa'i blo/ /kun don yon tan gsum gyi bdag /ces pa ni


de la grub pa'i mtha' la 'khrul pa med ni grub pa'i mtha' ste/ brtsams pa'i mtha' de la 'khrul ba med cing ma nges pa'i blo gros bral ba gang yin pa de ni grub pa'i mtha' la 'khrul pa med pa ni de nyid do/ /


de nyid kyi phyir na/ nor pa thams cad rnam par spangs/ /zhes pa ste/ don gyi rang bzhin ji ltar gnas pa yongs su shes pa'i phyir ro/ /

yang*/ don gsum the tshom med pa'i blo/ /zhes pa la the tshom med pa'i blo dang gang ldan pa de ni the tshom med pa'i blo ste/ 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i grub pa'i mtha' yongs su shes pa'i phyir ro/ /

don gsum ni 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang*/ da ltar gyi don te/[f. 98r]@#/ /de'i rang bzhin yang 'jam dpal lo/ /

kun don ni g.yo ba dang mi g.yo ba'i dngos po'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro/ /

yon tan gsum gyi bdag nyid ni snying stobs dang rngul dang*/ mun pa la 'jug pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ snying stobs dang rngul dang mun pa yang/ /gang phyir sems can don du gyur/ /de phyir kun du bzang po'i bdag /byang chub spyod pa ji bzhin 'gro/ /zhes so/ /


[pañcaskandhārthas triṣkālaḥ sarvakṣaṇavibhāvakaḥ |
ekakṣaṇābhisaṃbuddhaḥ sarvabuddhasvabhāvadhṛk || 141 ||]

[dus gsum phung po lnga yi don/ /
kad cig thams cad rnam bsgom pa/ /
skad cig gcig mngon rdzogs sangs rgyas/ /
sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin 'chang/ /]

phung po lnga don dus gsum du/ /skad cig thams cad bye brag phyed/ skad cig gcig gis rdzogs byang chub/ /sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin 'chang*/ /zhes pa ni 

de la phung po lnga don dus gsum du ni phung po lnga rnams kyi don ni dus gsum gyi rnam grangs kyi bdag nyid kyi phyir na/ phung po lnga don dus gsum nyid/ /ces so/ /de ltar yang chos mngon pa las gsungs pa/ 
	'dus byas chos rnams de dag kyang*/ /
	gzugs la sogs pa'i phung po lnga/ /
	de dag nyid dus gtam bzhi dang*/ /
	nges par 'byung bcas bzhi dang bcas/ /
	gang dag zag bcas nyer len pa'i/ /
	phung po 'ang de dag 'thab bcas dang*/ /
	sdug bsngal kun 'byung 'jig rten dang*/ /
	lha bcas srid pa 'ang de dag yin/ /
zhes so/ /

skad cig thams cad bye brag phyed ni rgyu'i gnas skabs na sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la sogs pa'i dge pa'i rtsa ba bsags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba bsags shing thos pa dang bsams pa dang bsgoms pa las byung ba'i thabs dang shes rab kyi chos thams cad rig pas na/ skad cig thams cad bye brag phyed/ /ces gsungs so/ /

'bras bu'i gnas skabs su ni/ /skad cig gcig mngon rdzogs byang chub ste/ skad cig kyang de yin la gcig kyang de yin pas skad cig gcig go/ /gang gis skad cig ma gcig kho na la zad pa'i ye shes dang mi skye ba'i ye shes kun du bzang po zhes bya ba mngon du byed pa de ni skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas so/ /

sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin 'chang ni dus gsum du gnas pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rang bzhin 'di kho na ste/ 'di ltar/ 
	skad cig gcig mngon rdzogs byang chub/ /
ces bya ba'o/ /de 'dzin pas sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin 'chang ngo*/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 
	sangs rgyas thams cad tshogs dang [f. 98v]ni/ /
	chos sku 'gro ba'i don spyod pas/ /
	mnyam pa nyid du sku tshe dang*/ /
	rigs dang sku bong tshad dag min/ /zhes so/ /


[anaṅgakāyaḥ kāyāgryaḥ kāyakoṭivibhāvakaḥ |
aśeṣarūpasaṃdarśī ratnaketur mahāmaṇiḥ || 142 ||
samatājñānagāthāś caturviṃśatiḥ]

[lus med sku ste sku yi mchog/
sku ni bye ba rnam par 'gyed/ /
gzugs rnams ma lus kun tu ston/ /
nor bu chen po rin chen tog/
mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi tshigs su bcad pa nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o// //]

lus med lus te lus kyi mchog /lus ni bye ba 'phro bar byed/ /gzugs rnams ma lus ston pa po/ /nor bu chen po rin chen tog /ces pa ni 


...[ms-c f. 95r img. 164]ṅgaḥ kāyo yasya so 'naṅgakāyaḥ | dharmadhātusvabhāvatvāt | 

de la lus med lus te ni lus yod pa ma yin pa ni lus med de/ med pa'i lus dang gang ldan pa de lus med lus te/ chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ata eva kāyāgrya iti | kāyānāṃ sāṃbogikādīnāṃ ...

de nyid kyi phyir na lus kyi mchog ste/ longs spyod rdzogs pa la sogs pa'i sku'i nang na mchog ste/ rab ces pa'i don to/ /


(...)(ms; kāyakoṭivibhāvaka em.) iti | kāyānāṃ murttīnāṃ koṭayaḥ (kāyakoṭayaḥ)(ms-c pc – marginal) | asaṃkhyākāyās tān vibhāvayati spharayatīti |kāyakoṭivibhāvakaḥ | ...

lus rnams te sku bye ba ni lus bye ba grangs med pa'o/ /de rnams 'gro bar byed pa ste/ 'phro bar byed pas na lus ni bye ba 'phro bar byed pa'o/ /


(...)(ms-c; ata evāśeṣarūpasaṃdarśīti | aśe em.)ṣānir avaśeṣāṇi rūpāṇi vineyānāṃ samyagdarśa○yituṃ śīlaṃ yasyāsau aśeṣarūpasandarśī | sa eva bhagavān ...

de nyid kyi phyir na/ gzugs rnams ma lus ston pa po/ /zhes te/ ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i gzugs kyis 'dul ba rnams la yang dag par ston pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de gzugs rnams ma lus ston pa po ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


...(ms-c; ratnaketur iti |  sarvajagat em.) rañjanārthanaratnaṃ ratnāṅgitaḥ ketu ratnaketuḥ sa e○va mudrā tadvārako bhagavān dānapāramitayā | sarvāśā(ya em; deest is ms-c)paripūraṇāt (...)(sarvatathāgata)pāramitāyāṃ niyojanatvāc ca ratnakoetur mañjuśrīḥ | ○ 

rin chen tog ni 'gro ba thams cad chags par byed pa'i don gyis rin chen no/ /rin chen des mtshan pa'i tog go/ /de nyid phyag rgya ste/ de 'dzin pa yang bcom ldan 'das te/ sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa nyid kyis bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir dang*/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa la nges par sbyor ba nyid kyi phyir na rin chen tog ni 'jam dpal zhes so/ /

idānīṃ ratnasambhavasvabhāvo py asau bhagavān iti | sadnarśyopasaṃharann āha || mahāmaṇiri [$6]((ti)) | sarvatathāgatānantatayā | etad uktam bhavati | ana○ntatathāgatamahāratnasambhavatvāt | samatājñānasya tena hi sarvatathāgatānāṃ (abhisabuddhaā)(ms-c abhisaṃbuddhā em.) [$7]svamudrayā traidhātukadharmarājābhiṣeko dīyate | yatas tasmāt mahāmaṇir ity ucyate | bhagavān mañjuśrīḥ | 
 
da ni rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rang bzhin du yang bcom ldan 'das de bstan pa nye bar bsdu ba gsungs pa/ nor bu chen po zhes te/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mtha' yas pa nyid kyis 'di ltar gsungs par 'gyur te/ de bzhin gshegs pa mtha' yas pa nor bu chen po las byung ba'i phyir na mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes te/ des kyang de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa rnams rang gi phyag rgyas khams gsum pa'i chos kyi rgyal po chen por dbang bskur ba sbyin par byed pas na de'i phyir na nor bu chen po zhes gsungs te/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal nyid do/ /


athedānīṃm ākāśagarbhasamādhistho bhagavā[ms-c f. 95v img. 165]((nmā))ñjuśrīḥ | daśadiganantāparyantāni buddhakṣetrāṇi gatvā mātsaryopahatān satvadhātūn svavimokṣamukhena saṃśodhya yāni ca caturuttaraśatānipañcadhā pravibhaje [$2] .. svatādikulabhedena ekaikasmin kule ekaviṃ○śatināmāny anyavidhāya taiś ca buddhakṛtyaṅ kṛtvā punar apy āgatya vajradhātumahāmaṇḍalasya va[$3]hyaś caturthacakre svavarṇo para((ṅgi))tāny akṣarāṇi bhūtvā yathāparipādyāvyavasthitaḥ | 

de nas da ni nam mkha'i snying po'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal phyogs bcu mtha' [f. 99r]@#/ /yas 'byam klas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du gshegs nas sems can gyi khams rnams kyi ser sna bcom ste/ rang gi rnam par thar pa'i sgo nas dag par byas nas gang mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig brgya rtsa bzhi de rnams rtag pa la sogs pa'i rigs kyi dbye bas rnam pa lngar bgos te/ rigs re ra las nyi shu rtsa re rer mtshan pa rnams rjas su sbyar te/ de rnams kyis kyang sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byas te/ yang slar log nas rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyi rol 'khor lo bzhi pa la rang rang gi kha dog gis kha dog bsgyur ba'i yi ge rnams su gyur te/ ji ltar go rims bzhin du rnam par gzhag go/ /

tataś ca pūrvoktaṃ traidhātuakarūpam ātmānam ava.. mantramukha[$4]caryācārī kulaputro vā kuladuhitā vā imān nāma○saṅgītim paṭan pūrvoktāneva guṇānavāpnotīty āmnāyaḥ || 

de ltar yang gong du gsungs pa'i gzugs rnam pa gsum du bdag nyid dmigs te/ sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa'i rigs kyi bu 'am rigs kyi bu mos 'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa klog pas ni 'og nas gsungs pa'i yon tan cher thob ces man ngag go/ /


ārya(...)(ms-c; nāmasaṅgīti)[$5]ṭikāyāṃ nāmamantrārthāvalokinyāṃ samatājñānasva○bhāvena stutyadhikāro navamaḥ ||    || gāthāś caturviṃśati.... [$6] raśatañ ceti || 103 || 

tshigs su bcad pa ni nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o/ /mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge grangs ni brgya rtsa bzhi'o/ /'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba zhes pa las mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin gyi bstod pa'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa ste dgu pa'o// //


