athātaḥ kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñā○namukhena bhagavataḥ sarvatathāgatajñānakāyasya stu.... 

da ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi sgo nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku'i bstod pa 'di brjod pa'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa/ /


[sarvasaṃbuddhaboddhavyo buddhabodhir anuttaraḥ |
anakṣaro mantrayonir mahāmantrakulatrayaḥ || 143 ||]

[sangs rgyas kun gyis rtogs bya ba/ /
sangs rgyas byang chub bla na med/ /
gsang sngags skye gnas yi ge med/ /
gsang sngags chen po rigs gsum pa/ /]


[$7]...ddhaboddhavyo buddhabodhir anuttaraḥ | anakṣaro mantrayonir mahāmantrakulatraya iti || 

sangs rgyas kun gyis rtogs bya ba/ /sangs rgyas byang chub bla na med/ /gsang sngags las byung yi ge med/ /gsang sngags chen po rigs gsum pa/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra sarvasambuddhaboddhavya iti ... [ms-c f. 96r – img 166] yaḥ | sākṣātkarttavyaḥ | sa eva bhagavān iti | sarvasambuddhaboddhavyaḥ || tathā coktaṃ śrītatvasaṅgrahe || 
	tvadadhīnā hi sambo...
	nti tvām āsādya tathāgatā iti |
[cannot easily find in Tattvasaṅgraha]

de la sangs rgyas kun gyis rtogs bya ba ni dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis rtogs par bya zhing shes par bya ba mngon du bya ba ni bcom ldan 'das de nyid yin pas sangs rgyas kun gyis rtogs bya ba'o/ /de ltar yang dpal de nyid 'dus pa las gsungs pa/ /
	mngon par byang chub khyed la brten/ /
	khyed ni kun gzigs yab yin te/ /
	byung dang 'byung bar 'gyur ba yi/ /
	de bzhin gshegs rnams khyed la brten/ /
zhes so/ /

buddhabodhir iti | tra○yāṇāṃ śrāvakādibuddhānāṃ bodhir buddhabodhiḥ || tathā hi ... [$3]ḥ | pratyekabodhiḥ | samyaksambodhiś ca triprakāro pi ○ sa eva ||

sangs rgyas byang chub ni nyan thos la sogs pa gsum [f. 99v]po'i byang chub ni sangs rgyas byang chub po/ /'di lta ste/ byang chub rnam pa gsum ni ji skad gsungs pa'i nyan thos kyi byang chub dang*/ rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub dang*/ yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub rnams so/ /rnam pa gsum yin yang de nyid bla na med pa zhes bya ba ste/ 


anuttara iti | ata eva na vidyate uttaro ...

'di las bla na med pas bla na med pa'o/ /


... [$4] iti | na vidyante 'kṣarāṇi vācyavācakalakṣaṇāni ○ yasminn asāv anakṣaraḥ | dharmadhātusvabhāvatvāt ||

mantrayonir iti | lo... [$5] | utpattisthānātvāt mantrayoniḥ kāraṇaṃ || 

gsang sngags las byung ba ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gsang sngags rnams kyi skye ba'i gnas nyid kyi phyir na gsang sngags 'byung ba ste/ byed rgyu zhes pa'i don to/ /

yi ge med ni gang la brjod par bya ba dang*/ brjod pa'i mtshan nyid kyi yi ge rnams med pa de ni yi ge rnams med pa ste/ chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /


mahā○mantrakulatraya iti | mahāṃś cāsau mantraś ca mahāmantraḥ kulānāṃ śāśvatākṣobhyaamitābhā[$6]nāṃ trayaṃ kulatrayaṃ | mahāmantrātmakaṃ kulatrayaṃ yasya ○ sa mahāmantrakulatrayaḥ | kāyavākcittavajrasya ākāśatulyatvāt || tathācoktaṃ śrīsamā[$7]((jatantre)) | 
	atha te mahābodhisatvāḥ sarvatathāgatakāyavākcittam ākāśākāreṇa niyo((jya)) idam udānam udānayām āsur iti | 
[Guhyasamāja ch. 2]

gsang sngags chen po rags gsum pa ni sngags kyang de yin la chen po yang de nyid yin pas gsang sngags chen po ste/ rtag pa dang*/ mi bskyod pa dang*/ snang ba mtha' yas te rigs gsum po rnams ni rigs gsum mo/ /

gsang sngags chen po'i bdag nyid rigs gsum dang gang ldan pa de ni gsang sngags chen po rigs gsum pa ste/ sku gsung thugs nam mkha' dang mnyam pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de yang dpal gsang ba 'dus pa las/ 
	de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po de dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje nam mkha'i tshul nges par sbyor zhing ched du brjod pa 'di ched du brjod do
zhes so/ /

[sarvamantrārthajanako mahābindur anakṣaraḥ |
pañcākṣaro mahāśūnyo binduśūnyaḥ śatākṣaraḥ || 144 ||]

[gsang sngags don kun skyed pa po/ /
thig le chen po yi ge med/ /
stong pa chen po yi ge lnga/ /
thig le stong pa yi ge drug /]

sarvamantrārthajanako mahā[ms-c f. 96v – img. 167]... ranakṣaraḥ | pañcākṣaro mahāśūnyo binduśūnya ṣaḍ akṣaraḥ || 

gsang sngags don kun skyed pa po/ /thig le chen po yi ge med/ /stong pa chen po yi ge lnga/ /thig le stong pa yi ge drug /ces pa ni 


tatra sarvamantrārthajanaka iti | laukikalokottarāṇāṃ sarvamantrāṇāṃ arthas tasya janaka utpādako bha[$2]gavān sa eva ||

de la gsang sngags don kun skyed pa po ni 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gsang sngags thams cad kyi don te/ de skyed pa ni 'byin par byed pa ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


mahābindur iti | akārādihakārā○ntāḥ svaravyañjanā mahābindur ity ucyate | sa ca bhagavān eva || 

thig le chen po ni dang po'i yi ge a nas ha la thug pa'i bar du dbyangs dang gsal byed rnams ni thig le chen po zhes gsungs te/ de yang bcom ldan 'das nyid do/ /


anakṣara iti | paramā[$3]..svarūpatvāt || 

yi ge med ni don dam pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


pacñākṣara iti | śāśvatādīnāñ ca ○ | āḥ hūṁ oṁ hrīḥ aḥ | ity akṣarātmakatvāt pañcākṣara ity ucyate ||  

mahāśūnya iti | ((so))ḍaśākāraśūnyatāsvabhāvatvāt |

stong pa chen po ni stong pa nyid rnam pa bcu drug gi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

yi ge lnga ni rtag pa la sogs pa'i yi ge 'bru r oM hUM hrIḥ aḥ zhes pa'i bdag nyid kyi phyir na yi ge a zhes gsungs so/ /


binduśūnya iti | ○ bindu bījākṣaran tasyāpi paramāṛthato 'nupalalabdhisvabhāvatvāt | 

[f. 100r]@#/ /thig le stong pa zhes pa la thig le ni sa bon gyi yi ge'o/ /de la don dam par mi dmigs pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /


