yi ge drug ni oM wa' gI shwa ri muM zhes te yi ge drug pa'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[sarvākāro nirākāraḥ ṣoḍaśārdhārdhabindudhṛk |
akalaḥ kalanātītaś caturthadhyānakoṭidhṛk || 145 ||]

[rnam pa thams cad rnam pa med/ /
bcu drug phyed phyed thig le 'chang/ /
cha med cha ldan las 'das pa/ /
bsam gtan bzhi pa'i rtse mo ]


sarvākāranirā○kāraṣoḍaśārddhārddhanindudhrk || akalaḥ kalanātītaś catu... 

rnam pa kun gyi rnam pa med/ /bcu drug phyed phyed thig le can/ /yan lag med pa'i rtsis las 'das/ /bsam gtan bzhi yi rtse mo can/ /zhes pa ni 


[$6]kāranirākāra iti | sarvākārā dvātriṃśatmahāpuru○ṣalakṣaṇādayo dharmās taiḥ | sarvākārer nirgato ... [$7] tathācoktam āryatriśatikāyāṃ | tat kiṃ manyase subhūte lakṣaṇasampadā tathāgato draṣṭavyaḥ | subhūtir āha | no... [f. 97ø98 missing]

de la rnam pa kun gyi rnam pa med ni rnam pa kun ni skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa'i chos de rnams kun gang yin pa las 'das shing med pa'i rnam pa'i yan lag dang gang ldan pa de de lar gsungs so/ /de ltar yang 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sum brgya pa las gsungs pa/ 
	rab 'byor de ji snyam du sems/ mtshan phun sum tshogs pas de bzhin gshegs par blta'am/ rab 'byor gyis gsol pa/ bcom ldan 'das mtshan phun sum tshogs pas de bzhin gshegs par blta bar bya ba 'di ni ma lags so/ /de ci'i phyir zhe na/ gang mtshan phun sum tshogs pa de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa de nyid mtshan phun sum tshogs pa ma lags pa'i slad du'o/ /bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan par rab 'byor la bka' stsal pa/ rab 'byor ji srid ji srid du mtshan phun sum tshogs pa de srid du brdzun no/ /ji srid du mtshan phun sum tshogs pa med pa de srid du brdzun pa ma lags so/ /de ci'i phyir zhe na/ de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan ma yin par blta bar bya'o zhes te/ de kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro/ /

bcu drug phyed phyed thig le can/ /yan lag med pa'i rtsis las 'das/ /bsam gtan bzhi yi rtse mo can ni de bdag gi bla ma'i lung yin pa'i phyir na tshig rkang gsum gyi don bdag gis ma bshad do/ /de'i phyir na bdag cag gi bla mas ji lta ba bzhin du bdag la gsungs pa/ sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa las thams cad so sor rtogs pa dad pa dang yang dag par ldan pa'i slob ma rnams dus ring por mnyes par byed pa'i bsam pa'i khyad par las sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i mngon par byang chub pa'i bla ma'i man ngag snyan khung nas snyan khung du brgyud pa rab tu bstan par bya'o/ /de'i phyir de'i sbyor ba 'tsham de'i sbyor ba 'tshams pa bgoms pas [f. 100v]/'jigs pas TI kr las 'di rnam par ma spros so/ /


[sarvadhyānakalābhijñaḥ samādhikulagotravit |
samādhikāyo kāyāgryaḥ sarvasaṃbhogakāyarāṭ || 146 ||]

[bsam gtan yan lag kun shes shing/ /
ting 'dzin rig dang rgyud rig pa/ /
ting 'dzin sku ste sku yi mchog /
longs spyod rdzogs sku kun gyi rgyal/ /]

bsam gtan yan lag kun shes shing*/ /ting 'dzin rigs dang rgyud 'chang ba/ /ting 'dzin lus can lus kyi mchog /longs spyod rdzogs sku kun gyi rgyal/ /zhes pa ni 

de la bsam gtan yan lag kun shes shing ni bsam gtan kun ni bzhi rnams te/ rtog pa dang*/ dpyod pa dang*/ dga' ba dang*/ bde ba zhes pa rnams las so/ /de la rtog pa dang bcas/ dpyod pa dang bcas/ dben pa las skyes pa'i dga' ba dang bde ba can ni bsam gtan dang po'o/ /rtog pa dang dpyod pa spangs pa ni bsam gtan gnyis pa'o/ /dga' ba yang med cing btang snyoms dang dran pa yang dag par ldan pa ni bsam gtan gsum pa'o/ /sdug bsngal yang ma yin bde ba yang ma yin pa'i btang snyoms dang dran pa yongs su dag pa ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'o/ /bsam gtan bzhi po de dag gi yan lag ste cha shas 'di rnams so/ /lde shes na ni mkhas pa ste/ bsam gtan de rab tu 'byed pa la yang sbyor ba'i phyir te/ de la mos pa'i sems can kun du bzang po'i don yin no/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bsam gtan dang po la sogs pa mngon du byed de/ sems can gyi don gyis gnas pas na de'i dbang gis skye ba ni ma yin no/ /dre bzhin du 'og nas bshad pa las kyang lha cho ring por mi skye bar shes pa ste/ de rnams su skye ba la dbang thob pa'i phyir ro/ /

ting 'dzin rigs dang rgyud 'chang ba ni ting nge 'dzin rnams ni de yang mchog tu dge ba la rtse gcig pa'i rnam par bsgom pa nyid kyi phyir na bsam gtan dang po la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /go rims bzhin du rang gi ming dang don gyi rjes su dran pa'i rab tu dbye ba dpag tu med de/ de bas na de rnams kyi rigs dang rgyud ni gdon mi za bar nyan thos la sogs pa ste/ de 'dzin pas na ting 'dzin rigs dang rgyud 'chang ba'o/ /

ting 'dzin lus can lus kyi mchog ni ting nge 'dzin gyi lus ni lus kyi sku'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir sprul pa la sogs pa'i lus thams cad las mchog dang rab yin pas na ting 'dzin lus can lus kyi mchog ste/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[ms-c f. 99r – img 169]sarvasambogakāyarāṭ || tathācoktaṃ || 

longs spyod rdzogs sku kun gyi rgyal ni longs spyod [f. 101r]@#/ /rdzogs pa'i sku thams cad du gyur pa bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal 'khor thams cad kyi nang na che ba'i bdag nyid phun sum tshogs pa bden pa'i don 'bras bu dang bcas pa sna tshogs pa bsam du med pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dga' ba'i rgyu rab tu ston par byed pa'i phyir na bstan to/ /de 'ang de nyid bstan pa'i sgo nas mdzes shing 'bar bas na longs spyod rdzogs sku kun gyi rgyal lo/ /de ltar yang gsungs pa/ 


lokātītām cintyāṃ sukṛtasataphalāmātmano yo vibhūtim
parṣanmadhye vicitrā... [$2] kaprasṛta(ma)(pc – marginal)virato dārasaddharmaghoṣaṃ 
vande sambhogakāyan tamahamanupamaṃ dharmarājyapratiṣṭham iti ||
[Nāgārjuna Kāyatrayastava verse 2; see Sekoddeśaṭīkā ed. p. 171]

[As quoted in Bhavabhaṭṭa; attributed to Nāgārjuna in Jñānaśrīmitra
lokātītāmacintyāṁ sukṛtasaphalā( latā )mātmano yo vibhūtiṁ
parṣanmadhye vicitrāṁ prathayati mahatīṁ dhīmatāṁ prītihetoḥ
buddhānāṁ sarvalokaprasṛtamaviratoddhārasaddharmaghoṣaṁ
vande saṁbhogakāyaṁ tamahamihamahādharmarājyapratiṣṭham || iti || 3 ||]
	bdag gi sbyor ba 'jig rten las 'das bsam gyis mi khyab legs mdzad legs pa'i 'bru/ /blo chen rnams kyi dga' ba'i rgyu ni 'khor ba'i nang du sna tshogs rab ston cing*/ /dam pa'i chos kyi sgra chen rtag tu 'jig rten khams rnams kun dur rab 'phro ba/ /sangs rgyas chos kyi rgyal srid che la bzhugs pa de la 'dir ni phyag 'tshal lo/ /zhes so/ /


[nirmāṇakāyo kāyāgryo buddhanirmāṇavaṃśadhṛk |
daśadigviśvanirmāṇo yathāvajjagadarthakṛt || 147 ||]

[sprul pa'i sku ste sku yi mchog/
sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba/ /
phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs 'gyed/ /
ji bzhin 'gro ba'i don byed pa/ /]


nirmāṇakāya...
[$3]...nirmāṇo yathāvajjagadarthakṛd iti ||

sprul pa'i sku ste sku yi mchog /sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba/ /phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs 'gyed/ /ji bzhin 'gro ba'i don byed pa/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra nirmāṇakāyakā○yāgrya iti | nirmāṇātmakaḥ kāyo nirmāṇakāyaḥ | sa cāny... [$4]tvāt || agrya ity ucyate || tathā coktaṃ ||
	satvānāṃ pākahetoḥ ○ kvacid analatāṃ (..)(pc - marginal) vābhāti yo dīpyamānaḥ sambodhau dharmacakre kvacid pi pu... 
	naikākārapravṛttaṃ tribhavabhayaharaṃ viśvarūpair (a)(pc; u ac)pāyaiḥ |
	vande ○ nirmāṇakāyaṃ dadiganugataṃ tanmahārtham munīnām iti ||  

	[$5]nāṃ buddhānāṃ nirmāṇāni | 

[Quoted in Sekoddeśa Kāyatrayastava verse 3:
	sattvānāṃ pākahetoḥ kvacid anala ivābhāti yo dīpyamānaḥ 
	sambodhau dharmacakre kvacid api ca punar dṛśyate yaḥ praśāntaḥ |
	naikākārapravṛttaṃ tribhavabhayaharaṃ viśvarūpair upāyair
	vande nirmāṇakāyaṃ daśadiganugataṃ tanmahārthaṃ munīnām || ]

de la sprul pa'i sku ste sku'i mchog ni sprul pa'i bdag nyid kyi sku ni sprul pa'i sku'o/ /de 'ang gzhan 'jig rten pa'i sprul pa rnams kyi nang na rab kyi phyir na sku'i mchog ces gsungs so/ /de ltar yang gsungs ba/ 
	sems can rnams kyi smin pa'i rgyu phyir la lar 'bar pa'i me bzhin gang snang zhing*/ /
	la lar yang ni rdzogs byang chub dang chos kyi 'khor lo rab bzhir gang snang ba/ /
	rnam pa du mar 'jug cing srid gsum rab 'dzin sna tshogs thabs kyis 'joms mdzad pa/ /
	thub pa rnams kyi don chen phyogs bcur rjes mngon sprul sku de la phyag 'tshal lo/ /zhes so/ /


buddhanirmāṇavaṃśadhṛg iti | ... [$5]nāṃ buddhānāṃ nirmāṇāni | teṣāṃ vaṃśo 'nvayo buddhanirmāṇavaṃ○śas tad dhārayatīti buddhanirmāṇavaṃśadhṛk | sarvatathāgatavaṃśān yacchedakatvāt |
	% vaṃśān upacche?

sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba ni dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi sprul pa de rnams kyi rgyud ni rim pa ste/ sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud do/ /de 'dzin pas na sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba ste/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gdung rgyun mi gcod pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


daśadigviśvani[$6]rmāṇa iti | daśa dikṣa viśvāni nānāprakārāṇi nirmāṇāni yasyāsau daśadigviśvanirmāṇaḥ || 

phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs pa ni phyogs bcu po rnams su rnam pa sna tshogs tha dad pa'i sprul pa'i cho 'phrul dang gang ldan pa de phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs 'gyed pa'o/ /[f. 101v] 


yathāvatjagadarthakṛd iti | ata eva yathāvad ity aviparītadharmadeśanāmukhe[ms-c f. 99v – img. 170]najagadarthaṅ karotīti yathāvaj jagadarthakṛt || 

de nyid kyi phyir na ji bzhin 'gro ba'i don byed pa ste/ /ji bzhin phyin ci ma log par don bstan pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don byed pas na ji bzhin 'gro ba'i byed pa'o/ /


[devātidevo devendraḥ surendro dānavādhipaḥ |
amarendraḥ suraguruḥ pramathaḥ pramatheśvaraḥ || 148 ||]

[lha yi dbang po lha yi lha/ /
lha min dbang po sbyin byed bdag /
lha yi bla ma 'chi med dbang/ /
rab 'joms rab 'joms dbang phyug go/ /]


