devātidevo devendro 'surendro dālavādhipaḥ |
amarendraḥ su(ra)(pc; ru ac)guruḥ prathamaḥ prathameśvara iti ||

lha yi dbang po lha yi lha/ /lha min dbang po lha min bdag /'chi med dbang po lha yi bla/ /'joms byed 'joms byed dbang phyug po/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra devātideva iti | brahmātmakatvā[$2]t || devendra iti | viṣṇusvabhāvatvāt | asurendra iti | vairo○canabalirūpatvāt || dālavādhipa iti | rāhusvabhāvatvāt | 

de la lha'i dbang po ni khyab 'jug gi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /lha'i lha ni tshangs pa'i bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /lha min dbang po ni rnam par snang byed 'be le'i gzugs kyis so/ /lha min bdag ni gza' rr hu la'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


amarendra iti | purandarūpatvāt | [$3] || suragurur iti vṛhaspatisvabhāvatvāt || pramatha iti | ga○ṇasvabhāvatvāt | pramatheśvara iti | ((amba))kasvabhāvatvā | devādidevaityāvi(bhi)(pc – marginal)ḥ sa eva bhagava..bhi[$4]dhāyate || 

'chi med dbang po ni grong khyer 'jig gi gzugs nyid kyi phyir ro/ /lha'i bla ni gza' phur bu'i gzugs nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'joms byed ni tshogs bdag gi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /'joms byed dbang phyug ni ma hr de wa'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /lha'i dbang po la sogs pa rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das de nyid la mngon par brjod par bya'o/ /


[uttīrṇabhavakāntāra ekaḥ śāstā jagadguruḥ |
prakhyāto daśadigloka- dharmadānapatir mahān || 149 ||]

[srid pa'i dgon pa las brgal ba/ /
ston pa gcig pu 'gro ba'i bla/ /
'jig rten phyogs bcur rab grags pa/ /
chos kyi sbyin bdag che ba po/ /]

utīrṇṇabhavakāntāra ekaḥ śāstā jagadguruḥ | 
pra○khyātadeśadiglokadharmadānapatir mahān iti ||

srid pa'i dgon pa las brgal ba/ /ston pa gcig po 'gro pa'i bla/ /'jig rten phyogs bcur rab grags pa/ /chos kyi sbyin bdag che ba po/ /zhes pa ni 


tatra utīrṇabhavakāntāra iti ... [$5] sa eva kāntāro duruttaratvāt bhavakāntāraḥ | utīrṇṇabhava○kāntāraṃ yena sa utīrṇṇabhavakāntāraḥ | 

de la srid pa'i dgon pa las brgal ba ni srid pa ni 'khor ba'o/ /de nyid kyi dgon pa ste brgal dka' ba nyid kyi phyir na srid pa'i dgon pa'o/ /gang gis srid pa'i dgon pa las brgal ba de ni srid pa'i dgon pa las brgal ba'o/ /


eka ity advitīyas...

gcig pu ni gnyis su med pa ste/ /de dang 'dra ba med pa'i phyir ro/ /


...[$6]śāstā yat sarvasatvānāṃ kṛtyaṃ karoti taṃ sandarśayati ca | śā○stā sarvasatvānām ity aviśeṣeṇa bhagavān | ... [$7]thā hi || apāyopapannānām api prabhayā tathāgatavigrahasandarśanena praśādam upajanayya sugatau pratiṣṭhā...[f. 100r – img 171] 

de nyid kyi phyir na ston pa zhes pa ste/ ston pa ni gang sems can thams cad kyi bya ba ston par byed pas na ston pa yin no/ /de la sems can thams cad kyi ston pa ni khyad par med pa bcom ldan 'das 'dam dpal de nyid de/ sems can thams cad kyi bya ba ston par byed pa nyid kyis byed pa'o/ /'di lta ste/ ngan song du skyes pa rnam la yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku yi 'od zer las de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku bstan pas rab tu dang bar byas te mtho ris la so sor 'jog par byed do/ /mtho ris su skyes pa rnams la yang skal pa dang mi ldan pa kha cig rnams la gong du gsungs pa'i tshogs bsam pa yongs su dag par byas nas 'khor ba'i bde ba'i las sbyin pa la sogs pa la so sor 'jog [f. 102r]@#/ /par byed de/ /skal pa dang ldan pa rigs rnams la yang bsam pa rnam pa gnyis kyis nye par ston pa rnams kyis te/ dge ba'i rtsa ba ma bsags pa rnams kya dge ba'i rtsa ba bskrun par bya ba dang*/ dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su bskrun pa rnams ni dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su smin par byed do/ /dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su smin pa rnams ni yongs su grol bar byas te/ rigs ji lta ba bzhin du nyan thos la sogs pa la so sor 'jog go/ /da ltar ngan song dang mtho ris su skyes pa rnams kyi skal ba dang ldan pa dang mi ldan pa'i rigs rnams la bya ba mthun par bsgrub pa'i phyir na de nyid sems can thams cad kyi ston pa zhes gsungs so/ /

de nyid kyi phyir na 'gro ba'i bla ma ste/ 'gro ba rnams kyi bla ma yin pas 'gro ba'i bla ma'o/ /

'jig rten phyogs bcur rab grags pa/ /chos kyi sbyin bdag ni phyogs bcu rnams kyi 'jig rten ni phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten no/ /phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten kyang de yin la rab grags kyang de nyid yin pas 'jig rten phyogs bcur rab grags pa ste/ 'jig rten na phyogs bcur grags pa ste/ de rnams la chos kyi sbyin bdag gang yin pa de/ 'jig rten phyogs bcur rab grags pa/ /chos kyi sbyin bdag go/ /de nyid che ba po zhes te/ /g.yo bdang mi g.yo ba'i dngos po rnams la khyab pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar yang dbal bde mchog gi rgyud las gsungs pa/ 
	kun du kun nas thams cad du/ /
	bdag nyid rtag tu rnam pa kun/ /
	sangs rgyas la sogs brtan g.yo kun/ /
	kun gyi dngos por bdag gyur to/ /
zhes so/ /


[maitrīsaṃnāhasaṃnaddhaḥ karuṇāvarmavarmitaḥ |
prajñākhaḍgadhanurbāṇaḥ kleśājñānaraṇaṃjahaḥ || 150 ||]

[byams pa'i go cha chas pa ste/ /
snying rje yi ni ya lad bgos/ /
shes rab ral gri mda' gzhu thogs/ /
nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel/ /]


byams pa'i go cha chas pa ste/ /snying rje yi ni ya lad bgos/ /shes rab ral gri mda' gzhu thogs/ /nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel/ /zhes pa ni 


de la byams pa'i go cha chas pa ste ni/ byams pa ni sems can thams cad la bshes dang grogs dang bu gcig pa bzhin du byams pa rnams so/ khyams pa des go cha ni byams pa'i go cha gang gis chas pa ste/ byams pa'i go cha chas pa'o/ /

snying rje yi ni ya lang bgos ni snying rje ni ji snyed gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /de nyid ya lad de snying rje'i ya lad do/ /snying rje'i ya lad de bgos pas bsrung ba gang yin de snying rje'i ya lad [f. 102v]bgos so/ /

shes rab ral gri mnga' gzhu thogs ni/ shes rab ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i pu sti'o/ /ral gri ni ye shes kyi ral gri'o/ /mda' ni sems phra mo yongs su 'bigs pa'i bdag nyid do/ /gzhu ni rdo rje'i gzhu'o/ /des kyang ci gsung bar 'gyur zhe na/ byams pa'i go cha chas shing snying rje'i ya lad kyis bsrungs pa'i shes rab la sogs pa'i phyag rgya dang ldan pa nyon mongs pa'i mi shes pa ni 'dod chags pa'i gti mug go/ /

de nyid g.yul te 'thab mo'o/ /de sel zhing spong bas na bcom ldan 'das dngos po de nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel ba yin no/ /man ngag ni 'di'o/ /mdog dmar ba dang phyag bzhi par shes par bya'o/ /


dpa' bo bdud dgra bdud 'dul ba/ /bdud bzhi'i 'jigs pa sel bar byed/ /bdud kyi dpung rnams pham par byed/ /rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'jig rten 'dren/ /zhes pa ni 


[mārārir mārajid vīraś caturmārabhayāntakṛt |
sarvamāracamūjetā saṃbuddho lokanāyakaḥ || 151 ||]

[dpa' bo bdud dgra bdud 'dul ba/ /
bdud bzhi'i 'jigs pa mthar byed pa/ /
bdud dpung thams cad pham par byed/ /
rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'jig rten 'dren/ /]


de la bdud dgra ni bdud rnams te bgegs kyi dgra ste bdud dgra'o/ /de nyid bdud 'dul zhes pa ste/ rdo rje gdan la bzhugs nas bdud mi mthun pa'i phyogs rnams 'joms pas na bdud 'dul ba'o/ /de nyid kyi phyir na dpa' po ste/ mi mthun pa'i phyogs gzhan rnams kyis zil mi non pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

bdud bzhi'i 'jigs pa sel bar byed ni bdud rnams ni bdud bzhi'o/ /de rnams 'jigs pa ni bdud bzhi 'jigs so/ /de sel bar byed cing med par byed pas na bdud bzhi'i 'jigs pa sel bar byed do/ /


... [ms-c f. 100 – img. 171] ti caturmārabhayāntakṛt | 

sarvamāracamūjetā iti | sarvamārāṇāṃ camūḥ sarvamāracamū senātāṃ jetuṃ śīlaṃ yasyeti sarvaloracamūjetā || 

bdud kyi dpung rnams pham byed pa ni bdud thams cad kyi dpung ni bdud kyi dpung ste de'o/ /de pham bar byed pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de ni bdud kyi dpung rnams pham byed pa'o/ /


sambuddha iti | nāmnām upasaṃhāram āha | [$2] tad yathā bhagavān buddhasambuddha ity ādāv ārabhya yāvad etat paryantaṃ prāyeṇa nāmasaṅgītiḥ kathitā | lokanāyaka iti | 

rdzogs ba'i sangs rgyas ni mtshan rnams nye bar bsdu ba gsungs pa yin no/ /'di ltar sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das/ /rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhes pa dang po nas ji tsam 'di'i mthar thug pa'i bar du na 'jam dpal gyi mtshan yang dag par brjod pa phal cher la gsungs pa'o/ /

lokanāyaka iti | lakoānāṃ nāyako lokanāyakaḥ | saka[$3]lajagadabhyuddharaṇāt | 

'jig rten 'dren ni 'jig rten rnams kyi 'dren pa po 'jig rten 'dren te/ 'gro ba kun mngon par 'dod pa'i phyir ro/ /


[vandyaḥ pūjyo 'bhivādyaś ca mānanīyaś ca nityaśaḥ |
arcanīyatamo mānyo namasyaḥ paramo guruḥ || 152 ||]

[mchod 'os bstod 'os phyag gi gnas/ /
rtag tu rim gro bya ba'i 'os/ /
bkur 'os rjed bar bya ba'i 'os/ /
phyag byar 'os pa bla ma'i mchog /]


vandyaḥ pūjyo bhivādyaś ca mānanīya○ś canityasaḥ 
arccanīyatamo mānyo namasyaḥ paramo gurur iti ||

mchod 'os bstod 'os phyag gi gnas/ /rtag tu ri mor bya ba'i 'os/ /bkur 'os rjed par bya ba'i 'os/ /phyag byar 'os pa bla ma'i rab/ /ces [f. 103r]@#/ /pa ni 


tatra vandya iti | sadevakānāṃ [$4] lokānāṃ vandanārhatvāt |

pujya iti | śrutismṛtīnāṃm pa○ryantaṃ gataḥ puūjya udārhataḥ | bhagavāṃś ca mañjuśrīḥ |

sarvasiddhāntapāragatatvāt pūjya ity ucya[$4]te || 

de la mchod 'os ni thos pa dang dran pa rnams yongs su mthar phyin ba ni mchod 'os zhes brjod pa/ bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal yang grub pa'i mtha' thams cad kyi pha rol tu son pa'i phyir na mchod 'os zhes gsungs so/ /


ābhivādya iti | stutyarhatvāt || 

bstod 'os ni bstod par 'os pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


mānanīyaś ca nitya○śa iti | sarvaśrāvakādīnāṃ mānanīyatvāt |

phyag gi gnas ni lha rnams dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten rnams kyis phyag bya bar 'os pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

rtog tu ri mor bya ba'i 'os ni nyan thos la sogs pa thams cad kyis ri mor bya bar 'os pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


arccanīya iti | paripūrṇṇaguṇatvāt | mañjuśrīr eva sa[$6]rvabodhisatvānāṃ | 

bkur 'os ni yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa nyid kyi phyir na 'jam dpal nyid byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis so/ /


mānya iti | sarvatathāgatānāṃ mānyatvāt ○ ||

rjed par bya ba'i mchog ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis rjed par bya ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


namasya iti || mantramukhacaryā | cāriṇāṃ namasyatvāt | ata eva parama utkṛṣṭatvāt | 

phyag byar 'os pa ni sngags kyi sgo spyad pa spyod pa rnams kyis phyag byar 'os pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


gurur iti [$7] | sarveṣāṃ eva satvānām anuśāsanāt | sarvatathāgatajñānahṛdayavihāritvāc ca sa eva bhagavān || 

bla ma ni sems can 'di dag thams cad la rjes su ston pa'i phyir dang*/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kar gnas pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /de nyid kyi phyir na rab ni mchog gi phyir te/ de nyid bcom ldan 'das so/ /


[trailokyaikakramagatir vyomaparyantavikramaḥ |
traividyaḥ śrotriyaḥ pūtaḥ ṣaḍabhijñaḥ ṣaḍanusmrtiḥ || 153 ||]

['jig rten gsum po gom gcig bgrod/ /
mkha' ltar mtha' med rnam par gnon/ /
gsum rig gtsang ma dag pa ste/ /
mngon shes drug ldan rjes dran drug/]

trailokyaikakramagatir vyomāparyantavikramaḥ 
traividyaḥ śrotriyaḥ pūtaḥ [ms-c f. 100v – img 172] ṣaḍabhijñaḥ ṣaḍanusmṛtir iti ||

'jig rten gsum nyid gom gcig bgrod/ /mkha' ltar mtha' med rnam par gnon/ /gsum rig gtsang ma dag pa ste/ /mngon shes drug ldan rjes dran drug /ces pa ni 


tatra trailokyaikakramagatir iti | trayāṇāṃ lokānāṃ samahāras trilokaṃ | trilokam eva trailokyaṃ | tasmiṃ trailokyaṃ ekasyaiva kramasya pādasya ga[$2]tir gocaro yasya sa trailokyaikakramagatiḥ | anena ṝddhi○māhātmyan tasya bhagavataḥ sampradarśitaṃ || 

de la 'jig rten gsum nyid gom gcig bgrod ni 'jig rten gsum po rnams mnyam por bsdus pa ni 'jig rten gsum ste/ 'jig rten gsum nyid ni 'jig rten gsum mo/ /'jig rten gsum po de la gom pa gcig kho nas bgrod pa'i zhabs dang gang ldan pa de 'jig rten gsum nyid gom gcig bgrod do/ /des ni bcom ldan 'das de'i rdzu 'phrul chen po'i bdag nyid yang dag par bstan pa yin no/ /


vyomāparyantavikrama iti | vyoma ākāśaṃ tasyāparyaṃ[$3]taḥ | vyomāparyantaḥ | tasmin vikramaḥ parākramā yasya sa ○ vyomāparyantavikramaḥ | anena ca padena tasya bhagavataḥ satvāṛthakramo nirddiṣṭaḥ || 

mkha' ltar mtha' med rnam par gnon ni mkha' ni mkha'o/ /de yongs su mtha' yas pa ni mtha' ltar mtha' med pa'o/ /de rnam par gnon pa ni pa rol gnon pa gang yin pa de ni mkha' ltar mtha' med rnam par gnon no/ /tshig des kyang bcom ldan 'das de'i sems can gyi don du gnon pa nges par ston pa yin no/ /


traividya iti [$4] | vedavidāndarśanam āha | ṛgyajuḥsāmalakṣaṇās trisro○ vidyāḥ | trayā((nvīkṣi))kī | vārttā lakṣaṇā |  vā tad adhīte vetti vā traividyaḥ tatsvabhāvas sa eva bhaga[$5]vān athavā yānatritayasaṅgrahī(ta)(ms-c pc - marginal)piṭakatrayasvabhāvaṃ vi○dyā trayam adhītevel athavā ṛddhiparacittajñānāsravakṣayābhijñānasvabhāvaṃ vettīti trai[$6]vidyaḥ sa eva || 

gsum rig ni rig byed rig par bstan pa gsum ste/ nges brjod dang*/ mchod sbyin dang*/ snyan ngag gi [f. 103v]mtshan nyid rnams ni rig byed gsum po gsum ldan dang*/ rjes su lta ba dang*/ gtam gyi mtshan nyid kyang rung ba bsgrub pa 'am rig pas na gsum rig go/ /de'i rang bzhin yang bcom ldan 'das so/ /yang na theg pa gsum po nyid kyis bsdus pa ste sde snod gsum gyi rang bzhin rig pa ni gsum po sgrub pas sam rig pas na'o/ /yang rdzu 'phrul dang*/ pha rol gyi sems shes pa dang*/ zag pa zad pa'i mngon par shes pa'i rang bzhin rig pas na gsum rig pa'o/ /


srotriya iti | vedavidā(nda)rśanena ○ cchandodhyāyā srotriya ucyate | bhagavāś ca mañjuśrīr aparimitamahāyānacchandasodhyayanāt sro[$7]triya ity ucyate | 

de nyid kyi phyir na gtsang ma zhes pa ste/ rig byed rig pa'i rang bzhin lta ba yin la/ 'dun pas 'dod phyir na gtsang ma zhes gsungs so/ /bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal yang grangs med pa'i theg pa la 'dun pas 'dod pa'i phyir na gtsang ma zhes gsungs so/ /


pūta iti pūnanty neneti pūtaḥ | śuddhihetutvāt || tathā coktam mahābhāṣye || 
	āpaḥ pavitraṃ prathamaṃ pṛthivyām ((apām)) pavitram paramañ ca mantrāḥ | 
	teṣāñ ca [ms-c f. 101 – img. 173] sāmargyajuṣāṃ pavitraṃ mahārṣayo vyākaraṇāni cāhur iti ||
pavitratvāt sa eva bhagavān pūta ity ucyate || 

dag pa ni des dag par byed pas na dag pa ste/ dag pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar yang bshad pa chen po las gsungs so/ /
	sa la chu'i sa yongs su dag /
	chu la 'ang sngags rnams mchog tu dag /
	de yang dus tshod tshogs pas dag /
	drang srong chen pos lung bstan gsungs/ /
zhes gsungs so/ /de ltar yang bcom ldan 'das dag pa nyid kyi phyir na dag pa zhes gsungs so/ /


ṣaḍabhijña iti | divyaṃ (cakṣu divyaṃ)(ms-c pc – marginal)śrotraṃ paracittajñānaṃ | pūrvanivāsānusmaraṇaṃ [$2] ṛddhiḥ sarvāsravakṣayābhijñā ceti | etāḥ ṣaḍabhijñā ya○syāsau ṣaḍabhijñaḥ || 

mngon shes drug ldan ni lha'i rna ba dang pha rol gyi sems shes pa dang*/ sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa dang*/ rdzu 'phrul dang*/ zag pa zad pa'i mngon par shes pa rnams so/ /mngon par shes pa de rnams drug dang gang ldan pa de mngon shes drug ldan no/ /


ṣaḍanusmṛtir iti | yad uta buddhānusmṛtiḥ dharmanusmṛtiḥ | vajrānusmṛtiḥ | [$3] kulānusmṛtiḥ | krodhānusmṛtiḥ | samayānusmṛtiś ceti | atra etāḥ ṣaḍanu(smṛtiyo)(ms-c; smṛtayo em.) yasyāsau sa tathā ||
	% perhaps 3rd should be saṅghānusmṛti? 

rjes dran drug ni ji snyed gsungs pa'i sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa dang*/ chos rjes su dran pa dang*/dge 'dun rjes su dran pa dang*/ rigs rjes su dran pa dang*/ khro bo rjes su dran pa dang*/ dam tshig rjes su dran pa rnams so/ /de'i phyir rjes su dran pa dang gang ldan pa de la de skad ces gsungs so/ /


[bodhisatvo mahāsatvo lokātīto maharddhikaḥ |
prajñāpāramitāniṣṭhaḥ prajñātattvatvam āgataḥ || 154 ||]

[byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che/ /
rdzu 'phrul chen po 'jig rten 'das/ /
shes rab pha rol phyin pa'i mtha'/ /
shes rab kyi ni de nyid thob/ /]

bodhisatvo mahāsatvo lokātīto maharddhi[$4]kaḥ |
prajñāpāramitāniṣṭhaḥ prajñātatvatvam āgata i○ti || 

byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che/ /rdzu 'phrul chen po 'jig rten 'das/ /shes rab pha rol phyin pa'i mtha'/ /shes rab de nyid de nyid thob/ /ces pa ni 


tatra bodhisatva iti | bodhau sarvadharmāsaktatāyāṃ svārthasampadi satvam abhiprāyo yasya sa [$5] bodhisattvaḥ | śrāvako pi tarhi syād ity ata āha || mahāsa○tva iti | mahatyāṃ parārthasampadi satvaṃ yasya sa mahāsatvaḥ mahatvaṃ cānyathā pi tīrthikasādhujana[$6]vat syād iti | bodhisatvagrahaṇaṃ | ataevābhyāṃ padābhyāṃ ○ upalakṣitaḥ sa eva bhagavān || 

de la byang chub sems dpa' ni chos thams cad la chags pa med pas byang chub ste/ rang gi don phun su ma tshogs pa la sems dpa'i blo dang dang ldan pa de byang chub sems dpa'o/ /de ltar yin na nyan thos la thal bar 'gyur ro/ /de'i [f. 104r]@#/ /phyir gsungs pa/ sems dpa' che zhes pa ste/ gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa chen po la sems dpa'i blo dang gang ldan pa de sems dpa' che'o/ /chen po yang gzhan du 'gyur ta/ mu stegs kyi skye bo bzang po lta bu'o zhe na/ de'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' zhes gsungs so/ /de bas na tshig de gnyis kyis nye bar mtshon pa ni bcom ldan 'das de nyid yin no/ /


tataś ca lokātīta iti | saṃsāramahānadyāḥ | pratisrotrogā[$7]mitvāt |

de yang 'jig rten 'das zhes pa ste/ 'khor ba'i chu bo chen po'i rgyud las kun du brgal ba'i phyir ro/ /


maharddhika iti | paripūrṇṇapuṇyajñānasambhāratvāt || 

rdzu 'phrul chen po ni bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro/ 


prajñāpāramitāniṣṭha iti | prajñāyā dharmapravicayalakṣaṇāyāḥ pāramitā prajñāpāramitā | tasya ni[ms-c f. 101 – img. 174] ṣṭhā 'vaśānaṃ gato yaḥ prajñāpāramitāniṣṭhaḥ | 

shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mtha' ni chos rab tu rnam par 'byed pa'i mtshan nyid shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o/ /de'i mtha' ni mthar phyin cing mjug brtul bar son pa gang yin bde shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mtha'o/ /


prajñātatvam iti | prajñayāḥ tatvaṃ prajñātatvaṃ | prajñā 'advayajñānaṃ | sa eva bhagavān ||  

shes rab de nyid ni shes rab de kho na ste| shes rab gnyis su med pa'i ye shes te/ bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


tatvam āgata iti taṃ devādvayaṃ jñānaṃ prāpta āgato [$2] yaḥ sa tathocyate || 

de nyid thob pa ni gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kho na ste/ de thob cing mngon du gyur pa gang yin pa de la de skad ces gsungs so/ /


[ātmavit paravit sarvaḥ sarvīyo hy agrapudgalaḥ |
sarvopamām atikrānto jñeyo jñānādhipaḥ paraḥ || 155 ||]

[bdag rig gzhan rig thams cad pa/ /
kun la phan pa'i gang zag mchog/
'jig rten dpe las 'das pa ste/ /
shes dang shes bya'i bdag po mchog/]

ātmavit paravit sarvaḥ sarvīyo hy agra○pudgalaḥ |
sarvopamām atikrānto jñeyo jñānādhipaḥ para iti ||

bdag rig gzhan rig thams cad pa/ /kun la phan pa'i gang zag mchog/ dper bya kun las 'das pa ste/ shes dang shes bya'i bdag po mchog /ces pa ni 


tatra ātmavid iti | ātmānaṃ [$3] vettīti ātmavit || 

de la bdag rig ni bdag nyid rig pas na bdag rig go/ /


paravid iti | param vettīti paravi○t || 

gzhan rig ni gzhan rnams rig pas na gzhan rig go/ /


sarva iti | niḥśeṣabhāvasvabhāvasandarśanāt || 

thams cad ni ma lus pa'i dngos po bstan pa'i phyir ro/ /


sarvīya iti sarveṣāṃ hitaḥ sarvīyaḥ | 

kun la phan pa ni thams cad la phan pa byed pas na kun la phan pa ste/ 'gro ba kun la bu gcig pa bzhin du byams pa'i phyir ro/ /


sa[$4]kalajagadekaputraṣvematvāt ataś ca kāraṇād agrapudgalo ○ bhagavān || 

rgyu de'i phyir na gang zag mchog ste/ bcom ldan 'das so/ /


sarvopamām atikrānta iti | sarveṣām padārthānām upamā tasyām atiḥ sarvopamāmatis tāṃ [$5] ākrānto laṃghitavān yaḥ sa sarvopamāmatikrāntaḥ || 

dper bya kun las 'das pa ste ni dngos po 'di thams cad kyi dper bya kun no/ /dper bya de kun las 'das pa shin tu 'das pa gang yin pa de ni dper bya kun las 'das so 


jñeya ○ iti grāhyarūpatvāt |

zhes bya ba ni gzung ba'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /
	% Tib should probably read shes bya ni. There was evidently some corruption here. 


jñādhipa iti | hrāhakasvabhāvatvāt | 

shes pa'i bdag po ni 'dzin pa po'i rang bzhin gyi phyir ro/ /


para ity ukṛṣṭatvāt || 

mchog ni rab nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[dharmadānapatiḥ śreṣṭhaś caturmudrārthadeśakaḥ |
paryupāsyatamo jagatāṃ niryāṇatrayayāyinām || 156 ||]

[gtso bo chos kyi sbyin pa'i bdag /
phyag rgya bzhi po'i don ston pa/ /
'gro ba'i bsnyen bkur gnas kyi mchog /
nges 'byung gsum po bgrod rnams kyi/ /]


dharmadāna[$6]patiḥ śreṣṭhaś caturmudrārthadeśakaḥ |
paryupāsyatamo jagatāṃ ni○ryāṇatrayayāyinām iti || 

chos kyi sbyin bdag gtso bo ste/ /phyag rgya bzhi po'i don ston pa/ 'gro ba'i bsnyen bkur gnas kyi mchog/ [f. 104v] nges 'byung gsum po bgrod pa po/ /zhes pa ni/ 


tatra dharmadānapatir iti | yathābhavyatayā | avipa(rī)(ms-c pc; ri ms-c ac)tadharmadānāt || [$7]

de la chos kyi sbyin bdag ni skal ba ji lta ba bzhin du phyin ci ma log par chos kyi sbyin pa'i phyir ro/ /


ata eva śrēṣṭho bhigamanīyānāṃ madhye sa eva bhagavān | 

de nyid kyi phyir na gtso bo zhes bya ba ste/ mngon par 'gro bar bya ba rnams kyi nang na mchog ste/ bcom ldan 'das de nyid do/ /


caturmudrārthadeśaka iti | catusṛṇāṃ mahāmudrādīnām arthaś caturmudrārthas tasya deśakaḥ prakāśakaḥ sarvatathāgatajñā[ms-c f. 102r – img. 175]nakāyasvabhāvatvāt | 

phyag rgya bzhi po'i don ston pa ni phyag rgya chen po la sogs pa bzhi rnams kyi don ni phyag rgya bzhi'i don te/ de'i ston pa po ni rab tu ston pa po'o/ /de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi sku'i rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir/ 


paryupāsyatama iti | niryāṇatrayaṃ śrāva(kā)(ms-c pc – marginal)dinirvāṇan tena yātuṃ śīlaṃ yeṣāṃ te niryāṇatrayayāyinaḥ | atas teṣāṃ sarvaniryāṇatra<yā>yāyināṃ jagatā[$2]m asau bhagavān paryupāsyatamo bhavati | sarvamokṣasvabhā○vatvāt || 

'gro ba'i bsnyen bkur gnas kyi mchog/ ces bya'o/ /nges 'byung gsum po ni nyan thos la sogs pa'i nges par 'byung ba ste/ des bgrod pa'i tshul dang gang ldan pa de ni nges 'byung gsum gyis bgrod pa'o/ /de bas na nges 'byung gsum gyis bgrod ba'i 'gro ba thams cad kyi bsnyen bkur gyi gnas ni bcom ldan 'das de nyid de/ thar ba thams cad kyi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[paramārthaviśuddhaśrīś trailokyasubhago mahān |
sarvasaṃpatkaraḥ śrīmān mañjuśrīḥ śrīmatāṃ varaḥ || 157 ||
kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñānagāthāḥ pañcadaśa]

[don gyi dam pa rnam dag dpal/ /
'jig rten gsum gyi skal bzang che/ /
dpal ldan 'byor pa kun byed pa/ /
[8v]'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog/
bya ba sgrub pa'i ye shes kyi tshigs su bcad pa bco lnga'o// //]


paramārthaviśuddhaśrīḥ trailokyasubhago mahān |
sarvasampatkaraḥ śrīmān mañjuśrīḥ śrī[$3]matām vara iti ||

don gyi dam pa rnam dag dpal/ /'jig rten gsum na skal bzang che/ /dpal ldan 'byor pa kun byed pa/ /'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog /ces pa ni 


tatra paramārthena dharmadhātunā viśuddhā ○ śrīr yasyāsau paramārthaviśuddhaśrīḥ prajñopāyātmakatvāt | 

de la don dam chos kyi dbyings kyi rnam par dag pa'i dpal dang gang ldan pa de ni don gyi dam pa rnam dag dpal te/ thabs dang shes rab kyi bdag nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


ata eva trailokyasubhago iti [$4] | trailokya eka * (e)(ms-c pc – above line)va subhagaḥ | sarvasatvārthakaraṇāt || tathā ○ coktaṃ śrīsamvaratantre ||
	subhago bhagavān vajrī sarvasatvārthakāraṇāt |
	durbhagāḥ śrāvakāḥ [$5] sarve | atyantaparinirvṛtā iti || 
[Sarvabuddhasamāyoga, 2.73]

de nyid kyi phyir na 'jig rten gsum na skal bzang ni 'jig rten gsum kho na la skal ba bzang po ste/ sems can kun gyi don byed pa'i phyir ro/ /de ltar yang dpal bde mchog gi rgyud las gsungs pa/ 
	sems can kun don byed phyir na/ /
	skal bzang bcom ldan rdo rje can/ /
	gtan du mya ngan 'das phyir na/ /
	nyan thos thams cad skal ngan yin/ /
zhes gsungs so/ /


mahān iti sarvavyā○pakatvāt | 

che ni kun la khyab ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvasampatkara iti | sarvasampadādhārabhūtatvāt | 

śrīmān iti | bhāgyasampanna[$6]tvāt || 

dpal ldan ni skal ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa nyid kyi phyir ro/ /

'byor pa kun byed pa ni phun sum tshogs pa thams cad kyi rten gyi dngos po nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


mañjuśrīr iti | saṃjñābhidhānaṃ | 

'jam dpal ni mtshan brjod pa yin no/ /


śrīmatām vara iti ○ | tadvatāṃ śreṣṭha ity ārthaḥ || 

dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog ni de dang ldan pa'i nang na rab ces pa'i don to/ /


idam idānīṃ kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñānasvabhāvena sa eva bhagavān ma[$7]ñjuśrīḥ sarvatathāgatajñānasatvaḥ sarvatathāgatasarvamudrāsamadhigataviśvakāryakaraṇād aśeṣasarvasatvadhātusarvāśāparipūrakaḥ sarvadaśadigantāpa[ms-c f. 102v – img. 176].. ..  lokadhātūn gatvā nāmamantrākṣarapadānāṃ pa((ñca))navatīnāṃ kulabhedena ekaikasya ekonaviṃśatiṃ ekonaviṃśatiṃ pañcadhā pravibhajjya taiḥ sarvasatvānāṃ kauśīdyam a[$2]panīya kuśalapakṣeṣu saṃsthāpya (svavimokṣamuktena)(ms-c; *mukhena em?) tatpra○bhayā ca sarvatathāgataparṣadam avabhāsya punar āgatya tāni coktalakṣaṇair nāmamantrākṣarapadā[$3]ni kṛtvā vajradhātumahāmaṇḍalasya bahiḥ pañcamacakre ya○thānukramato vyavasthitaḥ 

de ltar de nas de ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin gyis bcom ldan 'das de nyid de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs [f. 105r]@#/ /pa thams cad kyi phyag rgya kun yang dag par rig pa'i bya ba sna tshogs mdzad pa'i phyir ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i sems can gyi khams thams cad la bsam pa kun yongs su rdzogs par byed pa de nyid phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad yongs su khyab par son pas/ mtshan gyi sngags kyi yi ge tshig dgu bcu rtsa lnga rnams rigs kyi dbye bas rnam pa lngar bgos te/ rnam pa re re zhing yang mtshan gyi yi ger gyur pa rnam pa bcu dgu bcu dgur byas te/ de rnams kyis sems can thams cad kyi le lo med par byas nas dge ba'i phyogs la gnas par byas te/ rang gi rnam par thar pa'i sgo nas de'i 'od kyis yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad gsal bar byas nas yang de rnams slar log nas gong du gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid rnams kyi sngags kyi yi ge'i tshig rnams su gyur te/ rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyi rol 'khor lo lnga pa la ji lta ba'i rim pas rnam par gnas so/ /


punar api yathoktarūpatrayam ātmānam ālambhya mantramukhacaryācārī ku[$4]laputro vā kuladuhitā vā āryanāmasaṅgītim paṭhan pu○rvoktān guṇān prāpnotīty āmnāyaḥ || 
	% purvokta? 

yang ji ltar gsungs pa'i gzugs su bdag nyid dmigs te/ sngags kyi sgo nas spyad pa spyod pa'i rigs kyi bu 'am rigs kyi bu mo 'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa klog pas 'og nas 'byung ba'i yon tan thob po zhes pa ni man ngag go/ /


āryanāmasaṅgītiṭīkāyāṃ nāmamantrārthāvā[$5]lokinyāṃ kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñānastutyadhikāro daśamaḥ || ○ ||    || gāthā pañcadaśa (nā)(ms-c pc – marginal)mamantrapadāni (pañco navatir)(ms-c ; pañcanavatir em.) aṅkato pi || 95 || 

'di la tshigs bcad ni bco lnga'o/ /mtshan gyi sngags kyi tshig rnams ni dgu bcu rtsa lnga ste grangs so/ /'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba las bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi sgo nas bstod pa'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa ste bcu pa'o// //


