adhunā mahā[$6]vairocanādayaḥ pañcatathāgatāḥ pañajñānāṭmikābhi○r gāthābhir bhagavantaṃ jñānamūrttiṃ vajradhātumahāmaṇḍalāntarvarttinaṃ samstuvati sma || tad yathā ||

da ni rnam par snang mdzad chen po la sogs pa de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i bdag nyid kyi tshigs bcad rnams kyi bcom ldan 'das kyi ye shes kyi sku rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i dbus na bzhugs pa la bstod pa 'di lta ste/ 

[namas te varada vajrāgrya bhūtakoṭi namo 'stu te |
namas te śūnyatāgarbha buddhabodhi namo 'stu te || 158 ||]

[mchog sbyin rdo rje mchog khyod 'dud/ /
yang dag mthar gyur khyod la 'dud/ /
stong nyid snying po khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas byang chub khyod la 'dud/ /]


[buddharāga namas te 'stu buddhakāma namo namaḥ |
buddhaprīti namas tubhyaṃ buddhamoda namo namaḥ || 159 ||]

[sangs rgyas chags pa khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas 'dod la phyag 'tshal 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas dgyes pa khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas rol la phyag 'tshal 'dud/ /]


[buddhasmita namas tubhyaṃ buddhahāsa namo namaḥ |
buddhavāca namas te 'stu buddhabhāva namo namaḥ || 160 ||]

[sangs rgyas 'dzum pa khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas snang la phyag 'tshal 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas gsung ba khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas thugs la phyag 'tshal 'dud/ /]


[abhavodbhava namas te ḥstu namas te buddhasaṃbhava |
gaganodbhava namas tubhyaṃ namas te jñānasaṃbhava || 161 ||]

[dngos med las byung khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas 'byung ba khyod la 'dud/ /
nam mkha' las byung khyod la 'dud/ /
ye shes las byung khyod la 'dud/ /]


[māyājāla namas tubhyaṃ namas te buddhanāṭaka |
namas te sarva sarvebhyo jñānakāya namo 'stu te || 162 ||
iti pañcatathāgatajñānastutigāthāḥ pañca |]

[sgyu 'phrul dra ba khyod la 'dud/ /
sangs rgyas gar mdzad khyod la 'dud/ /
thams cad thams cad khyod la 'dud/ /
ye shes sku khyod la 'dud do/ /
zhes pa de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i ye shes kyi bstod pa tshigs su bcad pa lnga'o// //]


namaḥ[$7]s te varadetyādi | ādarśamukhena || buddharāgetyādi | (dharmadhātujñānasvabhā√ena || buddhasmitetyādi | pratyavekṣaṇājñānadvāreṇa || abhavodbhavetyādi | samatājñānātmanā || māyājāletyādi) (ms-c pc – marginal) kṛtyānuṣṭhānajñānasvabhāvena | iti ||

mchog sbyin la sogs pas ni me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /sangs rgyas chags pa la sogs pas ni chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin gyi sgo nas so/ /sangs rgyas 'dzum pa la sogs pas ni so sor kun du rtog pa'i ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /med pa las byung [f. 105v]la sogs pas ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /sgyu 'phrul dra ba la sogs pas ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /


āryanāmasaṅgītiṭikāyān nāmamantrārthāvalokinyāṃ upasaṃhā[ms-c f. 103r – img 177]rastutyadhikāra ekādaśatamaḥ parisamāptaḥ || gāthāḥ pañca || 

tshigs bcad lnga'o/ /'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba las nye bar bsdu ba'i sgo nas bstod pa'i rim pa'i dbang du byas pa bcu gcig ba ste yongs su rdzogs so// //


