athedānīṃ bhagavān śākyamunir vajradharam āmantrya tenaivādhyeṣitatvāt tasyaivāmantraṇaṃ kṛtvā [$2] sānuśaṃsāṃ nāmasaṅgītim adhikṛtyāha || śarddāvatāṃ pra○vṛttihetoḥ | iyam asau vajrayāṇe vajradhareti | iyam asau nāmasaṅgītiḥ 

de nas da ni yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa la/ de la re zhig rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor dang po'i sgo nas yon tan gsungs pa/ phag na rdo rje rdo rje 'chang zhes pa la sogs pa ste/ bcom ldan 'das shrkya thub pas rdo rje 'dzin pa pos pa ni de kho na gsol pa btab pa'i phyir ro/ /de kho na la bos pa mdzad de/ mtshan yang dag par brjod pa yon tan dang bcas pa gsungs pa ni dang pa ldan pa rab tu 'jug pa'i phyir nas gsungs pa ste/ phag na rdo rje rdo rje 'chang 'di dang 'di dang 'di ni zhes pa ni 'di dang 'di ni mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'o/ /


he vajrapā[$3]ṇe | idam abhiṣekadvāreṇa || vajradhareti jñānadvāreṇa ○ | ubhayaguṇatvena saṅgītikārakatvenādhikṛtatvād bhagavato jñānamūrtteḥ sarvatathāgatajñāna[$4]kāyasya mañjuśrījñānasatvasya sambandhinī nāmasaṅgīti○ḥ | 

kye phyag na rdo rje zhes pa ni dbang bskur ba'i sgo nas so/ /rdo rje 'chang ni ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /yon tan de gnyis dang ldan pas sdud par byed pa nyid kyi dbang du byas pa'i phyir ro/ /bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi sku/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' dang 'brel pa'i mtshan yang dag par brjod pa yin te/ 


kim viśiṣṭā āveśikapariśuddhā | tatra veṇir miśrībhāvaḥ kleśaiḥ saha | na veṇir aveṇi[$5]ḥ | śuddhasvabhāvas tatra bhava āveṇikas tena pariśuddhāyā nā○saṅgītiḥ sā mayā deśiteti vakṣyamāṇena sambandhaḥ 

mi 'dra ba zhig ce na/ thun mong ma yin pa'i yongs su dag pa zhes pa ni/ /de la thun mong ni nyon mongs pa dang 'dres pa'o/ /nyon mongs pa rnams dang lhan cig ma 'dres pa ni thun mong ma yin pa ste/ dag pa'i rang bzhin ni/ srid pa dang ma 'dres pa yongs su dag pa'i mtshan yang dag par brjod pa de dag gis zhes bstan to zhes phyis 'byung ba'i tshig dang 'brel pa/ 


kim artham ity āha tavānuttaraprītiprasāda[$6]mahaudbilyasañjananārtham iti | tatranuttaraprītir harṣa○ḥ prasādaḥ śraddhā sā ca karmaphalasatyaranteṣv abhisampratyayaḥ | mahaudbilyaṃ vīryan tac ca kuśalapa[$7]..bhyutsāhaḥ |

ci'i don du zhe na/ gsungs pa/ khyod kyis dga' ba dang*/ dang ba dang*/ mgu ba chen po bla na med pa bskyed pa'i don dang zhes pa ni/ de la dga' ba ni spro ba'o/ /dad pa ni dad pa ste/ de yang las dang*/ 'bras bu dang*/ bden pa dang*/ dkon mchog rnams la yid ches pa'o/ /mgu ba chen po ni brtson 'grus so/ /de yang dge ba'i chos la mngon par spro ba'o/ /

eṣāṃ vajrapāṇe tava saṃjananārtham utpādanārthaṃ kāyavāṅmanoguhyapariśuddhyai kāyavāṅmanasaṃguhyaṃ bodhicittavajrasvabhāvaṃ | tasya pariśuddhyarthaṃ | 

phyag na rdo rje khyod kyis de rnams bskyed [f. 106r]@#/ /pa ni 'byung bar bya ba'i don du'o/ /lus dang ngag dang yid kyis gsang ba yongs su dag par bya ba'i don dang zhes pa la/ lus ngag yid rnams kyi gsang ba ni byang chub sems rdo rje'i rang bzhin te/ de yongs su dag par bya ba'i don du'o/ /


apa[ms-c f. 103v – img. 178]((ri))pūrṇṇāpariśuddhā bhūmipāramitā puṇyajñānasaṃbhāraparipūripariśuddhyai aparipūrṇṇā bhūmayaḥ | apariśuddhāś ca pāramitāḥ | aparipūrṇṇā pariśuddhabhūmi pārami[$2]tāḥ | tāsāṃ puṇyajñānasambhāras tasya paripūripariśu○ddhyarthaṃ || 

yongs su ma rdzogs pa'i dang*/ yongs su ma dag pa'i sa dang pha rol tu phyin pa dang*/ bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs de yongs su rdzogs pa dang yongs su dag par bya ba dang zhes pa/ yongs su ma rdzogs pa'i sa rnams dang yongs su dag pa ni pha rol tu phyin pa rnams te/ yongs su ma rdzogs pa rnams dang*/ yongs su ma dag pa'i sa dang*/ pha rol tu phyin pa rnams so/ /de rnams kyi bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs de yongs su rdzogs pa dang yongs su dag par byed pa'i don du'o/ /


ana(dhi)(ms-c pc – marginal)gatānuttarārthasyādhigamāya | anadhigataś cāsāv anuttarārthaś ca | anadhigatānutt[$3]rārthas tasyādhigamārthaṃ | 

bla na med pa'i don ma rtogs pa rtogs par bya ba dang zhes pa ni bla na med pa'i don yang de yin la ma rtogs pa yang de nyid yin pas bla na med pa'i don ma rtogs pa ste/ de rtogs par bya ba'i don du'o/ /


aprāptasya prāptyai | aprāptasya bu○ddhadharmādeḥ prāptyarthaṃ 

ma thob pa thob pa thob par bya ba dang zhes pa ni ma thob pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos la sogs pa thob par bya ba'i don du'o/ /


yāvat sarvatathāgatasadharmanetrīsandhāraṇārthañ ceti | yāvac chandaḥ kramāpe [$4]kṣī | sarvatathāgatasaddharmanetrī prajñāpāramitā | tasyā ○ advayajñānasvarūpeṇa samyagdhāraṇārthañ ca || 

ji srid de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi chos kyi tshul yang dag par gzung ba'i phyir zhes pa ni ji srid kyi sgra'i rim pa la ltos pa'o/ /de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dam pa'i chos kyi tshul ni shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ste/ de gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin gyis yang dag par gzung bar bya ba'i don du 


mayā deśiteti | bodhicittavajrasvabhāvena | sa[$5]mprakāśiteti | supariśuddhadharmadhātujñānamukhena || ○ vivṛteti | ādarśajñānarūpeṇa | vibhajiteti | samatājñānamukhena || uttānīkṛteti | pra[$6]tyavekṣaṇājñānātmanā || adhiṣṭhitā ceti | kṛtyānuṣṭhā○najñānadvāreṇa || 

ngas bshad cing zhes pa ni byang chub sems rdo rje'i rang bzhin gyi sgo nas so/ /kha stan te zhes pa ni shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /bkrol zhing zhes pa ni me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /rnam par phye la zhes pa ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /byin gyis brlab par bya'o zhes pa ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes kyi sgo nas so/ /


iyan nāmasaṅgītir he vajrapāṇe vajradhara tava santāne citte | sarvamantradharma[$7]tādhiṣṭhāneneti | sarvamantrāṇāṃ dharmatā śūnyatā tasyādhiṣṭhānaṃ sthirīkaraṇaṃ tenādhiṣṭhāneneti || prathamacakrasyeyam anusaṃśā ekādaśa padāni aṅkto pi | [ms-c f. 104r – img. 179] || 11 || (puśpikā) ||

kyi lag na rdo rje zhes pa ni bod pa'i don to/ /'di ni zhes pa ni mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i zhes pa'i don to/ /ngas zhes pa ni shrkya thub pa ngas zhes pa'i don to/ /khyod kyi rgyud la zhes pa ni khyod kyi sems kyi rgyud la'o zhes pa'i don to/ /gsang sngags thams cad kyi chos nyid kyis byin gyi rlabs [f. 106v]kyis brlab po zhes pa ni gsang sngags thams cad kyi chos nyid ni gsang sngags thams cad kyi chos nyid de/ stong ba nyid do/ /de byin gyis brlabs pa ni brtan par byed pa'o/ /'khor lo dang po yin tan te/ tshigs bcad bcu gcig ste grangs so/ /

suviśuddhaparyavadātasarvajñajñānakāyavāṅmanoguhyabhūtā 
atha dvitīyacakrasyānusaṃsām adhikṛtyāha || punar param iyaṃ vajrapāṇe vajradharanāmasaṅgītir iti | supariśuddhaparyavadātasarvajñajñānakāyavāṅma[$2]noguhyabhūteti || suṣṭhu pariśuddham supariśuddhaṃ pari○ samantād avadātaṃ paryavadātaṃ supariśuddhaparyavadātañ cetat sarvajñajñānañ ca | supariśuddha[$3]paryavadātasarvajñajñānaṃ tasya kāyavāṅmanāṃsi teṣāṃ ○ guhyabhūtā aprakāśyarūpatvāt | 

da ni 'khor lo gnyis pa'i phan yon gyi dbang du byas te gsungs pa/ lag na rdo rje rdo rje 'chang gzhan yang mtshan yang dag par brjod pa 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi shin tu dag cing yongs su byang ba'i thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang*/ sku dang gsung dang thugs gsang bar gyur ba'o zhes pa la/ kun nas yongs su bya ba ni shin tu yongs su dag cing yongs su byang ba yang de yin la thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang de nyid yin pas shin tu dag cing yongs su byang ba'i thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes so/ /de'i sku gsung thugs kyi cha de rnams gsang bar gyur pa ni snang ba ma yin pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvatathāgatānāṃ buddhabodhir iti | buddhānāṃ bodhiḥ | buddha[$4]bodhiḥ na śrāvakabodhir ity arthaḥ || 

sangs rgyas kyi byang chub po zhes pa ni sangs rgyas rnams kyi byang chub ni/ sangs rgyas kyi byang chub ste/ nyan thos kyi byang chub ma yin zhes pa'i don to/ /


samyaksambuddhānām a○bhisamaya iti | abhisamayo jñānaṃ | sarvajñajñānaṃ | 

yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis mngon par rtogs pa'o zhes pa ni mngon par rtogs pa ni ye shes te/ /thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes so/ /


sarvatathāgatānām anuttara iti na vi[$5]dyate uttaro 'smād ity anuttaraḥ || 

de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bla na med pa'o zhes pa ni de'i gong na med pa'i phyir bla na med pa'o/ /


dharmadhātugatiḥ suga○tānām iti || śūnyatāsvabhāvatvāt | 

bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi chos kyi dbyings thugs su chud pa'o zhes pa ni stong pa nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sarvamārabalaparājayo jinānām iti | caturmāra[$6]((balai))r aparājitatvāt | 

rgyal ba rnams kyis bdud kyi stobs thams cad pham par mdzad pa'o zhes pa ni/ bdud bzhi'i stobs kyis mi thub pa'i phyir ro/ /


daśabalabalitā sarvadaśabalānām iti | daśabalāni uktalakṣaṇāni | tāni vidyante yasyā nāmasaṅgīteḥ | sā daśavabalīnī | tasyābhā[ms-c f. 104v – img. 180](..)(ms-c; ve em.) daśabalabalitā || 

stobs bcu dang ldan pa thams cad kyi stobs bcu nyid do zhes pa ni stobs bcu ni gong du gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /de rnams dang mtshan yang dag par brjod pa dang ldan pa de stobs bcu'o/ /de'i dngos po ni stobs bcu nyid do/ /


sarvajñatāsarvajñajñānānāṃ iti | sarvajñānābhī(ti)(ms-c pc – marginal) sarvajñas tasyabhāvaḥ sarvajñatā | 

thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes rnams ni thams cad mkhyen pa nyid do zhes pa ni thams cad shes pas na thams cad mkhyen pa'o/ /de'i ngo bo ni thams cad mkhyen pa nyid do/ /


āgamaḥ sarvadharmāṇām iti | parasmād āgacchatīty āgamaḥ | sa ca [$2] dviḥ prakāraḥ | āgamalakṣaṇo dhigamalakṣaṇaś ca || 

sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad kyi lung ngo zhes bya ba ni gzhan las 'ongs pa'i phyir lung ngo*/ de yang rnam pa gnyis te/ lung gi mtshan nyid dang*/ [f. 107r]@#/ /rtogs pa'i mtshan nyid do/ /


sa○mudāgamaḥ sarvabuddhāṇām iti | śrāvakādīnāṃ sarvabuddhānāṃ śrāvakādisvarūpeṇa sākṣātkara[$3]ṇāt || 

sangs rgyas thams cad kyis yang dag par grub pa'o zhes pa ni nyan thos la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis te/ nyan thos la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rang gi ngo bos ma den du byed pa'i phyir ro/ /


vimalasupariśuddhapuṇyajñānasambhāraparipū○riḥ sarvamahābodhisatvānām iti | vimalaś cāsau supariśuddhaś ca vimalasupariśuddhaḥ [$4] sa cāsau puṇyajñānasambhāraś ca | bimalasupariśuddhapu○ṇyajñānasambhāraḥ | tasya paripūrir yasyāṃ nāmasaṅgītau | sā tathoktā ||

byang chub sems dpa' chen po thams cad kyi bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pa'i dri ma med cing shin tu rnam par dag pa'o zhes pa ni/ shin tu rnam par dag pa yang de yin la dri ma med pa yang de nyid yin pas na dri ma med cing shin tu rnam par dag pa ste/ de nyid bsod nams dang ye she kyi tshogs de yin la dri ma med cing shin tu rnam par dag pa yang de nyid yin la na dri ma med cing shin tu rnam par dag pa'i bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pa'i dri ma med cing shin tu rnam par dag pa'o/ /de yongs su rdzogs pa gang yin pa de ni mtshan yang dag par brjod pa ste/ de dang gang ldan pa de la de skad ces 
gsungs so/ /


prasūtiḥ sarva[$5]śrāvakapratyekabuddhānām iti | prasūtir iti | teṣām u○tpattisthānatvāt | 

nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi skye gnas ni de rnams kyi 'byung ba'i gnas nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


