adhu○nā pañcamacakrasyānusaṃsām adhikṛtyāha || punar aparaṃ vajrapāṇe vajradharetyādi | ya [$3] imān nāmasaṅgītin nāmaccūḍāmaṇiṃ pratyahaṃ pratidi○ne | akhaṇḍasamādānatas trihkṛtvā triguṇīkṛtya kaṇṭhagatām āvarttayiṣyati | 

