pustaka[$4]gatāṃ vā paṭhamāna iti | pāṭhaṃ varttayivyeti | bha○gavato mañjuśrījñānasatvasya rūpam ālambayan tadrūpam anuvicintayan | tadrūpam anu[$5]dhyāyann iti | pūrvoktakrameṇa dhārūpamanuvici○ntayantam eva bhagavantaṃ nirmāṇarūpakāyena na cirād eva śīgram eva vinayavaśam u[$6]pādāyeti || satvāśayavaśād drakṣyati | gaganatala○gatāṃś ca sarvabuddhabodhisatvā nānānirmāṇarūpakāyaiḥ sahagatād drakṣyati | 

