sa sārdhaṃ krodharājānaiḥ provācoccair i[$3]...
...numodāmahe nātha sādhu sādhu subhāṣitaṃ ○
kṛto 'smākaṃ mahān arthaḥ samyaksambodhiprāpaka iti 

de nas dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang*/ /dga' zhing mgu nas thal mo sbyar/ /mgon po bcom ldan de bzhin gshegs/ /rdzogs sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal nas/ /de ni mgon po gsang ba'i bdag /lag na rdo rje khro bo'i rgyal/ /sna tshogs gzhan dang lhan cig tu/ /gsang bstod nas ni tshig 'di gsol/ /mgon pa bdag cag yi [f. 115r]@#/ /rang ngo/ /legs so legs so legs par gsungs/ /bdag cag yang dag rdzogs pa yi/ /byang chub thob pa'i don chen mdzad/ /ces pa ni 


tatra he nātha sādvanumodāmahe | [$4] ... subhāṣitaṃ | suṣṭhu bhāṣitaṃ subhāṣitaṃ | a○smākaṃ mahānarthaḥ kṛtaḥ kim viśiṣṭo 'ath ity ata āha | samyaksambodhiprāpaka iti | buddha[$5]... 

de la/ /kye mgon po bdag cag yi rang ngo*/ /legs so legs so legs par gsungs so/ /shin tu gsungs pa ni legs par gsungs so/ /bdag cag gi don che byas so/ /don ci 'dra ba zhe na gsungs pa/ yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob pa ni sangs rgyas thob par byed pa'o/ /


[jagataś cāpy anāthasya vimuktiphalakāṃkṣiṇaḥ |
śreyomārgo viśuddho 'yaṃ māyājālanayoditaḥ || 166 ||]

['gro ba mgon med rnams dang ni/ /
rnam grol 'bras bu 'tshal ba yi/ /
rnam dag legs pa'i lam 'di ni/ /
sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i tshul bstan pa/ /]


jagataś cāpy anāthasya vimuktiphala○kāṃkṣiṇaḥ | śreyomārgo viśuddho yaṃ māyājālanayodita iti | 

rnam grol 'bras bu 'tshal pa yi/ /'gro ba mgon med rnams kyi yang*/ /sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i tshul ston pa/ /


tatra na kevalam atmā[$6]...yi jagato vimuktiphalakākṣiṇaś ca | ayaṃ māyājālanayodito rtho mahān | kim viśiṣṭo viśuddho dharmadhātusvabhāvatvāt | śreyomārga[ms-c f. 114v – img. 194] ... hetutvāt | 

'di ni rnam dag legs pa'i lam/ /zhes pa ni de la bdag cag nyi tsho'i ma yin te/ mgon po sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i tshul 'di ni/ /rnam grol 'bras bu 'dod pa yi/ /'gro ba mgon med rnams kyi yang don chen yin no/ /de ci 'dra zhes na/ rnam dag ces te/ chos kyi dbyings yi rang bzhin nyid kyi phyir ro/ /legs pa'i lam ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyu nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


[gambhīrodāravaipulyo mahārtho jagadarthakṛt |
buddhānāṃ viṣayo hy eṣa samyaksaṃbuddhadeśitaḥ || 167 ||
ity upasaṃhāragāthāḥ pañca ||]

[zab cing yangs la rgya che ba/ /
don chen 'gro ba'i don byed pa/ /
sangs rgyas rnams kyi yul 'di ni/ /
rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis bshad/ /
'di ni yang dag par spro ba nye bar bsdu ba'i tshigs su bcad pa lnga'o/ /]


gambhīrodāravaipulya mahārtho jagadarthakṛt | 
buddhānāṃ viṣayo hyeṣa sarvasambuddhadarśita iti | 

zab zing yangs la rgya che ste/ /don chen 'gro ba'i don byed pa/ /sangs rgyas rnams kyi yul 'di ni/ /rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis bshad/ /ces pa ni 


tatra eṣārtho hi yasmāt | gambhī[$2]... mahārthas tasmāt | buddhānām eva viṣa○yo gocaro nāmyeṣāṃ śrāvakādīnāṃ 

de la don ci'i phyir na zab cing yangs pa'i don che ba yin pa de'i phyir sangs rgyas rnams kyi spyod yul yin te/ nyan thos la sos pa gzhan rnams kyi ni ma yin na/ 


jagadarthakṛd iti | mahākaruṇoparigṛhītatvāt | 

de ci 'dra zhe na/ 'gro ba'i don byed pa zhes pa ste/ snying rje chen pos yongs su bzung ba nyid kyi phyir ro/ /


sa[$3]..kālyavarttibhir deśitaḥ sarvasambuddhade○śitaḥ ||

rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis bshad/ /ces pa ni dus gsum la gnas pa'i rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis 'di bshad pa yin no/ /


āryanāmasaṅgītiṭikāyāṃ nāmamantrārthāvalokinyām upasaṃhārādhikā[$4].. samāptaḥ || [puṣpikā] ||

'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba las bsdus pa'i rim par phye ba ste bcu bzhi pa'o// //

svamatisadṛśaśaktyā nāmasaṅgītigātau vivṛti .. ti vidhāyāś tad dhādurvṛtāyāṃ kuśalam atulam āptaṃ te [$5]rāyāṃ praśam ita bha carāgāḥ prāptuvattva gra○bodhiṃ || [puṣpikā] || 

bdag gi blo gros 'dra ba'i nus pas mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i tshul la ni/ /
blo gros zhan pas gzung bar dka' ba'i rim pas rnam par 'grel pa byas pa yin/ /
de yi dge bas dri ma med pa grangs med thob pas sems can sdug bsngal ba'i/ /
srid pa'i 'dod chags zhi bar byas nas mchog gi byang [f. 115v]chub dam pa thob gyur cig/ /


ārya ... tiṭikā samāptā || [puṣpikā] || gra? pramāṇam asyāḥ sāhasradvitayaṃ || [puṣpikā] || kṛtir ācāryavilāsavajrasya ratnadvīpanivāsinaḥ | śrīmad śineyasya pra ... rūpābhidhānasya || 

dhva?hīdhareṣu gaṇite smvatsare śaucikeśukle vādaśamīti thauyavibhūtaḥ śrīnāmasāṅgītikā | ṭikālekhanate | mayāsuvipulaṃ śrīsarvam intra śabhuyat pu[#2] ... rjataṃ ca nikhilo loko stu buddhas tataḥ || [space] śubhaṃ || [puṣpikā] ||

'phags pa mtshan yang dag par brjod pa'i rgya cher 'grel pa mtshan gsang sngags kyi don du rnam par lta ba zhes bya ba rgya gar gyi mkhan po sgeg pa'i rdo rje nyi ma can gyi rin po che gling na bzhugs pa dpal ldan byang chub mchog gi sla ba dang ldan pa gang gi mtshan dpal sna tshogs gzugs can du grags pa des mdzad pa rdzogs so// //


rgya gar gyi mkhan po smr-i ti dz+nyr na kI rtis bsgyur te bshad nas gtan la phab pa'o/ /phyis rgya gar gyi mkhan po phyag na rdo rje dang*/ lo tsr ba klog skya shes rab brtsegs kyis bcos nas gtan la 
phab pa'o/ /'di la gzhung tshad ni sh+lo ka nyis stong lnga brgya'o//[ <line/>]

